#: CommonEvents/Load Save:480:text
msgid "@niko \\p?\\>\\n\\@niko I had another dream..."
msgstr "@niko \\p？\\>\\n\\@niko 𨉟徠𢠩𠬠𥋏𡛤。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:481:text
msgid "@niko Mama was there.\\>\\n\\@niko_speak Did you see her?"
msgstr "@niko 𥪝妬𣎏媄𨉟。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 舅拱𧡊媄渚？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:491:text
msgid ""
"@niko_pancakes She made me pancakes!\\>\\n\\@niko I... think it was my "
"birthday."
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 媄𪵯餅喼朱𨉟！\\>\\n\\@niko 形如。。。𣋚妬𪜀生日𨉟。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:492:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Cuz people always get their favorite food on their birthday!"
"\\>\\nA whole lot of it!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 爲𤗆𠊛㫻咹𦁺㤇適𥪝𣈜生日𦓡！\\>\\n咹𡗉𪜀滕恪！"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:493:text
msgid "@niko Do you have a birthday, too?"
msgstr "@niko 舅拱𣎏咹生日渚？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:499:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Oh!\\>\\n\\@niko Then... what's your favorite food?"
"\\>\\n\\@niko_pancakes Is it pancakes?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 溩！\\>\\n\\@niko 丕時。。。舅適咹之一？\\>\\n\\@niko_pancakes 𣎏"
"沛餅喼空？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:500:text
msgid "@niko Wait, DO you like pancakes?"
msgstr "@niko 𦓡、舅𣎏適咹餅喼空丕？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:504:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed I see...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak Makes sense, since you're a god!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𫥨丕。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 拱合理催、舅𪜀𠎬全能𦓡！"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:505:text
msgid "@niko So...\\. do you like pancakes too?"
msgstr "@niko 丕時。。。\\. 舅拱適餅喼渚？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:513:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Me too!\\>\\n\\@niko On my last birthday, I ate ten of them."
"\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed I was so full I didn't eat anything else that day..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 𨉟拱勢！\\>\\n\\@niko 𣈜生日𠓀、𨉟𪵯𠬠繚𨑮丐㫻。"
"\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟𩛂𦤾餒𪥘󠄁𣈜空咹添之㫻。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:517:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Ah...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak Well, they're tasty!\\>\\n\\@niko "
"Maybe you should give them a chance, y'know?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed 啊。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 時、衆𤯆𡗋！\\>\\n\\@niko 舅拱𢧚"
"𦙴衆𠬠機會渚？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:520:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak My mama makes the best pancakes!\\>\\n\\@niko And some of the "
"neighbors make really good noodles."
msgstr "@niko_speak 媄𨉟𪵯餅喼超頂㫻！\\>\\n\\@niko 吧行𥯎𨉟𣎏仍𠊛𪵯麪拱𤯆𡛤。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:521:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak And oh! One of our neighbors make a lot of bread.\\>\\n\\@niko "
"Do you have any neighbors?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 啊！拱𣎏𠬠𠊛𪵯窒𡗉餅麪𡛤。\\>\\n\\@niko 舅𣎏行𥯎空？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:527:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! Do they share their food with you?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！𣱆𣎏𢺹𢩿𣘊咹喟舅空？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:533:text
msgid "@niko Ours do too!"
msgstr "@niko 行𥯎𨉟拱丕！"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:537:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed That's not very nice of them..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 空親善𡗋𠰚。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:543:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Oh...\\>\\n\\@niko That sounds a bit lonely."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 溩。。。\\>\\n\\@niko 唏孤單𠰚。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:546:text
msgid ""
"@niko Our neighbors and my mama take turns making food for the whole village "
"each day.\\>\\n\\@niko_speak Everyone also takes turns doing chores and "
"watching the little kids!"
msgstr ""
"@niko 行𥯎吧媄𨉟𠊝番僥𤍇咹朱𪥘󠄁廊每𣈜。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 𤗆𠊛拱𠊝僥𪵯役茹吧"
"矓僂稚𡛤！"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:547:text
msgid ""
"@niko I don't need to be watched anymore, though. \\>\\n\\@niko_speak I'm "
"old enough to help out!"
msgstr "@niko 扔𣇞𨉟空懃𠊛矓𡛤。 \\>\\n\\@niko_speak 𨉟覩𡘯抵輔役耒！"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:548:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...\\>\\n\\@niko I miss everyone."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。\\>\\n\\@niko 𨉟𢖵𤗆𠊛過。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:550:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed I've been gone for a while now, haven't I?"
"\\>\\n\\@niko_speak I wonder if they're worried about me..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟拱𠫾得可嘍耒董空？\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 空別𣱆𣎏當𢥈𢠯𧗱𨉟"
"空。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:552:text
msgid "@niko Ah, speaking of helping out, we should probably go now."
msgstr "@niko 啊、吶𧗱𡀯輔役、衆些𢧚𠫾催。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:606:text
msgid "@niko Hey.... \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 尼。。。。\\p？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:607:text
msgid "@niko I guess...you saw my dream?"
msgstr "@niko 昃𪜀。。。舅拱𧡊𥋏𢠩𧵑𨉟耒渚？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:615:text
msgid "@niko_distressed It was..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed 伮。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:616:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 .\\..\\..\\..\\.."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:619:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Come on, let's go..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 催、𠫾鬧。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:669:choice:0 Maps/Tower/Elevator/EV005:1:14:choice:0
msgid "Niko."
msgstr "尼孤。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:703:text
msgid "@niko ...Hello?\\>\\@niko_speak ...\\p?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。吀嘲？\\>\\@niko_speak 。。。\\p？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:705:text
msgid "@niko_speak Was that you just now?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 沛舅妬空？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:706:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I thought I...heard your voice?\\>\\n\\@niko ...in my dream..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 形如𨉟。。。𦖑𧡊舅？\\>\\n\\@niko 。。。𥪝𥋏𢠩𧵑𨉟。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:708:text
msgid "@niko ...\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed ...Ah, guess you're still not there..."
msgstr "@niko 。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 。。。啊、昃舅吻空於低。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:710:text Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric
#: npc:2:139:text grounds/EV188:1:143:text RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:118:text
#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:3:199:text Maps/Tower/Water/pc:1:52:text
msgid "@niko_distressed ..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed 。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:712:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Wait...there's something in my pocket. \\>\\n\\@niko I don't "
"remember putting it there..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 寬㐌。。。𣎏之妬𥪝襊襖𨉟。 \\>\\n\\@niko 扔𨉟𣎏朱伮𠓨低兜𠰚。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:722:text
msgid "@ed [Niko feels uneasy.]"
msgstr "@ed 【尼孤感𧡊不安。】"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:732:text Save:799:text Maps/POSTGAME green/Research
#: Station/Power room/EV004:1:3:text green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula
#: npc:2:15:text green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:33:text Maps/Red
#: ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:84:text
#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:107:text RED SKY/Elevator
#: deck/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:56:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/factory
#: interior/factory upstairs/ :1:8:text sky/City gate/tutorial/intro:1:37:text
#: gate/tutorial/intro:1:41:text Maps/Tower/Summit/Shatter/EV003:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:740:text
msgid "@niko_speak ....\\p?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。。\\p？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:741:text
msgid "@niko_surprised ......\\p!!! Can you hear me?"
msgstr "@niko_surprised 。。。。。。\\p！！！舅𣎏𦖑𧡊𨉟空？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:749:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Oh, phew..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𧘇它。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:750:text Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory
#: Entrance/courtyard/EV009:1:6:text
msgid "@niko_speak What happened?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𡀯之𣃣侈𫥨丕？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:751:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Everything went pitch black for a second..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 自𤼸𤗆次𠭤𢧚𣋁喑。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:758:text
msgid "@niko_speak \\p?"
msgstr "@niko_speak \\p？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:759:text
msgid "@niko_surprised Are you still there?"
msgstr "@niko_surprised 舅吻哙妬渚？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:761:choice:0
msgid "I'm here."
msgstr "𨉟於低。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:767:text Maps/Green/Ruins
#: In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:15:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed It happened again..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 伮徠侈𫥨耒。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:769:text
msgid "@niko_what Everything just went really dark..."
msgstr "@niko_what 𤗆次𣋁岑徠。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:770:text
msgid "@niko_speak So dark, the lightbulb doesn't even light it!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣋁𦤾餒琫畑拱空照𤏬得㫻！"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:773:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 Oh, and it's not because I don't have the lightbulb anymore, either!"
msgstr "@niko2 吧拱空沛爲𨉟當空擒琫畑𡛤兜！"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:774:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed It feels like a different kind of dark..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 感覺如妬𪜀𠬠矯𣋁恪。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:783:text
msgid "@niko_distressed Oh...."
msgstr "@niko_distressed 喂。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:784:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed \\p, let me know when you're back..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed \\p、哙𨉟欺舅𢮿徠唲。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:786:choice:0 Save:801:choice:0
msgid "I'm back"
msgstr "𨉟𢮿徠耒低"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:792:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I don't know why this keeps happening..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空別在哰伮吻據侈𫥨𡛤。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:807:text
msgid "@niko_speak I don't think anyone else is noticing it, either..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟拱空擬𣎏埃恪抵意𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:808:text
msgid "@niko_what Am I the only one who's seeing this?"
msgstr "@niko_what 𣎏沛每𨉟𨉟𧡊仍次尼空？"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:815:choice:0
msgid "Niko, I'm back"
msgstr "尼孤、𨉟𢮿徠耒低"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:821:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Hey, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 尼、\\p。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Load Save:822:text
msgid "@niko Welcome back."
msgstr "@niko 嘲𢜏𠭤徠。"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:3:text CommonEvents/paperbot:10:text
#: CommonEvents/paperbot:16:text CommonEvents/paperbot:22:text
#: CommonEvents/paperbot:30:text Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/EV177:1:1:text Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:5:text
msgid "[EVENING NEWS! EVENING NEWS!]"
msgstr "【時事𣇜𣋁！時事𣇜𣋁！】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:4:text
msgid "[I AM NOT CERTAIN THAT IT IS EVENING.]"
msgstr "【𪝬空昃𣊾𣇞𣎏沛𣇜𣋁咍空。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:5:text
msgid "[BUT MY LIGHT SENSORS ARE NOT DETECTING DAYLIGHT.]"
msgstr "【扔感變𧵑𪝬當空認得暎𣌝。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:6:text
msgid "[I WILL ASSUME IT IS EVENING.]"
msgstr "【𣋁𠱊墨定現當𪜀𣇜𣋁。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:11:text
msgid ""
"[MAINTENANCE IS STRUGGLING TO FIX THE MAJOR PIPELINE COLLAPSE IN THE NORTH "
"SECTOR.]"
msgstr "【隊保持當﨤𠸋𫩒𥪝欺處理務砬塘䈵渃𡘯於分區北。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:12:text
msgid ""
"[LIKELIHOOD OF AN IMMINENT WATER SHORTAGE IN THE INNER CITY IS NOW 84.2%]"
msgstr "【可能侈𫥨情狀少渃𣈜𣊾𣇞𥪝內城𪜀84.2%】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:17:text
msgid ""
"[DISTURBANCE WAS DETECTED FROM THE GROUND ACCESS ELEVATOR ON MAIN STREET.]"
msgstr "【㐌發現擾動自簜𣛠𬺗𩈘𡐙𨑗塘正。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:18:text
msgid ""
"[HOWEVER, THE ISSUE QUICKLY RESOLVED ITSELF BEFORE INVESTIGATIONS COULD TAKE "
"PLACE.]"
msgstr "【雖然、問題㐌自解決𠓀欺𣎏体進行調查。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:23:text
msgid "[THE MESSIAH IS CURRENTLY SPEAKING TO NEWSBOT UNIT #28.]"
msgstr "【𠎬救世現當交接喟單位信息数28。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:24:text
msgid "[WHICH IS ME.]"
msgstr "【正𪜀𪝬。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:25:text
msgid "[HELLO, MESSIAH.]"
msgstr "【吀嘲、𠎬救世。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:26:text Maps/POSTGAME green/burial
#: grounds/alula:1:14:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/factory interior/EV010:2:2:text
#: interior/EV017:2:2:text Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/Map
#: Events:2:5:text
msgid "@niko_speak Hi!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 吀嘲！"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:31:text
msgid "[STRANGE SOUNDS HAVE BEEN REPORTED FROM THE SLUMS.]"
msgstr "【㐌𣎏報告𧗱仍音聲𨓐𦤾自區隖𤝞。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:32:text
msgid "[THEIR SOURCE IS UNKNOWN.]"
msgstr "【空𤑟源㭲𧵑衆。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:33:text
msgid ""
"[THESE SOUNDS HAVE BEEN DESCRIBED AS \"FAINT BLEATING\" BY THE AREA'S "
"RESIDENTS.]"
msgstr "【仍音聲得各居民模寫𪜀偅如「㗂羝叫」。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:38:text
msgid "[EVENING NEWS COMMUNITY BULLETIN]"
msgstr "【版信共同𣇜𣋁】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:39:text
msgid ""
"[THE LIBRARY RELEASED SEVERAL NEW BOOKS BY THE ELUSIVE AUTHOR LAST WEEK.]"
msgstr "【旬𠓀書院㐌朱𫥨眜𠬠数頭冊㵋𤳸作者秘隱。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:40:text
msgid "[THE HEAD LIBRARIAN RECOMMENDS THEM.]"
msgstr "【衆得守書題出。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:41:text
msgid ""
"[THE ASSISTANT LIBRARIAN HAD NO COMMENT AS HE REPORTEDLY FLED THE SCENE "
"SOBBING.]"
msgstr "【守書輔空評論𢖖󠄁欺𣃣哭𣃣𠬃𧼋。】"

#: CommonEvents/paperbot:42:text
msgid ""
"[THE RECEPTIONIST HAD NO COMMENT EITHER BECAUSE THE RECEPTIONIST IS A ROBOT.]"
msgstr "【員禮賓拱空𣎏意見爲員禮賓𪜀𠊛𣛠。】"

#: CommonEvents/Translated Journal:2:text
msgid ""
"$Greetings, \\p.\\nIf you can finally read this, that means you are near the "
"Tower."
msgstr "$吀嘲、\\p。\\n裊伴𣎏体讀得仍𣳔尼、𣎏義𪜀伴當於近座塔。"

#: CommonEvents/Translated Journal:4:text
msgid "$The Tower is the domain of an elusive Entity."
msgstr "$座塔𪜀領地𧵑𠬠寔体秘隱。"

#: CommonEvents/Translated Journal:5:text
msgid ""
"$This being is connected to the world.\\nFor now, you can think of it as the "
"spirit of the world."
msgstr "$寔体尼連結喟世界。\\n伴𣎏体暫䁛伮如靈魂𧵑世界尼。"

#: CommonEvents/Translated Journal:7:text
msgid ""
"$It has no physical form, but it can communicate through computers and other "
"machinery."
msgstr "$伮空𣎏身殼物理、扔𣎏体相作通過𣛠併吧各類𣛠𢪮恪。"

#: CommonEvents/Translated Journal:9:text
msgid "$...You know who I am talking about, of course."
msgstr "$。。。必然伴別𣋁當指埃。"

#: CommonEvents/Translated Journal:11:text
msgid ""
"$When you first arrived here with our savior, it no doubt contacted you "
"right away."
msgstr "$欺伴𬧐低吝頭共𠎬救世、伮昃𥗜㐌聯絡喟伴𬆄即刻。"

#: CommonEvents/Translated Journal:13:text
msgid ""
"$Through its own means, the entity will guide the both of you to the Tower."
msgstr "$通過仍方式𥢆𧵑伮、伮𠱊引𪥘󠄁𠄩𠊛伴𦤾座塔。"

#: CommonEvents/Translated Journal:15:text
msgid ""
"$The entry room is at the Tower's base.\\nNot only do you need the sun "
"there, but also three pieces of the previous sun."
msgstr "$𡓃𠓨於蹎座塔。\\n伴空只懃𩈘𡗶於妬、𦓡沛𣎏添𠀧𤗖𧵑𩈘𡗶𫇰。"

#: CommonEvents/Translated Journal:17:text
msgid ""
"$The savior will not be able to do anything there.\\nYou, \\p, on the other "
"hand..."
msgstr "$𠎬救世𠱊空体𪵯之𥪝妬。\\n哙伴、\\p、。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Translated Journal:19:text
msgid ""
"$Look at the pattern on the floor. Do as it says.\\nThe window will be gone, "
"so you need to bring it back."
msgstr "$觀察仍畫節𨑗孱。𪵯蹺指引。\\n𫔤籔𠱊變𠅒、由妬伴𠱊沛𠀲伮𠭤徠。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:1:text
msgid "@niko I'm not sure where I am, exactly..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟空昃𨉟當於兜。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:2:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I can't see too far off, everything's so dark..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空体𥆾過賒、𤗆次過𣋁。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:3:text
msgid "@prophet [Our World Was Not Always This Dim.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【世界𧵑衆𣋁㐌曾𤏬欣勢尼。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:4:text
msgid "@prophet [Nor Was It So Broken.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【吧令𣵰欣。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:5:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [But Time Waits For Nobody, Not Even Saviors.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【扔時間空䟻待埃、怞朱𣎏𪜀𠎬救世。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:6:text
msgid "@prophet [The World Is Divided Into Three Regions.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【世界得𢺹𪵯𠀧塳。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:7:text
msgid "@prophet [You're On The Fringe Right Now, The Barrens.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【現伴當於紒外共、塳邊疆。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:8:text
msgid "@prophet [That Tower You See In The Distance Once Held Our Sun.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【座塔伴𧡊於滕賒其曾貯𩈘𡗶。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:9:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh, so that's what the tall thing was..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩、丕丐茹高高妬𪜀如丕。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:10:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [As You Go Further Towards The Center, You Will Cross The Other "
"Regions.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𥪝欺接近塳中心、伴𠱊𠫾過各塳哙徠。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:11:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [There Should Be A Map Still In This Outpost Somewhere...]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【形如吻哙𠬠𬌓版圖兜妬𥪝據点尼。。。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the world:12:text
msgid "@niko_speak Ooo..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:1:text
msgid "@niko I found it in the house I woke up in..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟尋𧡊伮𥪝間茹𨉟醒𧻭。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:2:text
msgid "@prophet [Within Your Hands Is Our New Sun.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𥪝𢬣伴𪜀𩈘𡗶㵋𧵑衆𪝬。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:3:text
msgid "@niko Your... \\.\\.\\@niko_speak sun?"
msgstr "@niko 𩈘𡗶。。。\\.\\.\\@niko_speak 𧵑各伴哰？"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:4:text
msgid "@prophet_omg [Yes!]"
msgstr "@prophet_omg 【董丕！】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:5:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [Years Ago,\\.\\. Our Previous Sun Sat Atop That Tower And Spilled "
"Its Life Into The Land.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【行𢆥𠓀、\\.\\. 𩈘𡗶𫇰𧵑衆𣋁座落𨑗頂座塔妬吧伴朱𩈘𡐙事𤯩。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:6:text
msgid "@prophet_sigh [But One Day, The Light Went Out.]"
msgstr "@prophet_sigh 【扔耒𠬠𣈜、暎畑挬𨄠。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:8:text
msgid "@prophet_sigh [The World Is Still Hanging On By A Thread.]"
msgstr "@prophet_sigh 【世界吻哙梭𠾾𤯩。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:9:text
msgid ""
"@prophet_hmm [The Surface Of This World Is Abundant With An Element Called "
"Phosphor.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【皮𩈘𧵑世界尼貯𣹓𠬠元素𠸜𪜀光素。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:10:text
msgid ""
"@prophet_hmm [Fortunately For Us, This Element Stored Light Energy From Our "
"Previous Sun.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【𠶣朱衆些、元素尼貯撜能量暎𤏬自𩈘𡗶𫇰。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:11:text
msgid ""
"@prophet_hmm [It's Now Our Only Source Of Illumination, But Its Energy Is "
"Finite.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【現伮𪜀源暎𤏬唯一𧵑衆𪝬、仍能量𧵑伮𪜀𣎏限。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:12:text
msgid ""
"@prophet_sigh [When The Last Of The Light Dies,\\.\\. Our World Will Too.]"
msgstr "@prophet_sigh 【欺暎𤏬𡳳共𨄠𠫾、\\.\\. 世界尼𠱊𣩂。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:13:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...\\.\\.\\@niko_eyeclosed Ah..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。\\.\\.\\@niko_eyeclosed 啊。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:14:text
msgid "@prophet [But Now That You Are Here With The New Sun, All Is Well.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【扔𣇞欺伴㐌於低喟𩈘𡗶㵋、𤗆次調穩。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:15:text
msgid "@prophet [You Will Need To Restore It To The Tower.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【伴𠱊沛㨋伮𧗱座塔。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:16:text
msgid "@niko2 That looks... pretty far off!"
msgstr "@niko2 矓拱。。。賒㗶蒂！"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:17:text
msgid "@prophet [Yes. So Begins Your Pilgrimage.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【董丕。局行鄉𧵑伴扒頭在低。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:18:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [Also, The Sun Is Fragile, So Be Careful.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【垌時、𩈘𡗶拱易𥒮、𢧚伴𢝙𢚸謹慎。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:19:text
msgid "@prophet_sigh [If The Sun Shatters, The World Will End In An Instant.]"
msgstr "@prophet_sigh 【裊𩈘𡗶𥒮潵、世界𠱊臨終𣈜即刻。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains the lightbulb:20:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout
#: point/Mineshaft entrance/server room/backroom/proto:3:260:text Maps/POSTGAME
#: green/Dock/fisherman npc:1:3:text
msgid "@niko3 Oh..."
msgstr "@niko3 溩。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:1:text Maps/POSTGAME green/burial
#: grounds/cedric npc:2:86:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:45:text Maps/Red
#: ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:19:text
#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Cabin/npc_silver:4:56:text
msgid "@niko Oh..."
msgstr "@niko 溩。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:2:text
msgid "@niko I don't mean to be rude, but I.."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟空𣎏意之兜、扔𦓡。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:3:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'm... not sure about this."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空。。。昃𡗋𧗱𡀯尼。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:4:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 I still don't know how I got here!"
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 𨉟哙空別在哰𨉟徠於低！"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:5:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I was just with my mama a few hours ago..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𠄧㗂𠓀𨉟哙當於𢭲媄𨉟𦓡。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:6:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 And now it feels like I'm in a bad dream..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 𣇞低𨉟如當𥪝𠬠𩂀惡夢丕。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:7:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I just want to go home..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟只㦖𧗱茹啐𦓡。。。"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:9:text
msgid "@prophet [...]"
msgstr "@prophet 【。。。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:10:text
msgid "@prophet [Your Mission Is To Save Our World.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【任務𧵑伴𪜀解救世界尼。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:11:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [Just As My Mission Is To Tell You About Our World.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【拱如任務𧵑𪝬𪜀解釋朱伴𧗱伮。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:12:text
msgid "@prophet [I Am Unable To Help You Beyond My Programming.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𪝬空体𢴇伴外仍之㐌得立程𠻿。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:13:text
msgid "@prophet_sigh [I Am Sorry.]"
msgstr "@prophet_sigh 【窒吀纇。】"

#: CommonEvents/prophet explains going home:14:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...oh."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。嗚。"

#: CommonEvents/rue vision:87:text CommonEvents/:87:text
msgid "@niko_shock \\|...\\.\\...."
msgstr "@niko_shock \\|。。。\\.\\.。。。"

#: CommonEvents/rue vision:92:text CommonEvents/:92:text
msgid "@niko_speak \\p! Did you see what happened?"
msgstr "@niko_speak \\p！舅𣎏𧡊蓋之𣃣侈𫥨空？"

#: CommonEvents/rue vision:94:choice:0 CommonEvents/:94:choice:0
msgid "Yeah?"
msgstr "哰丕？"

#: CommonEvents/rue vision:100:text CommonEvents/:100:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed My vision went blank for a second...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak And "
"then I saw something?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed 唪然眜𨉟𥊚𠫾。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 耒形如𨉟𧡊之妬時沛？"

#: CommonEvents/rue vision:101:text CommonEvents/:101:text
msgid "@niko Like a really short dream..."
msgstr "@niko 如𠬠𥋏𥊚超𠦯丕。。。"

#: CommonEvents/rue vision:103:text CommonEvents/:103:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I wonder what that was about..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 空別𪜀𣎏𡀯之𡛤。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 1:3:script
msgid "So you actually made it here."
msgstr "丕𪜀伴𡳃窮㐌𦤾得低。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 1:6:script
msgid "I... guess you win, \\p."
msgstr "昃。。。𪜀伴勝耒、\\p。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 1:9:script
msgid "I'll tell you how to save the world, then."
msgstr "丕𣇞𪝬𠱊指伴格解救世界尼。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 1:13:script
msgid "When you reach the summit, shatter the lightbulb, and..."
msgstr "欺伴𬨠𦤾頂座塔、㧺𥒮𡞗畑、歱耒。。。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 2:3:script
msgid "...I'm just humoring you."
msgstr "。。。𢴉啐。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 2:7:script
msgid "I know you've been getting help from a certain someone."
msgstr "𪝬別伴㐌認助𢴇自𠬠埃妬。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 2:10:script
msgid "He already told you about the choice, didn't he?"
msgstr "𣎏𨤔英些㐌朱伴別𧗱攄譔耒𠰚？"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 3:3:script
msgid "Are you still planning to save the world, \\p?"
msgstr "伴吻哙㦖救世界哰、\\p？"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 3:6:script
msgid "Why are you trying so hard for this?"
msgstr "哰伴吻哙固𠡚丕？"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 3:9:script
msgid "Haven't you even figured out what this world IS?"
msgstr "𪳨伴拱別世界尼𪜀之耒渚？"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 4:4:script
msgid "I told you at the beginning, your mission is to help Niko leave."
msgstr "𪝬㐌吶朱伴𬆄徐頭、哴任務𧵑伴𪜀𢴇尼孤阻𠭤𧗱。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 4:7:script
msgid "Because Niko isn't part of this world."
msgstr "爲尼孤空屬𧗱世界尼。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 4:10:script
msgid "Niko is the only thing worth saving here."
msgstr "只𣎏尼孤𪜀當救。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 4:15:script
msgid "...The final choice is up to you."
msgstr "。。。攄譔𡳃窮屬𧗱伴。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 4:18:script
msgid "I can't go against my programming."
msgstr "𪝬空体𠫾逆徠仍之㐌得立程𠻿。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 5:3:script Maps/Start/pc:1:90:script Maps/INIT/Start
#: purple/pc:1:62:script
msgid "You only have one shot, \\p."
msgstr "伴只𣎏𠬠機會啐、\\p。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 5:7:script
msgid ""
"If you choose to smash the lightbulb, then Niko wakes up back home, like it "
"was all a dream."
msgstr "裊伴㧺𥒮琫畑、尼孤𠱊醒丕於茹、如体𤗆次指𪜀𠬠𥋏𥊚。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 5:12:script
msgid ""
"But if you let Niko return the sun, the child will have to bear the weight "
"of this sacrifice."
msgstr "仍裊伴抵尼孤㨋徠𩈘𡗶、𠀲𥘷𠱊沛挭𨑗𦠘事犧牲尼。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 6:3:script
msgid "At least, tell Niko the truth."
msgstr "𠃣一時唉朱尼孤別事實𠫾渚。"

#: CommonEvents/Ed hallway 6:6:script
msgid "...you do care about Niko, don't you?"
msgstr "。。。伴關心𧗱尼孤𦓡、董空？"

#: CommonEvents/glowJournal:85:text
msgid "@niko2 Oh... I found this page."
msgstr "@niko2 溩。。𨉟𣃣尋𧡊張紙尼。"

#: CommonEvents/glowJournal:86:text
msgid "@niko It looks kind of like a drawing of this room."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠版𦘧𧵑間房尼。"

#: CommonEvents/glowJournal:87:text
msgid "@niko_speak Maybe it's telling us we should come here?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 伮當指衆些𦤾𡊲尼？"

#: CommonEvents/glowJournal:88:text
msgid "@niko Which we did, already."
msgstr "@niko 𦓡些當𨅸妬耒。"

#: CommonEvents/glowJournal:89:text
msgid "@niko_speak So... it looks like we're on the right track!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 丕時。。。䀡𫥨衆些當𠫾董向耒！"

#: CommonEvents/alula helps!:14:text
msgid "@alula I'm helping!"
msgstr "@alula 𨉟拱當𢴇低！"

#: CommonEvents/hi silver:2:text
msgid "@silver [Hello again.]"
msgstr "@silver 【𠬠吝𡛤、吀嘲。】"

#: CommonEvents/hi silver:3:text silver:6:text
msgid "@Niko Hello."
msgstr "@Niko 吀嘲。"

#: CommonEvents/hi silver:7:text
msgid "@silver2 [Do you... need anything?]"
msgstr "@silver2 【伴𣎏。。。懃之空？】"

#: CommonEvents/hi silver:8:text
msgid "@Niko Nah."
msgstr "@Niko 空。"

#: CommonEvents/hi silver:9:text
msgid "@silver [Okay.]"
msgstr "@silver 【嗚雞。】"

