msgstr "@niko 𫫡！"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 4 - squares/fisherman npc:1:14:text npc:1:22:text
msgid "Last week, I saw more of those squares while out fishing."
msgstr "旬𠓀、𪝬𧡊添仍形𣃱妬欺當鉤𩵜。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 4 - squares/fisherman npc:1:15:text npc:1:23:text
msgid "I knew better than to get too close, though."
msgstr "必然𪜀𪝬空𦤾過近。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 4 - squares/fisherman npc:1:16:text
msgid "@alula_oh Oh! \\>\\@alula_pout It was that stuff in the door..."
msgstr "@alula_oh 嗚！ \\>\\@alula_pout 𪜀蓋次𥪝𫔤。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 4 - squares/fisherman npc:1:17:text
msgid "Oh, so you saw it too, huh..."
msgstr "溩、丕舅拱𧡊伮耒𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 4 - squares/fisherman npc:1:18:text
msgid "@alula_oh Yeah! \\>\\@alula_pout My brother told me not to touch those!"
msgstr "@alula_oh 唹！\\>\\@alula_pout 英𨉟保𨉟空得動𠓨衆！"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 4 - squares/fisherman npc:1:19:text
msgid "Yeup. He gets it."
msgstr "董丕。英𧘇曉𡀯蒂。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 4 - squares/fisherman npc:1:24:text
msgid "@niko Squares?"
msgstr "@niko 𧗱𠇍形𣃱𧘇嘑？"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 4 - squares/fisherman npc:1:25:text
msgid "Squares, man.\\nThey're bad news."
msgstr "𧘇它、𠇍形𣃱。\\n䀨醜妬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/fish house/Map events:1:1:text Maps/Red
#: ground/ground
msgid "@niko_speak It's a big fishtank!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 伮𪜀𠬠蓋𣷭𩵜𡘯！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/EV007:1:1:text
#: GROUND/backalley/rue/EV008:1:1:text Maps/Red
#: ground/backalley/rue/EV007:1:1:text ground/backalley/rue/EV008:1:1:text
msgid "@niko There's no one here..."
msgstr "@niko 空𣎏埃於低𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/EV007:2:1:text
#: GROUND/backalley/rue/EV008:2:1:text Maps/Red
#: ground/backalley/rue/EV007:2:1:text ground/backalley/rue/EV008:2:1:text
msgid ""
"@niko It's a big tree, with leaves!\\>\\nHaven't seen one of these since I "
"was back home..."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠蓋𣘃𡘯、𣎏蘿𡛤！\\>\\n𨉟㐌空𧡊衆𠸥徐欺於茹。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:8:text
msgid "@rue !"
msgstr "！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:9:text
msgid "@rue You're here!!!"
msgstr "@rue 舅𦤾耒！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:11:text
msgid "@niko2 Rue!"
msgstr "@niko2 𠱋！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:12:text
msgid "@niko5 That's... you, right?"
msgstr "@niko5 𪜀。。。舅、董空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:13:text
#: GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:18:text
msgid "@rue Yes."
msgstr "@rue 董丕。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:16:text
msgid "@rue_talk Niko!"
msgstr "@rue_talk 尼孤！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:17:text
msgid "@niko2 Are you... are you Rue?"
msgstr "@niko2 舅。。。舅𣎏沛𪜀𠱋空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:21:text
msgid "@rue Did you... \\.\\.already meet the others?"
msgstr "@rue 舅㐌。。。 \\.\\.﨤仍𠊛哙徠耒渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:22:text
msgid "@niko2 Yeah... \\.\\.\\@niko_distressed2 but..."
msgstr "@niko2 耒。。。 \\.\\.\\@niko_distressed2 扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:23:text
msgid "@rue_sigh ...everything is in place, then."
msgstr "@rue_sigh 。。。丕時、𤗆次㐌𠻿𠳹耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/backalley/rue/rue:1:24:text
msgid "@rue Come on, let's go back to the clock room."
msgstr "@rue 鬧、衆些𢧚𢮿徠銅壺啐。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/fire action:1:1:text grounds/burial
#: grounds PLANE FIXED/fire
msgid "@niko It's a fire."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𡌽𪸔。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:64:text
msgid "@cedric_talk It's you!"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 正𪜀㛪！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:65:text
msgid "@niko !"
msgstr "@niko ！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:67:text
msgid "@cedric_smile You are Niko, right?"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 㛪𪜀尼孤、沛空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:68:text Maps/Red
#: ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:42:text
msgid "@niko_speak Mhm!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫫡！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:71:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm You... um..."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 㛪。。。𫫡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:72:text
msgid "@niko My name is Niko..."
msgstr "@niko 𠸜㛪𪜀尼孤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:73:text
msgid "@cedric_smile Ah!"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 啊！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:77:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_smile N-\\.\\.nice finally to meet you! \\@cedric_hmm \\>...no, wait."
msgstr ""
"@cedric_smile 實。。。\\.\\.實𢝙欺𡳃窮拱得﨤㛪！ \\@cedric_hmm \\>。。。啊"
"空、寬㐌。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:78:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh It is a pleasure to be of acquaintance at last, Niko."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 窒欣幸得同行窮英、尼孤。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:79:text
msgid "@cedric_smile My name is Cedric."
msgstr "@cedric_smile 𠸜英𪜀察嚦。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:80:text
msgid "@niko2 Oh!"
msgstr "@niko2 溩！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:81:text
msgid "@niko I'm supposed to be looking for you too!"
msgstr "@niko 㛪拱當尋英低！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:82:text
msgid "@cedric I am aware."
msgstr "@cedric 英別。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:83:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm Prototype had contacted me earlier, saying that you would be on "
"your way to the city."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 一號拱㐌連絡𢭲英、抵吶哴㛪當𨑗塘𦤾城鋪。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:84:text
msgid "@niko_speak He did?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 實哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:85:text
msgid "@cedric He sent me a message after his memories were restored."
msgstr "@cedric 英𧘇㐌寄英𠬠信𠴍𢖖󠄁欺恢復得記憶。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:87:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm He told me to wait in the city, but I thought it'd be faster for "
"me to pick you guys up."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 英𧘇𠸒英䟻𥪝城鋪、扔英擬哴直接𦤾迍各舅𠱊𪬭欣。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:88:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh ...Turns out, that was a terrible idea."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 。。。化𫥨、妬𪜀𠬠意想無窮頹弊。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:89:text
msgid "@niko2 Pick... us up?"
msgstr "@niko2 迍。。。衆𨉟唹？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:90:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes ...wait... YOU can fly that plane??"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 。。。寬㐌。。。英𣎏体俚𣛠𢒎哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:91:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm What...\\.\\.is a plane?"
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 𣛠𢒎。。。\\.\\.𪜀之丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:92:text
msgid "@niko_speak That thing behind you!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 蓋次騰𢖖󠄁英𧘇！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:98:text
msgid "@cedric_talk Oh! You mean the flying machine?"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 溩！意英𪜀飛行機哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:99:text
msgid "@niko_speak They're called planes in my world!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 世界𧵑㛪噲衆𪜀𣛠𢒎妬！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:100:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm Oh..."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 溩。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:105:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh ...I did not realize they existed in other worlds..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 。。。英空擬𪜀衆存在𥪝各世界恪。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:106:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak ...wait! Are you the friend that Calamus and Alula was talking "
"about, then?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。寬㐌！英𣎏沛𠊛伴𦓡哥羅𡃙吧阿瞜羅𠯅𦤾空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:107:text
msgid "@niko_speak Is this the same flying machine they were talking about?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏沛𪜀飛行機𦓡𣱆𠯅𦤾空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:108:text
msgid "@cedric I do not know anyone named Calamus or Alula."
msgstr "@cedric 英空慣埃𠸜𪜀哥羅𡃙或阿婁羅。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:109:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_talk I think... they're meant to be friends with my father. "
"\\>\\n\\@cedric_hmm ...in previous iterations of the..."
msgstr ""
"@cedric_talk 英擬。。。𣱆𪜀伴友𧵑仛英。\\>\\n\\@cedric_hmm 。。。𥪝各翻版𠓀"
"𧵑。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:110:text
msgid "@niko2 ...your father?"
msgstr "@niko2 。。。爸英哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:111:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_talk He was the original owner of the flying machine... "
"\\>\\n\\@cedric_hmm ...it's... one of his greatest inventions, actually."
msgstr ""
"@cedric_talk 翁𧘇𪜀主班頭𧵑飛行機尼。。。 \\>\\n\\@cedric_hmm 。。。寔𫥨伮"
"𪜀。。。𠬠𥪝仍發明偉大一𧵑翁𧘇。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:112:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes YOUR DAD INVENTED PLANES???"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 爸英發明𫥨𣛠𢒎哰？？？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:113:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm ...flying machine."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 。。。飛行機。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:114:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes IT'S COOL EITHER WAY!!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 吶終𪜀蒦杈𥷒無窮！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:115:text
msgid "@cedric_smile Thanks?"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 吀。。。感恩？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:116:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_talk But to answer your earlier question... I am proficient in "
"operating the machine."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 仍抵㨋𠳒句𠳨𣃣𣅅𧵑㛪。。。英𣎏体運行飛行機𠬠格醇熟。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:117:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm ...but...something weird happened to the engine when I was in "
"the air earlier..."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 。。。扔。。。𣎏之妬㐌侈𫥨𢭲動機𥪝欺英當𨑗空𣃣𣅅。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:118:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh I had to make an emergency landing on this tiny island before I "
"crashed into the city wall."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 英沛下𦑃緊急𨑗𡉕島𡮈𡭰尼𠓀欺𠛌𠓨墻城鋪。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:119:text
msgid "@niko3 You almost crashed? \\>\\n\\@niko4 That's terrible!"
msgstr "@niko3 英侐淶哰？\\>\\n\\@niko4 實驚恐！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:120:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh It was not pleasant, I will admit.\\n\\>"
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 英沛承認、空𠇍歡喜。\\n\\>"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:121:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm I wonder if the engine problem has to do with the square "
"particle disruptions..."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 英空𤑟料問題動機𣎏連關𦤾事擾動由分子𣃱空。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:122:text
msgid ""
"@cedric I checked, but... there isn't any of that square stuff inside the "
"machine itself."
msgstr "@cedric 𪝬㐌檢查、雖然空發現仍分子妬邊𥪝鈷𣛠。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:123:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm ...but I noticed some islands in the Glen are REALLY messed up "
"now."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 。。。仍英認𧡊𣎏𠬠數𡉕島𥪝區潭浰被墟害嚴重。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:124:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed They are..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 董丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:125:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh Sigh. \\>\\nGuess I should have listened to Proto in the first "
"place."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 𧘇它。\\>\\n當𫥨英𢧚𦖑蹺一號。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:126:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm ...say, where is he?"
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 。。。𠯅㵋𢖵、舅些頭耒？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:127:text
msgid "@cedric_talk He said he was coming with you..."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 舅𧘇㐌吶𪜀𠱊𠫾蹺㛪𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:128:text
msgid "@cedric Is he still back at the main islands?"
msgstr "@cedric 舅𧘇吻於徠𡉕島正嘑？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:129:text
msgid "@niko3 Oh... actually..."
msgstr "@niko3 唹。。。寔𫥨。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:130:text
msgid "@niko4 ...back at the Barrens, he..."
msgstr "@niko4 。。。於塳邊疆、英𧘇。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:132:text
msgid "@niko_upset There was a cave-in...\\.\\. and then a bunch of squares..."
msgstr "@niko_upset 𡌢𡎡被砬。。。\\.\\. 吧耒𠬠埬塊𣃱。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:133:text
msgid "@niko_upset2 ...he...\\.\\. and the robot lady..."
msgstr "@niko_upset2 。。。英𧘇。。。\\.\\. 吧姉𠊛𣛠。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:135:text
msgid "@niko_distressed_talk ...neither of them made it out."
msgstr "@niko_distressed_talk 。。。調空過𠺌。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:137:text RED
#: SKY/landing/cedric:1:114:text SKY/landing/cedric:1:116:text
#: SKY/landing/cedric:1:121:text
msgid "@cedric_eek ..."
msgstr "@cedric_eek 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:138:text
msgid "@cedric_eek No...."
msgstr "@cedric_eek 空体鬧。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:140:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 He...\\.\\. did give me this, though."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 扔英𧘇𣎏。。。\\.\\. 迻㛪丐尼。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:141:text
msgid "@niko3 This disk he pulled from his head..."
msgstr "@niko3 英𧘇捽隻𥐨尼自𥪝頭𫥨。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:142:text
msgid "@cedric_talk Oh!!!"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 溩！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:143:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh2 Oh thank goodness."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 𥚄主。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:144:text
msgid "@cedric_talk He gave you his main drive!"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 舅𧘇㐌迻㛪隖勁正𧵑𨉟！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:145:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm As long as I have this, I should be able to bring him back."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 𣎏伮時英𠱊𣎏体迻舅𧘇𠭤徠。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:146:text
msgid "@niko2 R-really?"
msgstr "@niko2 實唹？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:147:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh It's gonna be hard, but yes."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 𠱊空易揚、仍董丕。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:148:text
msgid "@cedric You need all three of us for the big door."
msgstr "@cedric 伴𠱊懃𪥘󠄁𠀧𠊛𪨠英𠓀𦑃𫔤𡘯。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:149:text
msgid "@niko2 The...?"
msgstr "@niko2 𦑃。。。？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:150:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm But first thing's first, we need to find a way to go to the city."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 扔𠓀歇、衆些沛尋塘𠓨城鋪㐌。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:151:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Right...\\>\\nThe city gate is kind of kaput now."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 董耒。。。\\>\\n𨶛𠓨𣎏𨤔歇救耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:152:text
msgid ""
"@cedric2 If this machine was working, we could just fly right in there..."
msgstr "@cedric2 裊如飛行機活動、衆些𣎏体𢒎𬆄𠓨𥪝。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:153:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm I've isolated the issue with the machine, but I can't repair it "
"with the stuff I have on hand."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 英㐌確定得問題喟鈷𣛠、扔英空体解決衆喟仍之當𣎏。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:154:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh? What's wrong with it?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩？伮被哰丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:155:text
msgid ""
"@cedric The \\c[2]battery\\c[0] in the engine is dead, and the engine has "
"some \\c[2]gears\\c[0] that need to be replaced."
msgstr ""
"@cedric 𫪐\\c[2]汴\\c[0]𥪝動機㐌𣩂、吧懃沛𠊝替𠬠数\\c[2]𨋣𪘵\\c[0]𥪝動機。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:156:text
msgid ""
"@niko ...\\>\\nDo you think you'll be able to fix it if \\p and I help you "
"find those things?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。\\>\\n英擬英𣎏体𢯢得伮裊㛪吧\\p𢴇英檢仍𦁺妬空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:157:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm ...maybe."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 。。。𣎏体。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:158:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh Problem is... the Glen isn't exactly a very high-tech area."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 問題𪜀。。。區潭浰空沛𪜀𠬠區工藝高之朱甘。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:159:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh ...I'm not sure if you'll be able to find anything so "
"specialized here."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 。。。英空昃㛪𣎏体尋仍零件𡀯用𦤾丕於低。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:160:text
msgid "@niko_speak We'll try anyway!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 怞哰時衆㛪吻𠱊固！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:2:161:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed We can't really do anything else right now..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣊾𣇞拱空哙之恪抵衆𨉟𪵯。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:2:text npc:3:25:text
msgid "@niko2 We found a battery..."
msgstr "@niko2 衆㛪尋𧡊𠬠𫪐汴。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:3:text npc:3:26:text
msgid "@cedric_talk Oh, nice!"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 溩、絕！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:4:text npc:3:27:text
msgid "@cedric3 I honestly wasn't expecting it..."
msgstr "@cedric3 實事英拱空懞待待之𡗉。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:5:text
msgid "@niko It's from the generator on one of the islands."
msgstr "@niko 伮於𥪝𣛠發電𨑗𠬠𡉕島。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:6:text
msgid "@cedric_talk The research station?"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 站研究哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:7:text RED GROUND/ground
#: 1/Library entrance/Lobby/npc_george2:3:5:text
msgid "@niko2 Yeah."
msgstr "@niko2 𫫡。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:8:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak It was powering all the robots there...\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed I "
"felt bad for taking it..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 伮𪜀源𤯩𧵑悉𪥘󠄁𠊛𣛠於妬。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 㛪𧡊罪纇"
"過。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:9:text npc:3:29:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm Ah..."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 啊。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:10:text
msgid "@cedric_smile ...we can always just give it back later."
msgstr "@cedric_smile 。。。𣅶𢖖󠄁衆些𫼳㨋徠拱貯晚。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:11:text
#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:167:text Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter
#: house/lenses:1:6:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Alright..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 得耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:19:text npc:3:39:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm We still need a few \\c[2]gears\\c[0] to put this engine back "
"together.\\>\\nPlease do what you must to find some."
msgstr ""
"@cedric_hmm 衆些吻擒𠬠𠄧\\c[2]𨋣𪘵\\c[0]抵擸撘徠動機。\\>\\n唉𪵯悉𪥘󠄁仍之伴𣎏"
"体抵尋衆。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:28:text
msgid ""
"@niko We found this one in the Barrens.\\>\\nIt wasn't working at first, but "
"\\p and I managed to fix it!"
msgstr "@niko 衆㛪尋𧡊丐尼於塳邊疆。\\>\\n伴頭伮空活動、仍㛪吧\\p㐌𢯢得伮！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:30:text
msgid "@cedric_smile ...it's good that you thought to bring it with you then."
msgstr "@cedric_smile 。。。實𢆪𪜀㛪㐌決定𫼳伮邊𨉟。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:31:text
msgid "@niko_speak Yup!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 董丕！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:45:text
msgid "@niko_speak We found a music box!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 衆㛪𣃣尋得𠬠匣樂！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:46:text
msgid "@niko It... should have gears in it, right?"
msgstr "@niko 伮。。。𣎏𨋣𪘵邊𥪝渚𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:47:text
msgid "@cedric I assume so, but...\\>\\n..."
msgstr "@cedric 英擬丕、仍。。。\\>\\n。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:48:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm This looks like one of the ones that my father made."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 丐尼矓偅如𠬠丐仛英製作。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:49:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes YOUR DAD MAKES MUSIC BOXES TOO?"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 爸英拱𪵯匣樂㫻？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:50:text
msgid "@cedric_smile My dad makes a lot of things!"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 仛英𪵯窒𡗉次！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:51:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm Where did you get this from, by the way?"
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 𦓡㛪檢丐尼於兜丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:52:text
msgid "@niko_speak A trader from the village gave it to me!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠬠俚販𥪝廊朱𨉟！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:53:text
msgid ""
"@cedric I see.\\>\\nI remember father saying that he used to trade with some "
"of the people here."
msgstr "@cedric 𫥨勢。\\>\\n英𢖵仛曾吶哴翁曾交商喟𠬠数居民於低。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:54:text
msgid "@cedric_smile He did always love traveling this world, despite..."
msgstr "@cedric_smile 翁㫻耽迷游玩世界尼、怞朱。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:55:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm ...well."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 。。。伴別蒂。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:56:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Ah, sorry, I started rambling."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 啊、吀纇、英徠𡗋𡀯𡛤耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:57:text
msgid "@cedric_talk The gears in there are compatible with the engine."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 𨋣𪘵𥪝妬相適喟動機。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:58:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Although it pains me to have to take it apart..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 雖哴窒𤴬𢚸欺沛操伮𫥨。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:59:text
msgid "@niko2 Oh...\\.\\. I'm sorry!"
msgstr "@niko2 溩。。。\\.\\. 㛪窒惜！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:60:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm It's fine..."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 空哰兜。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:68:text
msgid ""
"@cedric We still need a \\c[3]battery\\c[0] to get this engine running."
"\\>\\nPlease do what you must to find one."
msgstr ""
"@cedric 衆些吻懃𠬠𫪐\\c[3]汴\\c[0]抵動機𧼋。\\>\\n唉𪵯悉𪥘󠄁仍之㛪𣎏体抵尋伮。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:73:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Sorry... I forgot..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 吀纇。。。㛪悁𠅒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:74:text
msgid "@niko What parts do we need to find again?"
msgstr "@niko 衆𨉟沛尋仍之𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:76:text
msgid "@cedric We still need a \\c[3]battery\\c[0] to get this engine running."
msgstr "@cedric 衆些吻懃𠬠𫪐\\c[3]汴\\c[0]抵起動動機。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:80:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm We still need a few \\c[2]gears\\c[0] to put this engine back "
"together."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 衆些吻懃𠬠𠄧\\c[2]𨋣𪘵\\c[0]抵擸撘徠動機。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:83:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm A \\c[2]battery\\c[0] for the engine, and a few "
"\\c[2]gears\\c[0] to replace the broken ones."
msgstr ""
"@cedric_hmm 𠬠𫪐\\c[2]汴\\c[0]朱動機、吧𠬠𠄧\\c[2]𨋣𪘵\\c[0]抵𠊝替仍丐㐌閧。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/cedric npc:3:88:text
msgid ""
"@cedric If you could find me the parts I need, I should be able to get this "
"machine off the ground again."
msgstr "@cedric 裊㛪𣎏体尋仍零件英懃、英可昃𠱊𣎏体運行𠭤徠鈷𣛠尼。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV132:2:1:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/EV132:2:1:text
msgid "@niko We made it!"
msgstr "@niko 𬧐坭耒！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV132:2:3:text
msgid "@calamus C'mon, Alula.\\>\\nLet's go pay our respects..."
msgstr "@calamus 鬧、阿婁羅。\\>\\n𠫾怺媄催鬧。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV132:2:4:text
msgid "@alula Okay!"
msgstr "@alula 嗚雞！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:1:2:text
msgid "@calamus_smile2 At least I still got my sister..."
msgstr "@calamus_smile2 𠃣𫥨𨉟吻哙㛪𡛔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:1:5:text
msgid "@calamus_sad This is her grave..."
msgstr "@calamus_sad 低𪜀墓𧵑媄。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:1:6:text
msgid "@niko3 Ah..."
msgstr "@niko3 啊。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:1:9:text
msgid "@calamus_sad It's been years, but..."
msgstr "@calamus_sad 㐌𡗉𢆥耒、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:1:11:text
msgid "@calamus_sad ...It's still... \\.\\.hard, y'know?"
msgstr "@calamus_sad 。。。衆𨉟吻。。。\\.\\.𢖵媄𡗋、舅別空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:1:13:text grounds/EV188:1:33:text
#: grounds/EV188:1:149:text grounds/EV188:1:173:text green/Ruins In/Maize/map
#: events:1:35:text events:1:43:text RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/EV004:1:3:text entrance/Lobby/kip:1:381:text
#: entrance/Lobby/kip:1:453:text Maps/FINALE/Encounter/map events:4:53:text
#: events:4:65:text events:4:105:text SKY/Elevator deck/Office/observation
#: deck/Map Events:1:79:text Maps/Unused/pshot/EV001:1:27:text GROUND/To
#: Tower/map events:2:8:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft
#: entrance/server room/backroom/backhall/collapse/EV009:1:14:text
#: Maps/FINALE/Encounter PENG/map events:4:104:text
msgid "@niko4 ..."
msgstr "@niko4 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:1:14:text
msgid "@calamus_sad Sigh..."
msgstr "@calamus_sad 係。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:1:19:text
msgid ""
"@calamus_sad Alula....\\.\\.\\n\\@calamus_smile wanna help me look for some "
"flowers for mom later?"
msgstr ""
"@calamus_sad 阿婁羅。。。\\.\\.\\n\\@calamus_smile 㛪唉𢴇英尋花朱媄唲？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:1:20:text
msgid "@alula_gasp \\.\\.Y\\.E\\.S"
msgstr "@alula_gasp \\.\\.嗚\\.雞\\.㫻"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:1:22:text
msgid "@calamus_smile2 ..."
msgstr "@calamus_smile2 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:2:2:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/calamus:2:2:text
msgid ""
"@calamus We're just about done here, so let us know when you want to go back "
"to the ruins."
msgstr "@calamus 衆𨉟拱𢯛歱役耒、欺鬧㦖𠭤徠區殘跡時據哙衆𨉟唲。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:2:3:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/calamus:2:3:text
msgid "@niko Okay."
msgstr "@niko 嗚雞。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:2:6:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/calamus:2:6:text
msgid "@niko Hey, do you know where I could find a battery?"
msgstr "@niko 尼、舅𣎏別𡊲鬧𣎏汴空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:2:7:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/calamus:2:7:text
msgid "@calamus Good question.."
msgstr "@calamus 句𠳨唉妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:2:8:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/calamus:2:8:text
msgid "@calamus_heh We...\\.\\. don't really use electricity in the Glen."
msgstr "@calamus_heh 平常衆𨉟。。。\\.\\. 空用電𥪝塳潭浰。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:2:9:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/calamus:2:9:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Ah."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 啊。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:2:10:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/calamus:2:10:text
msgid ""
"@calamus_speak Oh, but there are robots at the research station!\\>\\nIf "
"there's a battery anywhere, they'd know where it is."
msgstr ""
"@calamus_speak 啊、扔𣎏𠊛𣛠在站研究蒂！\\>\\n裊𨒺低𣎏汴時𣱆𠱊別伮於兜催。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/calamus:2:11:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/calamus:2:11:text
msgid "@niko Gotcha, thanks!"
msgstr "@niko 㐌曉、感恩唲！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:1:2:text
msgid "@alula_speak I hope she can see us wherever she is!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 懞哴媄𣎏体𧡊衆些怞𣎏當於兜！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:1:7:text
msgid ""
"@alula_gasp MOM YOU'RE NOT GONNA BELIEVE WHAT HAPPENED TODAY WE MET THE "
"MESSIAH AND"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 媄㗒媄𠱊空体信浽仍之侈𫥨𣋚尼兜衆𡥵得﨤𠎬救世吧"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:1:9:text
msgid "@alula_oh ..."
msgstr "@alula_oh 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:1:13:text
msgid "@alula_speak ...hi Niko!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 。。。嘲尼孤！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:2:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:2:text
msgid "@alula Didja find any...\\@alula_pout ...any..."
msgstr "@alula 舅㐌尋𧡊丐。。。\\@alula_pout 。。。丐。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:3:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:3:text
msgid "@alula_oh ...what were you looking for again?"
msgstr "@alula_oh 。。。舅當尋之𧘇𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:4:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:4:text
msgid "@niko_speak Gears?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨋣𪘵嘑？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:5:text
msgid "@alula_speak Gears!\\>\\n\\@alula Didja find any of those?"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𨋣𪘵！\\>\\n\\@alula 舅㐌尋𧡊丐鬧𣗓？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:6:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:6:text
msgid "@niko No, but... I found this music box though!"
msgstr "@niko 𣗓、扔。。。𨉟𣎏尋𧡊丐匣樂尼！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:7:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:7:text
msgid "@alula_gasp Ooooh!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 溩－！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:10:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:10:text
msgid "@niko Do you know where I could find some gears?"
msgstr "@niko 舅𣎏別𡊲鬧𣎏𨋣𪘵空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:11:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:11:text
msgid "@alula Gears?\\>\\nWhat's... that?"
msgstr "@alula 𨋣𪘵？\\>\\n妬𪜀。。。丐之丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:12:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:12:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's like...\\.\\. A metal circle thing with teeth!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 偅如矯。。。\\.\\. 𠬠𠰳鉄形圇𣎏𪘵𧘇！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:13:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:13:text
msgid "@alula_speak A circle... with teeth?!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 形圇。。。𣎏𪘵哰？！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:14:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:14:text
msgid ""
"@alula_speak Haha, that sounds so silly!\\>\\nLike something Magpie would "
"have!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 哬哬、𦖑稚𡥵𠺳！\\>\\n𣎏欺㖼𩿙𣎏伮蒂！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:15:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:15:text
msgid "@niko Magpie?"
msgstr "@niko 㖼𩿙？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:16:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:16:text
msgid "@alula Y'know, the trader guy!"
msgstr "@alula 丐英俚販𧘇！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:17:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:17:text
msgid "@alula He collects all kinds of funny stuff!"
msgstr "@alula 英𧘇搜集覩𦁺𣘊𢳝勿㫻！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:18:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:18:text
msgid "@alula_speak I mean, he even keeps around broken glass and junk!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 愥哙𡨺徠𠇍𤗖水晶喟徠𣘊𠬃𡛤！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:20:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak ...Oh yeah!\\>\\n\\@niko I think I know who you're talking about."
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。啊唹！\\>\\n\\@niko 𨉟擬𨉟別舅當指埃耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/alula:2:21:text grounds/burial grounds
#: PLANE FIXED/alula:2:21:text
msgid "@alula_speak He's such a weirdo!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 英𧘇實奇啒！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:11:text
msgid "@cedric_smile Looks like the flying machine has a chance after all!"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 𣎏𨤔如吻哙機會朱飛行機！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:12:text
msgid ""
"@cedric I just have to assemble the pieces now, but it might take a while..."
msgstr "@cedric 𣇞英指懃擸𤗆次徠喟僥、仍𠱊可嘍蒂。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:13:text
msgid "@cedric_smile Do you mind keeping me company?"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 㛪𣎏体於邊𧣲英渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:25:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout
#: point/Mineshaft entrance/server room/silver stand:1:6:text stand:2:7:text
msgid "@niko How's it going?"
msgstr "@niko 𤗆次哰耒英？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:26:text
msgid "@cedric Slow..."
msgstr "@cedric 窒踸。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:27:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm The connectors in the battery were not designed for this type of "
"engine, so I have to shift around some of these ports."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 各頭㩒𧵑汴空得設計朱類動機尼、𢧚英沛移轉𠬠𠄧𨶛綏。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:28:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh ...and there's this bolt that keeps getting stuck, and..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 耒𣎏丐𥿀尼據被𠹳、耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:29:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...ah."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。啊。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:30:text
msgid "@cedric_smile ...don't worry! I am making decent progress!"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 。。。空哰𪥘󠄁！𤗆次當進展卒！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:31:text
msgid "@cedric We should be able to make it to the city by tonight."
msgstr "@cedric 衆些𣎏体𦤾城鋪𥪝𣋁𫢩。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:32:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed If you say so..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 裊英吶丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:34:text
msgid "@niko3 ...what...\\.\\. will happen once we get there?"
msgstr "@niko3 。。。衆些。。。\\.\\. 𠱊𪵯之欺𦤾坭丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:35:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm We need to bring Proto back first."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 衆些𠱊沛迻一號𠭤𧗱𠓀㐌。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:36:text
msgid "@cedric_talk And then we need to go find one more person."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 𢖖󠄁妬衆些沛尋𠬠𠊛𡛤。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:37:text
msgid "@cedric You may have already met her, actually..."
msgstr "@cedric 𣎏体㛪㐌﨤姑𧘇耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:38:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_talk Do you remember her from the last time you were in this world?"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 㛪𣎏𢖵吝𠓀伴於世界尼空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:39:text
msgid "@niko I..."
msgstr "@niko 㛪。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:41:text
msgid "@niko3 ...what does she...\\> look like?"
msgstr "@niko3 。。。姉𧘇。。。\\> 矓如勢鬧丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:42:text
msgid "@cedric2 This is going to sound strange, but..."
msgstr "@cedric2 𦖑窒𠸋曉、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:43:text
msgid "@cedric_talk She is a fox."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 姉𧘇𪜀𤞺。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:46:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...Rue?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。𠱋哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:47:text
msgid "@cedric_talk You've met?"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 㛪㐌﨤？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:48:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I... think so..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪。。。擬丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:50:text grounds/EV188:1:58:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed The memories are still really blurry, though..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 扔㛪。。。空𢖵𤑟𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:54:text
msgid "@niko2 ...oh..."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。溩。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:55:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I.... DO remember talking to a fox at one point..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪。。。𣎏𢖵㐌吶𡀯喟𠬠注𤞺。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:56:text
msgid "@cedric_talk You've met Rue?"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 㛪㐌﨤𠱋哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:59:text grounds/EV188:1:70:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh I see..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 𫥨丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:62:text
msgid "@niko2 Oh, um..."
msgstr "@niko2 啊、𫫡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:64:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I... don't think I know what you're talking about."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪。。。空別英當指埃。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:65:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Worth a shot."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 吻𢧚𠳨。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:66:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm Rue can be... elusive."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 𠱋𣎏体可。。。隱逸。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:67:text
msgid "@cedric_talk Even if she IS the least hidden one of us..."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 朱怞孤𧘇𪜀𠊛出現𡗉一𥪝数𪨠英。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:69:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed My memories are still really blurry, though..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 扔記憶𧵑㛪吻𥊚𩆪過。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:76:text
msgid "@niko_upset ....sigh."
msgstr "@niko_upset 。。。。係。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:77:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 It's just... hard... y'know?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 吻。。。𠸋𡗋。。。英別空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:78:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Proto told me to think of this world like a dream."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 一號𠸒㛪只懃䁛世界尼如𠬠𥋏𥊚。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:79:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 But then I get so caught up with..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 扔耒㛪被捲𠓨。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:80:text
msgid "@niko_distressed And I just...\\.\\.kinda... \\> forget..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed 吧㛪據。。。\\.\\.悁。。。 \\> 𠫾。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:81:text
msgid ""
"@niko_distressed2 I forget that everything here is supposed to be...\\."
"\\.not real..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 㛪悁哴𤗆次於蒂當𫥨只𪜀。。。\\.\\.假造。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:82:text
msgid "@niko_distressed ...and then... I remember."
msgstr "@niko_distressed 。。。吧耒。。。㛪𢖵𫥨。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:83:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...and then I just get really sad..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。吧耒㛪𧡊𢢇身𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:84:text
msgid "@niko_upset2 ...I know this is for me to go home, but..."
msgstr "@niko_upset2 。。。㛪別哴悉𪥘󠄁𪜀抵𢴇㛪𠭤𧗱茹、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:85:text
msgid "@niko_upset Knowing that none of it mattered in the first place..."
msgstr "@niko_upset 欺別哴拯𣎏之聯關𬆄自班頭。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:87:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...am I just\\.\\. trapped here for no reason...?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。丕𪜀㛪被\\.\\. 縸𠹳於蒂無故哰。。。？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:89:text
#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:23:text
msgid "@cedric2 ..."
msgstr "@cedric2 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:91:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Proto also told me to not ask anyone in the world about "
"this..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 一號拱𠯅㛪空得𠳨不其埃𧗱條尼。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:92:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 Saying how \"they don't understand\"..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 爲「𣱆空曉」。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:94:text
msgid "@niko_distressed But... what about him?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed 扔。。。英𧘇時哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:95:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 How did HE know....?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 在哰英𧘇別？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:96:text RED
#: SKY/landing/cedric:1:69:text
msgid "@cedric ..."
msgstr "@cedric 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:97:text
msgid "@niko3 ...How do YOU know?"
msgstr "@niko3 在哰正英拱別？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:98:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Aren't you guys ALL supposed to be code?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 當𫥨悉𪥘󠄁𤗆𠊛只𪜀仍𣳔碼催渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:99:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm ...well..."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 。。。時。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:100:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'm not sure what to even believe anymore..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪拯別沛信埃𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:102:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh ..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:103:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh I wish Rue was here..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 約之𠱋於低。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:104:text
msgid "@cedric3 She's SO much better at explaining this sort of thing."
msgstr "@cedric3 姉𧘇解適𡀯尼卒欣英𡗉。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:105:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh I'm doing a terrible job of it!"
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 渚英拱當𠸠󠄁𡗋低！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:106:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh2 I bet Proto was even less tactful, wasn't he..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 昃𪜀一號哙解適𢜗欣𪥘󠄁英𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:107:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh I'm afraid I must risk sounding callous, but..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 昃𪜀英𠱊沛唏不懃𠬠𡭧、扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:108:text
msgid ""
"@cedric2 ...please, you need not concern yourself with how \"real\" "
"everything is, for now."
msgstr "@cedric2 。。。暫時、吀㛪揨過關心療𤗆次𣎏「實」咍空。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:109:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_talk The plan is already in motion, we cannot allow for distractions."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 計劃㐌扒頭、衆些空体被嗃𢥉。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:110:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm Father is putting everything into this one last run of the world."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 仛㐌打挶𤗆次𠓨𠬠吝𧼋𡳳窮𧵑世界尼。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:111:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh The last chance for him to fix everything."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 機會𡳳共抵翁𢯢𢵻𤗆次。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:112:text
msgid "@niko2 Your father... is involved in the World Machine?"
msgstr "@niko2 仛英。。。𣎏參加𠓨鈷𣛠全世哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:113:text
msgid "@cedric3 You... \\.\\.could say that."
msgstr "@cedric3 㛪。。。\\.\\.𣎏体吶丕。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:114:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh The acceleration of square particle anomalies was not accounted "
"for at all, though."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 雖然度加速𧵑各分子𣃱㐌㑲外預斷。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:116:text
msgid ""
"@cedric The patch was only built to accomodate the normal rate they appear, "
"but..."
msgstr "@cedric 版𦀪只𣎏体活動蹺速度出現通常𧵑衆、扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:117:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh2 ...they're accumulating at frightening speeds, now."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 。。。𣇞衆當攔外尋檢詧。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:118:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Proto even lost his body..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 𪥘󠄁一號拱㐌𠅒殼耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:119:text
msgid "@cedric2 Thankfully, he gave you the disk just in time."
msgstr "@cedric2 𢆪𪜀舅𧘇迻㛪隖𥐨及時。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:120:text
msgid "@niko3 So... what happened to him anyway?"
msgstr "@niko3 丕時。。。英𧘇被哰丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:122:text
msgid "@niko3 What happens  to...\\.\\. ANYONE who gets caught in the squares?"
msgstr "@niko3 仍𠊛被𠹳𥪝各塊𣃱。。。\\.\\.𣱆𠱊被哰丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:123:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I only know it's bad..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪只別𪜀伮窒醜。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:124:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm Well, you know how the simulation works, right?"
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 時、㛪別程模倣活動勢鬧、董空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:126:text
msgid "@niko_upset2 How everything...\\.\\.is code....?"
msgstr "@niko_upset2 𪜀𤗆次調。。。\\.\\.𪜀碼哰。。。？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:128:text
msgid "@cedric Specifically, everything is generated from pre-existing code."
msgstr "@cedric 吶董欣、𤗆次得造𫥨自碼源𣎏𠻿。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:129:text
msgid "@cedric The squares can cause damage to that code..."
msgstr "@cedric 仍塊𣃱𣎏体𪵯墟損仍段碼妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:131:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh ...most of the time, irreversible damage."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 。。。多份𪜀空体𢯢𢵻。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:132:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh Father has lost some friends in previous iterations of the "
"simulation."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 仛㐌𠅒𠬠𠄧𠊛伴𥪝各吝𧼋𠓀𧵑程模倣。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:133:text
msgid ""
"@cedric3 It took him forever to develop the current, much more stable "
"version."
msgstr "@cedric3 翁㐌懃窒𡗉時間抵發展番版穩定欣窒𡗉現在。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:134:text
msgid ""
"@niko4 ...you're making it sound like...\\.\\. your dad built the simulation "
"himself..."
msgstr "@niko4 。。。𦖑偅如矯。。。\\.\\. 仛英自𢬣侈𥩯程模倣丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:135:text
msgid "@niko3 ...wait, DID he?"
msgstr "@niko3 。。。寬、翁𣎏𪵯丕實空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:136:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Yeah..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 𣎏。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:137:text
msgid "@niko4 But... how?"
msgstr "@niko4 扔。。。憑格鬧？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:138:text
msgid "@niko_what If everyone in this world is code..."
msgstr "@niko_what 裊𤗆𠊛調𪜀碼。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:139:text
msgid "@niko2 ...how can he build...\\.\\.\\@niko_what himself...?"
msgstr "@niko2 。。。時𪵯哰翁𧘇𣎏体𥩯。。。\\.\\.\\@niko_what 正𨉟。。。？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:140:text
msgid ""
"@cedric2 That's...\\.\\.um...\\>\\n\\@cedric_sigh not really what happened."
msgstr ""
"@cedric2 寔𫥨時。。。\\.\\.妬。。。\\>\\n\\@cedric_sigh 空沛仍之實事㐌演𫥨。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:141:text
msgid "@niko3 So... what happened?"
msgstr "@niko3 丕。。。翁𧘇𪵯之？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:142:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh2 ...like I said, you shouldn't concern yourself with..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 。。。如英㐌吶、㛪空𢧚過關心𧗱。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:144:text
msgid "@cedric4 ...with"
msgstr "@cedric4 。。。𧗱"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:145:text
msgid "@niko_distressed ....."
msgstr "@niko_distressed 。。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:146:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh ...alright, alright...."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 。。。鬧、鬧。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:148:text
msgid "@cedric3 Did Prototype....\\.\\. ever tell you about the old world?"
msgstr "@cedric3 一號㐌。。。。\\.\\.𠸥朱㛪𧗱世界𫇰𣗓？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:150:text
msgid ""
"@niko3 He... DID say something about being built to greet the messiah of the "
"old world."
msgstr "@niko3 英𧘇。。。𣎏吶之妬𧗱役英𧘇得設計抵迍𠎬救世𧵑世界𫇰。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:151:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed I was um...\\.\\. too caught up with the other stuff at the "
"time to think about it..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪𫫡。。。\\.\\.過絆喟仍次恪欺妬𢧚空抵心𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:152:text
msgid "@cedric2 Ah, you know OF it at least, then."
msgstr "@cedric2 啊、丕𠃣一𪜀㛪𣎏別𧗱伮。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:153:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Alright... here we go."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 嗚雞。。。鬧些扒頭。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:155:text
msgid "@cedric My father... myself... the other two..."
msgstr "@cedric 仛英。。。英。。。𠄩𠊛其。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:156:text
msgid "@cedric3 None of us are part of the simulation itself."
msgstr "@cedric3 衆英寔𫥨空屬𧗱程模倣。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:157:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh Our home world....\\>the \"real\" world... \\.\\.was actually "
"destroyed a long time ago."
msgstr ""
"@cedric_sigh 世界𫇰𧵑衆英。。。。\\>世界「寔」。。。 \\.\\.㐌被破毀窒嘍𧗱𠓀。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:158:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout
#: point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map Events:2:26:text green/Ruins
#: In/Maize/maize:2:43:text In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:5:text
#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:3:2:text entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:3:173:text
msgid "@niko_shock ..."
msgstr "@niko_shock 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:159:text
msgid ""
"@cedric In the years leading up to the calamity, scientists from all over "
"the world tried to stop it, but the outlook was bleak."
msgstr ""
"@cedric 𥪝仍𢆥𠓀欺慘禍侈𫥨、各茹科學自七世界㐌固𠡚拫捍銀冊、扔空𣎏𠇍希望。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:160:text
msgid ""
"@cedric A vague prophecy about a messiah from another world became "
"everyone's last bastion of hope."
msgstr "@cedric 𠬠𠳒先知矑𥊚𧗱𠬠𠎬救世自𠬠世界恪𠭤城𣈢希望𡳳共𧵑𤗆𠊛。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:161:text
msgid ""
"@cedric3 Prophetbot....\\.\\.er, Prototype... \\.\\.was built to predict the "
"future, about the specifics of this messiah."
msgstr ""
"@cedric3 𠊛𣛠先知。。。\\.\\.唹、一號。。。\\.\\.得設計抵預斷將來、𧗱指節𧵑𠎬"
"救世尼。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:162:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh2 But as his predictions turned out, the messiah would not have "
"been able to arrive to our world in time."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 扔董如𠳒預斷𧵑英𧘇、𠎬救世𠱊空体𦤾坭及時。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:163:text
msgid ""
"@cedric4 In fact, the messiah would not even have been born before our world "
"ended."
msgstr "@cedric4 甚至、𠎬救世哙空𫥨𠁀𠓀欺世界尼臨終。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:164:text green/Ruins
#: In/Maize/maize:2:22:text RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/kip:1:394:text Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory
#: Entrance/courtyard/EV010:1:2:text Maps/FINALE/Encounter/map
#: events:4:107:text events:4:111:text events:4:132:text events:4:137:text
#: events:4:139:text SKY/landing/City gate/EV013:1:2:text SKY/Elevator
#: deck/npc_plight:2:77:text deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:27:text
#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:2:6:text deck/Office/locked room/map
#: events:4:9:text ground/backalley/EV064:1:2:text deck/Office/observation
#: deck/Map Events:1:87:text Events:1:156:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout
#: point/Mineshaft entrance/server room/backroom/proto:3:55:text
#: room/backroom/proto:3:323:text Maps/Tower/Elevator/EV005:1:90:text
#: Maps/FINALE/Encounter PENG/map events:4:106:text events:4:110:text
#: events:4:131:text events:4:136:text events:4:138:text
#: GROUND/backalley/EV064:1:2:text green/Gate/map events:1:7:text
msgid "@niko3 ..."
msgstr "@niko3 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:165:text
msgid ""
"@cedric Disheartened, most people abandoned their research and resolved to "
"peacefully live out their final years."
msgstr "@cedric 失望、𡗉𠊛㐌辭𠬃研究吧決定𤯩訥仍𢆥𣎃哙徠𥪝安平。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:166:text
msgid "@cedric3 But... some people did the opposite."
msgstr "@cedric3 仍。。。𠬠数𠊛㐌𪵯逆徠。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:167:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh Even though saving the world was impossible, they didn't want "
"our existence to be in vain."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 雖空体解救世界、𣱆空㦖局𠁀𧵑衆些𠭤𢧚無義。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:168:text
msgid "@cedric2 And that's...\\.\\. where my father came in."
msgstr "@cedric2 吧妬𪜀欺。。。\\.\\.仛英𨀈𠓨。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:169:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_talk With the last of his resources...\\>\\nhe built his most "
"ambitious project yet."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 喟仍財源𡳳共𧵑翁。。。\\>\\n翁㐌起工預按貪望一𧵑𨉟。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:170:text
msgid "@cedric ...\"The World Machine\"."
msgstr "@cedric 「𣛠全世」。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:171:text
msgid ""
"@cedric2 A large, detailed facsimile of the old world, generated from a pool "
"of memories collected from everyone he knew."
msgstr "@cedric2 𠬠版抄𡘯、枝節𧵑世界𫇰、得𤄮攤自仍記憶𧵑悉𪥘󠄁仍𠊛翁慣。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:172:text
msgid ""
"@cedric4 ...after a heavy amount of modification and an added narrative, my "
"father was able to convert the entire structure into code."
msgstr "@cedric4 𢖖󠄁𠬠量空𡮈整𢯢吧𠬠骨傳補𣻢、仛㐌成工轉𢷮𤗆次城碼𣛠併。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:174:text
msgid "@niko3 ...how did that code.... escape the old world?"
msgstr "@niko3 。。。段碼妬。。。脫𠺌世界𫇰勢鬧丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:175:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm I have no idea."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 英空別。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:176:text
msgid ""
"@cedric What I do know is, there is no equipment back home that was powerful "
"enough to run the code independently."
msgstr "@cedric 英𣎏別哴、空𣎏𣛠莯鬧於妬覩猛抵𧼋段碼妬𠬠格獨立。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:177:text
msgid ""
"@cedric So, asides from the standard hardware, it also needed to borrow the "
"mental processing abilities of a living person."
msgstr "@cedric 由妬、外份勁標準、伮哙沛摱可𣌝處理心神𧵑𠬠𠊛𤯩。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:178:text
msgid ""
"@cedric Father used himself for that, during the initial testing phases."
msgstr "@cedric 仛㐌用正𨉟抵𪵯丕、𥪝仍階段試驗班頭。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:179:text
msgid ""
"@cedric2 Like I said, it took many iterations for him to make the experience "
"stable enough."
msgstr "@cedric2 如英㐌吶、翁㐌損窒𡗉吝𢯢抵𣥱驗覩穩定。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:180:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh2 ...but as you can see, even that's breaking down."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 。。。扔㛪𣎏体𧡊、𬆄𪥘󠄁伮拱當𢴍𨀎𢭰。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:181:text
msgid "@niko2 Ah..."
msgstr "@niko2 啊。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:182:text
msgid ""
"@cedric Father caught on to the issue in the last minute, but did not have "
"enough time to fix it."
msgstr "@cedric 仛㐌扒得問題𠓨𤼵𡳳、扔空𣎏覩時間抵𢯢伮。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:183:text
msgid ""
"@cedric4 After the world ended...\\.\\. the code kinda just ended up..."
"\\>\\n\\@cedric3 floating in the void, indefinitely."
msgstr ""
"@cedric4 𢖖󠄁欺盡世𦤾、\\.\\.段碼只。。。\\>\\n\\@cedric3 籚𠻴𥪝曠空無盡。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:184:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh ...waiting for a willing operator to install it onto their own "
"hardware."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 。。。䟻待𠬠埃妬𠻿𠳹掑伮𠓨份勁𧵑𨉟。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:185:text
msgid "@niko3 ...\\p?"
msgstr "@niko3 。。。\\p？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:186:text
msgid "@cedric Yeah."
msgstr "@cedric 董丕。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:187:text
msgid ""
"@cedric The operator... \\.\\.\\p.... \\.\\.would then generate the universe "
"using the code, becoming god in the process."
msgstr ""
"@cedric 𠊛運行妬。。。\\.\\.\\p。。。。\\.\\.𠱊造𫥨宇宙憑段碼、同時𠭤城𠎬全"
"能。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:188:text
msgid "@niko So... \\p was the living person you needed to borrow?"
msgstr "@niko 丕。。。\\p𪜀𠊛𤯩𦓡英懃摱抄？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:189:text
msgid "@cedric3 ....No?"
msgstr "@cedric3 。。。。空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:190:text
msgid "@cedric That.... would be you."
msgstr "@cedric 𠊛妬。。。𪜀㛪。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:191:text
msgid "@niko3 But why me?"
msgstr "@niko3 扔抄徠𪜀㛪？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:192:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:56:text
msgid "@niko ...."
msgstr "@niko 。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:194:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed (I... should've asked that question a long time ago, "
"shouldn't I...)"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed （當𫥨。。。𨉟沛𠳨句尼自嘍耒㵋董。。。）"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:195:text
msgid "@cedric3 I do not know."
msgstr "@cedric3 英空別。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:1:197:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm ...we...\\.\\. really need to get going."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 。。。衆些。。。\\.\\.實事沛𠫾催。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:2:1:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's a plane!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣛠𢒎箕！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:2:4:text
msgid "@cedric2 ...flying machine!"
msgstr "@cedric2 ...飛行機箕！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:2:5:text
msgid "@niko Right."
msgstr "@niko 沛耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV188:3:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a tent."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠丐寮。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV208:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Just a wrench."
msgstr "@niko 指𪜀𠬠丐鉗。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV213:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a crowbar."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠錆㖼𩿙。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/EV214:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Looks like a piece from this plane."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠𤗖𥒮自隻𣛠𢒎。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Photo center/photo spot:1:4:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
