#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Photo center/photo:1:13:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko Good thinking, \\p.  It's a good idea to have a backup."
msgstr "@niko 合理妬、\\p。𣎏𣘊預防㫻㫻𪜀意咍。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Photo center/photo:1:21:text center/photo:1:30:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko It's another photo of me..."
msgstr "@niko 徠𪜀𠬠𬌓影𧵑𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Photo center/photo:1:22:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: GROUND/ground
