#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Photo center/photo:1:84:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko It's a photo of me..."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𬌓影𧵑𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Photo center/photo:1:85:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed And the camera is out of film now..."
