#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/Map Events:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A jar of some sort of grain."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𤮗籺之妬。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/Map Events:2:1:text
msgid "@niko This looks like flour!"
msgstr "@niko 矓𣎏𨤔偅𥹸麪！"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/Map Events:3:1:text
msgid "@niko Oats."
msgstr "@niko 五穀。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/Map Events:4:1:text
msgid "@niko Heads of wheat."
msgstr "@niko 仍葻穭。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:2:text
msgid "A cat does sound nice..."
msgstr "𣎏貓𦖑拱𢝙𫥨㗶。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:3:text
msgid "Maybe I'll ask my cousin to find one in the city for me."
msgstr "𣎏𨤰𨉟𠱊吀英𣱆尋𠬠哙𨑗城鋪。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:4:text
msgid "He just moved there."
msgstr "影𣃣轉𦤾妬於。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:7:text
msgid "This is it... the last of our grain surpluses..."
msgstr "低𪜀。。。仍之哙𨔊徠𠸋穭衆𪝬。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:8:text
msgid "And now we're dealing with a vermin problem..."
msgstr "吧𣇞衆𪝬徠𣎏𤝞𦤾破𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:9:text
msgid "@niko Maybe you can get cats?"
msgstr "@niko 𣎏体伴𢧚檢𠬠哙貓"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:10:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Not that I'm a cat, I mean..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 空𣎏義𪜀𨉟𪜀貓兜唲。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:12:text
msgid "@alula What's a cat?"
msgstr "@alula 貓𪜀哙之丕？"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:13:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Something that I'm not!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𠬠哙𦓡空沛𨉟！"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:14:text
msgid "@alula ?"
msgstr "@alula ？"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:15:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak It's an animal that walks on four legs and hunts mice and rats!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 伮𪜀𠬠𡥵物𣎏𦊚蹎吧𤜬各類𤝞！"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:16:text
msgid "@alula_gasp Like a fox?"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 偅如𤞺嘑？"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:17:text Maps/Green/Ruins
#: In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:22:text
msgid "@niko I... guess?"
msgstr "@niko 昃。。。勢？"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 5 - storage/EV003:1:18:text
msgid "@alula_speak Foxes are cool!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𤞺實湡！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/npc_silver walk
#: in:1:2:text entrance/mineshaft/npc_silver:1:2:text
msgid "@silver2 [I'll be waiting here if you need me.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【姉𠱊䟻於低裊㛪懃。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/npc_silver walk
#: in:1:6:text entrance/mineshaft/npc_silver:1:6:text
msgid "@silver2 [Maybe you should inspect the journal a bit closer....]"
msgstr "@silver2 【𣎏𨤰㛪𢧚䀡察捲日記技𪨈欣。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/npc_silver walk
#: in:1:9:text entrance/mineshaft/npc_silver:1:9:text
msgid "@silver [Do be careful in here.]"
msgstr "@silver 【謹慎𥪝尼唲。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:1:2:text
msgid "@silver [Ready to leave?]"
msgstr "@silver 【𠻿𠳹𠫾耒渚？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:1:3:text Maps/Green/Gate/map events:1:71:text
msgid "@niko Mhm."
msgstr "@niko 𫫡。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:1:18:text
msgid "@niko It'd be rude to leave now..."
msgstr "@niko 𠱊唏失禮裊𨉟𠬃𠫾𣊾𣇞。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:9:text
msgid "@niko_speak Safety violation!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 犯規！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:12:text
msgid "@niko The yellow light is gone now."
msgstr "@niko 暎𤏬鐄變𠅒耒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:13:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Must've imagined it..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 昃𪜀由𨉟想像𫥨。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:45:text
msgid "@silver2 [Are you okay?]"
msgstr "@silver2 【㛪穩渚？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:46:text
msgid "@silver [You were starting to black out...]"
msgstr "@silver 【矓如㛪𢯛𤴥𠫾丕。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:47:text
msgid "@niko_speak I...\\>\\n\\@niko I saw something?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 㛪。。。\\>\\n\\@niko 𧡊之妬？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:48:text
msgid "@silver2 [?]"
msgstr "@silver2 【？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:49:text
msgid "@niko It was like a really short dream, just now."
msgstr "@niko 如矯𠬠𥋏𥊚窒𠦯。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:50:text
msgid "@silver2 [Oh?]"
msgstr "@silver2 【溩？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:51:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I saw something like...\\>\\n\\@niko A robot, with a yellow "
"eye..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 㛪𧡊。。。\\>\\n\\@niko 𠬠𠊛𣛠、𣎏眜𦭷鐄。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:52:text
msgid "@silver [...that's...\\>\\n\\@silver_eyeclosed ...strange.]"
msgstr "@silver 【。。。𨓐。。。\\>\\n\\@silver_eyeclosed ...𠰚。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:53:text
msgid "@silver2 [Are you sure you're okay?]"
msgstr "@silver2 【㛪昃𪜀㛪穩渚？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:54:text
msgid "@niko ...yeah."
msgstr "@niko 。。。𫫡。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:56:text
msgid "@silver [...You know, now that you have mentioned it.]"
msgstr "@silver 【。。。㛪𠯅𪵯姉𢖵𫥨。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:57:text
msgid ""
"@silver [There is a robot who always insisted on going back to the abandoned "
"mines.]"
msgstr "@silver 【𣎏𠬠𠊛𣛠據𠻞𠻞𠭤徠𡌢𡎡𠬃荒。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:58:text
msgid "@silver2 [...despite how long the mines have been in disrepair.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【。。。怞伮㐌被墟害自窒嘍耒。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:59:text
msgid "@silver_eyeclosed [I hope he's okay.]"
msgstr "@silver_eyeclosed 【懞舅𧘇安全。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:60:text
msgid "@niko He doesn't look broken or anything..."
msgstr "@niko 矓影𧘇空𣎏之𪜀墟閧𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:61:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...but I didn't really... SEE him see him, yknow?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。扔㛪拱空實事𧡊影意、姉曉渚？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:62:text
msgid "@niko Like I said, it was kinda like a dream..."
msgstr "@niko 如㛪吶妬、偅如𠬠𥋏𥊚。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:63:text
msgid "@niko_speak And he was up close!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 吧影𧘇拱於窒近𡛤！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:64:text
msgid "@silver2 [Sounds like some kind of visual glitch.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【 𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠纇圖畫。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:65:text
msgid ""
"@silver_eyeclosed [Or... hallucination.] \\>\\n\\@silver [Whatever it is "
"that living beings have.]"
msgstr ""
"@silver_eyeclosed 【或𪜀。。。幻覺。】 \\>\\n\\@silver 【丐𦓡仍𠊛𤯩被。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:66:text
msgid "@niko Hm..."
msgstr "@niko 嘘。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:67:text
msgid "@niko_speak Does the robot you know of have a yellow eye?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠊛𣛠姉慣𣎏眜𦭷鐄空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:68:text
msgid "@niko I don't think I've seen any other robots like that..."
msgstr "@niko 㛪𣗓曾﨤𠊛𣛠鬧如丕包𣇞。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:69:text
msgid "@silver_eyeclosed [I would not know.]"
msgstr "@silver_eyeclosed 【姉空別。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:70:text
msgid ""
"@silver [I never met him myself. Only heard of him from a friend of mine.]"
msgstr "@silver 【姉𣗓曾盡眜﨤英些。只㵋𦖑過自𠬠𠊛慣𧵑姉。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:71:text
msgid "@niko Your friend, huh..."
msgstr "@niko 𠊛慣。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:73:text
msgid "@niko Hold on... something in my pocket is..."
msgstr "@niko 䟻㐌。。。𣎏之妬𥪝襊襖㛪。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:90:text
msgid "@niko2 What's..."
msgstr "@niko2 丐尼𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:91:text
msgid "@niko_speak That wasn't glowing before!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠓀低伮兜𣎏發𤏬！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:92:text
msgid "@niko3 What IS this...?"
msgstr "@niko3 伮𪜀之丕？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:93:text
msgid "@silver2 [That... was going to be my question.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【姉。。。拱當定𠳨句妬。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:94:text
msgid "@silver [Where did you... get that book?]"
msgstr "@silver 【㛪。。。檢卷冊妬於兜丕？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:95:text
msgid "@niko2 Oh, uh..."
msgstr "@niko2 啊、唹。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:96:text
msgid "@niko It was with me when I woke up back at the house."
msgstr "@niko 伮於邊㛪欺㛪𥅞𧻭𥪝𡾵茹。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:97:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I didn't really question it at the time..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣅶妬㛪空疑㘈之𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:98:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 I flipped through a couple of pages, but I don't understand a word!"
msgstr "@niko2 㛪𣎏搮過𠄧張、扔㛪拯曉𡨸鬧歇！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:99:text
msgid "@niko Is that just something messiahs are supposed to wake up with?"
msgstr "@niko 各𠎬救世常醒𧻭喟仍次如丕嘑？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:100:text
msgid "@silver_eyeclosed [No... I have never heard of anything like that.]"
msgstr "@silver_eyeclosed 【空。。。姉𣗓曾𦖑𦤾不據次之如丕。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:101:text
msgid "@silver [But I... \\.\\.know who wrote the book.]"
msgstr "@silver 【扔姉。。。\\.\\.別埃㐌曰捲冊妬。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:102:text
msgid "@niko2 Oh?"
msgstr "@niko2 溩？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:103:text
msgid "@silver [However...]"
msgstr "@silver 【扔。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:104:text
msgid "@silver2 [I've only seen his books with a black clover on the cover.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【姉㵋只𧡊𦹯𠀧蘿黰𨑗柀冊𧵑翁𧘇。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:105:text
msgid ""
"@silver_lookup [If he went through the trouble of putting yellow phosphor in "
"it...]"
msgstr "@silver_lookup 【裊翁㐌實事𠬃工添光素鐄𠓨。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:106:text
msgid "@silver [And the fact that you woke up with it in the first place...]"
msgstr "@silver 【吧本身役㛪醒𧻭共喟伮。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:107:text
msgid "@silver2 [...Really has me intrigued.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【。。。𪵯姉實事可徂摸。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:108:text
msgid "@niko Yellow... phosphor?"
msgstr "@niko 光素。。。鐄唹？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:109:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Oh yeah! That's the rare phosphor that people think the sun is "
"made of, right?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 啊！伮𪜀類光素險𦓡𤗆𠊛擬哴𣎏𥪝𩈘𡗶、董空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:111:text
msgid "@niko_what2 ...wait a minute, how do I know this?"
msgstr "@niko_what2 。。。寬㐌、哰㛪徠別𡀯尼𠰚？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:112:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I don't think anyone's told me about it..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪空擬㐌𣎏埃𠸒朱㛪。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:113:text
msgid "@silver [Ah... \\.\\.I can show you if you'd like.]"
msgstr "@silver 【啊。。。\\.\\.姉𣎏体朱㛪䀡裊㛪㦖。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:119:text
msgid "@silver [My friend gave me this a long time ago.]"
msgstr "@silver 【𠬠𠊛伴𧵑姉朱姉丐尼窒嘍𧗱𠓀。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:120:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes Pretty!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 惵實！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:126:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! Looks like there's a clover in the necklace too!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！拱𠬠𣘃𣎏𠬠𣘃𦹯𠀧蘿𥪝𤥑𦙶𡛤！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:127:text
msgid "@niko6 ...like the book!"
msgstr "@niko6 。。。如卷冊丕！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:128:text
msgid "@silver2 [Well... it IS the same person.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【時。。。𪜀共𠬠𠊛𦓡。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:129:text
msgid "@niko Oooh."
msgstr "@niko 溩－－－。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:130:text
msgid ""
"@silver_eyeclosed [That's... why I think this journal would be important.]"
msgstr "@silver_eyeclosed 【爲勢𢧚。。。姉㵋擬哴捲日記妬𠱊關重。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:131:text
msgid "@silver2 [You said it JUST started glowing?]"
msgstr "@silver2 【㛪吶伮只𣃣㵋發𤏬哰？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:132:text
msgid "@niko_speak Yeah?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫫡？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:133:text
msgid "@silver2 [That was right after your vision, then...]"
msgstr "@silver2 【丕𪜀𬆄𢖖󠄁欺㛪𧡊幻影。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:135:text
msgid "@silver2 [...This HAS to mean something.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【沛𣎏理由𪥘󠄁。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:136:text
msgid "@silver2 [Maybe you should at least try to read it again...]"
msgstr "@silver2 【𣎏𨤰㛪𢧚試讀伮吝𡛤。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:157:text
msgid "@niko I can see a faint yellow glow in the distance..."
msgstr "@niko 㛪𧡊𠬠暎𤏬鐄溂於滕賒。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:158:text
msgid "@silver [Don't stand so close to the edge.]"
msgstr "@silver 【揨𨅸近壁𥒥丕唲。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:159:text
msgid "@niko Oh! Sorry!"
msgstr "@niko 溩！㛪吀纇！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:179:text
msgid "@silver [Looks like even the entrance tunnel collapsed off.]"
msgstr "@silver 【𣎏𨤔𦤾𪥘󠄁𫔤𡌢拱㐌砬。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:180:text
msgid "@silver [Without a vehicle, we can't proceed.]"
msgstr "@silver 【空𣎏方便時衆些空体接續。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:181:text
msgid "@niko Can't we walk?"
msgstr "@niko 空体𠫾步哰？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:182:text
msgid "@silver [I can.]"
msgstr "@silver 【姉時𣎏体。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:183:text
msgid "@silver [But for you it's a safety violation. I won't allow it.]"
msgstr "@silver 【仍對喟㛪時𪜀圍犯規則安全。姉𠱊空朱法。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:184:text
msgid "@niko What's ahead, anyway?"
msgstr "@niko 𦓡𥪝妬𣎏之丕？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:185:text
msgid ""
"@silver [It's a huge network of underground mines, the source of this "
"world's metal and non-phosphor fuel.]"
msgstr "@silver 【𠬠𦁸䋥𡌢𡎡㢅𡘯、𪜀源金類吧燃料常𧵑世界尼。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:186:text
msgid "@silver [This is what propelled the world into the industrial age.]"
msgstr "@silver 【仍次尼㐌迻伮𦤾紀元工業。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:187:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed So now it's lost forever?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 丕𪜀伮㐌𠅒永遠耒抄？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:188:text
msgid "@silver [It's been for a while now.]"
msgstr "@silver 【伮㐌如丕得𠬠時間耒。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:189:text
msgid ""
"@silver [When the sun went out, the mines were the first to be abandoned "
"amidst the initial panic.]"
msgstr "@silver 【欺𩈘𡗶𨄠、𡌢𡎡𪜀次頭先被𠬃徠𥪝事混亂班頭。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:190:text
msgid "@silver [Even the robots have been all cleared out and repurposed.]"
msgstr "@silver 【𦤾𪥘󠄁𠊛𣛠拱㐌被迻𪥘󠄁𫥨外吧再使用。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:191:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed That makes sense..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 拱合理。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:192:text
msgid "@silver [Though there was one that always insisted on going back...]"
msgstr "@silver 【雖𣎏𠬠𠊛㫻𠾕𢮿徠。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:193:text Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:108:text
#: Events:1:110:text Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map
#: Events:2:8:text entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map Events:3:67:text
#: Events:3:77:text Events:3:95:text Events:3:104:text Events:3:113:text
#: Events:4:160:text 1/fish house/npc_fishbowl:1:8:text sky/Elevator
#: deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:56:text point/Cabin/Map
#: Events:3:21:text point/Cabin/npc_silver:1:87:text
#: point/Cabin/npc_silver:4:32:text point/Cabin/npc_silver:4:40:text
#: entrance/server room/backroom/proto:2:35:text
#: In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:13:text In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:13:text
msgid "@niko Oh?"
msgstr "@niko 溩？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:2:194:text
msgid "@silver [I hope he's okay...]"
msgstr "@silver 【懞影𧘇吻安全。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:18:text Events:3:36:text
msgid "@niko2 ...what... just happened?"
msgstr "@niko2 。。。丐之。。。𣃣侈𫥨丕？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:19:text
msgid "@silver [I'm not sure... I wasn't looking.]"
msgstr "@silver 【空昃𡗋。。。姉空抵意。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:20:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed To be honest... neither was I..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 寔𫥨時。。。㛪拱空。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:21:text Events:3:49:text
msgid "@niko I was just taking a closer look at the journal..."
msgstr "@niko 㛪只𣃣㵋䀡察卷日記技𪨈欣。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:22:text Events:3:50:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 And then I found this page that looks like a drawing of this room..."
msgstr "@niko2 耒㛪𧡊𠬠張𣎏𨤔𪜀版𦘧𧵑防尼。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:23:text
msgid ""
"@niko3 When I looked back up, this minecart just... showed up out of thin "
"air!"
msgstr "@niko3 欺㛪𥆾𬨠、丐車𡎡尼突然。。。出現自虛空！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:24:text Events:3:52:text
msgid "@niko_what2 Should I be... worried?"
msgstr "@niko_what2 㛪𣎏𢧚。。。𢥈𢠯空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:25:text Events:3:53:text
msgid "@silver [Hmm...]"
msgstr "@silver 【嘘。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:38:text
msgid "@niko_speak Did you see that, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 舅𧡊空、\\p？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:39:text
msgid "@niko3 This minecart just... showed up out of thin air!"
msgstr "@niko3 丐車𡎡突然。。。出現自虛空！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:40:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed I wasn't looking, though... I was just looking at the "
"journal like you told me..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 扔𣅶妬𨉟徠空𥆾。。。𨉟當䀡卷日記如舅𠸒。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:41:text
msgid "@niko ...\\>\\nMaybe we should go find that robot lady."
msgstr "@niko 。。。\\>\\n𣎏𨤰衆些𢧚𠫾尋姉𠊛𣛠妬。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:51:text
msgid ""
"@niko When I looked back up, this minecart just... showed up out of thin air!"
msgstr "@niko 欺㛪𥈴𬨠、丐車𡎡尼突然。。。出現自虛空！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:57:text
msgid "@silver2 [This looks like a standard issue minecart, though.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠隻車𡎡標準。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:58:text
msgid ""
"@silver [...which means it likely detected the motion in this room and sent "
"itself over.]"
msgstr "@silver 【可能𤞺𪜀伮認得轉動𥪝房尼吧自𠫾過。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:59:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Ah... that does make sense."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 啊。。。拱合理。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:60:text
msgid "@silver_eyeclosed [I'm just surprised it still works.]"
msgstr "@silver_eyeclosed 【姉空擬𪜀伮哙活動。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:62:text
msgid "@silver [Guess that means we'll have a working vehicle now.]"
msgstr "@silver 【丕昃𪜀𣇞衆些𣎏𠬠方便用得。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:63:text
msgid ""
"@silver_eyeclosed [Not sure why you would want to visit the deeper mines, "
"but...]"
msgstr "@silver_eyeclosed 【空昃在哰㛪徠㦖𠓨邊𥪝𡌢𡎡、扔。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:64:text
msgid "@silver [If you wanted to, we now have that option.]"
msgstr "@silver 【裊㛪㦖、時𣇞衆些𣎏体。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:66:text
msgid "@niko_speak Is the minecart even going to fit both of us?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𦓡車𡎡𣎏𣃣𠄩衆些空丕？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:67:text
msgid "@silver_lookup [No.]"
msgstr "@silver_lookup 【空。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:68:text
msgid "@niko But I wanted you to come with us..."
msgstr "@niko 扔㛪㦖姉𠫾蹺共。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:69:text
msgid ""
"@niko I know I've got \\p, but... \\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed ...honestly? This "
"place gives me the creeps!"
msgstr ""
"@niko 㛪別㛪𣎏\\p、仍𦓡。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 。。。實事時𡊲尼矓超𢜝㫻"
"𧘇！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:70:text
msgid "@silver2 [Oh. I can still come with.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【溩。姉吻蹺得。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:71:text
msgid "@silver [I would just have to follow along on the rails.]"
msgstr "@silver 【姉只懃𠫾蹺𨑗塘倈𪜀得。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/mineshaft/Map
#: Events:3:72:text
msgid "@niko_what But doesn't it look a little... \\. \\.precarious...?"
msgstr "@niko_what 扔矓伮𣎏唏。。。 \\. \\.佂儝空？"

