#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:1:1:text
msgid "@shepherd So....."
msgstr "@shepherd 丕𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:1:2:text
msgid "@shepherd We meet again."
msgstr "@shepherd 衆些徠﨤僥。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:1:3:text
#: ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:32:text Maps/POSTGAME green/Research
#: Station/Power room/robot standing:1:7:text sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room5 -
#: roomba/EV003:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Hello..."
msgstr "@niko 嘲。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:1:4:text
msgid "@niko_speak Wait!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 寬㐌！"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:1:5:text
msgid "@niko Aren't you from...the village?"
msgstr "@niko 拯沛影𦤾自。。。𡾵廊哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:1:6:text
msgid ""
"@shepherd Yes, but the rams are ever-present.\\>\\nIn the village, in the "
"city..."
msgstr "@shepherd 董丕、扔羝時𣎏𩈘於𤗆坭。.\\>\\n於𥪝廊、𥪝城鋪。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:1:8:text
msgid "@shepherd even...\\.\\. in your heart."
msgstr "@shepherd 吧𪥘󠄁。。。\\.\\.𥪝尋伴𡛤。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:1:9:text
#: sky/Apartments/Hall1/Room2 - peng/EV001:1:6:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...okay."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。嗚雞。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:2:1:text
msgid "@shepherd If rams wore shoes..."
msgstr "@shepherd 裊羝𠫾鞢。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:2:2:text
msgid "@shepherd They would have... \\.flip-flops."
msgstr "@shepherd 衆𠱊𠫾。。。\\.搝𢭫。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:2:3:text
msgid "@niko ...I don't get it."
msgstr "@niko 。。。㛪空曉。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:3:1:text
msgid "@shepherd I used to host the official RAM club wiki site..."
msgstr "@shepherd 𪝬曾主持張威朞正式𧵑俱樂部羝。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:3:2:text
msgid ""
"@shepherd ...but we kept having page faults due to rams getting out of the "
"server room."
msgstr "@shepherd 。。。扔衆𪝬全﨤纇張爲羝𧼋𫥨𠺌房𣛠主。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:3:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...what?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:3:4:text
msgid "@shepherd 404 ram not found."
msgstr "@shepherd 404空尋𧡊羝。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:3:5:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I have no idea what any of that meant."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪空曉影𣃣吶𧗱丐之㫻。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:4:1:text
msgid "@shepherd Hmp. I guess that's it for my jokes."
msgstr "@shepherd 嘘。𢴉𦤾丕𪜀覩耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:4:2:text
msgid ""
"@shepherd It cannot be helped...\\n\\>\\@shepherd ...they were quite b-a-a-a-"
"a-a-a-a-d."
msgstr "@shepherd 𠹾催。。。\\n\\>\\@shepherd 𣎏体吶衆可𪜀幣－－－－。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/shephard:4:5:text
msgid "@niko_83c I got that one!"
msgstr "@niko_83c 丐妬時㛪曉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/demon ram:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed It's...good to see you too..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 拱。。。𢝙欺﨤英。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/read only:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_speak This ram doesn't react to me at all..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 哙羝尼空反應之歇。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/read only:1:2:text
msgid "@niko Instead, the word \"baa\" is written on its wool."
msgstr "@niko 𠊝𠓨妬、𨑗𦒮𧵑伮𣎏曰𡨸「𠾦」。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/read only:1:3:text
msgid "@shepherd That one isn't a RAM."
msgstr "@shepherd 哙妬空沛RAM（羝）兜。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/read only:1:4:text
msgid "@shepherd That one is...\\. \\. Read-Only."
msgstr "@shepherd 哙妬𪜀。。。\\. \\. 只讀。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/read only:1:5:text
msgid "@niko I...see..."
msgstr "@niko 𫥨。。。勢。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/EV015:1:1:text
msgid "@niko An electric kettle."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠丐𩐛超速。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/EV015:1:2:text
msgid "@niko Looks like it's boiling water."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔伮當焞渃。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/EV015:1:3:text
msgid "@shepherd Oh, right, it's almost lunch time."
msgstr "@shepherd 啊、董、𢯛𦤾𣇞𩚵曥耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/EV015:1:4:text
msgid "@shepherd Would you like to stay for a nice cup of..."
msgstr "@shepherd 伴𣎏㦖於徠𪵯𠬠𤭏。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/EV015:1:5:text
msgid "@shepherd \\....\\.RAMen?"
msgstr "@shepherd \\.。。。\\.騾麵空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/EV015:1:7:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'll... pass..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。催。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/EV015:2:1:text
msgid "@shepherd Come to think of it, we're probably out of ramen."
msgstr "@shepherd 𠯅㵋𢖵、形如些拱歇拉麵耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/static:1:4:text
#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/Map events:1:11:text
#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Cabin/EV006:3:4:text Maps/Green/Research
#: Station/Power room/EV004:2:11:text
msgid "@niko_what Ow!"
msgstr "@niko_what 喂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/static:1:5:text
msgid ""
"@shepherd Careful, if you touch a SRAM... \\.\\.\\nYou're in for a shock!"
msgstr "@shepherd 謹慎、裊伴𪮻沛𠬠錆SRAM。。。\\.\\.\\n伴𠱊被𪮞蒂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/static:1:6:text
msgid "@shepherd A STATIC shock!"
msgstr "@shepherd 𪮞靜電！"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/SECRET RAM CLUB/static:1:10:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Don't \"baa\" at me..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 揨𠾦𠓨𩈘㛪𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/stew:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Looks like moss..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𪜀𦼔。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/stew:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak I guess people eat those!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 昃𪜀抵咹！"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:2:text
msgid "If nothing else, I'm sure everyone would like to see the sun again!"
msgstr "怞哰、𪝬擬𤗆𠊛調㦖𧡊𩈘𡗶𠬠吝𡛤！"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:4:text
#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:44:text
msgid "@alula_speak Yeah!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 董耒！"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:10:text
#: npc:1:25:text
msgid ""
"It's slowly being chipped away already.\\nBut it's still trying to stay "
"alive, I think."
msgstr "伮當被𤷱𠫾𢴍𢴍耒。\\n扔𪝬擬伮吻當固𠡚𤯩𨔊。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:11:text
#: npc:1:26:text
msgid "Doesn't matter... one day the world will finally give up this fight."
msgstr "拯關重𡛤。。。𠱊𣎏𣈜世界𡳳共拱自𠬃局戰尼催。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:12:text
#: npc:1:27:text
msgid "I just hope I'm not alive to see it."
msgstr "𪝬只懞欺妬𪝬㐌謝世。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:13:text
msgid "@alula But the savior is here!"
msgstr "@alula 扔𠎬救世㐌𦤾耒！"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:14:text
#: npc:1:29:text
msgid "That won't fix the root of the problem."
msgstr "空解決得㭲𣑶問題兜。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:15:text
#: npc:1:30:text
msgid "@niko Just like the other lady said..."
msgstr "@niko 如姉其吶。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:16:text
msgid "@alula_oh Other... lady?"
msgstr "@alula_oh 姉。。。其？"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:17:text
msgid "@niko_speak Yeah! She's this robot and she seemed kinda sad..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫫡！姉𧘇𪜀𠊛𣛠吧𣎏𨤔𢞂。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:18:text
msgid "@alula_pout Ah..."
msgstr "@alula_pout 啊。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:19:text
msgid ""
"Oh! But don't lose heart!\\nWithout the sun, the world will die much faster."
msgstr "溩！仍揨𠬃局！\\n空𣎏𩈘𡗶、世界𠱊衰亡𨘱欣𡗉。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:20:text
#: npc:1:32:text
msgid ""
"At the very least...\\nI'm sure everyone would like to see the sun again."
msgstr "𠃣一。。。\\n𪝬擬𤗆𠊛調㦖𧡊𩈘𡗶𠬠吝𡛤。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:21:text
msgid "Right, little one?"
msgstr "沛空傉？"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:22:text
msgid "@alula_speak Yup!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 董丕！"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:28:text
msgid "@niko_speak I'm bringing back the sun, though..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔𨉟當𫼳𩈘𡗶𠭤徠𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Village/House 6 - death is coming/pessimistic npc:1:31:text
msgid ""
"But don't lose heart!\\nWithout the sun, the world will die much faster."
msgstr "仍揨𠬃局！\\n空𣎏𩈘𡗶、世界𠱊衰亡𨘱欣𡗉。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/stairwell/EV001:1:1:text Maps/Red ground/ground
#: entrance/stairwell/EV001:1:1:text
