"If I'm gonna die soon, I wanna die knowing I put out at least ONE original "
"idea out there!"
msgstr "裊𪝬𢯛𣩂、至𠃣𪝬拱㦖產出得𠬠意想獨到鬧妬渚！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:2:1:text
msgid ""
"Despite all this...\\.\\. I still really wish I could've met the Author..."
