msgstr "@george2_stress 𠬠𥪝仍作品㤇適𧵑𪝬、吀感恩窒𡗉。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_george2:2:4:text
msgid ""
"@george2_sigh ...it's the Author's book detailing the creation of Prophetbot."
