msgstr "@george2_sigh 𠅒空別包𡗉𪜀工飭號訂。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_george2:3:3:text
msgid "@george3_sad ...the Author's book on the creation of Prophetbot..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 。。。捲冊𧵑作者創世𧗱過程𡏦𥩯𣛠先知。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_george2:3:4:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sigh ...you know...\\.\\. the first robot you met in our world..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 。。。伴別蒂。。。\\.\\. 𠊛𣛠頭先伴﨤𥪝世界𧵑衆𪝬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_george2:3:6:text
msgid "@george3_worry ...oh...\\.\\.The book was quite detailed, too...."
msgstr "@george3_worry 。。。溩。。。\\.\\.伮拱可姉節𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_george2:3:7:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sigh It...\\.\\. would've been useful to your friend, I think..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 伮。。。\\.\\.㐌𣎏体窒有用對𢭲𠊛伴𧵑伴、𪝬擬丕。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_george2:3:8:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...yeah."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。𫫡。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_george2:4:3:text
msgid "@george4 The Author's book on the creation of Prophetbot!"
msgstr "@george4 卷冊𧵑作者創世𧗱過程造𫥨𣛠先知！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_george2:4:4:text
