"\\>\\n\\@george6_shrug 昃𥗜𪜀𠬠𥪝仍傑作𧵑慃、誓㫻。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_george2:6:6:text
