msgstr "@george1 觫。。。\\.\\.\\@george1_hm 𠱊空朱伴𫥨外其兜！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:242:text
msgid "@george1_hm The messiah will not walk into danger on my watch!"
msgstr "@george1_hm 𠎬救世𠱊空𠫾𠓨共危險澄鬧𪝬哙於低！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:243:text
#: entrance/Lobby/kip:1:267:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft
#: entrance/server room/backroom/proto:3:297:text
msgid "@niko3 But..."
msgstr "@niko3 扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:247:text
msgid "@george2_stress Are you KIDDING ME??"
msgstr "@george2_stress 㛪𢴉姉嘑？？？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:248:text
msgid "@george2_grr Kid, there is NO way we're letting you out there."
msgstr "@george2_grr 傉啊、空𠁀鬧𪨠尼抵㛪𫥨外兜。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:249:text
msgid "@niko3 But I really have to..."
msgstr "@niko3 扔㛪寔事懃𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:253:text
msgid "@george3_worry Um...\\.\\.um..."
msgstr "@george3_worry 𫫡。。。\\.\\.𫫡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:254:text
msgid "@george3_cry You...\\.\\. shouldn't go out there....!"
msgstr "@george3_cry 㛪。。。\\.\\.空𢧚𫥨外！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:255:text
msgid "@niko_distressed But..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed 扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:256:text
msgid "@george3_worry Oh.... \\.\\.help me out here, Kip...."
msgstr "@george3_worry 喂。。。\\.\\.喼㗒、𢴇𨉟喟。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:260:text
msgid "@george4 ...messiah, please."
msgstr "@george4 。。。𠎬救世、吀𠊛。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:261:text
msgid "@george4_golly We don't...want you to go out there."
msgstr "@george4_golly 𪨠姉實事。。。空㦖㛪𫥨外其兜。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:262:text
msgid "@george4_golly Not when everything is... \\.\\.well..."
msgstr "@george4_golly 欺𤗆次當。。。\\.\\.𫫡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:266:text
msgid "@george5_hmm Sweetie, you know we can't let you just walk into danger!"
msgstr "@george5_hmm 畺啊、畺別𪨠姉空体抵畺𠫾𠓨塳危險如丕得𦓡!"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:271:text
msgid ""
"@george6 Bruh...\\>\\n\\@george6_point You know we ain't gonna let you walk "
"into the fire like that!"
msgstr ""
"@george6 係。。。\\>\\n\\@george6_point 翁𡥙別𪨠尼𠱊空抵翁𡥙𨀈𠓨𡌽𪸔兜𦓡！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:272:text
msgid "@george6_shrug Fire... squares..."
msgstr "@george6_shrug 𡌽。。。𣃱。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:286:text
msgid "@kip_sigh George is right..."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 觫吶董蒂。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:287:text
msgid ""
"@kip_pout The squares seem to be targeting a lot of the weaker constructs in "
"the city."
msgstr "@kip_pout 仍塊𣃱𣎏𨤔當𠲏𦤾仍構築𪽳一𥪝城鋪。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:288:text
msgid ""
"@kip_sigh Only the library has enough structural integrity to withstand "
"collapse..."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 只𣎏書院𪜀覩凭抵𢶢徠事𨀎𢭰催。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:289:text
msgid "@kip_sad It's... best if you stayed here until things stabilize."
msgstr "@kip_sad 卒一。。。㛪𢧚於徠朱𦤾欺𤗆次𢠯𬺗。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:290:text
msgid "@kip_sigh ...however long that takes."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 。。。怞𣎏損包𡗉時間𠫾庄𡛤。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:293:text
msgid "@niko2 But....\\.\\.\\@niko4 but..."
msgstr "@niko2 扔。。。\\.\\.\\@niko4 扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:294:text
msgid "@niko2 What about...\\.\\. my mission?"
msgstr "@niko2 哙。。。\\.\\.任務𧵑㛪時哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:295:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Don't you guys want me to bring the sun back, at least?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𤗆𠊛空㦖㛪𫼳𩈘𡗶𠭤徠哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:297:text
msgid "@george1 Even if you do restore the sun, the squares will persist..."
msgstr "@george1 怞㛪𣎏𠀲𩈘𡗶𠭤徠、仍塊𣃱吻哙妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:301:text
msgid ""
"@george2_sigh The sun won't do us any good if the squares are just gonna "
"mess everything up."
msgstr "@george2_sigh 裊仍塊𣃱破毀𤗆次時𣎏𪥘󠄁𤾓𩈘𡗶拱無用催。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:305:text
msgid "@george3_worry Oh...\\.\\.but even if you do bring the sun back..."
msgstr "@george3_worry 唹。。。\\.\\.扔怞㛪𣎏𫼳𩈘𡗶𠭤徠。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:306:text
msgid "@george3_sigh ...the squares... they'll still be here..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 。。。仍塊𣃱。。。𠱊吻於低。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:310:text
msgid ""
"@george4_golly Even if you do bring back the sun, that's not gonna fix the "
"squares..."
msgstr "@george4_golly 裊㛪𣎏𫼳𩈘𡗶𠭤徠、伮拱空𢵻得仍形𣃱兜。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:314:text
msgid ""
"@george5 Even if you do restore the sun, I'm not sure that'll fix the "
"squares..."
msgstr "@george5 𠸥𪥘󠄁㛪𣎏恢復徠𩈘𡗶、姉拱空昃伮𣎏体𢵻得仍塊𣃱。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:318:text
msgid "@george6_shrug  ...sun ain't gonna make the squares go away, dude."
msgstr "@george6_shrug 。。。𩈘𡗶空解決得埬塊𣃱兜、翁𡥙啊。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:332:text
msgid "@kip_sigh Sadly..."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 當惜𪜀如丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:333:text
msgid "@kip_sad Not to mention... even getting there is going to be hard..."
msgstr "@kip_sad 哙𢵻𠸥。。。𦤾得妬拱𠸋𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:334:text
msgid ""
"@kip_pout If the world is like this... there's no telling what's going on in "
"the Tower!"
msgstr "@kip_pout 裊世界㐌如丕。。。空別邊𥪝座塔哙𣎏之𡛤！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:336:text
msgid ""
"@george1_hm And... if anything bad happened to the messiah, of all people..."
msgstr "@george1_hm 吧。。。𢙲𢆪𠎬救世𣎏命係之。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:337:text
msgid "@george1 ...George doesn't want to think about it."
msgstr "@george1 。。。觫空㦖擬𧗱伮兜。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:341:text
msgid ""
"@george2_stress And... if anything bad happened to the messiah, of all "
"people..."
msgstr "@george2_stress 吧。。。裊如𠎬救世﨤難。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:342:text
msgid "@george2_no ...NO!!! I won't allow it!!!"
msgstr "@george2_no 。。。空！！！姉𠱊空朱法伮侈𫥨！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:346:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sad And... if anything bad happened to the messiah, of all people..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 吧。。。𢙲𦓡𠎬救世﨤𡀯拯令。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:347:text
msgid "@george3_sigh I'm not sure if I'll be able forgive myself..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 姉𠱊空包𣇞赦恕本身。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:351:text
msgid ""
"@george4_golly And... if anything bad happened to the messiah, of all "
"people..."
msgstr "@george4_golly 𦓡裊如𠎬救世﨤危。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:352:text
msgid "@george4 I'm not sure what we'd do!"
msgstr "@george4 𪨠姉空別沛𪵯之𡛤！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:356:text
msgid ""
"@george5_hmm And... if anything bad happened to the messiah, of all people..."
msgstr "@george5_hmm 𢙲𦓡𠎬救世﨤危。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:357:text
msgid "@george5_sigh Oh... that would be so dreadful, dear..."
msgstr "@george5_sigh 喂。。。𠱊弊𡗋妬、畺啊。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:361:text
msgid "@george6 And... if the messiah got hurt, of all people..."
msgstr "@george6 𢙲𦓡𠎬救世﨤𡀯空𢆪。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:362:text
msgid ""
"@george6_shrug That's like...\\.\\.the exact opposite of radical, dude...."
msgstr "@george6_shrug 𠱊。。。\\.\\.空齊朱𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:375:text
msgid "@kip_sigh Sigh..."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 係。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:376:text
msgid "@kip_sad A friend of mine... said something about this forever ago..."
msgstr "@kip_sad 𠬠𠊛伴𧵑姉。。。㐌喟姉窒嘍𧗱𠓀。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:377:text
msgid "@kip_pout \"It's better for the world to die naturally.\""
msgstr "@kip_pout 「卒一𪜀𢧚抵世界𫥨𠫾𠬠格自然。」"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:378:text
msgid "@kip_sigh \"No living being should have to carry that burden.\""
msgstr "@kip_sigh 「空生物鬧𢧚挭重責妬𪥘󠄁・」"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:379:text
msgid ""
"@kip_sad At the time... I thought it was still her faulty code speaking..."
msgstr "@kip_sad 𣅶妬。。。姉吻想妬𪜀由份碼被纇𧵑姑𧘇當吶𡀯。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:380:text
msgid "@kip_sigh But now I... \\.\\.I'm starting to understand..."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 扔𣇞姉。。。\\.\\.姉㐌曉𫥨。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:383:text
msgid "@kip_pout Messiah... \\.\\.I'm sorry..."
msgstr "@kip_pout 𠎬救世。。。\\.\\.姉吀纇。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:384:text
msgid "@kip_sad I'm really, really sorry...."
msgstr "@kip_sad 姉窒、窒吀纇。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:385:text
msgid "@kip_sigh All this time, we've burdened you with our hope, our faith..."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 𠁸仍𣈜過、𪨠姉㐌撻𬨠㛪悉𪥘󠄁念信吧希望。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:386:text
msgid ""
"@kip_pout ...blissfully ignoring the fact that you are just a lost child."
msgstr "@kip_pout 。。。𦓡悁𠅒哴㛪吻只𪜀𠬠𠀲稚落。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:387:text
msgid "@niko3 Well..."
msgstr "@niko3 時。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:388:text
msgid "@kip_pout You're probably more scared than any of us, aren't you?"
msgstr "@kip_pout 𪳨𪜀㛪當𢜝𡗋沛空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:389:text
msgid ""
"@kip_pout We... have been dealing with tragedy for so long, it's become "
"background noise to us now."
msgstr "@kip_pout 𪨠姉。。。㐌𣥱過過𡗉悲劇𦤾餒伮𪜀𡀯常𣈜耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:390:text
msgid "@kip_sad But for you... \\.\\.it must be so terrifying..."
msgstr "@kip_sad 扔對喟㛪。。。\\.\\.𪳨𪜀伮驚恐𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:391:text
msgid "@kip_sad And now, you're stuck here with the rest of us..."
msgstr "@kip_sad 吧𣇞、㛪被縸𠹳於低喟𪨠姉。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:392:text
msgid "@kip_pout ...being held back by the very people you were told to save."
msgstr "@kip_pout 。。。被正仍𠊛當𫥨㛪沛救𡨺徠。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:393:text
msgid "@kip_sigh We must seem so ungrateful..."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 𪳨𪨠姉當無窮失禮喟㛪。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:395:text
msgid "@niko_distressed .....It's...\\>\\@niko_eyeclosed2 .....okay."
msgstr ""
"@niko_distressed 。。。。。空。。。\\>\\@niko_eyeclosed2 。。。。。哰兜。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:396:text
#: entrance/Lobby/kip:1:403:text entrance/Lobby/kip:1:474:text
msgid "@kip_pout ..."
msgstr "@kip_pout 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:397:text
#: entrance/Lobby/kip:1:428:text
msgid "@niko3 I..."
msgstr "@niko3 㛪。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:401:text
msgid ""
"@niko3 ...when I first came to this world... \\.\\.\\@niko4 a long time "
"ago...."
msgstr "@niko3 。。。欺㛪吝頭𦤾低。。。 \\.\\.\\@niko4 隔低窒嘍。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:402:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 ...back then, all I wanted was to go home."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 。。。欺妬、㛪只㦖𧗱茹催。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:407:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...\\p... do you remember?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。\\p。。。舅𢖵渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:408:text
msgid "@niko2 The very FIRST time..."
msgstr "@niko2 吝頭先。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:409:text
msgid "@niko5 I'm not sure how far back it was for you..."
msgstr "@niko5 𨉟空昃𪜀包嘍𧗱𠓀對喟舅。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:410:text
msgid ""
"@niko But... I remember towards the end...\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed I... "
"actually wasn't sure anymore."
msgstr ""
"@niko 扔。。。𨉟𢖵欺𢯛結束。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟。。。徠空昃𡗋。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:411:text
msgid "@niko_upset ...about going home."
msgstr "@niko_upset 。。。𧗱役𧗱茹。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:412:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Even knowing the world would be doomed eventually..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 朱怞𣎏別世界𠱊滅亡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:413:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 I... still wanted the people here to be happy..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 𨉟。。。吻㦖𤗆𠊛𤯩幸福。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:415:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed So...\\.\\. when you told me to return the sun, back then..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𢧚。。。\\.\\.欺舅𠸒𨉟㨋徠𩈘𡗶、欺妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:416:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I didn't even....\\.\\. question it..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟拱拯。。。。\\.\\.意見之。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:419:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed So...\\.\\. when you told me to return home, back then..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𢧚。。。\\.\\.欺舅𠸒𨉟𠭤𧗱茹、欺妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:420:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 I wasn't... \\.\\.sure..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 𨉟空。。。\\.\\.昃𥗜。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:421:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed But I trusted you more, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 扔𨉟㐌信舅欣、\\p。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:424:text
msgid "@niko4 ...but then I just... came back."
msgstr "@niko4 。。。扔耒𨉟徠。。。𢮿徠。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:425:text
msgid "@kip_pout You... what..."
msgstr "@kip_pout 㛪。。。之幾。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:429:text
msgid "@niko3 And I... went through that decision again, didn't I?"
msgstr "@niko3 吧𨉟。。。徠𨅸𠓀決定妬、董空𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:430:text
msgid "@niko_upset But...\\.\\. I came back again..."
msgstr "@niko_upset 扔耒。。。\\.\\.𨉟徠𢮿徠。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:431:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Even though you were able to do both... \\.\\.the effects "
"couldn't be permanent, could it?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 朱怞舅𢵬𪥘󠄁害攄𢵬。。。\\.\\.係果空沛𪜀永遠、董空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:436:text
msgid ""
"@niko_upset And then...\\.\\. I found out about the world being like this..."
msgstr "@niko_upset 吧耒。。。\\.\\.𨉟發現世界當𥪝狀態尼。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:440:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Prototype said to forget the things he told me... \\>\\nAnd "
"Cedric told me not to think about it too much, but..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed 一號𠸒𨉟唉悁𡚦仍之英𧘇吶朱𨉟。。。\\>\\n吧察嚦勸𨉟空𢧚擬過𡗉"
"𧗱伮、扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:441:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:443:text
msgid "@niko4 I'm sorry for getting upset at you... back at the mines..."
msgstr "@niko4 𨉟吀纇爲㐌浽𤎏喟舅。。。於重𡌢𡎡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:444:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed ...I thought... for you to know all that, yet continue doing "
"this..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。𨉟想哴。。。裊舅㐌別悉𪥘󠄁、𦓡吻𪵯如丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:445:text
msgid "@niko_upset2 It... just seemed cruel."
msgstr "@niko_upset2 時拯沛。。。過殘忍哰。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:446:text
msgid "@niko2 But then, I realized something..."
msgstr "@niko2 扔𢖖󠄁妬、𨉟認𫥨。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:449:text
msgid "@niko4 You... really wanted to save both the world and me..."
msgstr "@niko4 舅實事。。。㦖救𪥘󠄁世界吧𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:450:text
msgid "@niko_distressed But at the end, you can only choose one, right?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed 扔𡳳共時、舅只得𢵬𠬠、董空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:451:text
msgid "@niko_distressed_talk Is it... really hard for you too?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed_talk 伮𣎏。。。𠸋朱舅空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:452:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed It must be..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𪳨𪜀如丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:454:text
msgid ""
"@niko3 ...\\.\\.if the world isn't broken...\\.\\.will that choice still be "
"there?"
msgstr "@niko3 。。。\\.\\.裊世界空衰亡。。。\\.\\.料攄𢵬𣎏哙妬空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:455:text
msgid ""
"@niko4 ...do you...\\.\\. still need to choose between one or the other?"
msgstr "@niko4 。。。舅𣎏懃沛。。。\\.\\.𢵬𠬠𥪝𠄩空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:457:text
msgid "@niko_sad But... even if it is..."
msgstr "@niko_sad 扔。。。怞𣎏丕𡚦庄𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:459:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I... \\.\\.really want to save this world, \\p."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟。。。\\.\\.實事㦖救世界尼、\\p啊。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:460:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 Even if it's more dangerous this time around..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 怞𣎏危險欣吝𠓀。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:461:text
msgid ""
"@niko_distressed_talk Even if... so many of the nice people we met were.... "
"\\>\\@niko_distressed_meow were..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_distressed_talk 怞。。。仍哙𠊛親善衆𨉟㐌﨤𩈘。。。 "
"\\>\\@niko_distressed_meow 㐌被。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:462:text
msgid "@niko_sad ......"
msgstr "@niko_sad 。。。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:463:text
msgid ""
"@niko_distressed_talk \\p.... \\>\\n\\@niko_less_sad I'm not.... \\."
"\\.afraid, anymore...."
msgstr ""
"@niko_distressed_talk \\p。。。。 \\>\\n\\@niko_less_sad 𨉟。。。。 \\.\\.空"
"哙𢜝𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:467:text
msgid "@niko_cry *sniff*"
msgstr "@niko_cry ＊泏哳＊"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:468:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed That's why...\\>\\n\\@niko3 I think you guys should let me "
"go..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 勢𢧚。。。\\>\\n\\@niko3 㛪擬𤗆𠊛𢧚抵㛪𠫾。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:469:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 I... promise I'll be okay..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 㛪。。。許𪜀㛪𠱊穩。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:470:text
msgid "@niko_distressed ...please?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed 。。。𠫾𦓡？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:476:text
msgid "@george1 ..."
msgstr "@george1 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:477:text
msgid ""
"@george1_hm George has heard your conversation with \\p and is deeply moved!"
msgstr "@george1_hm 觫㐌𦖑得局會話𧵑伴喟\\p吧㐌感動漊色！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:478:text
msgid "@george1_smug That's why... George has full faith in you!"
msgstr "@george1_smug 由妬。。。觫𧵑念信絕對𠓨伴！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:482:text
msgid "@george2_grr ...well, I'm convinced."
msgstr "@george2_grr 。。。𫫡、姉𧡊覩說伏耒妬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:483:text
msgid ""
"@george2 After all that...\\.\\. it'd be SUPER rude for me to stop you, "
"wouldn't it?"
msgstr "@george2 𢖖󠄁悉𪥘󠄁仍𡀯妬。。。\\.\\.𠱊窒空沛裊姉𡨺㛪徠、董空鬧？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:487:text
msgid "@george3_sigh ...if you must..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 。。。裊㛪寔事㦖。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:488:text
msgid "@george3_sad It... wouldn't be right for me to keep you..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 𠱊。。。空沛裊姉𡨺㛪徠。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:492:text
msgid "@george4_golly Ohhhh..... \\>\\n\\@george4_omg That was BEAUTIFUL!!!"
msgstr "@george4_golly 溩－－－－。。。 \\>\\n\\@george4_omg 實感動！！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:493:text
msgid ""
"@george4_omg Kip!!! Did you hear that! The messiah was trying to encourage "
"\\p!"
msgstr "@george4_omg 喼！！！姉𣎏𦖑𧡊空！𠎬救世當動員\\p！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:494:text
msgid "@kip_heh I'm right here..."
msgstr "@kip_heh 𪝬𬆄低𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:495:text
msgid "@george4_omg I KNOW RIGHT!!! IT HAPPENED RIGHT IN FRONT OF OUR EYES!!!"
msgstr "@george4_omg 時蒂！！！伮㐌侈𫥨𬆄𠓀眜衆些！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:496:text
#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/trowel:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak ..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:497:text
msgid "@george4_oops ...sorry, got carried away..."
msgstr "@george4_oops 。。。𧘇𣩂、姉徠𡗋𠵘𡛤耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:498:text
msgid "@george4 ...but yes, I think it's only right that we let you go!"
msgstr "@george4 。。。扔沛耒、空体鬧空朱㛪𠫾得！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:502:text
msgid "@george5_sad Aww... sweetie..."
msgstr "@george5_sad 𫉩。。。畺啊。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:503:text
msgid ""
"@george5_sigh You are so brave...\\.\\. even braver than most grown-ups..."
msgstr "@george5_sigh 㛪窒勇敢妬。。。\\.\\.𡗉欺欣𪥘󠄁𠊛𡘯𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:504:text
msgid "@george5_hmm It... wouldn't be right for us to keep you, would it?"
msgstr "@george5_hmm 必然𪨠姉空体𡨺㛪徠、𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:505:text
msgid "@george5_aww Besides, how can I say no to those puppy-dog eyes!"
msgstr "@george5_aww 喟徠、𪵯哰姉𣎏体吶空𠓀對眜妬得！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:509:text
msgid "@george6_point Yo, kid...."
msgstr "@george6_point 尼、傉。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:510:text
msgid "@george6_smile You're real strong, you know that?"
msgstr "@george6_smile 傉窒猛瑪妬、別空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:511:text
#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:3:292:text
msgid "@niko4 I..."
msgstr "@niko4 㛪。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:512:text
msgid "@george6_fingerguns Go knock 'em dead, tiger!"
msgstr "@george6_fingerguns 朱衆別勢鬧𪜀禮會𠫾、小虎！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:525:text
msgid "@kip_heh Well, if George is fine with it..."
msgstr "@kip_heh 裊觫㐌同意。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:526:text
msgid "@kip_sigh I... \\.\\.guess we should let you go now, messiah..."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 𣎏𨤰。。。\\.\\.𪨠姉拱𢧚抵㛪𠫾催、𠎬救世。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:527:text
msgid "@kip_pout But... promise us you'll be careful, okay?"
msgstr "@kip_pout 扔。。。許喟姉哴㛪𠱊穩、唲？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/kip:1:529:text
msgid "@niko2 You guys be safe too..."
msgstr "@niko2 𤗆𠊛拱保重唲。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV169:1:2:text
msgid "[THIS IS THE LIBRARY / TEMPORARY SHELTER.]"
msgstr "【低𪜀書院兼坭住隱暫時。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_fishbowl:1:2:text
msgid "Sigh...."
msgstr "係。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_fishbowl:1:5:text
msgid ""
"I had to leave my aquarium behind when they were sounding the sirens "
"earlier..."
msgstr "𪝬㐌沛𠬃水宮𧵑𪝬於徠欺𣱆發螺警報𣅶𠓀。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/npc_fishbowl:1:6:text
msgid "I wish I had time to rescue my fish..."
msgstr "約之𪝬𣎏覩時間抵解救僤𩵜𧵑𪝬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV171:1:2:text
msgid "I won't lose hope."
msgstr "𪝬𠱊空辭𠬃。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV171:1:5:text
#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:5:text green/Dock/pessimistic npc:1:1:text
msgid "Sigh..."
msgstr "係。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV171:1:7:text
msgid "It's comforting to see the faith you have in \\p, messiah..."
msgstr "實安心欺𧡊念信伴𣎏朱\\p、𠎬救世。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV171:1:8:text
msgid "That's why... I won't lose hope either."
msgstr "由妬。。。𪝬拱𠱊空辭𠬃。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:2:text
msgid "Y'know, now that everyone's coming to me for help..."
msgstr "舅別空、𣇞低欺𤗆𠊛𦤾𠾒𪝬𢴇役。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:3:text
msgid "...it really makes me appreciate you more, messiah!"
msgstr "。。。𪝬𪨈𧡊別恩舅妬、𠎬救世啊！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:4:text
msgid "Thank you for all you've done for us."
msgstr "感恩爲悉𪥘󠄁仍之伴㐌𪵯朱衆𪝬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:7:text
msgid "Looks like my life's work is finally being put to good use!"
msgstr "𣎏𨤔工飭𪥘󠄁𠁀𪝬𡳳窮拱𢴇益耒！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:8:text
msgid "As long as we conserve the water we have on hand ..."
msgstr "澄鬧衆些節儉量渃當𣎏。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:9:text
msgid ""
"...my water pills should be able to keep everyone here from going thirsty "
"for weeks!"
msgstr "。。。仍圓渃𧵑𪝬𣎏体𢴇𤗆𠊛𢶢𩂀渴亙旬！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:1:text
msgid "@niko This stand smells... sugary."
msgstr "@niko 柜尼苿可。。。𤮾。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:2:text
msgid "Candy skewers, fresh off the grill!"
msgstr "釺𥼱㵋𤓢低！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:3:text
msgid "...Not very nutritious, I'm afraid."
msgstr "。。。𪝬㥋𪜀空營養朱𡗋。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:4:text
msgid "But at least they'll keep the evacuees from gettin' hungry!"
msgstr "扔𠃣一伮𠱊𢴇仍𠊛避難空被𩟡！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:1:text
msgid ""
"The city gate was destroyed a while back, I can't go into the Glen anymore..."
msgstr "𨶛城鋪㐌被破毀隔低𠃣嘍、𣇞𪝬空体𢮿徠區潭浰得𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:2:text
msgid ""
"I'm not sure where I'll be able to get my supply of fish, at this rate..."
msgstr "據柁尼𪝬空昃𠱊檢𩵜於兜𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:1:text
msgid "I still have plenty of these soup dumplings left!"
msgstr "扔𪝬吻哙窒𡗉仍隻湯包尼！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/!vendor:1:2:text
msgid "Looks like it should feed everyone here for at least another day."
msgstr "𣎏𨤔伮𠱊覩朱𤗆𠊛咹添𠃣一𠬠𣈜𡛤。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/npc_camera:1:1:text
msgid "Looks like I'll have to cancel my appointment..."
msgstr "𣎏𨤔𪝬沛毀歷﨤𩈘耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/npc_camera:1:2:text
msgid "This stinks!"
msgstr "驚恐！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV177:1:2:text
msgid "[EVERYTHING IS TERRIBLE]"
msgstr "【𤗆次調弊害】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV178:1:1:text
msgid "ZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ"
msgstr "𠺟𠺟𠺟𠺟𠺟𠺟𠺟𠺟𠺟𠺟𠺟"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV179:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed She's asleep..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 姉𧘇當𥄬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV179:1:5:text
msgid "*yawn*"
msgstr "＊哈＊"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV179:1:6:text
msgid "The lab complex got totaled, didn't it...."
msgstr "座茹研究㐌𨀎𢭰完全耒𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV179:1:7:text
#: GROUND/To Tower/plight:1:85:text
msgid "@niko3 Yeah..."
msgstr "@niko3 𫫡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV179:1:8:text
msgid "All those hours I put into my work, and now..."
msgstr "包饒時𣇞𪝬𢭰𠓨研究、吧𣇞。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV179:1:9:text
msgid "now...."
msgstr "𣇞時。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV179:1:11:text
#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/EV011:1:9:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed She fell asleep..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 姉𧘇徠𥄬接耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV180:1:1:text
msgid "Monitoring... monitoring..."
msgstr "當觀察。。。當觀察。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV180:1:2:text
msgid "Looks like our scouting unit #A27 is still doing okay..."
msgstr "𣎏𨤔單位偵探A27吻當暫穩。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV181:1:1:text
msgid "Robots are the only ones that we can send out there, now..."
msgstr "𣇞衆𪝬只𣎏体寄𠊛𣛠𫥨外妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV181:1:2:text
msgid ""
"Thankfully, we still have a couple of units that aren't too badly damaged..."
msgstr "𢆪𪜀衆𪝬吻哙𠬠数單位空被墟害過𥘀𡋂。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV181:2:1:text
msgid ""
"This little guy ran into some squares earlier and managed to escape mostly "
"intact."
msgstr "翁𡥙尼𣃣動沛塊𣃱𦓡吻脫𫥨近如原捖。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV181:2:2:text
msgid "These newer models are pretty tough!"
msgstr "仍母𠊛𣛠㵋尼勁哈㗶！"

#: Maps/Blue/Old factory/EV298:1:1:text
msgid ""
"$There's something weird about the robots who get sent to work near the gas "
"fields."
msgstr "$𣎏之妬可奇𨓐𧗱仍𠊛𣛠衆些寄𫥨𪵯役𨒺各塳開拓氣𪵤。"

#: Maps/Blue/Old factory/EV298:1:2:text
msgid "$They appear to accumulate rust at a much slower rate than the others."
msgstr "$衆𣎏𨤔積聚釲𡏥踸欣𡗉𬧺喟份哙徠。"

#: Maps/Blue/Old factory/EV298:1:4:text
msgid "$The few who work directly with gas harvesting look practically new!"
msgstr "$数𠃣直接參加收拾氣𪵤甚至哙矓如㵋！"

#: Maps/Blue/Old factory/EV298:1:5:text
msgid "$Is that a result of the atmosphere? Or am I just seeing things?"
msgstr "$𣎏沛𪜀由匏氣圈空？唉由𪝬當想像𫥨？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:1:12:text
msgid "@niko_speak Whoa!\\>\\n\\@niko \\p? Did you see that fox just now?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫽿！\\>\\n\\@niko \\p？舅𧡊注𤞺𣃣𣅅渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:1:13:text
msgid "@niko_speak It just ran behind the tree..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 伮𣃣𧼋𫥨𢖖󠄁㭲𣘃。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:2:1:text events:2:10:text
msgid "@rue_dark ..."
msgstr "@rue_dark 。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:2:4:text
msgid "@rue_dark I'm sorry if you are looking for me."
msgstr "@rue_dark 𪝬窒吀纇裊伴當尋𪝬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:2:6:text
msgid "@rue_dark But I cannot talk to you."
msgstr "@rue_dark 仍𪝬空体吶𡀯喟伴。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:2:7:text
msgid "@rue_dark Not now..."
msgstr "@rue_dark 空沛𣊾𣇞。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:2:11:text
msgid "@rue_dark But... can you promise me something?"
msgstr "@rue_dark 扔。。。舅𣎏体許喟𪝬𠬠條得渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:2:12:text Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map
#: Events:1:60:text In/Alula/alula:5:5:text sky/Apartments/Hall1/Room3 - bot
#: friend/EV003:1:8:text In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:13:text
msgid "@niko Huh?"
msgstr "@niko 嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:2:14:text
msgid "@rue_dark If... you can find a way to return..."
msgstr "@rue_dark 裊。。。舅𣎏体尋格𠭤𧗱。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:2:15:text
msgid "@rue_dark ...please do."
msgstr "@rue_dark 。。。吀唉𪵯丕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:2:16:text
msgid "@niko Er...\\.\\.\\@niko2 What... do you mean by that?"
msgstr "@niko 𫫡。。。\\.\\.\\@niko2 意舅。。。𪜀哰𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/map events:2:18:text
msgid "@niko ...\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed No reply..."
msgstr "@niko 。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 空𣎏回答。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:8:text
msgid "@rue We will meet again."
msgstr "@rue 衆些𠱊﨤徠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:9:text
#: ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:22:text ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:38:text
#: ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:61:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout
#: point/Cabin/npc_silver:1:61:text Maps/Tower/Elevator/EV005:1:42:text
msgid "@niko ...?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:12:text
msgid "@rue_talk So you found a way back after all."
msgstr "@rue_talk 如丕舅㐌尋得塘𠭤徠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:13:text
msgid "@niko_speak Eh? \\>\\n\\@niko But I've never been here before..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠯋？ \\>\\n\\@niko 仍𨉟貯𦤾低包𣇞𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:14:text
msgid "@rue That means..."
msgstr "@rue 義𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:15:text
#: ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:19:text ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:39:text
msgid "@rue ..."
msgstr "@rue 。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:16:text
msgid "@rue_talk Have you... met the others?"
msgstr "@rue_talk 伴㐌。。。﨤仍𠊛哙徠貯？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:17:text
msgid "@niko2 ...others? \\>\\n\\@niko2 You're the only fox I've seen..."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。哙徠？ \\>\\n\\@niko2 舅𪜀注𤞺頭先𨉟﨤妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:18:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Wait! There's that one plush in Calamus and Alula's house, right "
"\\p?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 寬！哙𡥵獸葻重茹哥羅𡃙吧阿瞜羅𡛤、沛空\\p？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:20:text
msgid "@rue_sad Sigh."
msgstr "@rue_sad 係。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:21:text
msgid "@rue It's not time."
msgstr "@rue 𣗓𦤾𣅶。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:23:text
msgid "@rue ...we will meet again."
msgstr "@rue 。。。衆些𠱊﨤徠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:31:text
msgid "@rue_smile Hello, Niko."
msgstr "@rue_smile 吀嘲、尼孤。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:35:text
msgid "@rue ...oh?"
msgstr "@rue 。。。溩？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:36:text
msgid "@rue_talk You're back again..."
msgstr "@rue_talk 伴㐌𢮿徠耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:37:text
msgid "@rue But...\\.\\.\\@rue_sad I said it was not time..."
msgstr "@rue 扔。。。\\.\\.\\@rue_sad 𪝬㐌吶𣊾𣇞𣗓沛𣅶。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:40:text
msgid "@rue Are you here to keep me company, then?"
msgstr "@rue 伴𦤾低抵匏伴共𪝬庄？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:41:text
msgid "@rue_smile Guess I can't refuse that."
msgstr "@rue_smile 勢時𪝬空辭挃得耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:42:text
msgid "@rue ...I am Rue."
msgstr "@rue 。。。𪝬𪜀𠱋。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:43:text
msgid ""
"@rue_sad You will probably not remember my name in a while.\\.\\."
"\\n\\@rue_smile ...But I would still like to know yours."
msgstr ""
"@rue_sad 𣎏𨤰伴𠱊悁𠸜𪝬𢖖󠄁𠃣嘍𡛤。\\.\\.\\n\\@rue_smile 。。。扔𪝬吻㦖別𠸜伴。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:44:text
msgid "@niko I'm... \\.\\.not sure what you're talking about."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟。。。\\.\\.空昃舅當吶𧗱丐之。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:45:text
msgid "@niko_speak But my name is Niko!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔𠸜𨉟𪜀尼孤！"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:46:text
msgid "@rue ...Niko."
msgstr "@rue 。。。尼孤。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:47:text
msgid "@rue_smile I shall remember that!"
msgstr "@rue_smile 𪝬𠱊𢖵𥙩伮！"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:56:text
msgid "@rue_smile I'm glad you do not mind coming back."
msgstr "@rue_smile 實𢝙爲伴空礙𢮿徠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:59:text
msgid "@rue_talk To be perfectly honest..."
msgstr "@rue_talk 抵𦓡吶。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:60:text
msgid "@rue_sad It may be this way for a while, actually."
msgstr "@rue_sad 𣎏体伮𠱊接續如勢尼𠬠時間𡛤。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:62:text
msgid "@rue ...But in time, that will change."
msgstr "@rue 。。。扔耒、伮𠱊𠊝𢷮。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:63:text
msgid "@niko2 The... sun?"
msgstr "@niko2 𩈘。。。𡗶哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:64:text
msgid "@rue_smile \\p can see this, right?"
msgstr "@rue_smile \\p𣎏体𧡊𤗆次、董空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:66:text
msgid "@rue_smile Then \\p will understand."
msgstr "@rue_smile 勢時\\p𠱊曉。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:72:text
msgid "@rue_smile Oh, you're here!"
msgstr "@rue_smile 溩、伴㐌𦤾耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:73:text
msgid "@rue I was starting to miss you..."
msgstr "@rue 𪝬拱扒頭𢖵伴耒妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:74:text
msgid "@rue_smile ...Guess I got used to your company, after all."
msgstr "@rue_smile 。。。𣎏𨤔𪝬㐌慣喟役𣎏伴於邊耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:75:text
msgid "@niko2 ...pardon?"
msgstr "@niko2 。。。哰機？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/rue/EV012:1:76:text
msgid "@rue Do not worry. Carry on."
msgstr "@rue 揨𢥈。接續𠫾。"

#: Maps/Start/Bathroom/plant:1:1:text
msgid "@ed [A \\c[7]withered plant\\c[0] sits here, stiff and dry.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𠬠\\c[7]丐𣘃枯𤉗\\c[0]、勁吧枯。】"

#: Maps/Start/Bathroom/plant:1:3:text
msgid "@ed [There's no need to do anything else to it.]"
msgstr "@ed 【空懃𪵯之恪喟伮。】"

#: Maps/Start/Bathroom/plant:1:6:text
msgid "@ed [A branch snaps off.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𠬠莄𣘃𢭮𫥨。】"

#: Maps/Start/Bathroom/mirror:1:1:text
msgid "@ed [A pair of \\c[3]luminous, yellow eyes\\c[0] stares back at Niko.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𠬠笈眜\\c[3]𤏬、鐄\\c[0]𥆾徠𧗱𠌨尼孤。】"

#: Maps/Start/Bathroom/EV005:1:1:text
msgid "@ed [There's no water in the toilet.]"
msgstr "@ed 【空𣎏渃𥪝盆橋。】"

#: Maps/Start/Bathroom/EV006:1:1:text Maps/Start/Bathroom/EV007:1:1:text
msgid "@ed [The tub won't run.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𦞑渃空沚。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/blocks npc:1:1:text Maps/Green/Ruins
msgid "@niko The pathway is blocked...."
msgstr "@niko 𡓃𠫾被浱。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/blocks npc:1:2:text Maps/Green/Ruins
msgid "@niko_speak ...by blocks!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。𤳸仍塊𣃱！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/blocks npc:1:5:text
msgid ""
"@niko_what2 Waaaait a minute.\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed I remember something "
"about this..."
msgstr "@niko_what2 寬㐌。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟𢖵𣎏体𪵯之妬𧗱丐尼。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/blocks npc:1:22:text
msgid "@niko_83c Never knew it'd be so easy!"
msgstr "@niko_83c 空㘈伮徠易𦤾丕！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/blocks npc:1:24:text
msgid "@niko_what ...\\>(ow my foot ow)"
msgstr "@niko_what 。。。\\>（喂喂𤴬蹎過喂）"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/glitch left:1:1:text
msgid "@niko3 The squares are blocking the doorway..."
msgstr "@niko3 仍塊𣃱當浱𡓃𠫾尼。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:3:text
msgid "@alula_pout Oh...\\>\\nThe door..."
msgstr "@alula_pout 溩。。。\\>\\n𦑃𫔤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:4:text
msgid ""
"@calamus_sad I knew we'd lose our home eventually, but...\\>\\nI wasn't "
"expecting it to happen so soon..."
msgstr ""
"@calamus_sad 英別衆些耒𠱊𠅒茹、扔。。。\\>\\n英空擬𪜀伮徠𦤾𣋽如丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:6:text
msgid "@niko_shock Oh jeez! \\>\\n\\@niko3 Are you guys okay?"
msgstr "@niko_shock 喂𡗶！\\>\\n\\@niko3 𠄩𠊛穩渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:17:text
msgid "@calamus_shame Oh my stars!\\>\\nYou're... the savior!"
msgstr "@calamus_shame 喂𡗶㗒！\\>\\n伴𪜀。。。𠎬救世！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:18:text
msgid "@alula_gasp !!!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp ！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:19:text
msgid "@calamus Um....\\.\\.uh...."
msgstr "@calamus 𫫡。。。\\.\\.唹。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:20:text
msgid "@calamus_shame It's an honor to meet you!"
msgstr "@calamus_shame 實榮譽得﨤伴！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:21:text
msgid "@alula_gasp Yes!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 𫫡！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:22:text
msgid "@calamus_heh I'd invite you inside, but as you can see, our home is..."
msgstr "@calamus_heh 𨉟𠱊𫬱伴𠓨茹、扔如伴𧡊妬、茹衆𨉟被。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:23:text
msgid "@alula_gasp It's got squares in it!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 伮𣎏塊𣃱於𥪝！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:24:text
msgid "@calamus_sad Yes, Alula, thank you."
msgstr "@calamus_sad 董耒、阿瞜羅、感恩㛪。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:25:text
msgid "@niko3 It's... \\.\\.getting everywhere now... isn't it?"
msgstr "@niko3 伮㐌。。。\\.\\.攔𫥨七坭。。。耒𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:26:text
msgid "@calamus Hm?"
msgstr "@calamus 嘘？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:27:text
msgid "@niko3 The squares... there are way more than before!"
msgstr "@niko3 仍塊𣃱。。。𣎏𡗉欣𠓀！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:28:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Even the gate to the Refuge is destroyed now. \\>\\n\\@niko3 "
"That didn't happen last time!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𪥘󠄁𦑃𨶛𦤾區避難拱㐌被破毀耒。 \\>\\n\\@niko3 吝𠓀伮兜𣎏丕！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:29:text
msgid "@calamus_speak ...last time?"
msgstr "@calamus_speak 。。。吝𠓀？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:31:text
msgid "@calamus ....."
msgstr "@calamus 。。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:32:text
msgid "@niko5 Uhh...\\>\\@niko6 nothing!"
msgstr "@niko5 啊唹。。。\\>\\@niko6 空𣎏之兜！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:33:text
msgid "@niko_what2 (almost let that slip, \\p...)"
msgstr "@niko_what2 （侐露歇𪥘󠄁𫥨妬、\\p。。。）"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:34:text
msgid ""
"@niko Guess I should introduce myself again...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak My name is "
"Niko!"
msgstr "@niko 昃𨉟𢧚介紹徠本身。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 𨉟𠸜𪜀尼孤！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:35:text
msgid "@calamus_speak Ni...\\.\\.ko..."
msgstr "@calamus_speak 尼。。。\\.\\.孤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:36:text
#: Maps/Green/Forest/calamus npc 2:2:31:text
msgid "@calamus_shame Oh gosh! Would it not be rude to call you by name?"
msgstr "@calamus_shame 喂𡗶！空沛哙舅憑𠸜𠱊窒失禮哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:37:text
msgid "@niko_speak No worries, Calamus!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 空哰兜、哥羅𡃙！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:38:text
msgid "@calamus_shame HOW DID YOU KNOW MY NAME!?"
msgstr "@calamus_shame 𪵯哰舅別𠸜𨉟丕！？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:39:text
msgid "@niko2 I... \\.\\.um... \\.\\.\\@niko_what uh..."
msgstr "@niko2 𨉟。。。\\.\\.𫫡。。。\\.\\.\\@niko_what 唹。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:40:text
msgid "@niko_what2 (not again!)"
msgstr "@niko_what2 （徠𡛤耒！）"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:41:text
msgid "@alula_speak The messiah just knows these things, Calamus!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𠎬救世別仍次尼𦓡、英哥！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:42:text
msgid "@alula Riiiight?"
msgstr "@alula 沛空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:43:text
msgid "@niko_speak Y-yes! Of course!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 啊唹！必然渚！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:44:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed (phew)"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed （哺）"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:45:text
msgid "@calamus Ah... you were saying... about the gate?"
msgstr "@calamus 啊。。。舅𣃣吶𧗱。。。𦑃𨶛？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:46:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh, right!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 啊、沛耒！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:47:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Looks like I can't get in the city through the old gate "
"anymore..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣎏𨤔𨉟空体𠓨城鋪過𦑃𨶛𫇰得𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:48:text
msgid "@niko_speak Do... either of you know another way to get in?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 各舅。。。𣎏別格鬧恪抵𠓨空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:49:text
msgid ""
"@niko I remember... \\.\\.\\@niko_speak I mean, I HEARD that there's some "
"sort of hidden passage around here somewhere!"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟𢖵。。。\\.\\.\\@niko_speak 𡍚、𨉟𦖑𪜀𣎏𠬠𡓃𠫾隱兜妬𨑜尼𦓡！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:50:text
msgid "@calamus_speak Oh!\\>\\nThe passage to the burial grounds?"
msgstr "@calamus_speak 溩！\\>\\n𡓃𠫾𦤾義莊哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:51:text
msgid "@niko_speak That's the one!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 正伮！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:52:text
msgid "@calamus Oh... but I'm not sure if that'll be of any use here..."
msgstr "@calamus 溩。。。扔𨉟空昃伮𠱊𢴇益之𣊾𣇞。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:53:text
msgid "@calamus_sad It's been flooded for a long time, and there's no boat..."
msgstr "@calamus_sad 伮㐌被汲窒嘍耒、吧空𣎏船抵過徠。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:54:text
msgid ""
"@calamus Not to mention, the burial grounds itself is pretty far from the "
"city!"
msgstr "@calamus 哙貯𠸥、義莊隔城庯可賒妬！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:55:text
msgid "@niko_speak That's ok! I would still like to see it!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 空哰！𨉟吻㦖𧡊伮！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:56:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed It's the only lead we have..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 妬𪜀頭䋦唯一𨉟𣎏。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:57:text
msgid "@calamus Alright, in that case..."
msgstr "@calamus 得耒、裊丕時。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Birdhall/alula:2:58:text
msgid "@calamus_smile ...please follow us."
msgstr "@calamus_smile 。。。唉蹺衆𨉟。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:2:text
msgid "[DO WHAT YOU MUST.]"
msgstr "【唉𪵯仍之伴沛𪵯。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:6:text
#: Maps/Green/Research standing:1:7:text
msgid "[THIS IS THE MAIN GENERATOR OF THE GLEN.]"
msgstr "【低𪜀𣛠發電正𧵑區潭浰。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:8:text
#: Station/EV010:1:1:text
msgid ""
"@niko Would you happen to know where I can find a battery for a flying "
"machine?"
msgstr "@niko 伴𣎏別𨉟𣎏体尋汴朱飛行機於兜空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:9:text
msgid "@niko2 It's... kind of an emergency."
msgstr "@niko2 𨉟當懃。。。可急。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:10:text
msgid "[I DO NOT KNOW WHAT A FLYING MACHINE IS.]"
msgstr "【𪝬空別飛行機𪜀之。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:11:text
msgid ""
"[BUT ANY SORT OF LARGE MACHINERY WOULD REQUIRE A HIGH CAPACITY POWER CELL.]"
msgstr "【扔不其類𣛠𢪮𡘯鬧𠱊懃𠬠源電𣎏飾貯𡘯。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:12:text
msgid "[FOR EXAMPLE, THE GENERATOR IN THIS ROOM UTILIZES SUCH A DEVICE.]"
msgstr "【譬喻、𣛠發電𥪝房尼𣎏𠬠設備如丕。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:13:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Oh right... I almost forgot..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 沛耒。。。子時𨉟悁𠅒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:14:text
msgid ""
"@niko We had to fix the battery for this thing in the Barrens, didn't we, "
"\\p?"
msgstr "@niko 衆些拱沛𢯢汴朱丐次尼𥪝塳邊疆、沛空\\p？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:16:text
msgid ""
"[IF THIS IS AN EMERGENCY FOR LIVING BEINGS...] \\>\\n[YOU CAN USE THE "
"BATTERY FROM THE GENERATOR.]"
msgstr "【裊事緊急尼𣎏聯關𦤾各生物𤯩。。。】 \\>\\n【伴𣎏体使用汴𥪝𣛠發電。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:18:text
msgid "@niko2 Wait... \\.\\.but if we take the battery here..."
msgstr "@niko2 扔。。。\\.\\.裊衆𨉟𥙩𫪐汴於低。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:19:text
msgid "@niko3 ...all of you guys would lose power, wouldn't you?"
msgstr "@niko3 。。。各伴𠱊調𠅒電、董空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:20:text
msgid "@niko4 Maybe \\p and I should go find another one."
msgstr "@niko4 𣎏𨤰\\p𦓡𨉟𢧚𠫾尋𠬠𫪐恪。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:21:text
msgid "[NEGATIVE.]"
msgstr "【否定。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:22:text
msgid ""
"[THIS IS THE ONLY BATTERY IN THE GLEN POWERFUL ENOUGH TO BE USED AS A "
"STANDALONE UNIT.]"
msgstr "【低𪜀𫪐汴唯一𥪝區潭浰覩猛抵使用𥢆。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:23:text
msgid "[IF IT IS A DIRE SITUATION, THEN DO WHAT YOU MUST.]"
msgstr "【裊情況危急、唉𪵯仍之伴沛𪵯。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:1:24:text
msgid "@niko4 Oh..."
msgstr "@niko4 溩。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/robot standing:2:1:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...we depowered it..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。衆些㐌捽源電耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/EV004:1:2:text
msgid "@niko3 ...I guess we have no choice but to take this, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko3 。。。𣇞衆些沛𥙩伮催、\\p。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/EV004:1:15:text
msgid "@niko Looks like a generator..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠𣛠發電。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/EV004:1:20:text
msgid "[PLEASE DO NOT STAND TOO CLOSE TO THE GENERATOR.]"
msgstr "【𢝙𢚸空𨅸過近𣛠發電。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/EV004:1:21:text
msgid "[IF YOU HAVE INQUIRIES, PLEASE ASK ME INSTEAD.]"
msgstr "【裊伴𣎏句𠳨、𢝙𢚸𠳨𪝬。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/EV004:2:1:text
msgid "@niko The battery's gone now..."
msgstr "@niko 𫪐汴空哙妬𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/EV004:2:2:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak We should remember to bring it back once we're done with it!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 衆些𢧚𢖵𫼳伮㨋徠𢖖󠄁欺歱役！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Research Station/Power room/fireflies:1:1:text
#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/fireflies:1:1:text Maps/Green/Research
#: Maps/Green/Village/House 1 - stew/fireflies:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A couple of fireflies are buzzing about in this jar."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𠄧哙炶炶當𢒎𥪝𤮗。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/courtyard/EV009:1:2:text
msgid "What am I gonna do!!!"
msgstr "𪝬沛𪵯之𣊾𣇞！！！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/courtyard/EV009:1:5:text
msgid "My robot!!!"
msgstr "𠊛𣛠𧵑𪝬！！！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/courtyard/EV009:1:7:text
msgid "I don't know! I left for a minute and..."
msgstr "𪝬空別𡛤！𪝬𠬃𠫾𣎏𠬠𤼵吧耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/courtyard/EV010:1:1:text
msgid "[P\\.\\.%LE\\.ASE \\.\\. D;O NOT \\.\\.\\.AP\\.PR##OACH]"
msgstr "【口\\.\\.%千\\.扌\\.\\.亭;扌\\.\\.\\.妾\\.辶##斤]"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:4:text
msgid ""
"@niko I think I have something I'd like to trade!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak You'll "
"take wool, right?\\>\\n\\@niko What can this wool get me?"
msgstr ""
"@niko 㛪擬㛪𣎏𦁺抵𢭂𢷮！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 英認縺、董空？\\>\\n\\@niko 淃縺"
"尼𣎏体𢷮朱㛪丐之？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:5:text
msgid "@magpie_hm Wool, huh?"
msgstr "@magpie_hm 縺嘑？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:6:text
msgid "@magpie That'll get you.\\..\\..\\.\\.This fine vial of..."
msgstr "@magpie 伮𠱊𢷮得朱㛪。\\..\\..\\.\\.𤮗。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:7:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_smile I'm not sure what this is, actually!\\>\\nSome sort of fabric "
"dye?"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 英拱空昃伮𪜀之𡛤！\\>\\n𠬠類𧆄染𡲫之妬庄？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:8:text
msgid "@niko Hmm... How about it, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 嘘。。。舅擬哰、\\p？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:8:choice:0
msgid "Take the offer!"
msgstr "得！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:8:choice:1
msgid "Ehh..."
msgstr "𫫡。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:11:text
msgid "@niko_speak I'll do it!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 得耒！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:15:text Events:1:32:text Events:1:140:text
msgid "@magpie_smile Pleasure doing business!"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 欣幸得交易喟貴客！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:20:text
msgid "@niko Wait, \\p... you want to...haggle?\\>\\n\\@niko_what ...really?"
msgstr "@niko 寬、\\p。。。舅㦖。。。嚜𪥘󠄁哰？\\>\\n\\@niko_what 。。。實㫻？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:21:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Alright then..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 得耒。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:22:text
msgid "@niko_speak \\p said they wanted a better offer!"
msgstr "@niko_speak \\p吶舅𧘇㦖𢷮賚欣！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:23:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_oh ...holy smokes!\\>\\n\\@magpie_smile Forgot I was doing a trade "
"with god for a second there..."
msgstr ""
"@magpie_oh 。。。喂𡗶㗒！\\>\\n\\@magpie_smile 悁𠅒英當交易喟𠎬全𥘀妬。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:24:text
msgid ""
"@magpie Okay, okay...\\>\\n\\@magpie_smile In that case, I'll also throw in "
"this commemorative T-shirt!"
msgstr ""
"@magpie 嗚雞、嗚雞。。。\\>\\n\\@magpie_smile 裊勢、英𠱊朱㛪添隻襖風紀念尼"
"𡛤！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:25:text
#: Maps/Green/Village/shephard:1:42:text
msgid "@niko Uh..."
msgstr "@niko 唹。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:37:text
msgid "@magpie Oh well, then.\\nCome back anytime."
msgstr "@magpie 喂、𢝜丕。\\n哏﨤徠貴客。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:45:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed \\p, no..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed \\p、空。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:50:text
msgid "@magpie_oh Hey! I just gave that to you!"
msgstr "@magpie_oh 尼！英𣃣朱㛪丐妬𦓡！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:51:text
msgid "@magpie_smile What, you wanna trade it back?"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 之、㛪㦖𢷮伮徠嘑？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:52:text Maps/POSTGAME green/burial
#: grounds/burial grounds PLANE FIXED/EV188:1:23:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Not really..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 空𪳨。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:53:text
msgid "@magpie Good, cuz I wasn't gonna!"
msgstr "@magpie 卒耒、爲英拱空定兜！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:58:text
msgid "@magpie I ain't takin that back!"
msgstr "@magpie 英空認伮徠兜！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:59:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_hm The shepherd was handing those out a while ago."
"\\>\\n\\@magpie_smile But does it LOOK like it'll fit me?"
msgstr ""
"@magpie_hm 𣎏𠬠澾𢬣𤛇易發襖妬朱𤗆𠊛。\\>\\n\\@magpie_smile 扔矓伮𣎏𣃣英空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:61:text
msgid "@magpie_smile T-Shirts aren't exactly made for people with wings!"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 襖風𪵯之得設計朱𠊛𣎏𦑃兜！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:66:text
msgid "@niko Wait, trade this?"
msgstr "@niko 寬、𢷮丐尼哰？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:67:text
msgid "@niko_speak Don't you want to find out what it says first, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 至𠃣舅拱𢧚別伮𥱬之𠓀渚、\\p？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:68:text
msgid "@magpie What's that? A book?"
msgstr "@magpie 之妬？冊嘑？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:69:text
msgid "@magpie_smile Uh, not sure if I wanna take books, I can't read!"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 唹、空昃英𣎏𢧚𥙩冊空、在英空別讀！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:75:text
msgid "@magpie_oh I can't take this!"
msgstr "@magpie_oh 英空認丐尼得！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:78:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'm not trading that, \\p!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空𢷮𦁺尼兜、\\p！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:79:text
msgid "@magpie You're not trading what?"
msgstr "@magpie 㛪空𢷮丐之幾？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:80:text
msgid "@magpie What's that? A feather?"
msgstr "@magpie 之妬？𦒮𪀄嘑？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:82:text
msgid "@magpie_hm Wait... \\.\\.\\@magpie_oh Oh my stars!"
msgstr "@magpie_hm 徐㐌。。。\\.\\.\\@magpie_oh 喂𡗶㗒！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:83:text
msgid "@magpie_oh That is NOT \"a\" feather!"
msgstr "@magpie_oh 空沛𦒮𪀄尋常兜！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:84:text
msgid "@magpie That is a feather from the late Prophet!"
msgstr "@magpie 妬𪜀𠬠隻𦒮羽𧵑茹先知㵋𠅒！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:85:text
msgid "@magpie_oh Probably one of the most sacred items there is!"
msgstr "@magpie_oh 𠬠𥪝仍物品得崇拜一現在！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:86:text
msgid "@magpie_oh How in the WORLD did you get a hold of THAT?"
msgstr "@magpie_oh 𪵯勢鬧㛪徠𣎏得伮丕？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:87:text
msgid "@magpie_hm ...Wait, I guess it would make sense for you to have one."
msgstr "@magpie_hm 。。。寬、昃拱𣎏理催。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:88:text
msgid "@magpie_smile Y'know, with you being the savior and all."
msgstr "@magpie_smile 時、爲㛪𪜀𠎬救世𦓡。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:89:text
msgid "@niko Um... okay."
msgstr "@niko 𫫡。。。嗚雞。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:96:text
msgid "@niko The seed left behind by the plant lady?"
msgstr "@niko 籺𥞖姉𠊛𣘃抵徠哰？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:97:text
msgid "@niko_huh Oh, but what if...\\. it's like...\\. her baby..."
msgstr "@niko_huh 唹、仍𢙲。。。\\.妬𪜀。。。\\.哙姉𧘇時哰。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:98:text
msgid "@niko_speak I can't give away someone's baby like that!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟空体朱𠫾哙𠊛恪易揚如世得！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:99:text
msgid "@niko_wtf2 Especially not to a bird..."
msgstr "@niko_wtf2 特別空得𠀲朱𪀄。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:100:text
msgid "@magpie_oh ...hey!"
msgstr "@magpie_oh 。。。尼！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:105:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I don't think it's right to trade this away, \\p ..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空擬𢧚𢷮丐尼𠫾兜、\\p。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:106:text
msgid "@magpie_oh Oh hey! You have one of those coin things!"
msgstr "@magpie_oh 嗚尼！㛪𣎏𠬠銅鏂！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:107:text
msgid "@magpie I've dug up a couple of these before."
msgstr "@magpie 英拱開掘得𠬠𠄧銅𠓀低。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:109:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_smile Yeah! There's this guy who would trade me the BEST things for "
"them."
msgstr "@magpie_smile 唹！𣎏翁尼𠱊𢷮朱英仍次絕𡸏一抵𥙩衆。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:111:text
msgid ""
"@magpie Like, one time he brought me this little machine that plays music!"
msgstr "@magpie 矯、𠬠吝慃𫼳朱英丐𣛠發樂𡮈𡥵尼！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:112:text
msgid "@magpie_hm I don't know what it's called, but you have to wind it up..."
msgstr "@magpie_hm 英空別伮哙𪜀之、扔沛𢱨爐爐軀。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:113:text
msgid "@niko_speak Music box?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 匣樂嘑？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:114:text
msgid "@magpie_smile That's it!"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 正伮！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:115:text
msgid ""
"@magpie I wish that guy would come back soon, I haven't seen him in forever."
msgstr "@magpie 約之慃𢮿徠𣋽、㐌嘍𡗋耒英空﨤慃。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:116:text
msgid "@magpie_smile I wanna do more trades with him!"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 英㦖𢭂𢷮添喟慃！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:121:text
msgid "@niko How about this...glass tube full of water I got from a robot?"
msgstr "@niko 哙丐。。。䈵驗水晶𣹓渃㛪𥙩𧵑𠬠𠊛𣛠時哰？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:122:text
msgid "@niko Do you like glass?"
msgstr "@niko 英𣎏適水晶空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:123:text
msgid "@magpie_smile Do I!"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 𠰚！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:124:text
msgid "@niko ...do you?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。英𣎏空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:125:text
msgid "@magpie I LOVE glass!"
msgstr "@magpie 英㤇水晶！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:126:text
msgid "@magpie_smile SO much."
msgstr "@magpie_smile 𡗉𡗋。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:127:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_hm ...so much that I have too much glass and not enough other things."
msgstr "@magpie_hm 。。。𦤾餒英𣎏過𡗉水晶吧空覩仍次恪。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:128:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_hm I gotta get rid of some of my old bottles and vials to make room "
"for new stuff!"
msgstr "@magpie_hm 英沛𠬃抔仍𥑂𤮗𫇰抵除𡊲朱仍𦁺㵋幾！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:129:text
msgid "@magpie That's why I set up a tradepost in the first place."
msgstr "@magpie 勢𢧚英㵋立站𢭂𢷮。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:130:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed So I guess that's a no-go..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 丕時𦁺妬空得耒。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:135:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed \\p... wasn't the whole point of trading was so that we "
"could make a pen?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𦓡\\p尼。。。拯沛徐頭衆些𢭂𢷮抵製𠬠隻筆哰？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:136:text
msgid "@niko Let's not trade this away..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟𢧚𡨺徠丐尼。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:143:text
msgid "@magpie Heya!\\>\\nYou here to trade?"
msgstr "@magpie 吀嘲！\\>\\n㛪𦤾低𢭂𢷮嘑？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:144:text
msgid "@niko Trade?"
msgstr "@niko 𢭂𢷮？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:145:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_smile Yeah!\\>\\n\\@magpie Is there anything you want to get rid of?"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 𫫡！\\>\\n\\@magpie 𣎏𦁺之㛪㦖𠬃𠫾空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:146:text
msgid "@magpie Make me an offer and I'll give you something in return!"
msgstr "@magpie 唉朱英𠬠𠳒提議吧英𠱊㨋徠㛪𠬠𦁺恪！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:1:147:text
msgid "@niko Hm...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak Do we have something like that, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 嘘。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 衆些𣎏𦁺之如丕空\\p？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:2:3:text
msgid "@niko It's a wagon stuffed with stuff!"
msgstr "@niko 𠬠隻車捁質𣹓質料！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:2:4:text
msgid "@magpie_smile It sure is!"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 董𪜀如丕！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:4:text
msgid "@niko Shiny things are spread out on the rug."
msgstr "@niko 仍𦁺𣘊𣈖𪵅𣥱𫥨𨑗毯。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:6:text
msgid "@niko They glimmer in the sunlight."
msgstr "@niko 衆垃𨀌𨑜暎𩈘𡗶。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:9:text
msgid "@niko They glimmer in the light of the lamp."
msgstr "@niko 衆垃𨀌𨑜暎畑。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:14:text
#: In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:20:text
msgid "@niko_speak Whoa!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫽿！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:15:text
msgid "@niko_speak That's a lotta shiny things!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 窒𡗉仍𦁺𣘊琫𠤩！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:16:text
msgid "@niko Glass shards, glass marbles..."
msgstr "@niko 𤗖水晶、啤水晶。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:17:text
msgid ""
"@niko ...empty glass bottles, mostly-empty glass bottles, glass bottles "
"filled with different things..."
msgstr "@niko 。。。𤮗水晶筩、𤮗水晶近筩、𤮗水晶貯仍次恪僥。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:18:text
msgid "@niko ...bits of string, colored wool, plain wool, fabric scraps..."
msgstr "@niko 。。。𠄧段黹、縺𦭷色、縺𤽸、𠇍𤗖𡲫。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:19:text
msgid "@niko ...a rusty bucket, scrap metal, shells, some rocks..."
msgstr "@niko 。。。𠬠丐搊釲、鉄砵、𤿭𧎷、𠄼𡉕𥒥。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:20:text
msgid "@niko_speak What's all this for, by the way?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𦓡仍次尼抵𪵯之丕英？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins Out/Map Events:3:21:text
