#: Maps/Start/Livingroom/key:1:2:text
msgid ""
"@ed [It appears to be a small metallic object,\\nwedged into a crack in the "
"floor.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠物体金類𡮈、\\n縸𠓨𠬠汫𨑗孱。】"

#: Maps/Start/Livingroom/key:1:3:text
msgid "@ed [Niko digs it out.]"
msgstr "@ed 【尼孤掏伮𫥨。】"

#: Maps/Start/Livingroom/niko hello:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak Helloooo?\\>\\n\\@niko ...anyone?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 吀嘲－－－？\\>\\n\\@niko 。。。𣎏埃空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/EV001:1:1:text Maps/Green/Ruins
#: In/Birdhall/Courtyard/EV001:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a ball."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠菓琫。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/EV001:1:9:text Maps/Green/Ruins
#: In/Birdhall/Courtyard/EV001:1:2:text
msgid ""
"@alula That's mine!\\>\\n\\@alula_pout It doesn't bounce around as much as "
"it used to, though..."
msgstr "@alula 𧵑𨉟妬！\\>\\n\\@alula_pout 雖伮空䄧𡗉如𠓀𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/calamus npc:2:1:text
msgid "@calamus_sad At least the courtyard is unaffected for now..."
msgstr "@calamus_sad 𠃣𫥨𡑝𥪝𣗓被作動。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/calamus npc:2:1:text
msgid ""
"@alula_pout We usually get to the burial grounds through our friend, but..."
msgstr "@alula_pout 衆𨉟常𦤾義莊喟𠬠𠊛伴、扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/calamus npc:2:2:text
msgid "@alula_oh ...he hasn't been here in forever!"
msgstr "@alula_oh 。。。舅𧘇㐌窒嘍耒空𦤾低！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/calamus npc:2:3:text
msgid "@calamus Normally this courtyard would be where we meet up..."
msgstr "@calamus 常衆𨉟𠱊﨤僥於低。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/calamus npc:2:4:text
msgid "@alula I hope he comes back soon..."
msgstr "@alula 懞舅𧘇𣋽𢮿徠。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE FIXED/EV132:2:2:text
msgid "@calamus C'mon, Alula.\\>\\nLet's go see mom."
msgstr "@calamus 𠫾鬧、阿瞜羅。\\>\\n𠫾探媄鬧。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE FIXED/EV132:2:3:text
#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:48:text
msgid "@alula_speak Okay!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 嗚雞！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/calamus:1:1:text
msgid "@calamus This is her grave..."
msgstr "@calamus 低𪜀墓𧵑媄。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE FIXED/alula:1:1:text
msgid "@alula Hi mom..."
msgstr "@alula 嘲媄。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE FIXED/alula:2:5:text
msgid "@alula_speak Gears!\\>\\@alula Didja find any of those?"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𨋣𪘵！\\>\\@alula 舅㐌尋𧡊丐鬧𣗓？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/alula:2:20:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak ...Oh yeah! \\@niko\\>I think I know who you're talking about."
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。啊唹！ \\@niko\\>𨉟擬𨉟別舅當吶𧗱埃。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE FIXED/EV188:1:8:text
msgid "@cedric ...it's fixed."
msgstr "@cedric 。。。如丕𪜀㐌歱。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE FIXED/EV188:1:9:text
msgid "@cedric We can leave in the next five minutes, if you are ready."
msgstr "@cedric 衆些𣎏体拮𦑃𥪝𠄼𤼵𡛤、裊㛪𠻿𠳹。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:10:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...alright."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。得耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:12:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh I understand if you are upset."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 英曉裊㛪𣎏不安。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:13:text
msgid "@cedric3 But please...\\.\\. try to understand."
msgstr "@cedric3 扔唉。。。\\.\\.固曉朱暎。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:14:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh My father is doing this to help all of us."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 仛英當𪵯役尼抵𢴇扡悉𪥘󠄁衆些。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:15:text
msgid "@cedric And that includes you, Niko."
msgstr "@cedric 包𠁟𪥘󠄁㛪𡛤、尼孤啊。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:16:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh2 The fact that you can't even go back home...\\> I'm sure it "
"upsets him greatly."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 役㛪空体𧗱茹。。。\\>昃𥗜伮㐌遣翁苦腦窒𡗉。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:17:text
msgid "@cedric It's..."
msgstr "@cedric 伮。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:18:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Sigh..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 係。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:19:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh2 The world means a lot to him, you know..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 世界窒關重喟翁𧘇、㛪𧡊妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:21:text
msgid "@niko2 So... \\.\\.how does flying...\\.\\. work?"
msgstr "@niko2 丕時。。。\\.\\.衆些𢒎。。。\\.\\.勢鬧？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:22:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_talk ...wait, don't these machines already exist in your world? "
"\\>\\n\\@cedric_hmm You should already know what to expect..."
msgstr ""
"@cedric_talk 。。。寬、拯沛衆𣎏存在𥪝世界𧵑㛪哰？ \\>\\n\\@cedric_hmm 㛪拱𢧚"
"別𢧚期望之耒渚𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:24:text
msgid "@niko I've only heard about them!"
msgstr "@niko 㛪㵋只𦖑𧗱伮催！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:25:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed They're usually... a lot bigger than this one, anyway."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 怞哰時衆常。。。𡘯欣丐尼窒𡗉。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:26:text
msgid "@cedric3 Ah..."
msgstr "@cedric3 啊。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:27:text
msgid "@cedric_talk Well, a word of precaution, before we take to the air..."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 丕時、𠬠𠳒警報、𠓀欺衆些𨖨𩈘𡐙。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:28:text
msgid "@cedric_talk Please try not to panic."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 唉固𠡚揨慌亂唲。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:29:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_smile It takes a few minutes of getting used to, but it's not that "
"bad once you are in the air."
msgstr "@cedric_smile 𠱊𠅒𠄧𤼵抵𪵯慣、扔空弊𦤾勢𠬠欺㛪當𢒎。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:30:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'll... try."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪𠱊。。。固。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:31:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Oh! I should probably tell Calamus and Alula where I'm going."
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！㛪拱𢧚𠸒哥羅𡃙吧阿瞜羅𨉟𢯛𠫾兜。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:34:text
msgid "@cedric_talk You mean those two running over here now?"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 𪜀𠄩𠀲𡮈當𧼋𧗱𠌨𨉟嘑？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:36:text
msgid "@alula_oh Niko!!!!"
msgstr "@alula_oh 尼孤！！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:76:text
msgid "@alula_oh Bad news!"
msgstr "@alula_oh 信醜！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:77:text
msgid "@calamus_shock The boat is gone!"
msgstr "@calamus_shock 隻船變𠅒耒！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:78:text
msgid "@niko3 What?!"
msgstr "@niko3 之幾？！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:79:text
msgid "@alula_oh It's the squares!"
msgstr "@alula_oh 𪜀仍形𣃱！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:80:text
msgid "@calamus_speak It looks like they're headed in this direction!"
msgstr "@calamus_speak 𣎏𨤔衆當進𧗱向尼！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:82:text
msgid "@cedric_eek ...fast..."
msgstr "@cedric_eek 。。。窒𨘱。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:88:text
msgid "@cedric_talk ...Calamus, right?"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 。。。哥羅𡃙、沛空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:90:text
msgid "@calamus Yeah?"
msgstr "@calamus 𫫡？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:91:text
msgid "@cedric_talk How...\\.\\. bad, is it?"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 伮。。。\\.\\.弊𦤾櫸鬧？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:92:text
msgid "@calamus Doesn't seem to be of immediate danger."
msgstr "@calamus 暫時𣗓過危險。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:97:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh Then... it is of priority that I take you to the city first, "
"Niko"
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 丕時。。。暎𠱊優先迻㛪𦤾城庯𠓀、尼孤。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:98:text
msgid "@niko2 But what about them...?"
msgstr "@niko2 扔哙𣱆時哰。。。？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:99:text
msgid ""
"@cedric I can make a detour later and drop you guys off in the city too, if "
"you want."
msgstr "@cedric 英拱𣎏体𢷮向𧗱𢖖󠄁吧抯𠄩𠊛於𥪝城庯、裊𠄩𠊛㦖。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:100:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_talk The city is better equipped to handle the squares, you'll be "
"safer there."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 城庯得裝備卒欣抵處理仍塊𣃱、各㛪𠱊案全欣於妬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:102:text
msgid "@alula_gasp YOU'RE TAKING US TO THE CITY!!!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 英𠱊迻衆㛪𦤾城庯！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:103:text
msgid "@cedric_smile If you wish."
msgstr "@cedric_smile 裊㛪㦖。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:104:text
msgid "@alula_gasp OH YEAH!!!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 絕𡸏！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:105:text
msgid "@cedric Alright."
msgstr "@cedric 得耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:106:text
msgid ""
"@cedric3 I will be back here in an hour, so please wait for me until then."
msgstr "@cedric3 英𠱊𢮿徠𢖖󠄁𠬠㗂、𢧚唉䟻英唲。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:107:text
msgid "@niko You guys sure you'll be fine here?"
msgstr "@niko 各舅擬𨉟𠱊穩於低渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:108:text
msgid "@alula Mhm!"
msgstr "@alula 𫫡！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:109:text
msgid "@calamus_speak The squares are still moving pretty slowly for now..."
msgstr "@calamus_speak 仍溩𣃱吻當移轉可踸。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:110:text
msgid "@niko2 Alright, then..."
msgstr "@niko2 得耒、丕時。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:111:text
msgid "@niko_speak Guess we'll run into each other again, soon..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 昃𪜀衆些𠱊𣋽﨤徠僥。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:115:text
msgid "@niko_speak I'm ready to go!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 㛪㐌𠻿𠳹！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/burial grounds/burial grounds PLANE
#: FIXED/EV188:1:116:text
msgid "@cedric_smile Alright!"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 得耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/left- pools/map
#: event:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A bunch of words are on the screen."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠埬句詞𨑗幔形。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/left- pools/map
#: event:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I don't understand any of it..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空曉𠬠子之𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/left- pools/map
#: event:2:1:text
msgid ""
"The luminescence index of liquid red phosphor decreased by a factor of 3.57% "
"this past week."
msgstr "指數發光𧵑光素𧹻𣿅㐌減3.57%𥪝旬過。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/left- pools/map
#: event:2:2:text
msgid ""
"Alarming, to say the least... that's the sharpest decline I've seen, and the "
"number is only increasing."
msgstr "窒當報動。。。𣞪減漊一𪝬曾觀察、吧𡥵数𣈜𪨈增𬨠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/left- pools/map
#: event:2:3:text
msgid ""
"We will have to further concentrate the phosphor now, for it to be of any "
"use."
msgstr "衆些沛增強濃度光素抵接續使用。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/left- pools/map
#: event:2:4:text
msgid ""
"It's hard to believe, but there's a good chance this city could run out of "
"light in as little as six months."
msgstr "窒𠸋信、扔可能窒高城庯𠱊歇暎𤏬只𢖖󠄁𦒹𣎃𡛤。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/left- pools/map
#: event:2:5:text
msgid "...What are we going to do?"
msgstr "。。。衆些沛𪵯之𣊾𣇞？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/left- pools/map
#: event:3:1:text
msgid ""
"If the city runs out of light, well...\\>\\nI don't want to think about what "
"happens then."
msgstr "裊城庯歇暎𤏬。。。\\>\\n𪝬空㦖擬𧗱仍之𠱊侈𫥨。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:1:2:text
msgid "[HAVE YOU FOUND THE SOURCE OF THE DISTRESS?]"
msgstr "【伴㐌尋得源𩂀𧵑事不穩𣗓？】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:1:5:text
msgid "[THESE VINES APPEARED MERE MINUTES AGO.]"
msgstr "【仍𧻭蹽尼㵋出現𠄧𤼵𠓀。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:1:8:text
msgid "@niko I just assumed it was cuz this place was abandoned..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟只墨定𪜀由𡊲尼㐌被𠬃荒耒催。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:1:9:text
msgid "[A SIGN OF DISTRESS.]"
msgstr "【𠬠𨁪號𧵑事不穩。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:1:11:text
msgid "[A LIVING BEING IS IN NEED OF HELP.]"
msgstr "【𠬠寔体𤯩當懃助𢴇。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:1:12:text
msgid "[BUT I CANNOT TRACE THE SOURCE.]"
msgstr "【扔𪝬空体追𫥨源㭲。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:1:13:text Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/Lobby/Map Events:4:14:text
msgid "@niko ...ah."
msgstr "@niko 。。。啊。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:2:1:text
msgid "[THE VINES RECEDED.]"
msgstr "【仍𧻭蹽㐌捽徠。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:2:2:text
msgid "[DO YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENED?]"
msgstr "【伴𣎏別條之㐌侈𫥨空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:2:3:text
msgid "@niko I found this... plant person."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟尋𧡊。。。姉𠊛𣘃尼。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:2:4:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed She was barely holding on..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 姉只當梭𡀾𤯩催。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:2:5:text
msgid "@niko I gave her the sun for now, but..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟㐌暫時迻姉𧘇𩈘𡗶、扔。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:2:6:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed She said it was too late for her..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 姉𧘇吶哴㐌過悶。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:2:7:text
msgid "[I UNDERSTAND.]"
msgstr "【𪝬曉。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/EV023:2:8:text
msgid "[I NEED TO REPORT THIS TO THE CITY.]"
msgstr "【𪝬懃沛報告𡀯尼朱城庯。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/map events:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A cluster of vines are blocking the way..."
msgstr "@niko 【𠬠㯲絏繚當浱塘。。。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:3:text
msgid "Don't worry, these are my own books. That I wrote."
msgstr "揨𢥈、低𪜀冊𧵑𪝬。由𪝬自曰。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:4:text
msgid ""
"I just pulled them off the shelves to modify them. I have to cross out some "
"sections..."
msgstr "𪝬𣃣捽衆𠺌架冊抵𢯢徠。𪝬沛劃𠬃𠬠𠄧份。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:5:text
msgid "...most sections."
msgstr "。。。侯歇各份。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:6:text
msgid "@niko_speak Eh? How come?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠯋？哰丕？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:7:text
msgid "Cuz otherwise they'll think I copied HIM."
msgstr "渚空時𣱆𠱊擬𪝬咹𢲩𧵑翁𧘇。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:8:text
msgid "@niko Him?"
msgstr "@niko 翁𧘇？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:9:text
msgid "The Author!"
msgstr "作者創世！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:10:text
msgid "I mean, I really don't see the point of writing anything anymore!"
msgstr "意𪜀、𪝬拱空別𢧚曰抵𪵯之𡛤！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:11:text
msgid ""
"The Author is just gonna write about the same thing, and then everyone will "
"love it!"
msgstr "作者𠱊徠曰𧗱董次妬、吧𤗆𠊛𠱊適迷朱䀡！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:12:text
msgid "And nobody's gonna remember the books that came out before his!"
msgstr "吧𠱊拯埃𢖵𧗱仍卷冊出版𠓀妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:13:text
msgid "@niko Oh, uh..."
msgstr "@niko 啊、唹。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:14:text
msgid "I mean, I ain't hatin'."
msgstr "意𪜀、空沛讎恄咍之兜。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:15:text
msgid ""
"I can see why people go nuts over his stuff. That guy's got major talent."
msgstr "𪝬曉在哰天下徠發狂欺讀仍次𧵑慃。慃𣎏才能超凡㫻妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:16:text
msgid "But...it just...hurts, y'know?"
msgstr "扔𦓡吻。。。損傷𡗋、㛪曉渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:17:text
msgid ""
"It's never fun when people call you a copycat for something you wrote about "
"first."
msgstr "𢪏𧗱伮𠓀𦓡被噲𪜀咹𢲩時𣎏𢝙包𣇞。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:18:text
msgid "@niko I can see that..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟曉。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:19:text
msgid "@niko_speak People call me a cat all the time!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𤗆𠊛全噲𨉟𪜀貓！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:20:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Even though I'm a person, and cats are pets."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 怞𨉟𪜀𠊛、𡀳貓𪜀獸𩝺。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:21:text
msgid "@niko ...and mousers."
msgstr "@niko 。。。吧獸𤜬𤝞。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:22:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I sure hope people don't think I eat mice..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 懞空埃擬𨉟咹𤝞。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:1:23:text
msgid "Heh, then I guess we're in the same boat, kiddo."
msgstr "嗘、勢時衆些共船耒、傉啊。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:2:1:text
msgid "Well, I think I changed at least half a book's worth of content."
msgstr "丕𪜀𪝬㐌𢯢徠曠姅卷冊耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:2:2:text
msgid "And even then, it's still too similiar!"
msgstr "𦓡矓伮吻偅版𫇰過！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:2:3:text
msgid "Looks like I'll just have to accept my fate..."
msgstr "𣎏𨤰𪝬沛執認數分催。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:2:4:text
msgid "@niko Well, I guess being a called a cat isn't all that bad..."
msgstr "@niko 𫫡、㛪擬被噲𪜀貓空弊𦤾勢。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV001:2:5:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...as long as people don't assume you eat mice."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。裊如𤗆𠊛空擬㛪咹𤝞。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV017:1:1:text
msgid "I'm on my 3rd cup."
msgstr "𪝬㐌𪵯𦤾𤭏次𠀧耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV017:1:2:text
msgid "I can't feel my limbs..."
msgstr "蹎𢬣𪝬調痺疲歇價耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV017:1:3:text
#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:24:text
msgid "@niko um..."
msgstr "@niko 唹。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV017:1:4:text
msgid "BUT I HAVE TO STAY AWAKE."
msgstr "扔𪝬沛𥅞。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV017:1:7:text
msgid "CURSE THE AUTHOR AND HIS BEAUTIFUL CLIFFHANGERS..."
msgstr "師佈作者吧仍丐結𠻴𧵑老。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:2:text
#: Events:1:9:text
msgid "@bookbot !"
msgstr "@bookbot ！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:3:text
#: Events:1:10:text
msgid "@bookbot [UNAUTHORIZED ENTRY.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【空分事免𠓨。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:4:text
#: Events:1:11:text Events:1:13:text
msgid "@bookbot [LIBRARY CARD REQUIRED FOR FURTHER ACCESS.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【懃𣎏𥮋書院抵𠓨𥪝。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:5:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I know, I know..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 別耒、別耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:12:text
msgid "@niko Wait, what?"
msgstr "@niko 寬、之幾？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:14:text
msgid "@niko_speak I don't have a library card, though!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔𨉟空𣎏𥮋書院！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:15:text
msgid "@niko Where can I get one?"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟𣎏彩𪵯沒丐於兜丕？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:16:text
msgid "@bookbot [THIS IS A QUESTION FOR THE HEAD LIBRARIAN, GEORGE.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【句𠳨尼𧶄朱守書觫。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:17:text
#: Events:2:90:text
msgid "@bookbot [ALLOW ME TO CALL HER.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【抵𪝬噲姑𧘇。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:28:text
msgid "@niko_huh . . ."
msgstr "@niko_huh 。 。 。 "

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:31:text
msgid "@niko_wtf2 . . . . ."
msgstr "@niko_wtf2 。 。 。 。 。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:34:text
#: Events:2:109:text
msgid "@bookbot [SHE IS NOT PICKING UP.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【姑𧘇空𢩮𣛠。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:36:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I figured..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟拱斷丕。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:37:text
msgid "@niko Are you sure you can't just... let me through?"
msgstr "@niko 舅實事空体。。。朱𨉟過哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:38:text
msgid ""
"@bookbot [LETTING YOU THROUGH WITHOUT A LIBRARY CARD IS AGAINST MY "
"PROGRAMMING.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【立程𧵑𪝬空朱法𪝬抵伴𠓨𦓡空𣎏𥮋書院。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:39:text
msgid "@niko_what Wh-"
msgstr "@niko_what 嘑－"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:40:text
msgid "@niko Even in an emergency?"
msgstr "@niko 𠸥𪥘󠄁欺緊急哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:41:text
msgid "@bookbot [MY PROGRAMMING IS NOT FLEXIBLE.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【立程𧵑𪝬空靈活。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:1:42:text
msgid "@bookbot [I HAVE NOT BEEN TAMED.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【𪝬𣗓得純化。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:4:text
msgid "@niko There's this book I found back in the barrens area."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏卷冊尼𨉟尋𧡊外漨邊疆。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:5:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Since this is a place for books, would you happen to know what "
"it says?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 爲低𪜀𡊲貯冊、舅𣎏別伮𢪏之空"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:6:text
msgid "@bookbot [I DO NOT RECOGNIZE THIS LANGUAGE]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【𪝬空別言語尼】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:7:text
msgid "@bookbot [BUT THE SYMBOL ON THE COVER IS OF IMPORTANCE]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【雖然表象𨑗柀冊𣎏意義關重】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:9:text
msgid "@bookbot [THE HEAD LIBRARIAN, GEORGE, CAN EXPLAIN IT.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【守書觫𣎏体解釋。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:10:text
msgid "@bookbot [WOULD YOU LIKE ME TO CALL HER?]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【伴𣎏㦖𪝬噲姑𧘇空？】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:11:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Please don't."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 吀揨。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:16:text
#: Events:2:36:text
msgid "@bookbot [AUTHENTICATING BARCODE...]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【確寔碼㩇。。。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:17:text
#: Events:2:37:text
msgid "@bookbot [EXECUTING FACIAL RECOGNITION...]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【認面𣟂𩈘。。。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:18:text
msgid "@bookbot [PHOTO MATCH... \\. FAILED.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【檢查影。。。\\.空𨨤。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:19:text
msgid "@bookbot [IT SEEMS YOU DO NOT RESEMBLE THE OWNER OF THE CARD.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【𣎏𨤔伴空偅主隻𥮋尼。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:20:text
msgid "@bookbot [YOU CANNOT USE THIS CARD.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【伴空体用𥮋尼。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:21:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Bummer..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 黰實。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:25:text
msgid "@bookbot [INVALID CARD!]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【𥮋空合例！】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:26:text
msgid "@bookbot [PHOTO IS MISSING.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【空𣎏影。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:27:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...why did I do that."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。在哰𨉟徠𪵯勢𠰚。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:32:text
#: Events:2:40:text Events:2:61:text
msgid "@bookbot [HAVE A NICE DAY, MISS KIP.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【祝𣈜㵋卒令、姑喼。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:33:text
#: Events:2:62:text
msgid "@niko Yup, that's... totally me."
msgstr "@niko 董耒、昃𥗜妬𪜀。。。𨉟。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:38:text
msgid "@bookbot [PHOTO MATCH... \\. SUCCESSFUL]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【檢查影。。。\\.成功。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:39:text
msgid "@bookbot [YOU'RE GOOD TO GO!]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【伴得過！】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:41:text
#: sky/Elevator deck/button:3:22:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:44:text
#: sky/Apartments/Hall1/Room2 - peng/EV003:1:17:text Maps/Green/Ruins
#: In/Birdhall/alula npc:1:121:text Maps/Unused/pshot/EV001:1:14:text
#: Maps/Unused/pshot/EV001:1:21:text
msgid "@niko_what ..."
msgstr "@niko_what 。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:42:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...maybe I should've changed the name."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。當𫥨𨉟𢧚𢷮𠸜𨑗𥮋。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:51:text
msgid "@niko So I'm guessing you don't give out library cards?"
msgstr "@niko 丕𨉟斷舅空給𥮋書院嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:52:text
msgid "@bookbot [I ONLY HANDLE BOOK TRANSACTIONS.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【𪝬只管里役㨋吧摱冊。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:53:text
msgid "@bookbot [...FOR PEOPLE WHO ALREADY POSSESS CARDS.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【。。。朱仍𠊛㐌𣎏𠻿𥮋。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:54:text
#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Cabin/npc_silver:4:21:text
msgid "@niko Ah."
msgstr "@niko 啊。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:55:text
msgid ""
"@bookbot [TO ACQUIRE A CARD, YOU WOULD NEED TO CONTACT THE HEAD LIBRARIAN, "
"GEORGE.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【抵𣎏𥮋、伴沛連係守書觫。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:56:text
msgid "@bookbot [ALLOW ME TO CALL HER-"
msgstr "@bookbot 【𪝬吀法噲姑𧘇－】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:57:text
msgid "@niko_surprised Don't!!"
msgstr "@niko_surprised 揨！！！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:65:text
msgid ""
"@bookbot [THE HEAD LIBRARIAN, GEORGE, IS IN THE ARCHIVAL ROOM UPSTAIRS.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【守書觫𪵯役𥪝房留貯𨑗層。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:80:text
msgid "@niko Excuse me!"
msgstr "@niko 舅㗒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:81:text
msgid "@bookbot [OH. YOU ARE THE MESSIAH.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【溩。伴𪜀𠎬救世。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:82:text
msgid "@bookbot [WELCOME.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【吀嘲。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:83:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak When I first entered the city, a big robot told me to look for a "
"library on the surface!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 欺𨉟𠓨城庯吝頭、𠬠𠊛𣛠𡘯㐌指𨉟𠫾尋𠬠書院𨑗𩈘𡐙！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:84:text
msgid "@niko This is the same library, right?"
msgstr "@niko 低𪜀書院妬、沛空𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:85:text
msgid "@bookbot [AFFIRMATIVE.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【肯定。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:86:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh, goody!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 嗚、唁！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:87:text
msgid "@niko Well...we're here...what do we do now?"
msgstr "@niko 耒、衆些㐌𦤾低耒。。。𪵯之𣇞？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:88:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed The big robot only said there'd be clues here..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𠊛𣛠𡘯只吶𪜀𠱊𣎏萌䋦於低。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:89:text
msgid "@bookbot [THAT IS A QUESTION FOR THE HEAD LIBRARIAN, GEORGE.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【句𠳨𥯉𧶄朱守書觫。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:111:text
msgid "@niko_speak Is she...not here?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 姉𧘇。。。空𣎏𩈘哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:112:text
msgid "@bookbot [SHE IS HERE. SHE IS IN THE ARCHIVAL ROOM UPSTAIRS.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【姑𧘇𣎏於低。現姑𧘇當𥪝房留貯𨑗層。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:113:text
msgid ""
"@bookbot [WHEN SHE IS CONCENTRATING ON HER WORK, SHE WILL IGNORE ANY AND ALL "
"PHONECALLS.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【欺集中𪵯役、姑𧘇𠱊空認不其局噲鬧。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:114:text
msgid "@bookbot [...FOR SEVERAL DAYS.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【。。。𡗉𣈜連。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:115:text
msgid "@niko_what Yikes!"
msgstr "@niko_what 喂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:116:text
msgid "@niko Can you go get her in person, then?"
msgstr "@niko 丕舅𣎏体𠫾﨤姉𧘇空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:117:text
msgid "@bookbot [LEAVING THIS POST IS NOT IN MY PROGRAMMING.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【立程空朱法𪝬𨖨位置尼。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:118:text
msgid "@niko Then...can I go myself?"
msgstr "@niko 勢時。。。𨉟自𠫾得渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:119:text
msgid "@bookbot [OF COURSE.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【必然。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:120:text
msgid ""
"@bookbot [THE ARCHIVAL ROOM IS ACCESSIBLE THROUGH THE STAIRWELL BEHIND ME.]"
msgstr "@bookbot 【𣎏体𦤾房留貯憑橋簜𠌨𢖖󠄁𪝬。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:2:121:text
msgid "@niko_speak Gotcha, thanks!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 得耒、感恩唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:4:2:text
msgid "I guess that's why the library is always so packed."
msgstr "𪝬斷爲勢𢧚書院𣅶鬧拱𠑦𠊛。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:4:3:text
msgid "...and this is a slow day, mind you!"
msgstr "。。。𦓡𣋚尼㐌𪜀𣈜𠃣佟耒蒂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:4:6:text
msgid "The Author's books cover a wide range of topics."
msgstr "仍頭冊𧵑作者創世包含𡗉主題恪遶。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:4:7:text
msgid "It seems there are no subjects he does not write about."
msgstr "𣎏𨤔空𣎏門學鬧𪜀翁貯𢪏𧗱𪥘󠄁。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:4:8:text
msgid "Quite the renaissance man, don't you think?"
msgstr "果𪜀𠬠𡥵𠊛復興！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:4:9:text
msgid "@niko I guess so!"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟擬丕！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:4:10:text
msgid "But he's been focusing on documenting the world, as of late."
msgstr "扔近低翁集中𠓨𥱬劄𧗱世界。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:4:12:text
msgid "They say this city is the last bastion of civilization."
msgstr "𣱆吶城庯尼𪜀據点𡳳窮𧵑文明人類。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:4:13:text
msgid ""
"Soon, these books may be the only thing we have to remember the rest of the "
"world by."
msgstr "𣎏𨤰、衆些𢯛只哙仍卷冊尼抵代面朱份哙徠𧵑世界。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:2:text
msgid "@niko I haven't seen any superheroes in this world."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟貯𧡊超英雄鬧於低。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak Saw a lot of robots, though!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔㐌𧡊窒𡗉𠊛𣛠！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:4:text
msgid "Well, I guess robots are more plausible than superpowers..."
msgstr "時、𪝬擬𠊛𣛠時可施欣超能力。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:5:text
msgid "@niko True!"
msgstr "@niko 合理！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:8:text
msgid ""
"The Author publishes books at a highly accelerated, almost inhuman pace."
msgstr "作者創世出版冊貝速度𣈜𪨈增、近如超凡。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:9:text
msgid ""
"In fact, he has put out more books in one year than most authors do in a "
"lifetime."
msgstr "甚至、翁𧘇㐌出版𡗉冊𥪝𠬠𢆥欣𡗉作者𥪝𠁸局𠁀𧵑𣱆。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:10:text
msgid ""
"According to the head librarian, there is still a large amount of material "
"he has written, but not yet published."
msgstr "蹺守書、吻哙𠬠量𡘯材料翁㐌𢪏、扔𣗓出版。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:11:text
msgid ""
"One cannot help but to wonder where he can get so much done in so little "
"time."
msgstr "些只𣎏体𠺚𡂷憑格鬧翁𣎏体𪵯役𡗉𦤾如勢𥪝𠬠曠時間𠦯如丕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:12:text
msgid "I did the calculations, and the numbers simply do not add up."
msgstr "𪝬㐌併算、吧仍𡥵數單簡𪜀空合理。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:13:text
msgid "@niko Maybe he... \\.\\.\\@niko_speak can stop time?"
msgstr "@niko 別兜翁𧘇𣎏体。。。\\.\\.\\@niko_speak 仃時間時哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:14:text
msgid "No such mechanism exists in this world."
msgstr "機制妬空存在於低。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:15:text
msgid "...Is that actually possible in your home dimension?"
msgstr "。。。伮𣎏存在𥪝朝空間𧵑伴嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:16:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Nah, I just saw it in a movie once..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𪵯之𣎏、𨉟只𧡊伮𠬠吝𥪝眨催。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:5:17:text
msgid "@niko About... superheroes and stuff."
msgstr "@niko 眨𧗱。。。英雄、大類丕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:6:2:text
msgid "There's a couple of his books in this room that aren't occupied yet."
msgstr "𣎏𠬠𠄧卷冊𧵑翁𧘇𥪝房尼𣗓被埃占。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:6:3:text
msgid "Hurry before someone takes them!"
msgstr "𨘱𬨠𪢤𣎏𠊛𨪞𠅒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:6:6:text
msgid "So, what do you think about the Author?"
msgstr "丕時、伴擬之𧗱作者創世？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:6:7:text
msgid "@niko I... don't know?"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟。。。空昃？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:6:8:text
msgid "Have you read his stuff yet?"
msgstr "伴㐌讀冊𧵑翁𧘇𣗓？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Map Events:6:9:text
msgid "If not, you should!"
msgstr "裊𣗓、伴𢧚讀衆𬆄𠫾！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV052:1:3:text
msgid "@niko Same."
msgstr "@niko 𫫡。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV052:1:9:text
msgid "Yeah! The author doesn't only write books, he also illustrates them!"
msgstr "𫫡！作者空只𢪏冊、翁哙𦘧明畫𡛤！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV052:1:10:text
msgid "Sometimes he makes books out of only pictures."
msgstr "𣎏欺翁哙創作冊只全幀影。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV052:1:11:text
msgid "@niko Neat!"
msgstr "@niko 咍蒂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV054:1:2:text
msgid "Oh, and picture books, those too."
msgstr "啊、吧冊幀、𪥘󠄁衆𡛤。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV054:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak I like pictures!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟倜幀！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV054:1:6:text
msgid "The Author's latest books are really something, yeah?"
msgstr "冊㵋𧵑作者拱𫥨之蒂渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV054:1:7:text
msgid "The head librarian just released a bunch last week!"
msgstr "守書𣃣朱𫥨眜𠬠埬𬆄旬𠓀㫻！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV054:1:9:text
msgid "They're big compendiums, you'll see them if you look around."
msgstr "衆𪜀仍選集𣘊數、伴𠱊𧡊衆欺𠫾𨗺𨒺。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV054:1:10:text
msgid "Kinda different from his earlier works, though."
msgstr "扔衆可恪別𬧺貝仍工程𠓀𧵑翁。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV054:1:11:text
msgid "I'm used to reading his travel logs and novels, mostly."
msgstr "𪝬常慣讀仍日記遊歷吧小說𧵑翁𧘇欣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:2:text
msgid "Hopefully one day he'll show up!"
msgstr "懞哴𠬠𣈜翁𧘇𠱊出現！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:6:text
msgid "I mean, I don't think many people have ever seen him in person."
msgstr "意𪜀、𪝬空擬𣎏𠇍埃㐌曾﨤𩈘翁𧘇外𠁀。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:7:text
msgid "...or know what he looks like!"
msgstr "。。。或別翁𧘇矓如勢鬧！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:8:text
msgid "Everyone's heard OF him through secondhand accounts, though."
msgstr "扔𤗆𠊛調別𦤾翁𧘇過𠳒傳𠰘。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:9:text
msgid "...oh! But he did reply to my letter that one time!"
msgstr "。。。溩！扔𣎏𠬠吝翁𧘇㨋𠳒書𪝬𢪏！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:10:text
msgid "I got it framed immediately."
msgstr "𪝬㐌𫼳伮𠫾㨂椌𬆄吧㫻。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:15:text
msgid "Oh, hello! Do you need directions?"
msgstr "溩、吀嘲！伴𣎏懃引塘空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:16:text
msgid ""
"Let's see...this area here is mostly historical accounts, the reference "
"section is downstairs, and, uh..."
msgstr "䀡鬧。。。區尼份𡘯𪜀冊歷史、區冊參考於𨑜層、吧唹。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:17:text
msgid "I'm not sure where the children's section is... sorry!"
msgstr "𪝬空昃區冊少兒於兜。。。吀纇唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:18:text
msgid "@niko_speak That's ok! \\.\\.\\@niko I'm not really looking for books."
msgstr "@niko_speak 空哰！\\.\\.\\@niko 𨉟拱空尋冊。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:19:text
msgid "Oh! Are you here to... look for the Author, then?"
msgstr "溩！丕伴於低抵。。。尋作者創世庄？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:20:text
msgid "@niko ...no?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:21:text
msgid "Oh, that's good!"
msgstr "溩、卒耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:22:text
msgid "Er, I mean... that means you won't be disappointed!"
msgstr "唹、意𪜀。。。𠃣一伴𠱊空失望！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:23:text
msgid ""
"I've been volunteering here for months, and I've never seen him, not even "
"once!"
msgstr "𪝬㐌𪵯情願於低行𣎃𡗶、𦓡𪝬𣗓曾𧡊𩈘翁𧘇怞只𠬠吝！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:24:text
msgid ""
"He works together with the head librarian on publishing, so you'd think he "
"would at least show up once in a while..."
msgstr "翁𧘇𪵯役共守書𧗱問題出版、𢧚伴𠱊擬慃𠱊出現兜妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:25:text
msgid "@niko_speak But... he doesn't?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔。。。翁𧘇空哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:26:text
msgid "Yeah... he seems kiiinda reclusive."
msgstr "唹。。。慃𣎏𨤔可孤立。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:27:text
msgid "...which is weird for a guy who supposedly travels the world."
msgstr "。。。𬧺貝𠬠𠊛周遊世界。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/Whitney:1:28:text
msgid "Maybe it's just around people..."
msgstr "𣎏体𪜀慃礙𡥵𠊛。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV057:1:2:text
msgid ""
"...y'know, I've tried looking for the flying machine with my binoculars for "
"ages!"
msgstr "。。。別之空、𪝬㐌試尋飛行機憑䈵𥉰窒偻耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV057:1:3:text
msgid "Never saw such a thing, though..."
msgstr "扔𪝬𣗓曾實事𧡊伮。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV057:1:6:text
msgid "The Author is so cool!"
msgstr "作者創世湡實妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV057:1:7:text
msgid "I heard he can travel all over the world with a flying machine!"
msgstr "𦖑吶慃𧘇𣎏体𠫾泣世界憑飛行機𧵑𨉟！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV057:1:8:text
msgid "That's how he gathers material for his books."
msgstr "妬𪜀格翁𧘇收拾與料抵𢪏冊。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV057:1:9:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map Events:4:126:text
msgid "@niko_speak Wow!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫽿！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV065:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_huh He just glared at me."
msgstr "@niko_huh 英𧘇𣃣䁠𨉟。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV065:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I don't think we should bother him, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟擬𪜀空𢧚𪵯煩影𧘇兜\\p啊。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV065:1:7:text
msgid ".....WHAT??!?"
msgstr "。。。。。哰蒂？？！？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV065:1:8:text
msgid "@niko_huh Wh-\\.\\.\\@niko I didn't say anything."
msgstr "@niko_huh 嘑－\\.\\.\\@niko 㛪㐌吶之兜。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV065:1:9:text
msgid "Well stop staring at me then!"
msgstr "勢時揨𣎏𥆾𪝬𢲥𢲥𡛤！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV065:1:10:text
msgid "@niko_speak I was just looking at your book..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 㛪𥋴卷冊𧵑影催𦓡。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV065:1:11:text
msgid "Yes. You are in a library. There's books. In the library."
msgstr "董。伴當於𥪝𠬠書院。𣎏冊。𥪝書院。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/Lobby/EV065:1:13:text
msgid "...Go bug the chatty one upstairs."
msgstr "。。。𠫾𦓡撌𠀲𡗋𡀯𨑗層𠫾。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:11:text
msgid "@alula_pout ...Niko!"
msgstr "@alula_pout 。。。尼孤！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:12:text
#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula
msgid "@alula_oh Niko? What's wrong?"
msgstr "@alula_oh 尼孤？舅穩渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:13:text
#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:14:text
msgid "@calamus_shock You looked like you were about to faint!"
msgstr "@calamus_shock 矓如舅𢯛𤴥丕！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:19:text
msgid "@niko2 It's... not the first time it's happened."
msgstr "@niko2 寔𫥨。。。空沛吝頭𨉟被如丕。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:20:text
msgid "@calamus ...oh?"
msgstr "@calamus 。。。溩？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:22:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Earlier I was in the Barrens, and I...\\>\\n\\@niko6 saw "
"something like this too."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟𣃣於漨邊疆、吧𨉟。。。\\>\\n\\@niko6 拱𧡊𠬠次相似。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:23:text
msgid "@niko2 It was like a dream, but only for a split second..."
msgstr "@niko2 偅如𠬠𥋏𢠩、扔只𥪝祝𣋩催。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:24:text
msgid "@calamus ...sounds like a vision."
msgstr "@calamus 。。。𣎏𨤔𪜀啓像。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:25:text
msgid "@calamus_speak Like something a prophet would see!"
msgstr "@calamus_speak 矯如仍之𠬠茹先知𠱊𧡊丕！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:26:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 I... guess?\\n\\>\\@niko_eyeclosed The robot lady I was with earlier "
"had a fancy word for it, though..."
msgstr ""
"@niko2 昃。。。勢？\\n\\>\\@niko_eyeclosed 扔姉𠊛媄𣛠𣅶𠓀𣎏𠬠詞華美。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:28:text
#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:84:text
msgid "@niko2 Wait..."
msgstr "@niko2 寬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:30:text
msgid "@niko6 Lemme... check something."
msgstr "@niko6 抵𨉟。。。䀡丐尼發。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:45:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh!\\>\\nI was right!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！\\>\\n𨉟㐌董！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:46:text
msgid "@calamus ...huh?"
msgstr "@calamus 。。。嘑？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:51:text
msgid ""
"@niko When I had the vision back at the Barrens... the book started glowing "
"too!"
msgstr "@niko 欺𨉟𧡊幻影在漨邊疆。。。卷冊拱發𤏬勢尼！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:52:text
msgid "@niko2 I wanted to see if I could get it to happen again, and..."
msgstr "@niko2 𨉟定䀡伮𣎏侈𫥨徠空、吧。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:53:text
msgid "@alula_gasp Where did you get that!!!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 舅檢丐妬於兜丕！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:54:text
msgid ""
"@niko Oh, uh... \\>\\@niko_speak I had it with me when I woke up in this "
"world!"
msgstr "@niko 啊、唹。。。 \\>\\@niko_speak 𨉟𣎏伮欺醒𧻭𥪝世界尼！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:55:text
msgid "@alula_speak It looks like one of our friend's books!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 偅如𠬠卷冊伴衆𨉟𢪏！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:56:text
msgid "@alula ...Except it's glowy!"
msgstr "@alula 。。。扔伮發𤏬！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:57:text
msgid "@niko2 ...that's what the lady said too..."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。姉𠊛𣛠拱吶丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:58:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Hm..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 嘘。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:59:text
msgid ""
"@niko \\p... let's see if we can do anything with the journal in this room..."
msgstr "@niko \\p。。。抵䀡衆些𣎏体用捲日記𥪝間房尼空。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:3:1:text
msgid "@alula I wonder when our friend will come back..."
msgstr "@alula 空別包𣇞𠊛伴妬㵋𢮿徠。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:1:text
msgid "@alula_gasp Woah!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 𫽿！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:2:text
msgid "@calamus_shock How did that boat get there?"
msgstr "@calamus_shock 𪵯哰𡥵船妬𦤾低得丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:6:text
msgid "@niko Okay, I'm pretty sure it has to do with this journal, now..."
msgstr "@niko 嗚雞、𣇞時𨉟可昃伮連關𦤾卷日記尼。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:7:text
msgid "@niko2 The exact same thing happened back at the Barrens."
msgstr "@niko2 於漨邊疆拱依頡如丕。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:8:text
msgid "@calamus_speak Seriously?"
msgstr "@calamus_speak 實㫻？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:11:text
msgid "@niko The journal was glowing, so I wanted to take a closer look at it."
msgstr "@niko 卷日記發𤏬、𢧚𨉟㵋䀡察伮技欣。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:12:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 Then, I found a page that looked like a drawing of the room we were "
"in, and then..."
msgstr "@niko2 歱、𨉟𧡊𠬠張𣎏𠬠幅𦘧間房𨉟當𨅸𥪝、吧耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:13:text
msgid "@niko_speak A minecart showed up!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 自然𠬠隻車𡎡出現！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:14:text
msgid "@calamus_shock What!"
msgstr "@calamus_shock 實㫻！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:15:text
msgid "@alula_gasp What!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 實哰！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:16:text
msgid "@calamus_speak That sounds freaky..."
msgstr "@calamus_speak 𦖑怯實蒂。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:17:text
msgid "@alula_speak No it doesn't!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 兜𣎏！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:18:text
msgid "@alula_gasp \\p must've done something!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 𪳨𪜀由\\p㐌𪵯之妬！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:19:text
msgid "@calamus Still..."
msgstr "@calamus 扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:21:text
msgid "@alula_gasp ...Hey! We have a boat now!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 。。。尼！些𣎏船耒尼！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:22:text
msgid "@alula_speak We can go to the burial grounds and visit mom again!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 衆些徠𣎏体𦤾義莊探媄耒！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:23:text
msgid "@calamus But..."
msgstr "@calamus 扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:24:text
msgid "@alula_speak Come on, Calamus!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𠫾催英哥羅𡃙！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:25:text
msgid "@alula Niko and \\p are with us!"
msgstr "@alula 尼孤吧\\p扶護衆些！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:26:text
msgid ""
"@calamus Well... \\.\\.\\nif \\p made the boat appear... it should be safe..."
msgstr "@calamus 丕。。。\\.\\.\\n裊\\p造𫥨隻船。。。時昃𪜀𠱊穩催。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:4:27:text
msgid "@niko2 What...\\.\\. do you think, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko2 舅。。。\\.\\.擬哰、\\p？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:5:1:text
msgid "@alula_gasp Can we go yet?"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 衆些𠫾得𣗓？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/calamus npc:2:2:text
msgid "@calamus This passage must be where fireflies congregate..."
msgstr "@calamus 塘𡌢尼嘑𪳨沛𪜀坭炶炶集合。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/calamus npc:2:5:text
msgid "@calamus I wonder how long this passage is..."
msgstr "@calamus 空別伮𨱽𦤾兜𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/calamus npc:2:6:text
msgid "@calamus_speak Looks like there's some lights at the end..."
msgstr "@calamus_speak 𣎏𨤔𣎏𠬠𠄧暎𤏬於曲𡳳。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/calamus npc:2:7:text
msgid "@alula_speak Those are fireflies!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 炶炶妬！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/calamus npc:3:1:text
msgid "@calamus_smile We can leave whenever you're ready."
msgstr "@calamus_smile 衆些𣎏体起行欺㛪𠻿𠳹。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Ruins In/Courtyard/passage/get onto boat:2:2:text
msgid "@alula_gasp Here we go!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 𠫾鬧！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/right-3d
#: printers/EV005:1:2:text
msgid "$It may help you to go one color at a time!  -Management"
msgstr "$伴𣎏体試曾𦭷𠬠！  －班管理"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/right-3d
#: printers/EV006:1:2:text
msgid "$It can also help to write down previous attempts. -Management"
msgstr "$𥱬徠仍答案𠓀拱𣎏体𢴇益。 －班管理"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/right-3d
#: printers/EV008:1:2:text
msgid "$If all else fails, wait for the puzzle to reset."
msgstr "$裊悉𪥘󠄁調空得、唉䟻句賭撻徠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/right-3d
#: printers/EV008:1:3:text
msgid "$Maybe you'll get an easier one next time..."
msgstr "$𣎏体伴𠱊中𠬠句易欣。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/right-3d
#: printers/EV012:1:1:text 1/npc_randy:1:1:text
msgid "[BEEP BOOP]"
msgstr "【芣芣】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/right-3d
#: printers/EV012:1:2:text
msgid "[THIS IS THE PRINTER ROOM, WHERE MACHINE PARTS ARE MADE.]"
msgstr "【低𪜀房印印、坭各零件𣛠𢪮得製造。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/right-3d
#: printers/EV012:1:3:text
msgid "[ALSO, ROBOTS.]"
msgstr "【共各𠊛𣛠。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:1:text
msgid "@niko What should I do, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 𢧚𪵯之𣇞\\p？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:3:choice:0
msgid "Give her the sun"
msgstr "迻孤𧘇𩈘𡗶"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:3:choice:1
msgid "Don't"
msgstr "揨"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:7:text Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:52:text
msgid "@niko Here!"
msgstr "@niko 低！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:8:text
msgid "@maize .\\..\\..\\..\\..\\.."
msgstr "@maize 。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:9:text
msgid "@maize .......\\.warm..."
msgstr "@maize 。。。。。。\\.𤋾。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:10:text
msgid "@maize_smile1 I have... almost forgotten..."
msgstr "@maize_smile1 姉㐌。。。近如悁𠅒。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:11:text
msgid "@maize_smile1 It's so warm..."
msgstr "@maize_smile1 𤋾過。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:12:text
msgid "@niko That's... good, right?"
msgstr "@niko 如丕𪜀。。。卒、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:13:text
msgid "@maize_smile1 Th...the vines should be gone now..."
msgstr "@maize_smile1 仍絏蹽。。。調變𠅒𪥘󠄁耒。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:1:14:text In/Maize/maize:2:1:text
msgid "@maize_smile2 I'm not afraid anymore."
msgstr "@maize_smile2 姉空哙𢜝𡛤。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:2:2:text
msgid "@maize_smile2 Thank you..."
msgstr "@maize_smile2 感恩㛪。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:2:7:text
msgid "@alula_oh ...\\.\\.\\@alula_pout ..."
msgstr "@alula_oh 。。。\\.\\.\\@alula_pout 。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:2:8:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...Alula? You okay?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。阿瞜羅？舅穩渚？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:2:10:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...she just looked away."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。姉𧘇只𥋓𠫾。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:3:1:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 She's gone..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 姉𧘇變𠅒耒。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:3:2:text
msgid "@niko Oh... \\>\\nThere's something on the ground here."
msgstr "@niko 溩。。。\\>\\n𨑗𩈘𡐙𣎏𠬠物之妬。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:3:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak It looks like...a kernel of corn?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏𨤔𪜀。。。𠬠籺吳？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/maize:3:4:text
msgid "@niko She must've left it behind."
msgstr "@niko 𪳨𪜀由姉抵徠。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:2:text
msgid "@maize ...S...\\.\\.savior...?"
msgstr "@maize 。。。𠎬。。。\\.\\.𠎬救世？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:3:text
msgid "@maize I can't believe it...\\.\\.\\nYou're real..."
msgstr "@maize 空体信得。。。\\.\\.\\n𠎬𣎏實。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:4:text
msgid "@niko_shock ....miss?"
msgstr "@niko_shock 。。。姉？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:5:text
msgid "@niko_speak Are you... alright?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 姉𣎏。。。穩空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:6:text
msgid "@maize No...."
msgstr "@maize 空。。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:7:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak W-we should get you to the village! \\.\\.\\nMaybe they could-"
msgstr "@niko_speak 衆－衆些𢧚迻姉𧘇𧗱廊！\\.\\.\\n𣎏欺𣱆𣎏体－"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:8:text
msgid "@maize It's....okay...\\.\\nIt's okay.....\\.\\n...too late for me."
msgstr ""
"@maize 空。。。哰兜。。。\\.\\n空哰兜。。。。。\\.\\n。。。㐌過晚抵救姉耒。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:9:text
msgid "@niko_speak But..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:10:text
msgid "@maize ...the sun...."
msgstr "@maize 。。。𩈘𡗶。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:11:text
msgid "@maize I haven't seen it... I haven't felt it in so long..."
msgstr "@maize 姉㐌空𧡊伮。。。姉㐌空感認伮自窒哰偻耒。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:12:text
msgid ""
"@maize ...\\.\\.Savior, if it's not too much trouble...\\.\\.\\nCan you lend "
"me the sun for a while?"
msgstr ""
"@maize 。。。\\.\\.𠎬救世、裊空過煩。。。\\.\\.\\n㛪𣎏体朱姉摱𩈘𡗶𠬠𣅶渚？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:13:text
msgid "@niko I...\\.\\.\\@niko_speak Will it make you better?"
msgstr "@niko 㛪。。。\\.\\.\\@niko_speak 伮𠱊𢴇姉渚？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:14:text
msgid "@maize .\\..\\..\\.No.\\. It will not save me."
msgstr "@maize 。\\.。\\.。\\.空。\\.伮𠱊空救姉。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:15:text
msgid ""
"@maize I just want to experience the sun one more time before I... \\."
"\\.Well..."
msgstr "@maize 姉只㦖感認𩈘𡗶𠬠吝𡛤𠓀欺。。。\\.\\.㛪別蒂。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/map events:1:17:text
msgid "@maize Would it...\\.\\.\\nWould it be too selfish of me to ask?"
msgstr "@maize 料姉𣎏過。。。\\.\\.\\n貪婪空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:2:1:text
msgid "@niko2 It's the sun."
msgstr "@niko2 𪜀𩈘𡗶。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:2:2:text
msgid "@niko We're leaving it with her for now."
msgstr "@niko 衆些當暫抵姉𧘇𡨺伮。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:2:4:text
msgid "@alula_pout ...ah."
msgstr "@alula_pout 。。。啊。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:3:1:text
msgid "@niko_surprised T-\\.The light's gone out...!"
msgstr "@niko_surprised 暎－\\.暎𤏬𤎕𠅒耒！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:3:3:text
msgid "@niko_distressed \\p..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed \\p。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:3:4:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 Do you know... what happened?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 舅𣎏別。。。𡀯之㐌侈𫥨空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:3:13:text
msgid "@niko_speak You...\\.\\.\\@niko really?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 舅。。。。\\.\\.\\@niko 實哰？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:3:14:text
msgid "@niko_speak but...\\. but...\\.\\."
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔。。。\\.扔。。。\\.\\."

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:3:15:text
msgid "@niko_distressed Oh....."
msgstr "@niko_distressed 喂。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:3:16:text
msgid "@niko_distressed What am I gonna do?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed 𨉟沛𪵯之𣊾𣇞？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:4:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak It... \\. lit up again?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 伮。。。 \\. 𤏬徠耒尼？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Maize/lightbulb:4:4:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...phew."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。哺。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Forest DOTN USE THIS/Forest w/ bridges/EV004:1:1:text
#: Maps/Green/Forest/EV004:1:1:text
msgid "@calamus_unknown Alula?\\>\\nAlula? Where did you go?"
msgstr "@calamus_unknown 阿瞜羅？\\>\\n阿瞜羅？㛪兜耒？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Forest DOTN USE THIS/Forest w/ bridges/EV004:1:2:text
#: Maps/Green/Forest/EV004:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak \\p, did you hear that?"
msgstr "@niko_speak \\p、舅𦖑𧡊渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Forest DOTN USE THIS/Forest w/ bridges/EV004:1:3:text
#: Maps/Green/Forest/EV004:1:3:text
msgid "@calamus_unknown Alula!"
msgstr "@calamus_unknown 阿瞜羅！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Forest DOTN USE THIS/Forest w/ bridges/EV004:1:4:text
#: Maps/Green/Forest/EV004:1:4:text
msgid "@niko I think it's coming from south-east of here."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𪜀自向東南。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Forest DOTN USE THIS/Forest w/ bridges/robot
#: standing:1:1:text Maps/Green/Forest/robot THIS/robot
msgid "[WATER SAMPLE COLLECTION IN PROGRESS...]"
msgstr "【當進行𥙩母渃。。。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Forest DOTN USE THIS/Forest w/ bridges/worried
#: npc:1:1:text
msgid "The bridge to the forest was just restored..."
msgstr "𣘃橋𠓨棱𣃣得恢復。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Forest DOTN USE THIS/Forest w/ bridges/worried
#: npc:1:2:text
msgid "The village evacuees should be able to find better fishing spots here."
msgstr "仍移民自廊𣎏体尋各𡊲鉤個卒欣於低。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Forest DOTN USE THIS/Forest w/ bridges/worried
#: npc:1:4:text
msgid "The plant spirit is really looking out for us, isn't she?"
msgstr "靈魂𧵑𣘃樻當扶護衆些、沛空𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Forest DOTN USE THIS/Forest w/ bridges/worried
#: npc:1:5:text
msgid "@niko_upset2 ...yeah."
msgstr "@niko_upset2 。。。唹。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak So...\\.\\. we're filling up the syringe, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 丕𪜀。。。\\.\\. 衆些𠱊唿𣹓䈵尖哰、\\p？"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:4:text
msgid "@niko I guess it's kind of like a funnel..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔伮偅𠬠丐瓿。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:5:text
msgid "@niko But the liquid might be a bit too thick to fit in the needle..."
msgstr "@niko 扔質𣿅𣎏体過特抵針尖唿。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:7:text
msgid "@niko Hey, it actually went in!"
msgstr "@niko 嗚、伮𨄺得耒尼！"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:8:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Gross."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㕭。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:16:text
#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:31:text
msgid "@niko You want me to fill the bottle with this stuff, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 舅㦖𨉟𢭰𣹓丐尼𠓨𥑂哰、\\p？"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:18:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed It's too goopy to fit in the bottle opening..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 伮過𣻂抵𢯰過𠰘𥑂。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:19:text
msgid ""
"@niko It's like that one time years ago when I tried to put tomato chowder "
"in a baby bottle..."
msgstr "@niko 偅如丐吝𨉟試朱𥹙茄䣷𠓨𥑂㛪𡮣。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:20:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...and then it got everywhere!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。歱伮𢏑泣坭㫻！"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:21:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed On the table, on my clothes, on the baby, on the baby's "
"clothes..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𬨠盤、𬨠襖𨉟、𬨠㛪𡮣、𬨠群襖㛪𡮣。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:22:text
msgid ""
"@niko The grown-ups thought it was hilarious.\\> \\@niko_eyeclosed They took "
"a bunch of pictures."
msgstr "@niko 各姑注擬伮窒𢞂唭。\\> \\@niko_eyeclosed 歱𣱆𠌷包饒𪜀影。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:23:text
msgid "@niko_speak And then they taught me how to use funnels!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 耒𣱆指𨉟格用瓿！"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:24:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed And then they also told me I shouldn't try to babysit until "
"I'm older."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 吧𣱆拱勸𨉟空𢧚矓𥘷朱𦤾欺𨉟𨁥𡘯。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:25:text
msgid "@niko ...anyway we should probably look for a funnel or something!"
msgstr "@niko 。。。怞哰時衆些拱𢧚尋𠬠丐瓿咍之妬！"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:32:text
msgid "@niko Alright... lemme just take out the cork, and..."
msgstr "@niko 得耒、抵𨉟𢱨𢲫鈕、吧。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:34:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...all the smoke escaped."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。氣脫𫥨歇耒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:41:text
msgid "@niko_speak There's already some of this stuff in the bottle, \\p!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟㐌𣎏𠻿質妬𥪝𥑂耒、\\p！"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:45:text
msgid "@niko This pond sure looks different..."
msgstr "@niko 丐湖尼唏異常實。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:46:text
msgid "@niko The water looks like... jelly?"
msgstr "@niko 𩈘渃矓偅。。。𦚈？"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/!specialpool:1:47:text
msgid "@niko It's formed a bubble over the surface of the pond."
msgstr "@niko 伮㐌浽成琫琫包𥙩𩈘湖。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/small vent:1:3:text vent:1:18:text
msgid "@niko I guess you want me to fill the bottle with this gas, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟擬舅㦖𨉟泵𣹓氣𠓨𥑂尼嘑\\p？"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/small vent:1:6:text
msgid "@niko That oughta do it."
msgstr "@niko 勢昃𪜀得耒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/small vent:1:13:text
msgid "@niko This bottle is already full of this smoke!"
msgstr "@niko 𥑂㐌𣹓氣𠻿耒！"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/small vent:1:19:text
msgid "@niko Alright lemme just ...\\> turn this bottle upside down..."
msgstr "@niko 得耒抵𨉟。。。\\> 𪵅逆丐𥑂。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/small vent:1:21:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...aaaaand there goes the pond water."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。吧渃湖㐌㵢𠫾歇。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/small vent:1:22:text
msgid "@niko But at least we have this smoke..."
msgstr "@niko 扔𠃣𫥨衆些哙量氣尼。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/small vent:1:28:text
msgid "@niko_speak This vent is on the ground!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𡓇脫氣尼於𨑜𩈘𡐙！"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/small vent:1:29:text
msgid "@niko All the others are taller than me."
msgstr "@niko 悉𪥘󠄁仍丐恪調高欣𨉟。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV047:1:1:text
msgid "[THE SKY IS DARK.]"
msgstr "【匏𡗶黰桀。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV047:1:2:text
msgid "@niko That it is."
msgstr "@niko 果𪜀丕。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV047:1:3:text
msgid "[DO YOU KNOW WHEN THE SUN WILL BE BACK UP?]"
msgstr "【伴𣎏別包𣇞𩈘𡗶𠱊𠚐𠭤徠空？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV047:1:4:text
msgid "@niko_speak We're working on it!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 衆𨉟當故𠡚！"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV339:1:1:text
msgid ""
"$Initially, the amount of noxious fumes emitted by the natural gas vents "
"caught our team off-guard."
msgstr "$班頭、量氣毒害捨𫥨自各𡓇脫氣自然㐌遣隊𧵑𪝬不㘈。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV339:1:2:text
msgid "$Thank goodness the medical team reacted as quickly as they did."
msgstr "$𢆪𪜀隊醫濟㐌反應及時。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV339:1:4:text
msgid ""
"$Despite its failure, that first expedition did bring up some interesting "
"observations about the Barrens."
msgstr "$怞失敗、局考察吝頭㐌𫼳徠𡗉結果趣味𧗱漨邊疆。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV339:1:5:text
msgid "$We found that there's not one, but two such vent zones."
msgstr "$衆𪝬認𫥨𣎏空只𠬠、 𦓡𪜀𠄩漨脫氣如丕。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV339:1:7:text
msgid "$With fumes being pumped out at such high concentrations..."
msgstr "$喟濃渡氣汰高𦤾丕。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV339:1:8:text
msgid "$...it seems a miracle that the gas hasn't spread anywhere else."
msgstr "$。。。役仍氣尼𣗓攔𫥨𩵜𩹭漨恪想如𪜀法𦭷。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV339:1:10:text
msgid ""
"$Our biologists concluded that the phosphor shrimp in the crater pools were "
"actively consuming the gas."
msgstr "$各茹生學𧵑衆𪝬結論哴𩵽光素𥪝各𣷭渃當積極銷售氣𪵤尼。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV339:1:11:text
msgid ""
"$The shrimp in the ocean also prevent the gas from wafting off into the Glen."
msgstr "$𩵽𥪝㴜拱拫空朱氣𪵤攔𦤾漨潭浰。"

#: Maps/Blue/Swamp/EV339:1:13:text
msgid "$If that's the case, then we owe a lot to these little guys!"
msgstr "$裊董𪜀如丕、衆些實事𧴱衆窒𡗉蒂！"

#: Maps/Green/Gate/Bed room/EV003:2:2:text Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/Bed
#: Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/map event:1:2:text
msgid "@niko I'm not sleepy anymore."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟歇𢞂𥄬耒。"

#: Maps/Green/Gate/Bed room/EV003:2:8:text Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/Bed
#: room/EV003:2:12:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I can't sleep now, \\p!\\>\\n\\@niko I need to get Alula to her "
"brother first."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣊾𣇞𨉟空𥄬得兜\\p！\\>\\n\\@niko 𨉟沛迻阿瞜羅𧗱喟英𠓀㐌。"

#: Maps/Green/Gate/Bed room/EV003:2:15:text Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/guest room/EV003:2:13:text sky/Tower
#: deck/EV009:2:7:text Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/Bed room/EV003:2:21:text
#: sky/Elevator deck/sleepville/Map events:1:12:text RED SKY/Elevator
#: events:1:8:text Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/map event:1:15:text
#: sky/Office/stairwell/locked events:3:11:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'm a little tired from walking."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟唏痗𢖖󠄁氣𠫾徠。"

#: Maps/Green/Gate/Bed room/EV003:2:16:text Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/guest room/EV003:2:14:text sky/Tower
#: deck/EV009:2:8:text Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/Bed room/EV003:2:22:text
#: sky/Elevator deck/sleepville/Map events:1:13:text RED SKY/Elevator
#: events:1:9:text Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/map event:1:16:text
#: sky/Office/stairwell/locked events:3:12:text
msgid "@niko_speak Is it alright if I take a nap?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟𣎏体𥊝眜子得渚？"

#: Maps/Green/Gate/Bed room/EV003:2:78:text Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/guest room/EV003:2:75:text sky/Tower
#: deck/EV009:2:69:text Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/Bed room/EV003:2:84:text
#: sky/Elevator deck/sleepville/Map events:1:74:text RED SKY/Elevator
#: events:1:70:text Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/map event:1:60:text
#: sky/Office/stairwell/locked events:3:74:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Ah, well... \\>\\n\\@niko I suppose there's more work to do."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 係、丕時。。。 \\>\\n\\@niko 昃𪜀𨉟哙役沛𪵯。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:16:text
msgid "@alula_gasp You saved me!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 舅㐌救𨉟！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:17:text
msgid "@alula Thank you!"
msgstr "@alula 感恩舅！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:18:text
msgid "@alula I was trapped in there for so long..."
msgstr "@alula 空別𨉟㐌搩𥪝妬包偻𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:19:text
msgid "@niko So are you Alula?"
msgstr "@niko 丕舅𪜀阿瞜羅哰？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:20:text
msgid "@alula_gasp ..."
msgstr "@alula_gasp 。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:21:text
msgid "@alula_gasp You... knew my name?"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 舅。。。別𠸜𨉟哰？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:22:text
msgid "@alula_speak Wow! The messiah really does know everything!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𫽿！果然𠎬救世別歇𤗆次！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:23:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Actually...\\.\\. \\@niko_speak I just met your brother "
"earlier."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 寔𫥨。。。\\.\\. \\@niko_speak 𨉟𣃣﨤英舅。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:24:text
msgid "@alula_oh Oh, right!"
msgstr "@alula_oh 溩、董耒！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:25:text
msgid "@alula_pout Gosh... Calamus must be so worried..."
msgstr "@alula_pout 係。。。哥羅𡃙昃當𢥈焠𨀒。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:3:26:text
msgid "@alula Can you bring me to him?"
msgstr "@alula 舅𣎏体迻𨉟𦤾𡊲英𧘇得渚？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:3:text
msgid ""
"@niko Wait a minute...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak How did you know that I was the,"
"\\. um,\\. messiah?\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed I don't have the sun with me..."
msgstr ""
"@niko 寬㐌。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 𪵯哰舅別𨉟𪜀、\\.唹、\\.𠎬救世丕？"
"\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟𣎏當𫼳蹺𩈘𡗶兜𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:4:text
msgid "@alula Your eyes!"
msgstr "@alula 𪜀對眜舅妬！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:6:text
msgid "@alula_speak They reminded me of the sun!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 衆𪵯𨉟擬𦤾𩈘𡗶！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:8:text
msgid "@alula That's why you're our messiah, right?"
msgstr "@alula 丕𢧚舅㵋𪜀𠎬救世、沛空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:9:text
msgid ""
"@niko Well...\\. I... \\>\\n\\@niko_speak A lot of people back in my home "
"world have eyes like mine..."
msgstr ""
"@niko 時。。。\\.𨉟。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 窒𡗉𠊛自世界𧵑𨉟拱𣎏眜偅勢"
"尼。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:10:text
msgid "@alula_pout Home... world?"
msgstr "@alula_pout 世界。。。𧵑舅哰？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:11:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Yeah! \\>\\@niko I'm actually from another world, you see!"
"\\>\\nIt's a place where the sun is in the sky and not in a Tower."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 𫫡！\\>\\@niko 舅𧡊蒂、寔𫥨𨉟𦤾自𠬠世界恪！\\>\\n於妬𩈘𡗶空於𥪝𠬠"
"座塔𦓡於𨑗𡗶。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:12:text
msgid "@alula Do you like this world too?"
msgstr "@alula 舅拱適世界尼渚？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:13:text
msgid "@niko I...\\>\\@niko_speak Yeah."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟。。。\\>\\@niko_speak 𣎏。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:14:text
msgid ""
"@alula_speak Yay!\\>\\n\\@alula_pout Calamus keeps saying how this world is "
"getting more dangerous by the minute."
msgstr ""
"@alula_speak 𢜏過！\\>\\n\\@alula_pout 哥羅𡃙據吶哴世界尼當危險欣曾𤼵𠬠。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:15:text
msgid ""
"@alula_speak But that's ok! You're here now!\\>\\n\\@alula You can make "
"everything better!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 扔空哰！舅㐌於低耒！\\>\\n\\@alula 舅𣎏体𪵯𤗆次卒欣！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/alula:5:16:text Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory
#: Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:62:text room/Kip/first meeting:1:13:text
msgid "@niko Yeah..."
msgstr "@niko 唹。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/map events:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_speak W-What in the world is this thing in the doorway?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 丐－丐𤠲之於𥪝行廊丕？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/map events:1:2:text
msgid ""
"@niko It reminds me of what I saw a while ago, at the cliffs...\\nFor some "
"reason, I'm afraid to touch it."
msgstr "@niko 伮𪵯𨉟𢖵𦤾仍之𨉟㐌𧡊於壁𥒥、𣅶𠓀。。。\\n空曉哰𨉟窒𢜝動沛伮。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Alula/map events:2:1:text
msgid "@alula_oh Hey! Where are you going?"
msgstr "@alula_oh 尼！舅𠫾兜丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:37:text
#: HERE:1:46:text HERE:1:66:text RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map
#: events:4:19:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:3:384:text
#: room/backroom/backhall/collapse/EV004:1:10:text
#: room/backroom/backhall/collapse/EV008:1:10:text
#: room/backroom/backhall/collapse/EV009:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_upset2 ..."
msgstr "@niko_upset2 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:47:text
msgid "@niko_upset2 I... think I remember something..."
msgstr "@niko_upset2 𨉟。。。擬𨉟𢖵哴。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:48:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I remember... what I did at the end."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟𢖵。。。𨉟㐌𪵯之𡳳窮。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:50:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I remember... putting in the sun..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟㐌。。。撻𩈘𡗶𠓨。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:51:text
msgid "@niko3 And then everything got really bright..."
msgstr "@niko3 吧𤗆次𤏬𤆷𬨠。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:54:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I... remember being in a dark room."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟𢖵。。。𨉟於𥪝𠬠間房𣋁。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:55:text
msgid "@niko3 There was a light at the end of a long hallway..."
msgstr "@niko3 𣎏𠬠暎𤏬於𡳳行廊𨱽。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:56:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I thought I was going back home, but..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟想𨉟𢯛𠭤𧗱茹、扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:59:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I... \\.\\.don't remember a lot of the details."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟。。。\\.\\.空𢖵𤑟𡗋。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:61:text RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:31:text
#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:3:221:text
#: room/backroom/backhall/collapse/EV008:1:17:text
#: room/backroom/backhall/collapse/EV008:1:21:text
msgid "@niko_upset ..."
msgstr "@niko_upset 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:63:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 ...But none of it matters now, does it?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 。。。怞哰時拱空關重𡛤、𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:65:text
msgid "@niko_upset I just got brought back anyway...."
msgstr "@niko_upset 怞哰時𨉟吻被召𧗱。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/NIKO STARTS HERE:1:67:text
#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/backhall/collapse/EV004:1:4:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ....."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/mines exit/EV007:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed We can't go back now, \\p."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 衆些空体𢮿徠𡛤兜、\\p。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Top floor/Map Events:1:3:text
msgid "@niko The door is locked from the inside."
msgstr "@niko 𨷶被銙債自邊𥪝。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:4:text
#: room/npc_mechanic:1:21:text
msgid "[I AM THE POWER ROOM MECHANIC.]"
msgstr "【𪝬𪜀技師房給電。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:5:text
#: room/npc_mechanic:1:22:text
msgid "[DO YOU HAVE AN ISSUE TO REPORT?]"
msgstr "【伴𣎏問題之懃報告空？】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:6:text
msgid "@niko Do you know anything about an elevator code?"
msgstr "@niko 伴𣎏別之𧗱碼簜𣛠空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:9:text
msgid "[ELEVATOR CODE...]"
msgstr "【碼簜𣛠。。。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:10:text
msgid "[COMMAND NOT RECOGNIZED]"
msgstr "【令空存在】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:11:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Well, worth a shot."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 怞哰時拱𢧚試𠬠吝。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:23:text
msgid "@niko Yeah, actually..."
msgstr "@niko 唹、寔𫥨。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:24:text
msgid "@niko_speak The surface access elevator appears to be broken!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏𨤔簜𣛠𬺗𩈘𡐙被閧耒！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:25:text
msgid "@niko There's a button missing, and..."
msgstr "@niko 簜𣛠被𠅒𠬠鈕、吧。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:26:text
msgid "@niko_speak Can you go take a look?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 舅𠫾檢查得渚？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:27:text
#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV009:1:4:text
msgid "[...]"
msgstr "【。。。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:28:text
msgid "[LEAVING THIS ROOM IS NOT IN MY PROGRAMMING.]"
msgstr "【𪝬空得立程抵𨖨房尼。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:29:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Ah, nevermind..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 啊、空哰兜。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:36:text
msgid "[I AM ONLY ABLE TO FIX ISSUES IN THIS BUILDING.]"
msgstr "【𪝬只𣎏体𢯢𢵻各問題𥪝座茹尼。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:37:text
msgid "[SORRY FOR THE INCONVENIENCE.]"
msgstr "【吀纇爲事不便尼。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/npc_mechanic:1:38:text
msgid "@niko It's okay..."
msgstr "@niko 空哰兜。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/computer:1:1:text Maps/POSTGAME
#: RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry
msgid "@niko Some kind of computer terminal..."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𣛠入令之妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/tape:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A tape dispenser."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𣛠𠰹繃頴。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/tape:1:4:text
msgid "@niko Oh, of course! I gotta tape it together or it might fall apart."
msgstr "@niko 溩、董耒！𨉟沛繃伮徠𪢤伮𨮇歇𪥘󠄁𫥨。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/tape:1:14:text
msgid "@niko Oh, I could hold it together with tape."
msgstr "@niko 溩、𨉟𣎏体𡨺𬘋衆徠憑繃頴。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/tape:1:15:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I should've done this in the first place..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 當𫥨𨉟沛𪵯勢尼自頭。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/tape:1:23:text
msgid ""
"@niko If I cut off a piece of tape to keep it would just lose its stickiness."
msgstr "@niko 裊𨉟𥙩𠬠斷時伮𠱊歇頴𠅒。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/tape:1:27:text
#: room/stapler:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's bolted to the table..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 伮被㨂釘𠓨盤。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/stapler:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A stapler."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠隻𡏽捦。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/EV008:1:2:text
msgid "$They are just bolted so people won't steal them."
msgstr "$𪝬只㨂釘衆抵防𠅒𢲩催。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/Power room/EV008:1:3:text
msgid "$Feel free to use, though!"
msgstr "$據用𢗷㜥唲！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:5:text
msgid "@ed [By the way, the effect is temporary.]"
msgstr "@ed 【因便、效應只𪜀暫時催。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:6:text
msgid "@ed [It will be gone once you no longer need it.]"
msgstr "@ed 【伮𠱊變𠅒氣伴空哙懃伮𡛤。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:11:text
msgid "@ed [Still haven't figured it out?]"
msgstr "@ed 【𣗓擬𫥨哰？】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:12:text
msgid "@ed [...you remember the document, correct?]"
msgstr "@ed 【伴𢖵𣜿材料、沛空？】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:13:text
msgid "@ed [This time it's even more obvious.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𣊾𣇞伮哙易尋欣。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:14:text
msgid ""
"@ed [What's the most \\c[2]easily accessible\\c[0] place on your machine?]"
msgstr "@ed 【坭\\c[2]易𦤾一\\c[0]𨑗𣛠伴𪜀坭鬧？】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:25:text
msgid "@ed [Hello again, \\p.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𠬠吝𡛤、吀嘲\\p。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:26:text
msgid "@ed [It seems I need to help you again.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𣎏𨤔𪝬徠沛𢴇伴耒。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:27:text
msgid "@ed [Niko will not be able to progress otherwise.]"
msgstr "@ed 【裊空尼孤𠱊空体接續。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:28:text
msgid ""
"@ed [This time, the information you need has fallen to the most easily "
"accessible place on your machine.]"
msgstr "@ed 【吝尼、通信伴懃㐌淶𠓨坭易𧡊一𨑗𣛠伴。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:28:condition
msgid "Do you see it?"
msgstr "伴𣎏𧡊伮空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:30:text
msgid "@ed [You'll know what to do with it, then.]"
msgstr "@ed 丕伴𠱊別沛𪵯之喟伮。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:33:text
msgid ""
"@ed [I know you're not exactly that bright for a god, \\p, but this "
"shouldn't be difficult.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𪝬別伴𪜀𠬠位神唏少聰明、\\p啊、扔寔事空𠸋兜。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:1:34:text
msgid "@ed [Just poke around a bit. It really isn't hard to miss.]"
msgstr "@ed 【只懃𥆾𥄭衆𨒺𠬠𡭧催。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:2:4:text
msgid "@ed [...This...]"
msgstr "@ed 【。。。丐尼。。。】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:2:5:text
msgid "@ed [How did you already know the answer?]"
msgstr "@ed 【𪵯哰伴𣎏体別𠓀答案？】"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Computer Room/pc:2:6:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost
#: interior/pc:2:29:text Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/pc:2:9:text
