msgid "[CHECKING...CHECKING...]"
msgstr "【當檢查。。。當檢查。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/EV003:1:2:text
msgid "[TERMINAL DOES NOT RESPOND.]"
msgstr "【𣛠入令空返回。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/EV003:1:3:text
msgid "[THIS IS A PROBLEM.]"
msgstr "【衆些𣎏問題。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/EV005:1:1:text
msgid "[ALL OF THESE TERMINALS DO NOT BOOT.]"
msgstr "【全部仍𣛠入令尼調空起動得。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/EV005:1:2:text
msgid "[I AM NOT SURE WHAT TO DO NOW.]"
msgstr "【𪝬空別沛𪵯之。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/EV006:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Some of the ink on this page is faded."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠份墨印𨑗張紙尼野㗑。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/EV006:1:2:text
msgid "$-likely due some sort of electrical or magnetic interference."
msgstr "$－可能由擾動電磁。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/EV006:1:3:text
msgid ""
"$I'm afraid this operation can no longer be sustained, if the servers "
"continue to fail so much that maintenance cannot keep up the pace."
msgstr "$𪝬𢥈礙空体接續活動、裊𣛠主﨤纇𡗉𦤾𣞪隊保持空体蹺及。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/EV006:1:5:text
msgid "$Fortunately, it does not seem to be happening to the robots."
msgstr "$𢆪𠼷、𣎏𨤔𠊛𣛠空被作動。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/EV006:1:6:text
msgid "$At least, not at a significant rate."
msgstr "$𠃣一、空被作動過𡗉。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/EV006:1:7:text
msgid "$Time will tell."
msgstr "$衆些共䟻䀡。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/server room/map events:1:1:text
msgid "@niko I'm pretty sure these are computers, now..."
msgstr "@niko 可昃低調𪜀𣛠併、𫽿。。。"

