msgid "[Are You. An Intruder?]"
msgstr "【𤾰。𣎏沛仉突入空？】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall1/Room1 - bot/npc_protectbot:1:3:text
msgid ""
"[Because If You Are... I, Model 8-XM Home Security Bot (TM) Serial Number "
"39232B839W4, Will Have To Report You.]"
