msgstr "@proto2 【哰自凌㛪𠳨丕？】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:13:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 Well, I'm gonna leave soon, so I just wanted to ask one more question!"
msgstr "@niko2 時、㛪𢯛𠫾耒、𢧚㛪㦖𠳨𠬠句妬𡛤催！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:14:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed There aren't many robots in my home world..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 於世界𧵑㛪空𣎏𡗉𠊛𣛠𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:15:text
msgid "@proto2 [Ah.]"
msgstr "@proto2 【啊。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:16:text
msgid "@proto2b [It's... nice.]"
msgstr "@proto2b 【可。。。得。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:17:text
msgid "@cedric_smile I suppose it's alright!"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 英擬𪜀穩妬！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:18:text
msgid "@rue_smile Haha, that's a tough question, Niko!"
msgstr "@rue_smile 哬哬、尼孤𠳨𠸋妬！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:19:text
msgid "@rue_smile I mean...\\.\\.do you like being a person?"
msgstr "@rue_smile 𧘇姉𪜀。。。\\.\\.㛪𣎏適𪵯𠊛空？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:20:text
