msgstr "@rue_smile 空𣎏之兜！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:31:text
msgid ""
"@proto2 [...In the end, the World Machine was starting to create its own "
"code.]"
msgstr "@proto2 【𡳳共時、𣛠全世㐌自造碼朱正𨉟。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:32:text
msgid ""
"@proto1c [Going above and beyond its programming, not as the result of "
"error, but as a conscious choice on the part of the machine...]"
msgstr "@proto1c 【越𫥨𠺌仍之㐌得立程𠻿、空沛由纇、𦓡由鈷𣛠自決定。。。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:33:text
msgid "@proto1b [...Being able to generate its own path forward.]"
msgstr "@proto1b 【。。。自𢪏接句𡀯𧵑正伮。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:34:text
msgid "@proto2b [That's...\\.\\. what being tamed is all about.]"
msgstr "@proto2b 【妬。。。\\.\\.正𪜀本質𧵑純化。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV064:1:35:text
msgid "@cedric_smile I couldn't have said it better myself."
msgstr "@cedric_smile 英拱空体演達卒欣勢。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV065:1:2:text
