msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 怞哰時。。。衆㛪拱㐌𧶄可𡗉時間於低。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV069:1:15:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 Both of us...\\.\\. never really stopped believing in this world."
msgstr "@niko2 𪥘󠄁𠄩衆㛪。。。\\.\\.貯包𣇞凝信𠓨世界尼。"

