"@niko_eyeclosed The World Machine just needed to realize that, I guess..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𢧚𣛠全世只懃認𫥨條妬催。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV069:1:17:text
msgid "@rue That... \\>\\@rue_talk Sounds like a possibility..."
