msgstr "@plight_shock 𪜀㛪！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV070:1:6:text
msgid "@plight_sigh Glad to see you in one piece..."
msgstr "@plight_sigh 實𢜏欺𧡊㛪吻哙原捖。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV070:1:7:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Glad to see you're ok, too!\\>\\n\\@niko5 After the whole "
"elevator thing."
msgstr "@niko_speak 㛪拱𢜏欺英穩！\\>\\n\\@niko5 𢖖󠄁仍之侈𫥨𥪝簜𣛠。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV070:1:8:text
msgid ""
"@plight_worry That was uh...\\>\\nThat was the most awkward elevator ride "
"I've been through."
msgstr "@plight_worry 妬𪜀。。。\\>\\n妬𪜀轉𠫾簜𣛠𠸋寫一𠁀英。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV070:1:9:text
msgid ""
"@plight_why ...and by \"awkward\" I mean terrible bad awful the absolute "
"worst."
msgstr "@plight_why 。。。「𠸋寫」義𪜀超無窮弊害𦤾癲𪥘󠄁𠊛𧘇。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV070:1:11:text
msgid "@plight_worry The squares like, started leaking into the room, right?"
msgstr "@plight_worry 塊𣃱扒頭𣼼𠓨房尼。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV070:1:12:text
msgid "@plight_worry2 And I was trapped like a rat."
msgstr "@plight_worry2 吧英被抪𥪝𧣳如𤝞𡥌。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV070:1:13:text
msgid "@plight_worry And they just kept filling in the room faster, right..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 吧衆據𣼼𠓨𪨈𣅶𪨈𨘱。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV070:1:14:text Maps/Red sky/Elevator
#: deck/npc_plight:5:18:text deck/button:4:18:text
msgid "@plight_worry ..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV070:1:15:text
msgid "@plight_wtf ...AM I DEAD!?"
msgstr "@plight_wtf 。。。英𤻒耒嘑！？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Credits/EV070:1:17:text Maps/FINALE/Credits/map events:5:23:text
msgid "@niko_speak No no, you're fine!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 空空、英穩𦓡！"

