#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/backhall/protowalk/EV011:1:52:text
msgid ""
"@proto1C [When you're in the city, go find someone named Cedric. Give him "
"the disk.]"
msgstr "@proto1C 【欺㛪𠓨成庯、唉尋𠬠𠊛𠸜𪜀察嚦吧迻𥐨尼朱英𧘇。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/backhall/protowalk/EV011:1:53:text
