#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV031:1:2:text
msgid "$Hey sweetie,"
msgstr "$寄𡥵㤇、"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV031:1:3:text
msgid "$Six more weeks until you can come home!"
msgstr "$哙𦒹旬𡛤𪜀𡥵得𧗱茹耒！"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV031:1:4:text
msgid "$'bout time, huh?"
msgstr "$拱𦤾𣅶耒𠰚？"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV031:1:6:text
msgid ""
"$Gosh, I can't imagine living in that awful capsule wall...dorm... thing!"
msgstr "$𡗶吖、媄空体想像浽𤯩𥪝丐茹。。。奇宿。。。𡥵蛹妬！"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV031:1:7:text
msgid ""
"$But guess what? Soon you'll get to sleep in a real bed and eat real food "
"again!"
msgstr "$別之空？𡥵𢯛得𥄬𨑗床實吧咹𣘊咹實𠭤徠耒妬！"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV031:1:9:text
msgid "$Write back soon!"
msgstr "$𢪏徠𣋽唲！"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV031:1:10:text
msgid "$\\n"
msgstr "$\\n"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV031:1:11:text
msgid "$\\n-love, mom."
msgstr "$\\n－㤇𡥵、媄。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV031:1:13:text
msgid "@niko Aww..."
msgstr "@niko 𫉩。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV032:1:1:text
msgid ""
"$Looks like we're supposed to pack stuff for the evacuation starting today..."
msgstr "$𣎏𨤔衆些沛扒頭㨂襘𣘊度抵移散自𣋚𠉞。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV032:1:2:text
msgid ""
"$I wish these books weren't so heavy...it's gonna be a pain to carry them "
"onto the ship."
msgstr "$埬冊𡲈尼𥘀癲。。。𫼳衆𬨠得船𠱊窒苦低。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/117 - mom/EV032:1:4:text
msgid "$But they're by the Author! I can't just throw them away!"
msgstr "$扔衆𪜀冊傎𧵑作者創世！𪵯哰𦓡𢪥𠫾得！"

#: Maps/Green/Gate/Inside 2/glitch activate:1:16:text
msgid "@niko3 What in the world..?"
msgstr "@niko3 丐之丕。。。？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/niko remarks about
#: silver/kip:1:2:text
msgid "@niko Hey \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 尼\\p？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/niko remarks about
#: silver/kip:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak Doesn't the lady look...kind of familiar to you?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 姉𧘇拯矓窒慣。。。哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/niko remarks about
#: silver/kip:1:4:text
msgid ""
"@niko I wonder if she's related to the robot lady who gave me the amber."
msgstr "@niko 空別姉𧘇𣎏關係喟姉𠊛𣛠迻𨉟𠰳琥珀空。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/niko remarks about
#: silver/kip:1:5:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I almost want to ask her about it..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟㦖𠳨姉𧘇𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/niko remarks about
#: silver/kip:1:6:text
msgid "@niko ...should I?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。扔𣎏𢧚空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/EV011:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed She's still asleep..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 姉𧘇當𥄬。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/EV011:1:5:text
msgid "None of us have been sleeping very well in light of recent events..."
msgstr "𦒹𠁻事件近低空𠬠埃𥄬安得𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/EV011:1:6:text
msgid "The square particles took out a few of my robots last week, and"
msgstr "仍塊𣃱㐌𪵯閧𠅒𠬠𠄧𠊛𣛠𧵑𪝬旬𠓀、吧"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/EV012:1:1:text
msgid "I can barely keep my eyes open, man..."
msgstr "𪝬哙空体𡨺眜𢲫浽𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/EV012:1:2:text
msgid "How does Dr. Silverpoint get all that energy?"
msgstr "教師銀点𥙩能量自兜𫥨丕？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/EV013:1:1:text
msgid "Hmm... I wonder what The Author would do in this situation..."
msgstr "嘘。。。空別𥪝情勢尼作者創世𠱊𪵯之。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/EV013:1:2:text
msgid "Dr. Silverpoint usually references his works."
msgstr "教師常摘引各作品𧵑翁。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/EV028:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A coffee machine. It's almost empty."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𣛠𢯠咖啡。㐌近𣴓。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/EV029:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A warm pot of coffee."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠瓶咖啡𤋾。"

