#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/EV001:1:1:text
msgid "This plane doesn't have a runway because night said so that's why. -GIR"
msgstr "𣛠𢒎𦛉𣎏塘𬦋爲night吶勢。 -GIR"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:31:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh ...phew."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 。。。哺。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:32:text
msgid "@cedric_smile Made it!"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 𬧐坭耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:33:text SKY/landing/cedric:1:38:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes ..."
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:35:text
msgid "@cedric3 You...\\.\\.okay, there?"
msgstr "@cedric3 㛪。。。\\.\\.穩渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:36:text
msgid ""
"@niko_pancakes ...\\>That was the coolest thing I have ever done in my "
"entire life."
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 。。。\\>妬𪜀條湡一㛪曾𪵯𥪝𠁀。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:37:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_smile Heheh...\\.\\. reactions from first-timers are always "
"delightful to watch."
msgstr "@cedric_smile 嗘嗘。。。\\.\\.反應自仍𠊛𢒎吝頭𣅶鬧拱窒趣味。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:43:text
msgid "@niko5 ..."
msgstr "@niko5 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:44:text
msgid "@niko6 Hey, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko6 尼、\\p？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:45:text
msgid "@niko2 That... was really fun."
msgstr "@niko2 𣃣𣅅。。。𢝙𡗋妬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:46:text
msgid "@niko_speak Did you... have fun too?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 舅拱。。。𢝙渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:47:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I mean... you weren't on the plane with me, but..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 意𪜀。。。舅怞空𢒎共𨉟、扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:48:text
msgid "@niko_speak You got to watch it at least, right?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠃣一時舅拱得䀡、董空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:53:text
msgid "@niko And... \\.\\.Cedric...?"
msgstr "@niko 吧。。。\\.\\.察嚦。。。？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:54:text
msgid "@cedric3 Yeah?"
msgstr "@cedric3 𫫡？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:55:text Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe
#: inside/cafe counter:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Thanks..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 感恩英。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:57:text
msgid "@cedric3 ....\\.\\.What for?"
msgstr "@cedric3 。。。。\\.\\.在哰丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:59:text
msgid "@niko_speak Flying!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 爲㐌朱㛪𢒎妬！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:61:text
msgid "@cedric Oh, um..."
msgstr "@cedric 啊、唹。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:62:text
msgid "@cedric_smile You're... \\.\\.welcome?"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 空。。。\\.\\.𣎏之？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:65:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed And... for answering my questions back there, too..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 吧。。。拱爲㐌㨋𠳒句𠳨𧵑㛪𠓀妬𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:66:text
msgid "@niko5 And... \\.\\.for telling me more about the World Machine."
msgstr "@niko5 爲。。。\\.\\.𠸥朱㛪別𧗱𣛠全世。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:67:text
msgid ""
"@niko_upset I'm just.... \\.\\.really sorry about what happened to your old "
"world, though..."
msgstr "@niko_upset 只𪜀㛪。。。\\.\\.窒惜仍之㐌侈𫥨喟世界𫇰𧵑英。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:68:text
msgid "@niko2 So...\\.\\. I'll help you the best that I can."
msgstr "@niko2 𢧚。。。\\.\\.㛪𠱊𢴇影歇飭𣎏体。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:71:text
msgid ""
"@niko4 And...\\.\\. even if it's all just a machine, this world is still..."
"\\.\\.\\@niko2 nice..."
msgstr ""
"@niko4 吧。。。\\.\\.裊悉𪥘󠄁只𪜀模倣、世界尼吻窒。。。\\.\\.\\@niko2 惵。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:72:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I mean, I got to fly... \\.\\.I got to see the ocean..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 意𪜀、㛪㐌得𢒎。。。\\.\\.吧得𥋴㴜𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:73:text
msgid ""
"@niko And...\\.\\.I got to meet a lot of nice people!\\n\\>\\@niko_speak "
"People like you!"
msgstr "@niko 吧。。。\\.\\.㛪﨤得窒𡗉𠊛卒𡛤！\\n\\>\\@niko_speak 仍𠊛如英！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:74:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...and Prototype, even if he's broken right now."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。吧一號、怞愥當被閧。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:76:text
msgid "@cedric ...\\>\\@cedric_smile I'm glad you are taking it so well, Niko."
msgstr "@cedric 。。。\\>\\@cedric_smile 實𢜏欺㛪吻哙樂觀如丕、尼孤啊。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:77:text
msgid "@cedric2 And... I'm glad that we have met as well."
msgstr "@cedric2 吧。。。英拱窒𢝙㐌得﨤媄。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:79:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh ...Despite the...\\.\\. circumstances."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 。。。怞環境𣎏唏。。。\\.\\.㛪別蒂。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:82:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_talk Ah, speaking of Proto... \\@cedric_hmm I should probably head "
"off now."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 啊、𠯅𦤾一號。。。\\@cedric_hmm 英𢧚𠫾催。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:84:text
msgid "@cedric I need to go pick up the siblings too..."
msgstr "@cedric 英拱沛迍𠄩英㛪其𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:86:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 That's true...\\.\\. those two have been waiting for a while now..."
msgstr "@niko2 董耒。。。\\.\\.𠄩伴𧘇拱䟻偻㗶耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:88:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm In the meantime..."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 𥪝欺妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:89:text
msgid "@cedric_smile Do you remember what to do to get to the surface?"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 㛪𣎏𢖵𨉟㐌𪵯之抵𬺗𩈘𡐙空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:90:text
msgid "@niko_speak I remember having to fix an elevator button!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 㛪𢖵沛𢯢鈕𧵑簜𣛠！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:91:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm Alright, you should attend to that, then."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 得耒、丕㛪𢥈務妬唲。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:92:text
msgid "@cedric_talk Let's meet up here in an hour, okay?"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 衆些𠱊𠻷僥於低𢖖󠄁曠𠬠㗂、唲？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:93:text
msgid "@niko Got it!"
msgstr "@niko 得耒！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:95:text
msgid "@cedric Alright, now lemme just-"
msgstr "@cedric 𣇞時抵英。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:115:text
msgid "@niko_shock No!"
msgstr "@niko_shock 空！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:117:text
msgid "@niko_shock ...\\.\\.they're...\\.\\. trapped on the island..."
msgstr "@niko_shock 。。。\\.\\.𠄩伴𧘇被。。。\\.\\.搩𨑗島。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:119:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 ......Calamus....\\>Alula...."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 。。。。。。哥羅𡃙。。。。\\>阿瞜羅。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:120:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 ...they're ...."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 。。。𣱆㐌。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:126:text
msgid "@cedric_eek ....we\\.\\....don't have much time left."
msgstr "@cedric_eek 。。。。衆些\\.\\.。。。空哙𡗉時間。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:128:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh2 Niko... change of plans."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 尼孤。。。計劃㵋。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:129:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Please give me the memory disk."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 唉迻英𥐨𢖵。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:130:text
msgid "@niko2 ...alright..."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。得耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:135:text
msgid "@cedric2 Listen carefully."
msgstr "@cedric2 𦖑朱技唲。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:136:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh2 It's likely I'll be targeted again, so we should split up to "
"keep you safe."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 可能窒高英𠱊被進攻接、𢧚衆些𢧚剒𫥨抵㛪安全。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:137:text
msgid "@cedric I want you to find a door under a large clock."
msgstr "@cedric 英㦖㛪尋𠬠𦑃𨷶𨑜𠬠隻銅壺𡘯。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:138:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh The room behind it houses a pair of ground access elevators."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 間房滕𢖖󠄁𦑃𨷶妬𣎏𠬠笈簜𣛠𬺗𩈘𡐙。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:139:text
msgid ""
"@cedric Once you get to the ground, immediately find Rue and bring her back "
"to the room."
msgstr "@cedric 𠬠欺㛪𦤾坭、𬆄立即尋𠱋吧迻姉𧘇𠭤徠間房。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:140:text
msgid "@cedric She will know what to do in the meantime."
msgstr "@cedric 姉𧘇𠱊別役沛𪵯𢖖󠄁妬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:142:text
msgid "@niko2 Alright...\\.\\.\\@niko3 What about you, though?"
msgstr "@niko2 㐌曉。。。\\.\\.\\@niko3 哙英時哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:143:text
msgid "@cedric3 I'm going to bring Prototype back."
msgstr "@cedric3 英𠱊回生一號。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:169:text
msgid "@niko_surprised WH-"
msgstr "@niko_surprised 嘑－"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:170:text
msgid "@niko_surprised Are you okay???"
msgstr "@niko_surprised 英穩空？？？？？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:172:text
msgid "@cedric_talk WHAAAAAT????"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 哰勢？？？？？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:173:text
msgid "@niko_speak ARE YOU OKAAAAAY???"
msgstr "@niko_speak 英穩空？？？？？？？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:174:text
msgid "@cedric_talk DON'T WORRYYY I'M FINEEEE"
msgstr "@cedric_talk 揨𢥈英空哰𪥘󠄁－－－"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:176:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...don't scare me like that..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。揨唑㛪如勢渚。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:184:text
msgid "@niko_upset2 ...."
msgstr "@niko_upset2 。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:185:text
msgid "@niko2 Hey, \\p...?"
msgstr "@niko2 尼、\\p。。。？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/cedric:1:186:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Let's... do our best."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 共。。。固歇飭唲。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/first aid kit:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a box of medical tools."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠匣用具醫濟。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/first aid kit:1:2:text
msgid "@niko Most of them are broken or rusted beyond use, but..."
msgstr "@niko 份𡘯㐌閧或過釲𡏥、扔。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/first aid kit:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak This plastic syringe seems to be okay."
msgstr "@niko_speak 䈵尖𣺾尼𣎏𨤔吻用得。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV006:1:1:text Maps/Green/Ruins
#: In/Junction/EV001:1:1:text
msgid "[HELLO, PERSON!]"
msgstr "【吀嘲、𡥵𠊛！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV006:1:2:text
msgid "[ARE YOU SEEKING ADMISSION INTO THE INFIRMARY?]"
msgstr "【伴𣎏當懃使用房醫濟空？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV006:1:3:text Maps/Red ground/ground
#: 2/npc_camera:1:24:text
msgid "@niko No?"
msgstr "@niko 空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV006:1:4:text
msgid "[OH. CARRY ON, THEN.]"
msgstr "【啊。丕時據自然唲。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV009:1:1:text
msgid "[HELLO, PERSON OF ORGANIC MAKEUP!]"
msgstr "【吀嘲、𡥵𠊛有機！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV009:1:2:text
msgid "[WELCOME TO THE INFIRMARY]"
msgstr "【嘲𢜏𦤾喟房醫濟】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV009:1:3:text
msgid "[SCANNING FOR INJURIES...]"
msgstr "【當𢭯尋𤵖傷。。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV009:1:6:text
msgid "[SCAN COMPLETE]"
msgstr "【完畢】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV009:1:7:text
msgid "[INJURIES DETECTED: NONE]"
msgstr "【震傷尋𧡊：空】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV009:1:8:text
msgid "[TREATMENT REQUIRED: NONE]"
msgstr "【調治懃寔現：空】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV009:1:9:text
msgid "[YOU ARE GOOD TO GO.]"
msgstr "【伴穩耒。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/112 - infirmary/EV009:1:10:text
msgid "@niko Er...thanks?"
msgstr "@niko 唹。。。感恩？"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/Start/window:1:2:text Maps/INIT/Start/window:1:2:text
msgid "@ed [How do you still have the remote??]"
msgstr "@ed 【哰伴吻擒丐調遣丕？？？】"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/Start/window:1:5:text
msgid "@niko I wonder where that light is coming from..."
msgstr "@niko 空別暎𤏬妬自兜𫥨𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:3:text
#: room/Kip/kip:1:40:text
msgid "@kip You should hold on to that amber, okay?"
msgstr "@kip 㛪唉𡨺𥙩𠰳琥珀實謹慎、唲？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:8:text
msgid "@kip_huh ....oh?"
msgstr "@kip_huh 。。。。溩？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:9:text
msgid "@kip_pout T...\\.that's....."
msgstr "@kip_pout 妬。。。\\.妬𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:10:text
msgid "@kip2 How...\\.did you get this?"
msgstr "@kip2 𪵯哰。。。\\.㛪檢得伮丕？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:11:text
msgid "@niko This robot lady in the Barrens gave it to me!"
msgstr "@niko 𣎏姉𠊛𣛠尼外漨邊疆迻㛪！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:12:text
msgid "@niko_speak She looked... kinda like you?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 姉𧘇矓𣎏𨤔。。。偅姉？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:13:text
msgid "@kip_sigh I see..."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 𫥨勢。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:15:text
msgid "@kip_sad ..."
msgstr "@kip_sad 。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:17:text
msgid ""
"@kip_sigh Sigh. \\>\\nIt was supposed to be such a breakthrough, y'know?"
msgstr "@kip_sigh 係。\\>\\n當𫥨妬沛𪜀𠬠𨀈突破、㛪別空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:18:text
msgid "@kip_pout I even based her on myself so I'll KNOW it works!"
msgstr "@kip_pout 姉哙𡏦𥩯㛪𧘇澦𨑗正姉抵姉昃𥗜㛪𧘇活動！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:19:text
msgid "@niko_speak Break...through?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨀈。。。突破哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:20:text
msgid ""
"@kip2 We wanted to build a robot that acts like a person, thinks like a "
"person..."
msgstr "@kip2 𪨠姉㦖𡏦𥩯𠬠𠊛𣛠行處如𡥵𠊛、思維如𡥵𠊛。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:21:text
msgid "@kip_pout ...a robot that isn't bound by its own code."
msgstr "@kip_pout 。。。𠬠𠊛𣛠空被碼𧵑正伮𦀾𫃚。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:23:text
msgid "@kip_sigh But turns out, you can't really BUILD something like that."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 扔化𫥨、寔𫥨空体鬧𡏦𠬠次如丕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:24:text
msgid "@kip_pout Too many contradictions in the code... made her unstable."
msgstr "@kip_pout 過𡗉矛盾𥪝碼源遣㛪𧘇𠅒穩定。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:25:text
msgid "@kip_sad ...that was the only time I've ever seen a robot go rogue."
msgstr "@kip_sad 。。。妬𪜀吝唯一姉𧡊𠊛𣛠𠅒檢察。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:26:text
msgid "@kip_sigh Scariest day of my life, tell you what!"
msgstr "@kip_sigh 𣈜𢜝一𠁀姉、誓㫻！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:27:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...rogue?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。𠅒檢詧？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:28:text
msgid "@niko But...\\|\\@niko2 she seemed so nice when we talked!"
msgstr "@niko 扔。。。\\|\\@niko2 姉𧘇吶𡀯窒親善喟㛪𦓡！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:29:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...even if she talked a little weird..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。怞姉𧘇𣎏唏奇啒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:30:text
msgid "@kip2 Ah, she's been repaired for some time now."
msgstr "@kip2 啊、㛪𧘇㐌得𢯢𢵻耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:31:text
msgid ""
"@kip_pout My friend was able to stabilize her volatile state through his own "
"means."
msgstr "@kip_pout 伴姉㐌成功鉗制狀態𠅒檢察𧵑㛪𧘇憑方法𥢆。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:32:text
msgid "@kip2 A real miracle worker, that..."
msgstr "@kip2 實事𪜀𠬠法𦭷妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:33:text
msgid ""
"@kip_pout  After he was through, she ended up turning out just like how I "
"wanted."
msgstr "@kip_pout  𢖖󠄁欺英𧘇歱役、㛪𧘇𠭤𢧚董如意姉㦖。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:34:text
msgid "@kip_sad ...but the damage was already done."
msgstr "@kip_sad 。。。扔𢖖󠄁窮時𤗆事㐌耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:35:text
msgid "@kip_sigh ...\\|I gave up on her back then... we all did."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 。。。\\|欺妬姉㐌自𠬃。。。𤗆𠊛拱丕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:36:text
msgid ""
"@kip_pout I'm sure she realized that...\\n\\>\\@kip_sigh and now she won't "
"ever come back."
msgstr "@kip_pout 昃𪜀㛪𧘇㐌認𫥨。。。\\n\\>\\@kip_sigh 吧𠱊空包𣇞𢮿徠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:37:text
msgid "@kip_sad She won't even answer my letters..."
msgstr "@kip_sad 㛪𧘇哙空㨋𠳒書𧵑姉𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:38:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'm sorry..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪窒惜。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:39:text
msgid "@kip_pout Ah, sorry for rambling."
msgstr "@kip_pout 啊、姉𢙲吶唏𡗉耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:49:text
msgid ""
"@kip Oh! I see you put your own photo on there!\\>\\n\\@kip_wink Does that "
"mean your name is Kip now?"
msgstr "@kip 溩！㛪㐌𬖭影𧵑㛪𬨠𥮋耒𠰚。\\>\\n\\@kip_wink 丕𣊾𣇞𠸜㛪𪜀喼嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:50:text
msgid "@kip ...that was a joke."
msgstr "@kip 。。。姉𢴉催。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:55:text
msgid "@kip Is there anything else you need?"
msgstr "@kip 㛪𣎏懃之𡛤空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:56:text
msgid "@niko Nope!"
msgstr "@niko 空吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:57:text
msgid "@kip_wink Well, feel free to stick around if you want!"
msgstr "@kip_wink 丕時據自然如於茹唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:60:text
msgid "@kip Oh hey, you're back!"
msgstr "@kip 溩、㛪㐌𠭤徠！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:61:text
msgid "@kip Can I help you with anything else?"
msgstr "@kip 姉𣎏体𢴇之㛪空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:63:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:14:text
msgid "@niko Do you know how I can get a library card?"
msgstr "@niko 姉別檢𥮋書院於兜空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:64:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:15:text
msgid "@kip_huh A library card?"
msgstr "@kip_huh 𥮋書院嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:65:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:16:text
msgid "@kip You'll have to ask the library for that!"
msgstr "@kip 㛪沛𦤾𠳨書院渚！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:66:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:17:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I tried..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪試耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:67:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:18:text
msgid ""
"@niko I need it to see the head librarian, but I can't get to see her "
"without a library card"
msgstr "@niko 𣎏伮時㛪㵋﨤得守書、扔㛪徠空﨤得姉𧘇𦓡空𣎏𥮋"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:68:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:19:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed ...but at the same time, she's the one who gives out library "
"cards..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。扔姉𧘇徠𪜀𠊛發行𥮋書院丕。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:69:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:20:text
msgid "@kip_huh Really..."
msgstr "@kip_huh 丕哰。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:70:text
msgid "@kip_heh Heh...that sounds like George alright!"
msgstr "@kip_heh 嗘。。。勢時董𪜀觫耒蒂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:71:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:22:text
msgid "@kip_huh I'm sorry you caught her on a bad day!"
msgstr "@kip_huh 窒惜㛪﨤姉𧘇董𣋚債𩙍𠭤𡗶！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:72:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:23:text Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:105:text
msgid "@niko Aw..."
msgstr "@niko 𫉩。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:73:text
msgid "@kip2 ...wait, I know!"
msgstr "@kip2 。。。寬、姉𣎏格尼！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:74:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:25:text
msgid "@kip_wink I can just give you my library card!"
msgstr "@kip_wink 姉朱㛪摱𥮋𧵑姉𪜀得！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:75:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:26:text
msgid "@kip It won't be hard for me to get another one."
msgstr "@kip 姉檢𥮋㵋易空𧘇𦓡。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:76:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:27:text
msgid "@niko_speak Wow, thanks!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫽿、感恩姉唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:80:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:31:text
msgid "@kip There! You're all set, I think..."
msgstr "@kip 妬！姉擬勢𪜀得耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:81:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:32:text
msgid "@kip_huh Wait."
msgstr "@kip_huh 寬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:82:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:33:text
msgid "@kip_huh Shoot!"
msgstr "@kip_huh 𣩂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:83:text
msgid "@kip_heh I forgot...the front desk library bots have facial recognition"
msgstr "@kip_heh 姉悁𠅒。。。𠊛𣛠禮賓於書院𣎏職能認面𣟂𩈘。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:84:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:35:text
msgid "@kip_heh And my photo on the card won't match you..."
msgstr "@kip_heh 吧影姉𨑗𥮋𠱊空𨨤𩈘㛪。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:85:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:36:text
msgid "@kip_wink ...unless I tape a photo of my face to your face!"
msgstr "@kip_wink 。。。除欺姉𬖭影𩈘姉𬨠𩈘㛪！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:86:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:37:text 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:9:text
msgid "@niko Um-"
msgstr "@niko 唹－"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:87:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:38:text
msgid "@kip That was a joke."
msgstr "@kip 𢴉催。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:88:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:39:text
msgid ""
"@kip2 Who knows, maybe you'll get lucky and the robot will take it anyway!"
msgstr "@kip2 埃別、𣎏欺㛪吻𢆪慜過𩈘伮得𧘇渚！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:89:text
#: room/Kip/first meeting:1:40:text
msgid ""
"@kip Worse comes to worse, you can always find somewhere to take a photo."
msgstr "@kip 𦁂𡗋時㛪尋𡊲執𪜀得。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:97:text
msgid "@kip_wink Don't overwork yourself, okay?"
msgstr "@kip_wink 揨𪵯役過飭唲？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:98:text
msgid "@kip Your journey is just as important as your end goal."
msgstr "@kip 行程拱關重昂的𦤾丕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:99:text
msgid "@kip_wink Cliche, but true!"
msgstr "@kip_wink 唏古魯士、扔吻董！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:102:text
msgid "@kip So..."
msgstr "@kip 丕𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:103:text
msgid "@kip_wink You've been walking all over the world, huh?"
msgstr "@kip_wink 㛪㐌𠫾泣世界尼耒哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:105:text
msgid "@kip Geez...I can't imagine..."
msgstr "@kip 𫽿。。。空体想浽。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:106:text
msgid "@kip_huh Do you get really tired sometimes?"
msgstr "@kip_huh 對欺㛪拱𤻻痗渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:107:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Kinda..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 對欺。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:108:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak But I don't mind!\\n\\@niko_pancakes It's actually really pretty!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔空哰𪥘󠄁！\\n\\@niko_pancakes 㛪𧡊伮窒惵！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:109:text
msgid "@kip_wink Haha, I'm glad you think so!"
msgstr "@kip_wink 呵呵、㛪擬丕𪜀卒妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:110:text
msgid "@kip Even with the sun gone, the world is still a beautiful place."
msgstr "@kip 怞𩈘𡗶空哙、世界尼吻惵悌如𣇫鬧。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:111:text
msgid "@niko_speak What did the world look like with the sun?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 世界欺哙𩈘𡗶矓勢鬧丕？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:112:text
msgid "@kip_huh Oh, \\>\\@kip2 uh..."
msgstr "@kip_huh 啊、\\>\\@kip2 唹。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:113:text
msgid ""
"@kip_sigh ...y'know, it's kind of embarassing to admit how little of it I "
"have actually seen."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 。。。怞窒醜𢜜、扔姉沛認哴姉實事𣗓勘破伮𡗉𡗋。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:114:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...oh?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。溩？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:115:text
msgid "@kip_heh Ironic, isn't it?"
msgstr "@kip_heh 𢞂唭𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:116:text
msgid ""
"@kip2 Even though I'm the world's leading researcher..."
"\\>\\n\\@kip_sigh ...All I do is stay here and build robots."
msgstr ""
"@kip2 怞姉𪜀茹研究行頭世界。。。\\>\\n\\@kip_sigh 。。。姉只全𧀓𧀓𥪝茹𡏦𠊛"
"𣛠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:117:text
msgid ""
"@kip_sigh They're the ones exploring the world, I just write down the data, "
"crunch numbers, generate graphs..."
msgstr ""
"@kip_sigh 𣱆㵋𪜀仍𠊛勘破世界、哙姉只𥱬劄與料、𢱖𢵯仍𡥵數、吧𦘧表圖𦓡催。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:118:text
msgid "@niko Right... \\.\\.\\@niko_speak I've been seeing robots everywhere!"
msgstr "@niko 沛耒。。。\\.\\.\\@niko_speak 㛪𧡊𠊛𣛠泣坭㫻！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:119:text
msgid ""
"@niko I just thought it was cuz the world was too dangerous for most people "
"to explore..."
msgstr "@niko 㛪據想𪜀由世界過危險抵𡥵𠊛勘破。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:120:text
msgid "@kip2 That's not far from the truth, actually."
msgstr "@kip2 吶丕拱空差兜。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:121:text
msgid "@kip But I know someone who still does his research firsthand!"
msgstr "@kip 扔姉𣎏慣𠬠𠊛吻哙自𢬣研究𤗆次妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:123:text
msgid ""
"@kip2 ...even after segments of land started collapsing and access to the "
"more remote areas became difficult."
msgstr "@kip2 。。。𠸥𪥘󠄁欺仍斷𡐙扒頭𨀎𢭰吧役移轉𦤾各漨𪸊𨀌𠭤𢧚𠸋𫩒欣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:124:text
msgid ""
"@kip_huh I mean, he outright built a machine that could fly! "
"\\>\\n\\@kip_huh Something we all thought was not physically possible!"
msgstr ""
"@kip_huh 意𪜀、慃哙𡏦得𠬠鈷𣛠𣎏体𢒎幾𦓡！\\>\\n\\@kip_huh 𠬠條𠓀低被𢪱物理䁛"
"𪜀不可施！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:125:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! That's..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！妬𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:126:text
msgid ""
"@kip I asked him about working with us, so he provides us with all sorts of "
"insights from time to time."
msgstr "@kip 姉𣎏合作喟翁𧘇、𢧚對欺慃朱𪨠姉𨁥類見識。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:127:text
msgid "@kip_heh ...but for some reason, he REALLY didn't want to build robots."
msgstr "@kip_heh 。。。扔空曉哰慃徠窒窒空𢛨役𥩯𠊛𣛠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:128:text
msgid "@kip_sigh Or, more specifically, coding them."
msgstr "@kip_sigh 正確欣𪜀役立程衆。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:129:text
msgid "@niko_speak How come?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 哰丕？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:130:text
msgid "@kip2 Beats me!\\> \\@kip_huh I mean, he's happy to work with robots!"
msgstr "@kip2 姉𠹾！\\> \\@kip_huh 𧘇𪜀、慃吻窒𢝙𨤔𪵯役喟衆𦓡！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:131:text
msgid "@kip In fact, he even- \\.\\@kip2 ..."
msgstr "@kip 甚至、翁哙－\\.\\@kip2 。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/kip:1:132:text
msgid ""
"@kip_heh ...ah. It's been a while since we last talked.\\@kip \\>\\nHe must "
"be busy with his books now, yeah."
msgstr ""
"@kip_heh 。。。啊。姉㐌空吶𡀯喟翁𧘇可偻耒。\\@kip \\>\\n𪳨𣊾𣇞慃當絆褓喟冊𡲈"
"𧵑𨉟。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:1:text
msgid "@niko ...Hello?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。吀嘲？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:5:text meeting:1:45:text
msgid "@kip_huh Oh, shoot!"
msgstr "@kip_huh 喂、𣩂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:6:text
msgid ""
"@kip_huh If I had known you would be here so soon, I would've turned off the "
"darned lock!"
msgstr "@kip_huh 裊姉別㛪𠱊𦤾低𣋽欣時姉㐌𤎕丐隖銙𣩂截妬𠫾耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:7:text meeting:1:47:text
msgid "@kip Hello there!"
msgstr "@kip 吀嘲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:8:text meeting:1:48:text
msgid "@kip_heh Sorry about the weird... security measures."
msgstr "@kip_heh 吀纇爲方式保密唏。。。奇啒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:9:text meeting:1:49:text
msgid "@niko It's okay!"
msgstr "@niko 空哰！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:10:text meeting:1:50:text
msgid "@niko \\p helped me solve it!"
msgstr "@niko \\p㐌𢴇㛪解伮耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:11:text meeting:1:51:text
msgid "@kip Did they now!"
msgstr "@kip 實哰！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:12:text meeting:1:52:text
msgid "@kip So... can I help you with anything?"
msgstr "@kip 丕。。。姉𣎏体𢴇之㛪空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:21:text
msgid "@kip_wink Heh...that sounds like George alright!"
msgstr "@kip_wink 嗘嗘。。。勢董𪜀觫耒蒂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:24:text
msgid "@kip ...wait, I know!"
msgstr "@kip 。。。寬、姉別耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:34:text
msgid ""
"@kip_heh I forgot...the front desk library bots have facial recognition."
msgstr "@kip_heh 姉悁𠅒。。。𠊛𣛠禮賓𣎏性能認面𣟂𩈘。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:46:text
msgid ""
"@kip_huh If I had known you would be here so soon, I would've turned off the "
"system!"
msgstr "@kip_huh 裊姉別𠓀㛪𠱊𦤾低時姉㐌𤎕系統𠫾耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:53:text
msgid "@niko Yeah, where's the library?"
msgstr "@niko 𫫡、姉𣎏別書院於兜空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:54:text
msgid "@kip_huh The library? That's all the way on the other side of town!"
msgstr "@kip_huh 書院哰？伮於㘉邊其城庯幾！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:55:text
msgid ""
"@kip2 The fastest route is where you take the shortcut through the "
"backalley, but..."
msgstr "@kip2 塘𨘱一𪜀𠫾過𡉦𢖖󠄁、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:56:text
msgid "@niko I think that's how we got here, actually!"
msgstr "@niko 㛪擬寔𫥨衆㛪𦤾低憑塘妬妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:57:text
msgid "@kip Oh good!"
msgstr "@kip 溩、唁耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:58:text
msgid ""
"@kip2 You should head back to that direction and walk to the east a bit."
msgstr "@kip2 丕時㛪𢧚𢮿徠塘妬吧𠫾𠬠𡭧𧗱𠌨東。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:59:text
msgid "@kip You'll find it eventually!"
msgstr "@kip 耒㛪𠱊尋𧡊伮催！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/first
#: meeting:1:60:text sky/City gate/EV013:2:18:text sky/Apartments/Communal
#: area/EV009:1:7:text Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula
#: npc:2:54:text
msgid "@niko_speak Thank you!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 感恩姉𡗉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/screwdriver:1:1:text
#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Cabin/screwdriver:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Something is poking out from this shelf."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏之妬攂𫥨𠺌架冊尼。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/screwdriver:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's a tube of glitter glue."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠬠䈵膠金線。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/screwdriver:1:3:text
msgid "@kip You can have that if you want!"
msgstr "@kip 裊㛪㦖時據𥙩唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/screwdriver:1:4:text
msgid "@kip_wink Never know when you need to glitter things up, right?"
msgstr "@kip_wink 𢙲𣎏𣅶懃時哰、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/screwdriver:1:5:text
#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Cabin/screwdriver:1:5:text
msgid "@niko Oh! Are you sure?"
msgstr "@niko 溩！姉昃渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/screwdriver:1:6:text
msgid "@kip_wink Yeah! I have tons of those!"
msgstr "@kip_wink 空哰兜！𠇍丐蒂姉𣎏𣹓𧘇𦓡！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/Kip/screwdriver:1:7:text
#: 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:9:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:44:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout
#: point/Cabin/screwdriver:1:7:text Maps/Green/Dock/intro to the glen:1:4:text
msgid "@niko Thank you!"
msgstr "@niko 感恩姉唲！"

#: Maps/Blue/Start point/terminal room/Map Events:2:2:text Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed
#: room/map event:2:2:text
msgid "@niko These machines look like computers."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𪜀𣛠併。"

#: Maps/Blue/Start point/terminal room/Map Events:2:5:text Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed
#: room/map event:2:5:text
msgid "@ed [What's left of a computer terminal.]"
msgstr "@ed 【仍之哙𨔊徠𧵑𠬠𣛠入令。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/landing/City gate/EV013:1:1:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [P l`e\\>a#se do n ot ap`/p `r oa\\>c%%h.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【忄`盃\\>弄#心空彳`/來`貝\\>%%斤。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/Map Events:2:4:text
msgid "[HELLO!]"
msgstr "【吀嘲！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/Map Events:2:6:text
msgid "@niko What are you doing up there?"
msgstr "@niko 舅當𪵯之𨑗妬丕？"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/Map Events:2:7:text
msgid "[I AM STATIONED HERE.]"
msgstr "【𪝬𣎏𢱝更於低。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/Map Events:2:8:text
msgid "@niko By yourself?"
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𨉟哰？"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:2:text voice/EV031:1:5:text
msgid "@niko A picture of a robot."
msgstr "@niko 影𠬠𠊛𣛠。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:6:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak ...Y'know, I've never been around so many robots before, \\p!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。舅別之空、𠓀𣇞𨉟𣗓曾於𨒺𡗉𠊛𣛠𦤾丕兜妬、\\p啊！"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:7:text
msgid "@niko Or... \\.\\. any robots at all..."
msgstr "@niko 或。。。\\.\\.不期𠊛𣛠鬧。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:8:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I mean, I see them in cartoons and stuff, but I've never seen "
"one in person!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 意𪜀、𨉟㐌𧡊衆𥪝活形耒、扔𨉟𣗓曾𧡊𠬠𡥵外𠁀寔兜！"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:9:text
msgid "@niko They're pretty neat, don't you think?"
msgstr "@niko 衆拱便用㗶妬、舅擬丕渚？"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:10:choice:1
msgid "Hey Niko do a robot voice"
msgstr "尼尼孤假𠰩𠊛𣛠𠫾"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:14:text Maps/Red
#: ground/ground 1/EV008:1:10:text sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room4
#: bird/EV002:1:3:text
msgid "@niko Yeah!"
msgstr "@niko 𫫡！"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:19:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...What?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。嘑？"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:20:choice:0
msgid "Try talking like a robot!"
msgstr "試吶𡀯如𠊛𣛠𠫾！"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:25:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed *ahem*"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed ＊嘘嘘＊"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:26:text
msgid "@niko [BEEEP BOOP]"
msgstr "@niko 【芣芣】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:27:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak [I'M A ROBOT AND I... \\. EAT BATTERIES...\\. INSTEAD OF NORMAL "
"PEOPLE FOOD!]"
msgstr "@niko_speak 【𪝬𪜀𠊛𣛠。。。\\.咹汴。。。\\.𠊝爲𣘊咹平常！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:28:text
msgid "@niko_83c Hehe..."
msgstr "@niko_83c 嗘嗘。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:29:text
msgid "[THAT IS NOT CORRECT.]"
msgstr "【信妬𣗓準。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:42:text
msgid "[ROBOTS DO NOT CONSUME BATTERIES IN THE SAME WAY PEOPLE CONSUME FOOD.]"
msgstr "【𠊛𣛠空銷售汴蹺格𡥵𠊛銷售𣘊咹。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:43:text
msgid "[IN FACT, ROBOTS DO NOT POSSESS DIGESTIVE SYSTEMS.]"
msgstr "【寔𫥨、𠊛𣛠空所有系消化。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:44:text
msgid "[SOME ROBOTS DO NOT EVEN HAVE MOUTHS.]"
msgstr "【𠬠數𠊛𣛠甚至空𣎏𠰘。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/118 - robot voice/EV031:1:53:text
msgid "@niko \\p...\\. \\>\\@niko_eyeclosed you made me look silly..."
msgstr "@niko \\p。。。\\. \\>\\@niko_eyeclosed 舅𪵯𨉟𠅒𩈘耒妬。。。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/Start/Bathroom/plant:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a little tree."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠丐𣘃𡮈。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/Start/Bathroom/mirror:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's a mirror!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠬠隻鑒！"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/Start/Bathroom/EV005:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Just a toilet..."
msgstr "@niko 只𪜀𠬠丐盆橋。。。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/Start/Bathroom/EV006:1:1:text
#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/Start/Bathroom/EV007:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a metal bathtub."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠盆浸金類。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/exit:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I don't want to go back..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空㦖𢮿徠兜。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:1:2:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [...Interesting Book You Got There...]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【。。。伴𣎏卷冊趣味妬。。。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:1:3:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [It Is Written In A Language I Do Not Recognize.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【伮得𢪏憑𠬠言語𪝬空体認樣。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:1:4:text
msgid ""
"@red_gatekeeper [...Perhaps You Should Find A Way To Decipher It When You're "
"At The Library.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【。。。𣎏𨤰伴𢧚尋格解碼伮欺𦤾書院。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:1:5:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [It May Be Of Help.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【𣎏体伮𠱊𢴇益朱伴。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:1:13:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [Hello Again, Messiah, Do You Need Help?]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【吀嘲𠬠吝𡛤、𠎬救世、伴𣎏懃𢴇之𡛤空？】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:1:14:text
msgid "@niko Well..."
msgstr "@niko 時。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:1:14:choice:0
msgid "Explain again"
msgstr "解釋徠"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:1:17:text
msgid ""
"@red_gatekeeper [Very Well. You Need To Find A Way To Get To The Library On "
"The Surface.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【得催。伴懃尋塘𦤾書院𨑜𩈘𡐙。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:1:20:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [Off You Go Then, Off You Go...]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【𠊛𠫾保重唲。。。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:1:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [Ah, The Sun.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【啊、𩈘𡗶。。。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:2:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [Hello, Messiah. Welcome To The Refuge.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【吀嘲、咳𠎬救世。嘲𢜏𠊛𦤾喟區避難。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:3:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [Do You Understand What You Must Do Here?]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【𠊛曉本身沛𪵯之於低渚？】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:4:text
msgid "@niko I'm supposed to go inside the Tower, right?"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟沛𠓨座塔、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:5:text
msgid "@niko I already see the Tower! So I guess we must be close."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟㐌矓𧡊伮耒！𪳨𪜀𨉟當窒近伮。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:6:text
msgid "@niko_speak Where's the entrance?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𡓃𠓨於兜丕？"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:7:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [On The Surface.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【伮於𨑜𩈘𡐙。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:8:text
msgid "@niko_speak The surface?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𩈘𡐙唹？"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:9:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [Look Down, Small One.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【唉𥆾𬺗、咳哙𠊛𡮈𡮣。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:10:text
msgid "@niko Oooh, \\.\\.\\@niko_speak we're pretty high up!"
msgstr "@niko 溩、\\.\\.\\@niko_speak 衆𨉟於𨑗高㗶𠰚！"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:11:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I guess I gotta get down a lot of stairs! \\>\\n\\@niko Or find "
"an elevator."
msgstr "@niko_speak 丕昃𨉟沛𠫾𬺗窒𡗉橋簜。\\>\\n\\@niko 或尋簜𣛠。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:12:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [Correct.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【正確。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:13:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [However, The Tower Is A Sacred Place.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【雖然、座塔𪜀𠬠坭靈𪬮。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:14:text
msgid ""
"@red_gatekeeper [Finding The Entrance May Be Easy, But That Alone Will Not "
"Be Enough.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【𡓃𠓨𣎏体易尋、扔只饒妬𪜀空𨁥。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:15:text
msgid "@niko What...do you mean?"
msgstr "@niko 意伴。。。𪜀哰丕？"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:16:text
msgid ""
"@red_gatekeeper [Once You Reach The Surface, I Recommend Visiting The "
"Library For Leads.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【𢖖󠄁欺𬺗𩈘𡐙、𪝬提出伴𦤾書院尋萌䋦。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:2:19:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [Off You Go, Then. I Wish You Luck.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper【保重唲。𪝬祝伴𢆪慜。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:4:1:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [I'm Afraid This Area Is Off-Limits For You.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【㥋𪜀伴空体𠓨區域尼。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:4:2:text
msgid ""
"@red_gatekeeper [Only The Bearer Of The Sacred Kernel Is Permitted Access To "
"The Garden.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【只𣎏𠊛𫼳𨑗𨉟籺𥞖𪬮得法進𠓨區園聖。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:4:4:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! \\.\\.\\@niko Like...\\.\\. a kernel of corn...?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！\\.\\.\\@niko 矯如。。。\\.\\.𠬠籺吳𧘇嘑。。。？"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:4:5:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I have this! \\.\\.\\>\\@niko It was left behind by the plant "
"lady in the Glen."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟𣎏丐尼！ \\.\\.\\>\\@niko 姉𠊛𣘃重漨潭浰㐌抵徠伮。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:4:6:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [...\\>\\nThat Is Indeed The Kernel.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【。。。\\>\\n妬果然𪜀籺𥞖𪬮。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:4:7:text
msgid ""
"@red_gatekeeper [Then, It Is Your Duty To Regrow Her.\\>\\nDo You Understand "
"What You Must Do?]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【丕時、任務𣑺徠姑𧘇屬𧗱伴。\\>\\n伴㐌曉役沛𪵯耒渚？】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:4:11:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [Good.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【卒。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:4:14:text
msgid ""
"@red_gatekeeper [Take The Seed To The Garden.\\>\\nPlant It In The Pot In "
"The Center.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【唉𫼳籺𥞖𦤾園聖。\\>\\n𣑺伮重𡊱𣘃中心。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/EV013:4:17:text
msgid "@red_gatekeeper [You May Now Pass Through Here To Access The Garden.]"
msgstr "@red_gatekeeper 【𣇞伴𣎏体𠓨園聖憑𡓃尼。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/left-terminals/EV001:1:1:text
msgid "Monitoring...monitoring...."
msgstr "當觀測。。。當觀測。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/left-terminals/EV012:1:1:text
msgid "I'm picking up some more disruptions in sector 8 of the city."
msgstr "𪝬當認𠬠數信號擾亂在郡8。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/left-terminals/EV012:1:2:text
msgid "This is consistent with our earlier findings... not good at all..."
msgstr "悉𪥘󠄁調𨨤喟與料𠓀妬。。。空卒𠬠𡭧鬧。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/left-terminals/EV013:1:1:text
msgid ""
"The Barrens engineer just reported another sighting of the particles in the "
"cliff area."
msgstr "技師漨邊疆𣃣報告添𠬠吝發現各份子在區域壁𥒥。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/left-terminals/EV013:1:2:text
msgid "...well, nothing unusal at this point."
msgstr "。。。時、拱空𣎏之不常。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/left-terminals/EV014:1:1:text
msgid ""
"Ugh, those squares particles just took out two of my robots in the Glen."
msgstr "譃、𠇍塊𣃱妬𣃣𪵯閧𠄩𠊛𣛠𧵑𪝬於漨潭浰。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/left-terminals/EV014:1:2:text
msgid "We might have to put off the water analysis project for now."
msgstr "𣎏𨤔衆些沛暫凝進行預案分析質量渃。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/left-terminals/map
#: event:1:2:text
msgid ""
"@niko I want to press all of the buttons...\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed But I "
"must resist!"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟㦖𢶸歇悉𪥘󠄁各鈕。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 扔𨉟沛𢶢拒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/left-terminals/map
#: event:1:5:text
msgid ""
"@niko There sure are a lot of computers here...\\>\\nAnd they look "
"important, too."
msgstr "@niko 於低𣎏𡗉𣛠併實。。。\\>\\n吧矓衆拱關重𡛤。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:2:12:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:3:4:text
msgid "@prophet [Ah!]"
msgstr "@prophet 【啊！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:2:text
msgid "@prophet [That Lightbulb...! You Are Here!]"
msgstr "@prophet 【琫畑妬。。。！伴㐌𦤾耒！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:3:text
msgid "@niko M- \\.\\.\\@niko2 me?"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟－ \\.\\.\\@niko2 𨉟唹？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:4:text
msgid "@prophet [Yes!]"
msgstr "@prophet 【董丕！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:5:text
msgid "@prophet [Welcome To Our World, Friend!]"
msgstr "@prophet 【吀嘲𢜏𦤾喟世界𧵑衆𪝬、咳朋友！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:6:text
msgid "@prophet [I Am Most Humbled By Your Presence.\\. Yes!]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𪝬窒榮譽得嘲迍伴。\\.董丕！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:7:text
msgid "@niko Uh, thanks..."
msgstr "@niko 唹、感恩唲。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:11:text
msgid "@niko3 .\\..\\.."
msgstr "@niko3 。\\.。\\.。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:12:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Sorry...\\.\\. I'm a little lost..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 吀纇。。。\\.\\.𨉟唏𦇒腦𠬠𡭧。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:13:text
msgid "@prophet [Ah Right!\\.\\. Allow Me To Explain Some Things.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【沛耒！\\.\\.𪝬吀法解釋𠬠數次。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:14:text
msgid "@prophet [May I First Ask How You Arrived Here?]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𠓀歇、伴𣎏体朱別格伴𦤾得低空？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:15:text
msgid "@niko3 I'm... not sure..."
msgstr "@niko3 𨉟。。。空昃𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:16:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 I woke up in this...\\.\\. weird house.\\>\\n\\@niko_speak It was "
"really dark!"
msgstr ""
"@niko2 𨉟醒𧻭𥪝𠬠𡾵茹。。。\\.\\.奇𨓐。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 𤗆次𣋁喑㫻！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:17:text
msgid ""
"@prophet_omg [Oh!] \\>\\n\\@prophet [So You Woke Up In An Unfamiliar, Dark "
"Location?]"
msgstr "@prophet_omg 【溩！】 \\>\\n\\@prophet 【義𪜀伴𥅞𧻭在𠬠地點𣋁吧𨓐？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:19:text
msgid "@prophet_omg [Just As My Prophecy Foretold. Yes!]"
msgstr "@prophet_omg 【董如𠳒先知𧵑𪝬㐌預斷。董丕！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:20:text
msgid "@prophet [You Are The Savior We Have Been Waiting For!]"
msgstr "@prophet 【伴正𪜀𠎬救世衆𪝬䟻懞曊偻𠉞！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:21:text
msgid "@prophet [You Will Be The One To Save Our World From Eternal Darkness.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【伴𠱊𪜀𠊛救世界𧵑衆𪝬𠺌𣈖𣋁永恆。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:33:text Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator
#: deck/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:121:text
msgid "@niko2 ...um."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。𫫡。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:35:text
msgid "@prophet [Please Ask Me Anything!]"
msgstr "@prophet 【唉𠳨𪝬不期條之！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:36:text
msgid "@Niko Ah, well...."
msgstr "@Niko 啊、時。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:38:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:24:text
msgid "@niko_speak Can you tell me about..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 伴𣎏体解釋朱𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:39:choice:0
#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:127:choice:0
msgid "...this world"
msgstr "。。。𧗱世界尼"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:39:choice:1
#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:127:choice:1
msgid "...the lightbulb"
msgstr "。。。𧗱琫畑"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:39:choice:2
msgid "...about \\p"
msgstr "。。。𧗱\\p"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:39:choice:3
#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:127:choice:3
msgid "...going home"
msgstr "。。。格𠭤𧗱茹"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:51:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:143:text
msgid "@prophet [\\p Is The Name Of Our God.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【\\p𪜀𠸜𧵑𠎬全能𧵑衆𪝬。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:52:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:146:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [Always Look To Them For Guidance.]\\>\\n[You've Already Received "
"More Than You Realize...]"
msgstr "@prophet 【唉㫻㫻尋指引𧵑𠎬。】\\>\\n【伴拱㐌認得𡗉欣𨉟擬耒妬。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:55:text
msgid ""
"@niko When I woke up in that house...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak For some reason, I "
"called out a name."
msgstr ""
"@niko 欺𨉟𥅞𧻭𥪝𡾵茹妬。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 空別在哰、𨉟㐌吶𫥨𠬠丐𠸜。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:56:text
msgid "@niko \"\\p\"."
msgstr "@niko 「\\p」。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:57:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed I'm not sure why I did that.\\>\\n\\@niko_speak But then, I "
"saw it on a computer too!"
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空別在哰徠𪵯丕𡛤。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 扔耒、𨉟𧡊伮𨑗幔形𣛠"
"併紐啊！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:58:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:156:text
msgid "@prophet_omg [Ah,\\.\\. That Would Be Our God!]"
msgstr "@prophet_omg 【啊、\\.\\.妬𪜀𠎬全能𧵑衆𪝬！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:59:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes Oh!\\> Right!\\>\\n\\@niko I... think I..."
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 啊！\\>沛耒！\\>\\n\\@niko 𨉟。。。擬𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:60:text
msgid "@niko3 ...I feel like I remember something about that."
msgstr "@niko3 。。。形如𨉟𣎏𢖵之妬𧗱舅𧘇。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:61:text
msgid "@prophet_omg [You do?]"
msgstr "@prophet_omg 【實哰？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:62:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [But wait... Did You Not Just Arrive Here?]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【扔。。。拯沛伴𣃣𦤾低哰？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:63:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [I Was The One Who Was Supposed To Inform You Of That.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【當𫥨𨉟㵋𪜀𠊛吶朱舅通信妬。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:64:text
msgid "@prophet [So... How Did You Know?]"
msgstr "@prophet 【勢時。。。哰舅徠別得？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:65:text
msgid "@niko_speak ... \\>\\@niko ...hm..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。 \\>\\@niko 。。。嘘。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:66:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed It just made sense, I guess!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 時、昃𪜀𨉟𧡊伮合理催！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:67:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [Ah...]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【啊。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:68:text
msgid "@prophet_omg [Have You Already Contacted \\p, Then?]"
msgstr "@prophet_omg 【丕時、伴㐌聯絡\\p𣗓？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:69:text
msgid "@niko Nope!\\>\\nI just have to close my eyes and focus, right?"
msgstr "@niko 𣗓！\\>\\n𨉟只懃𥄮眜吧集中、董空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:77:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed2 ...hey, \\p? ...God?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed2 。。。尼、\\p？主？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:78:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed This is going to sound weird, but... "
"\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed2 Have we... met... before?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed 𦖑窒奇、扔。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed2 衆些㐌。。。﨤僥𠓀低"
"𣗓𠰚？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:84:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed2 Ah!\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed But...I don't know who you are, "
"though..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed2 啊！\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 扔。。。𨉟空別舅𪜀埃。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:85:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed It's just a weird feeling that I have..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 只𪜀𠬠推擬奇𨓐𧵑𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:86:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed2 Oh... I bet I'm just being silly, aren't I..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed2 昃𪜀𨉟吶𡀯𢞂唭𡗋、董空。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:87:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft
#: entrance/server room/backroom/proto:4:7:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Sorry..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 吀纇唲。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:91:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Ah, I thought not..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 啊、𨉟想𪜀空。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:92:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed2 That was a silly question..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed2 句𠳨呆𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:95:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed But...\\.\\. it's nice to meet you, \\p!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 扔。。。.\\.窒𢝙得﨤舅、\\p！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:96:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:184:text
#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:240:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed My name is Niko!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟𠸜𪜀尼孤！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:106:text
msgid "@niko_speak I just contacted \\p, yeah!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫫡、𨉟𣃣聯絡得喟\\p！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:107:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [Do Not Be Afraid To Ask \\p For Assistance.]\\>\\n[You Are The "
"Messiah After All.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【揨垠礙吀事助𢴇自\\p。】\\>\\n【伴𪜀𠎬救世𦓡。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:115:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:316:text
msgid "@prophet [Remember Your Duty.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【唉𢖵𥙩任務𧵑伴。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:127:choice:2
msgid "...the computer"
msgstr "。。。𣛠併"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:140:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [The Name Of Our God Is Apparently \\p.\\nI Must Admit This Is A "
"Surprise...]"
msgstr ""
"@prophet 【䀡𫥨𠸜𧵑𠎬全能𧵑衆些𪜀\\p。】\\n【𪝬沛承認低𪜀𠬠不㘈。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:149:text
msgid "@niko In the house, I found this... computer."
msgstr "@niko 𥪝間茹、𨉟𧡊𠬠。。。𣛠併。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:150:text
msgid ""
"@niko It kept saying stuff like\\n\\>\\@niko_speak \"Your actions here will "
"affect Niko.\""
msgstr "@niko 伮據吶仍次矯如\\n\\>\\@niko_speak 「行動𧵑伴於低𠱊影響𦤾尼孤。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:151:text
msgid "@niko_speak But... \\.\\. \\c[3]I'm\\c[0] Niko!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔。。。.\\. \\c[3]𨉟\\c[0]𪜀尼孤𦓡！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:152:text
msgid "@niko Are those messages meant for someone else?"
msgstr "@niko 仍信𠴍妬𧶄朱𠊛恪哰？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:153:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [Hm...]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【嘘。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:154:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [If I Had To Guess, They Might Be Trying To Pass The Message To "
"\\p.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【裊沛斷、𪝬擬𪜀𣱆當固傳達信𠴍妬𬧐\\p。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:155:text
msgid "@niko ... \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。\\p？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:157:text
msgid "@prophet [If You Are Here, That Means \\p Is Here Also.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【裊伴當於低、\\p拱當於低。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:158:text
msgid "@prophet [\\p Will Provide Guidance For Your Journey.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【\\p𠱊助𢴇伴𨑗行程尼。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:159:text
msgid "@prophet [In Fact, They Already Have.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【寔𫥨、𣱆㐌吧當𪵯丕耒。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:160:text
msgid "@niko_speak Really?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 實哰？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:161:text
msgid "@niko I haven't seen anyone though..."
msgstr "@niko 扔𨉟𣗓﨤埃𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:162:text
msgid "@prophet [Have You...\\.\\. Not Contacted \\p Yet?]"
msgstr "@prophet 【伴。。。\\.\\.𣗓聯絡喟\\p哰？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:163:text
msgid "@niko I don't think so."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟空擬丕。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:164:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [Being The Bringer Of Our Sun, You Have The Sacred Ability To "
"Communicate Directly With \\p.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𪜀𠊛捻𡨺𩈘𡗶、伴𣎏權能神聖𪜀交接喟\\p。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:165:text
msgid ""
"@prophet_hmm [...An Ability That No One Else Possesses, Certainly Not I.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【。。。𠬠權能空埃恪所有、吧昃𥗜空沛𪝬。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:166:text
msgid "@prophet [Please Close Your Eyes And Focus.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𢝙𢚸𥄮眜徠吧集中。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:175:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Hello?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 吀嘲？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:176:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...\\p?\\nAre you... \\| there?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。\\p？\\n伴。。。\\|𣎏妬空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:178:choice:1
msgid "That is not my name"
msgstr "𠸜𨉟空沛丕"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:182:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed2 Oh!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed2 溩！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:183:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:239:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed2 N-\\. nice to meet you, \\p!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed2 窒－\\.窒𢝙得﨤舅、\\p！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:188:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed O-\\|oh..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 嗚－\\|溩。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:189:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Well.\\..\\..\\. what is your name, then?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 勢時。\\.。\\.。\\.𠸜舅𪜀之？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:192:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed But that's... what I said."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 扔。。。𨉟𣃣吶董如丕𦓡。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:196:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed2 Oh! Your name is... \\>\\n\\@niko_what ..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed2 溩！𠸜舅𪜀。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_what 。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:197:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed2 I don't think I'm supposed to say that word, but..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed2 𨉟空擬𨉟𢧚吶詞妬、扔。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:202:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes Really? \\>\\nThat's your name too?"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 實唹？>\\n舅拱得撻𠸜尼哰？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:207:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! \\>\\n\\@niko That's almost the same as my name..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！\\>\\n\\@niko 𠸜近偅𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:208:text
msgid "@niko_speak In fact, I think they're actually pronounced the same!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 形如發音拱偅僥㫻時沛！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:213:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed2 Is that your... name?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed2 妬𪜀。。。𠸜舅嘑？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:214:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed But I already have parents..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 扔𨉟拱𣎏仛媄𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:215:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed This'll be confusing..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𠱊窒𦇒啉低。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:216:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Anyways..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 怞哰時。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:221:text
msgid "@niko_what ....really?\\>\\n\\@niko_what2 That's... your name?"
msgstr "@niko_what 。。。。實唹？\\>\\n\\@niko_what2 妬𪜀。。。𠸜舅嘑？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:222:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed2 Gross!\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed Er... I mean...."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed2 㕭！\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 啊。。。意𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:253:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I actually heard someone! \\>\\n\\@niko They said their name is "
"\\p, though..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 𨉟寔事㐌𦖑𧡊埃妬吶𡀯！\\>\\n\\@niko 扔舅𧘇吶舅𧘇𠸜𪜀\\p。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:254:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:299:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes This is incredible..."
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 空體信浽。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:255:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:292:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [It Seems The Recorded Name Was Incorrect.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【𣎏𨤔𠸜得留𥪝部𢖵空正確。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:256:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:270:text
#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:280:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:293:text
msgid "@prophet [Updating Database...]"
msgstr "@prophet 【當及日基礎與料。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:262:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:272:text
#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:282:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:295:text
msgid "@prophet [Update Complete.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【及日完畢。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:266:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I actually heard someone! \\>\\n\\@niko_pancakes They told me "
"their name is actually \\p!"
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 𨉟𣎏𦖑𧡊埃妬！ \\>\\n\\@niko_pancakes 舅𧘇𠸒𨉟舅𧘇𠸜𪜀\\p！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:267:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes The same as mine!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 依如𠸜𨉟！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:268:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:278:text
msgid "@prophet [Ah. Perhaps It Was Fate.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【啊。𣎏𨤰𪜀緣分。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:269:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:279:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [But It Seems The Recorded Name Was Incorrect.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【扔𣎏𨤔𠸜得留𥪝部𢖵空正確。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:276:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I actually heard someone!\\>\\n\\@niko_pancakes They told me "
"their name is actually \\p!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟㐌𦖑𧡊𠰩𠊛！\\>\\n\\@niko_pancakes 舅𧘇𠸒哴舅𧘇𠸜𪜀\\p！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:277:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes It sounds just like my name!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 𦖑依如𠸜𨉟！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:286:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:298:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I actually heard someone! \\>\\n\\@niko They said their name is "
"\\p..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟㐌寔事𦖑𧡊𠰩𠊛！\\>\\n\\@niko 舅𧘇吶𠸜舅𧘇𪜀\\p。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:287:text
msgid "@niko_wtf2 I still don't think I should be saying that..."
msgstr "@niko_wtf2 𨉟吻擬𨉟空𢧚吶詞妬。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:288:text
msgid "@prophet [Why?]"
msgstr "@prophet 【在哰丕？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:289:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed It's a bad word!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 妬𪜀詞俗𦓡！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:290:text
msgid "@prophet [Bad...\\.\\. Word?]"
msgstr "@prophet 【詞。。。\\.\\.俗唹？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:291:text Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:45:text Maps/POSTGAME
#: green/Research Station/EV010:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Nevermind."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 偈𠫾。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:308:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [Do Not Be Afraid To Ask \\p For Assistance.]\\n\\>[You Are The "
"Messiah After All.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【揨垠礙𠾒\\p助𢴇。】\\n\\>【伴𪜀𠎬救世𦓡。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:329:text
msgid "@prophet [Surely You Have More Questions!]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𪳨伴吻哙仍句𠳨恪！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:353:text
msgid "@niko I think that's all I have to ask for now."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟擬現在𨉟㐌𠳨覩耒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:4:354:text
msgid "@prophet [Excellent!] \\>\\n[I Wish You Luck.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【絕𡸏！】\\>\\n【祝伴𢆪慜。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:2:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:13:text
msgid "@prophet [I Wish You Luck On The Rest Of Your Journey.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𪝬祝伴𢆪慜𨑗行程尼。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:6:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:17:text
msgid "@prophet [Hello Again.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【㐌﨤徠伴耒。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:8:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak \\p and I are gonna leave now! \\@niko We found a robot that can "
"take us closer to the Tower!"
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 𨉟吧\\p𢯛𨖨𠫾低！\\@niko 衆𨉟㐌尋𧡊𠬠𠊛𣛠𣎏体迻衆𨉟𬧐近座塔欣！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:9:text
msgid "@prophet_omg [Oh!]"
msgstr "@prophet_omg 【溩！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:10:text
msgid "@niko Thanks for helping me and answering my questions!"
msgstr "@niko 感恩舅㐌㨋𠳒句𠳨吧𢴇扡𨉟唲！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:11:text
msgid "@prophet_omg [That Means I have Fulfilled My Purpose!]"
msgstr "@prophet_omg 【擬𪜀𪝬㐌完全使命！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:18:text
msgid "@prophet [Are There More Questions You Wish To Ask?]"
msgstr "@prophet 【伴哙舅𠳨鬧恪空？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:19:text
msgid "@niko"
msgstr "@niko"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:23:text
msgid "@prophet [Go On Then, Ask Away.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【丕時唉𠳨𠫾。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:24:choice:0
msgid "...the barrens"
msgstr "。。。塳邊疆"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:24:choice:1
msgid "...the prophecy"
msgstr "。。。𠳒先知"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:24:choice:2
msgid "...the tower"
msgstr "。。。座塔"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:27:text
msgid "@niko It's so...\\.\\. empty here..."
msgstr "@niko 於低。。。\\.\\.𥧪𣥱過𠫾。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:28:text
msgid "@prophet [That's Why It's Called The Barrens.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【勢𢧚㵋哙𪜀塳邊疆。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:29:text
msgid "@niko ...are there... ANY people living in this area?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。於低。。。𣎏埃𤯩空丕？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:30:text
msgid "@niko ...besides robots, I mean."
msgstr "@niko 。。。意𪜀、除𠊛𣛠𫥨。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:31:text
msgid "@prophet [I Do Not Know.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𪝬空別。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:32:text
msgid "@prophet [I Was Not Built To Wander.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𪝬空得設計抵𠫾徠。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:33:text
msgid "@niko ...not...\\.built to?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。空得。。。\\.設計哰？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:34:text
msgid ""
"@niko So... \\.\\. you just stand here? \\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed Must be "
"boring..."
msgstr ""
"@niko 丕𪜀。。。\\.\\.舅只𨅸妬催哰？\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 𢥇𡗋𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:35:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Do you at least have friends? \\>\\n\\@niko Robot...\\. friends?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 舅𣎏伴佊空？\\>\\n\\@niko 伴。。。\\.𣛠？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:36:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [I Cannot Desire Companionship.]\\n\\> \\@prophet_hmm [I Have Not "
"Been Tamed.]"
msgstr ""
"@prophet 【𪝬空𣎏可能𫻎㦖情伴。】\\n\\> \\@prophet_hmm 【𪝬𣗓得純化。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:37:text
msgid "@niko Not... tamed?"
msgstr "@niko 𣗓。。。純化？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:38:text
msgid "@prophet [There Was No Time.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【空𣎏時間。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:39:text Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:57:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:56:text Maps/Red
#: ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map Events:4:178:text
#: Events:7:44:text Events:7:65:text deck/Office/locked room/map
#: events:5:30:text ground/backalley/EV007:1:19:text
msgid "@niko I see..."
msgstr "@niko 𫥨丕。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:42:text
msgid "@niko So...\\.\\.\\n\\@niko_speak What is this prophecy, exactly?"
msgstr "@niko 丕時。。。\\.\\.\\n\\@niko_speak 𠳒先知尼𪜀𧗱之丕？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:43:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [The Prophet Predicted That A Savior Will Arrive From Another Land.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【茹先知㐌預斷哴位救星𠱊𬧐自𠬠塳𡐙恪。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:44:text
msgid ""
"@prophet [The Savior Will Wake Up In A Strange House, Find The Sun, And "
"Illuminate The World.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𠎬救世妬𠱊𥅞𧻭𥪝𠬠間茹𨓐、尋𩈘𡗶、𦓡𤏧𤏬世界。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:46:text
msgid "@niko_speak What else did you...uh, foresee?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 舅哙別𠓀條之恪空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:47:text
msgid "@prophet [What Do You Mean?]"
msgstr "@prophet 【意伴𪜀之？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:48:text
msgid "@niko_speak What else did you see in the prophecy?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏之恪𥪝𠳒先知丕？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:49:text
msgid "@prophet [???]"
msgstr "@prophet 【？？？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:50:text
msgid "@niko_speak Wait... \\.\\. You ARE the prophet, right?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 寬。。。\\.\\.舅正𪜀茹先知、沛空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:51:text
msgid "@prophet [Good Heavens, No!]"
msgstr "@prophet 【𡗶㗒、空！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:52:text
msgid "@niko_speak But you called it \"my prophecy\" earlier..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔𠓀妬舅哙伮𪜀「𠳒先知𧵑𪝬」𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:53:text
msgid "@prophet [That Just Means It Is Built Into My Programming.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【義𪜀𥪝碼源𧵑𪝬𣎏貯伮催。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:54:text
msgid "@niko ...Your... \\.\\.\\@niko_speak what?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。丐之。。。 \\.\\.\\@niko_speak 𧵑舅幾？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:55:text
msgid "@prophet [Ah. My Programming Is What Guides Me.]"
msgstr "@prophet 【啊。碼源𧵑𪝬𪜀次指導𪝬。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:56:text
msgid "@prophet_hmm [I Am A Robot, After All.]"
msgstr "@prophet_hmm 【𢖖󠄁共時、𪝬𪜀𠬠𠊛𣛠。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/prophet:5:60:text
msgid "@niko_speak How tall is the Tower?"
