msgstr "@plight_worry2 團移民當矓䟻𪥘󠄁𠓨伮。。。\\>𠓨英。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:49:text
msgid ""
"@plight_worry But... I've been here for hours and can't figure out a thing!"
