msgid "@niko3 Oh...."
msgstr "@niko3 溩。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:54:text
msgid ""
"@plight_sigh Right now everyone's crowded in the cafe.\\nWe really want to "
"get everyone to the surface as soon as possible, though."
msgstr ""
"@plight_sigh 現在𤗆𠊛當聚集在館咖啡。\\n雖然、𪨠英㦖迻𤗆𠊛𬺗𩈘𡐙𪨈𨘱𪨈卒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:55:text
msgid ""
"@plight3 The library on the surface doubles as a shelter for situations like "
"this."
msgstr "@plight3 書院𨑜妬𣎏体𪵯茹住隱朱仍場合如勢尼。"

