#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:78:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed ... Looks like \\p and I will need to find another way down "
"altogether..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。䀡𫥨\\p吧㛪𠱊沛尋塘恪抵𬺗。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:79:text
msgid "@plight_worry But...\\.\\. this is the only elevator in the area..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 扔。。。\\.\\.低𪜀簜𣛠唯一𥪝區尼𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:80:text
msgid "@niko We'll... think of something."
msgstr "@niko 𪨠㛪𠱊。。。尋𠬠格鬧妬。"

