#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/113 - ocean/EV031:1:1:text
msgid ""
"$I remember being taught in school about how the waters surrounding the "
"forest stretched until the boundries of space."
msgstr "$𨉟𢖵㐌學於場𧗱塳㴜𨒺棱𣥱𨱽㘉𦤾盡窮𧵑宇宙。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/113 - ocean/EV031:1:2:text
msgid ""
"$But at some point, the prehistoric oceans receded, forming what is now the "
"Barrens."
msgstr "$扔耒、仍大洋原始㐌捽𨆢、造𫥨塳邊疆𣈜𠉞。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/113 - ocean/EV031:1:4:text
msgid "$I wonder where all that water went..."
msgstr "$空別量渃妬變𠫾兜𠅒耒𠰚。。。"

