msgstr "@niko  㛪㦖別格𬺗𩈘𡐙吖！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:13:text
msgid "@plight_2 ...yeeahh...I was afraid you were gonna say that..."
msgstr "@plight_2 。。。唹。。。英當𢜝𪜀㛪𠱊𠳨中句妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:14:text
msgid ""
"@plight Right now, this elevator is the only way to access the surface. "
"But..."
msgstr "@plight 現在、簜𣛠𪜀格唯一抵𬺗𩈘𡐙。扔。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:15:text
msgid "@plight ....yeah, just take a look at it."
msgstr "@plight 。。。。唹、𥆾伮𠫾。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:21:text
msgid "@niko I-It looks like an elevator..."
msgstr "@niko 時－時伮𪜀𠬠蓋簜𣛠。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:22:text
msgid "@plight_2 Well, you're not wrong, but..."
msgstr "@plight_2 時、拱空差、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:2:23:text
msgid "@plight_why Go look at the button panel."
msgstr "@plight_why 𥆾榜鈕𠫾。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:3:1:text
msgid "@plight_2 I am not the button panel."
msgstr "@plight_2 榜鈕空𣎏𨑗𩈘英兜。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:2:text
msgid "@plight_shock Whoa! How did you make this?"
msgstr "@plight_shock 𫽿！㛪製𫥨丐尼矯之丕？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak Out of a coffee can!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 自錀咖啡啞！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:4:text
msgid "@plight_worry ...Coffee comes from cans?"
msgstr "@plight_worry 。。。咖啡𦤾自錀嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:5:text
msgid "@plight_worry ......."
msgstr "@plight_worry 。。。。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:6:text deck/npc_plight:4:21:text
msgid "@plight_2 ...Uh, go see if it works!"
msgstr "@plight_2 。。。唹、㛪據試䀡𣎏得空！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:11:text
msgid "@plight_shock Oh nice, are those magnets?"
msgstr "@plight_shock 溩、南針妬嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:12:text
msgid "@plight_2b Looks like they're a bit loose, but...."
msgstr "@plight_2b 矓咳𣿅、扔。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:13:text
msgid "@plight_2 ...Ah well, go see if it works!"
msgstr "@plight_2 。。。催時、沛試㵋別得！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:18:text
msgid "@plight_shock Oh wow, that sure is a lotta tape...."
msgstr "@plight_shock 喂𡗶、𡗉繃穎㗶𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:19:text
msgid "@plight But better safe than sorry, right?"
msgstr "@plight 催時、謹則無曖𢖱、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:20:text
msgid "@plight You don't want it to break on ya."
msgstr "@plight 𤗆次空淶𫥨𪜀得耒。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:26:text
msgid "@plight_why It was worth a shot, yeah."
msgstr "@plight_why 唹時、拱當試𠬠吝。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:33:text
msgid ""
"@plight_why I'm losing so much time...\\nI'm not even timing it anymore..."
msgstr "@plight_why 損時間過。。。\\n英哙𠁙饞點𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:37:text
msgid ""
"@plight_why I'm losing so much time...\\nProbably \\v[22] minutes of work "
"already."
msgstr "@plight_why 損時間過。。。\\n形如英㐌𠅒\\v[22]𤼵𪵯工耒。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:40:text
msgid "@plight_why I'm losing so much time..."
msgstr "@plight_why 損時間過。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:45:text
msgid "@plight_why I hate this...."
msgstr "@plight_why 媄。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:48:text
msgid "@plight Do you think you'll be able to make that button?"
msgstr "@plight 㛪擬𣎏体製𫥨丐鈕妬空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:49:text
msgid "@plight_2 Well, no pressure, kid."
msgstr "@plight_2 啊時、據平靜催傉。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:50:text
msgid "@plight_2b I'll just... stick with my original plan for now..."
msgstr "@plight_2b 英𠱊。。。蹺計劃班頭催。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:51:text
msgid "@plight_2b Time to kick the door again."
msgstr "@plight_2b 𦤾𣅶跢𫔤發𡛤耒。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:4:70:text
msgid "@plight_why My foot hurts..."
msgstr "@plight_why 𤴬蹎過。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:5:text
msgid "@plight 6, 3, 0, 1, 4..."
msgstr "@plight 6、3、0、1、4。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:16:text deck/button:4:15:text
msgid "@plight_shock What!"
msgstr "@plight_shock 𢭶！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:17:text deck/button:4:16:text
msgid "@plight_shock It works!"
msgstr "@plight_shock 得實尼！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:19:text
msgid "@plight Guess I did it."
msgstr "@plight 丕𪜀英𪵯得耒哬。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:20:text
msgid "@niko_speak You sure did!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 董丕妬！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:21:text deck/button:4:24:text
msgid "@plight ...Anyway, ready to go? I'll be up ahead."
msgstr "@plight 。。。催時、𠫾𣗓㛪？英䟻於滕𠓀。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:37:text
msgid "@plight \\v[26], \\v[27], \\v[28], \\v[29], \\v[30]..."
msgstr "@plight \\v[26]、\\v[27]、\\v[28]、\\v[29]、\\v[30]。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:38:text deck/npc_plight:5:70:text
#: deck/button:4:40:text
msgid "[\\c[1]ACCESS DENIED.\\c[0]]"
msgstr "【\\c[1]權追及被辭挃。\\c[0]】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:39:text
msgid "[PLEASE MAKE HIM STOP.]"
msgstr "【吀唉拫𪝳些徠。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:46:text
msgid "@plight Hi."
msgstr "@plight 吀嘲。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:49:text
msgid "@plight ...Can I help with anything?"
msgstr "@plight 。。。英𣎏体𢴇之空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:50:text
msgid "@plight Anything at all?"
msgstr "@plight 不據之？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:51:text
msgid ""
"@plight_worry Being so unproductive for so long... It's really getting to "
"me..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 𡎥空嘍過。。。英扒頭𤻭𢬣耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:52:text
msgid "@niko I think \\p and I got it handled!"
msgstr "@niko 㛪擬\\p吧㛪㐌𣎏格！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:53:text
msgid "@niko What do you think, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko \\p、舅擬哰？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:55:choice:0
msgid "Tell him to use random codes"
msgstr "𠸒愥𢶸耚碼"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:55:choice:1
msgid "Tell him to stand there"
msgstr "𠸒愥𨅸安妬"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:60:text
msgid "@niko Maybe you can just try out some numbers until you get it..."
msgstr "@niko 昃𪜀英據入耚碼朱𦤾欺中催。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:62:text
msgid "@niko_speak I mean, \\p and I did it before!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 意𪜀、𠓀低㛪吧\\p㐌試吧成功！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:63:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Took us a while, but..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 唏損時間、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:64:text
msgid "@plight_worry ....seriously?"
msgstr "@plight_worry 。。。。實㫻？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:68:text
msgid "@plight Alright, I suppose that's better than doing nothing."
msgstr "@plight 拱得、卒欣𡎥空𪵯之。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:69:text
msgid "@plight Let's see... 0, 0, 0, 0, 0..."
msgstr "@plight 䀡鬧。。。0、0、0、0、0。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:71:text
msgid "@plight_why Yep, gonna be here for a while. 0, 0, 0, 0, 1....."
msgstr "@plight_why 唹、𠱊損𠬠𣅶蒂。0、0、0、0。1。。。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:72:text
msgid ""
"[\\c[1]ACCESS DENIED.\\c[0]\\| ...YOU AREN'T SERIOUSLY DOING THIS, ARE YOU?]"
msgstr "【\\c[1]權追及被辭挃。\\c[0]\\| 。。。伴實事𪵯役尼嘑？】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:76:text
msgid "@niko Maybe you can just take it easy for a while?"
msgstr "@niko 昃𪜀英據儗𢯕𠬠𣋩𠫾？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:77:text
msgid "@plight_why Hooray..."
msgstr "@plight_why 歡呼。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/npc_plight:5:78:text
msgid "@plight_why My least favorite thing to do..."
msgstr "@plight_why 條英恄𪵯一。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:2:1:text
msgid "@Niko It's an elevator."
msgstr "@Niko 簜𣛠。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:2:2:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Apparently broken?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣎏𨤔當閧？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:3:1:text
msgid "@niko_speak Let's fix the elevator!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠫾𢯢簜𣛠鬧！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:4:1:text
msgid "@niko_speak It needs a code."
msgstr "@niko_speak 衆些懃𠬠碼𢲫銙。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:2:text
msgid "@niko_yawn *yawn* ..."
msgstr "@niko_yawn ＊哈＊。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:3:text
msgid ""
"@niko I'm having trouble staying awake, \\p.\\>\\nWe should find a place for "
"me to take a nap..."
msgstr "@niko 眜𨉟扒頭𢬢徠耒\\p。\\>\\n𨉟懃尋𡊲𥄬。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:19:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Oh! Thank you for holding the elevator door open for me, mister!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！感恩英㐌𡨺𫔤朱㛪唲！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:20:text
msgid "@plight No prob, hop in."
msgstr "@plight 空哰、𠓨氐。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:23:text
msgid "@plight Oh hey, welcome back..."
msgstr "@plight 溩、嘲𢜏㛪𠭤徠。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:24:text
msgid "@plight_worry That... sure took you a while, huh..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 㛪𠫾拱。。。嘍㗶𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:25:text
msgid "@niko2 Oh, shoot! You've been waiting this whole time?"
msgstr "@niko2 喂！英𨅸䟻𠁸自妬𦤾𣇞哰？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:26:text
msgid "@niko And... holding the door open?"
msgstr "@niko 吧。。。𡨺𧵑𢲫？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:27:text
msgid "@plight_worry Well I uh...\\.\\. didn't want to be rude..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 時英唹。。。\\.\\.空㦖失禮。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:28:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'm sorry, I should've told you to go on ahead..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣩂、當𫥨㛪𢧚𠸒英據𠫾𠓀𠫾。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:6:29:text
msgid "@plight Eh, don't worry about it."
msgstr "@plight 啊、空哰兜𦓡。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/elevator doors:8:1:text
msgid "@niko I'll need to push the button to open the doors."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟𠱊沛𢶸鈕抵𢲫𫔤。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:2:text
msgid "@niko_what Huh, there aren't any buttons..."
msgstr "@niko_what 嗚、空𣎏鈕。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:5:text
msgid "@plight_why Yuuup, that's a problem."
msgstr "@plight_why 唹、問題於妬妬。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:6:text
msgid ""
"@plight_2b There's usually a big button here that says \"GROUND\" on it."
msgstr "@plight_2b 平常𣎏𠬠丐鈕孔路𥱬「𩈘𡐙」於低。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:7:text
msgid "@plight_2b Y'know, cuz it takes you to the ground area."
msgstr "@plight_2b 時、在爲伮迻㛪𬺗𩈘𡐙。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:8:text
msgid "@plight_wtf But now it's been ripped out? Or something?"
msgstr "@plight_wtf 扔𣎏𨤔伮被伆𫥨耒？唉哰妬？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:9:text
msgid "@plight_2 I tried looking everywhere for it, to no avail."
msgstr "@plight_2 英㐌試檢七坭、𦓡𠁙𧡊之叱。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:10:text
msgid "@plight_worry M...maybe it exploded..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 𣎏。。。𣎏欺伮砮噌耒拱𢧚。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:11:text
msgid "@niko_speak Do you think we'll have to make a new one?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 英擬𣎏沛𪵯徠丐㵋空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:12:text
msgid "@plight_worry ...what?"
msgstr "@plight_worry 。。。嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:13:text
msgid "@plight_worry How?"
msgstr "@plight_worry 憑格鬧？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:2:14:text
msgid "@niko We'll figure it out!"
msgstr "@niko 據抵𪨠㛪𢥈！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:2:text
msgid ""
"@niko That man said something about magnets, but I don't see a way to fit "
"these in the panel by themselves."
msgstr "@niko 愥𣎏吶之妬𧗱南針、扔𨉟空擬𣎏体據勢陧衆𠓨榜鈕。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:7:text
msgid "@niko The button fits snugly in the slot, but..."
msgstr "@niko 鈕𣃣𢝛𠓨溪、扔。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:8:text
msgid "@niko I'm not sure how to \"connect\" it."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟空別「結綏」伮𫥨哰。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:9:text
msgid "@plight Hmm..."
msgstr "@plight 嘘。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:10:text
msgid ""
"@plight All I know is that the button works by some kind of magnetic "
"technology."
msgstr "@plight 英只別𪜀丐鈕活動憑𠬠矯磁性之妬。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:11:text
msgid ""
"@plight_why ...Don't ask me how magnets work, though. I didn't even finish "
"high school..."
msgstr "@plight_why 。。。扔揨𠳨英南針活動勢鬧唲。英哙空學歇級𠀧。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:18:text
msgid "@niko_speak Alright, let's hope this works!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 得耒、懞丐尼活動！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:19:text
msgid "@niko The button fits snugly, and..."
msgstr "@niko 鈕𣃣𢝛𠓨𡓇、吧。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:20:text
msgid "@niko_speak I think I hear the machine powering on!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 形如𣛠𢪮當活動𠭤徠！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:23:text
msgid "@niko_what The button completely fell apart!"
msgstr "@niko_what 丐鈕𥒮散𫥨耒！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:24:text
msgid "@plight_2b Hey, you tried."
msgstr "@plight_2b 催時、㛪㐌固耒。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:34:text
msgid "@niko Let's hope this works..."
msgstr "@niko 懞丐尼活動。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:62:text
msgid "[REACTIVATING ELEVATOR SERVICES.\\|.\\|.]"
msgstr "【當起動徠役務簜𣛠。\\|。\\|。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:63:text
msgid "[PLEASE INPUT SECURITY CODE TO CONTINUE]"
msgstr "【𢝙𢚸入碼保密抵接續】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:64:text
msgid "@plight_shock ...What?"
msgstr "@plight_shock 。。。嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:65:text
msgid "@plight_wtf That's... never happened before."
msgstr "@plight_wtf 丐蒂。。。𢵻曾侈𫥨𠓀低。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:66:text
msgid "@niko_speak The... squares?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 塊。。。𣃱𧘇嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:67:text
msgid "@plight_worry Huh?"
msgstr "@plight_worry 嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:68:text
msgid "@niko_speak You saw them, right?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 英拱𧡊𦓡、董空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:69:text
msgid "@niko They were on the door, and..."
msgstr "@niko 衆於𨑗𫔤、吧。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:70:text
msgid "@plight_2b Oh, nah. The square stuff happens all the time."
msgstr "@plight_2b 啊、空。塊𣃱出現如𩚵𩛷𧘇𦓡。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:71:text
msgid "@plight I meant the whole \"security code\" thing."
msgstr "@plight 意英𪜀務「碼保密」幾。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:72:text
msgid "@plight But then again, the elevator hasn't been this broken before..."
msgstr "@plight 扔時、拱爲簜𣛠𣗓被閧勢尼包𣇞。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:73:text
msgid "@niko Hmmm...."
msgstr "@niko 嘘。。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:74:text
msgid "@niko_speak I guess we should go look for a code, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 昃𪜀𨉟沛𠫾尋碼催\\p。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:83:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed That's not gonna work..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 如勢空得兜。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:87:text
msgid "@niko Hmmm..."
msgstr "@niko 嘘。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:88:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak If it's been ripped out, how come there aren't any broken wires "
"inside the empty slot?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 裊伮被伆𫥨、勢哰徠空𣎏絏綏鬧𥪝溪丕？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:91:text
msgid "@plight Well, I'm no engineer, but...."
msgstr "@plight 時、英拯沛技師之、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:3:92:text
msgid ""
"@plight_2b It's powered by some kind of magnetic technology, I know this "
"much."
msgstr "@plight_2b 英𣎏別𪜀伮活動憑𠬠類工藝磁性鬧妬。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:4:1:text
msgid "[PLEASE INPUT SECURITY CODE TO CONTINUE.]"
msgstr "【𢝙𢚸入碼保密抵接續。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:4:17:text
msgid "@plight_shock I don't know what you did, but it actually works!"
msgstr "@plight_shock 英空別㛪𣃣𪵯之、扔伮活動耒尼！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:4:19:text
msgid "@plight Good job, kid."
msgstr "@plight 唉𡗋妬傉。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:4:20:text
msgid "@plight You're a genius, you know that?"
msgstr "@plight 㛪𪜀天才妬、㛪別空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:4:21:text
msgid "@niko_speak Well, I had help from \\p too!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 啊、㛪拱得\\p𢴇扡𦓡！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:4:22:text
msgid "@plight_worry ...Oh, right."
msgstr "@plight_worry 。。。啊、沛耒。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:4:23:text
msgid "@plight_worry The whole messiah business."
msgstr "@plight_worry 爲㛪𪜀𠎬救世𦓡。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/button:5:1:text
msgid "@niko_speak The button works!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 鈕𢶸活動耒！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Map Events:2:14:text
msgid "@niko What was that?"
msgstr "@niko 之妬？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Map Events:4:7:text Maps/SQUARES BE GONE/Elevator
msgid "@plight_unknown WHY. ISN'T. THIS. WORKING??!?"
msgstr "@plight_unknown 在。哰。伮。閧？？！？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Map Events:4:8:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...I..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Map Events:4:9:text
msgid "@niko_speak ....think someone might need help."
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。。擬𣎏埃妬懃𢴇扡。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/you tried:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Oh well..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𧘇它。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/screen5:1:1:text Maps/FINALE/study/EV047:1:1:text
#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV048:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A bulletin board with lots of papers on it."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠榜信釘窒𡗉紙詞。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:1:2:text Events:1:5:text
msgid "@niko It's a shelf full of books."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠架𣹓冊。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:2:2:text
msgid "@niko It's a tea set."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠部𩐛盞茶。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:2:5:text
msgid "@niko There's a glass tea set on the table."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠬠部𩐛盞水晶𨑗盤。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:2:6:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm Tea DOES sound really nice right now..."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 𣊾𣇞㕵茶拱窒合蒂。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:2:7:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Too bad there's no water in here..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 惜𪜀𥪝尼空𣎏渃。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:3:1:text
msgid "@niko Black clovers in a glass case."
msgstr "@niko 𦹯𠀧蘿黰𥪝匣鏡。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:4:2:text Events:4:5:text
msgid "@niko It's a big book on the table."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠卷冊𡘯𨑗盤。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:5:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a pilot's helmet."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠隻𢃱保險𧵑飛工。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:6:2:text
msgid "@niko The door is gone."
msgstr "@niko 𦑃𫔤㐌變𠅒。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:6:5:text
msgid "@niko2 The door is... gone?"
msgstr "@niko2 𦑃𫔤。。。變𠅒耒哰？"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:6:6:text
msgid "@proto2b [Well, the door does not exist without us there.]"
msgstr "@proto2b 【時、裊𪨠英空𣎏𩈘時𦑃𫔤𠱊空存在。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:6:7:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Guess I can't go back out, huh..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 丕𪜀𨉟空𠭤𫥨外得、𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:6:8:text
msgid "@proto2 [...Do you need to?]"
msgstr "@proto2 【。。。㛪𣎏懃空？】"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:6:9:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...not really."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。空𪳨。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:7:34:text
msgid "@rue_sigh That was... quite peculiar..."
msgstr "@rue_sigh 可𪜀。。。𨓐常妬。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:7:35:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh2 I'll say!"
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 英同意！"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:7:36:text
msgid "@proto_jealous [...]"
msgstr "@proto_jealous 【。。。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:7:38:text
msgid "@cedric_talk Hey, this is..."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 尼、低𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:7:88:text
msgid "@rue_oh ...The World Machine."
msgstr "@rue_oh 。。。𣛠全世。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:8:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's a blueprint!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠬠版𦘧！"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:8:5:text
msgid "@niko A big, detailed drawing of a machine with lots of tv screens."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅𦘧𡘯、𣘊數𠬠鈷𣛠𡘯喟𡗉幔形無線。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:8:6:text
msgid "@proto2b [...That's called a blueprint, Niko.]"
msgstr "@proto2b 【。。。哙𪜀版𦘧妬、尼孤。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/Map Events:8:8:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes ...So THAT's what a blueprint is!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 。。。丕版𦘧𪜀如丕哰！"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV019:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_speak They're watercolor sticks!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔錆𦭷渃！"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV027:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a piece of amber on a string."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𠰳琥珀𨑗絏傳。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV027:1:2:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Looks just like that necklace the robot lady showed me..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 矓依如丐𤥑𦙶姉𠊛𣛠朱𨉟䀡。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV028:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A coat rack with a scarf and a big jacket."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠架撩𣎏𠬠隻巾𫏈𦙶吧襖𢸠𡘯。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV040:1:1:text
msgid "@rue_talk The room ahead doesn't really lead anywhere, but..."
msgstr "@rue_talk 間房𠌨𠓀寔𫥨空𠫾𦤾兜、扔。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV040:1:2:text
msgid "@rue \\p should still remember what to do here."
msgstr "@rue \\p𣎏𨤰吻𢖵役懃𪵯𣊾𣇞。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV041:1:2:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Of course, this is just a copy of it..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 必然、低只𪜀𠬠版抄𧵑伮。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV041:1:5:text
msgid "@cedric This is my father's study."
msgstr "@cedric 低𪜀書房𧵑仛。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV041:1:6:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh It feels like...\\.\\. he's still here, doesn't it?"
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 感覺如。。。\\.\\.仛吻於低、沛空？"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV041:1:7:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh ...like he's still with us."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 。。。如体仛吻哙喟衆些。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV041:1:8:text
msgid "@rue_sad ...Yeah."
msgstr "@rue_sad 。。。𫫡。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV042:1:2:text
msgid "@proto2b [...This place contains a lot of memories.]"
msgstr "@proto2b 【。。。坭尼貯撜無萬記憶。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV042:1:3:text
msgid "@proto_eyeclosed [I am... grateful, to see it again.]"
msgstr "@proto_eyeclosed 【英窒。。。別恩、欺得𧡊伮吝𡛤。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV046:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a stack of books."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𥔧冊。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV047:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak Photos too!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 吧影𡛤！"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV048:1:2:text
msgid "@niko A scribbly drawing is pinned up here."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅𦘧㨯擭得釘𨑗尼。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV049:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a big photo."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅影𡘯。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV049:1:2:text
msgid "@niko2 Wait, no...\\.\\. it's a painting!"
msgstr "@niko2 啊、空。。。\\.\\.𪜀𠬠幅𦘧！"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV049:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Hard to tell at first..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 唏𠸋分別𠬠𡭧。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV053:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A box filled with folders and loose paper."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠匣貯鋏材料吧紙𡊠。"

#: Maps/FINALE/study/EV054:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A box full of notebooks and sketchbooks."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠匣𣹓籔𥱬劄吧籔樸草。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV005:1:1:text
msgid "These robots are malfunctioning at a frightening rate."
msgstr "仍𠊛𣛠當﨤難喟速度窒當𢥈礙。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV005:1:2:text
msgid ""
"Physical damage from square-particle anomalies is almost impossible to "
"revert."
msgstr "作動物理自各事固塊𣃱近如空体倒逆。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV005:1:3:text
msgid "No living person can touch them, unless they have a death wish."
msgstr "空𠬠𠊛𤯩鬧𣎏体𪮻𠓨衆、除欺㦖𣩂。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV005:1:4:text
msgid ""
".\\..\\..But if we're lucky, sometimes the squares go away on their own."
msgstr "。\\.。\\.。扔裊𢆪慜、𢷮欺扔形𣃱𠱊自捽𨆢。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV005:1:5:text
msgid "...but not before taking away one of the robot's arms, or legs."
msgstr "。。。只𢖖󠄁欺𥙩𠅒𠬠𢬣、或蹎𧵑𠊛𣛠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV005:1:6:text
msgid "...or head."
msgstr "。。。或頭。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV005:1:7:text
msgid "@niko_huh ...okay."
msgstr "@niko_huh 。。。嗚雞。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV005:2:1:text
msgid ""
"I don't know if you've ever seen a headless robot before, but it is quite a "
"sight to behold."
msgstr "空別㛪㐌包𣇞𧡊𠊛𣛠𠅒頭貯、扔果寔𪜀𠬠奇觀。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV005:2:2:text
msgid "And also quite dangerous."
msgstr "吧拱窒危險𡛤。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV006:1:1:text
msgid "[I CANNOT STOP SPINNING.]"
msgstr "【𪝬空体凝搓。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:1:1:text
msgid "This is so tedious!"
msgstr "𢥇過！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:1:2:text
msgid "I miss the good ol' days before our robot-repairing-robots broke down."
msgstr "𪝬𢖵仍𣈜𣎃𠓀欺仍𠊛𣛠𢵻𠊛𣛠𧵑衆𪝬被閧。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:1:3:text
msgid "Now all the robots have to be assembled by actual people."
msgstr "𣇞𠊛𣛠調沛由𠊛實擸撘。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:1:4:text
msgid "@niko_speak But... aren't you a robot?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔。。。拯沛伴𪜀𠊛𣛠哰?"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:1:5:text
msgid "No?"
msgstr "空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:1:6:text
msgid "I mean, Do I SOUND like a robot to you?"
msgstr "意𪜀、伴𣎏𧡊𪝬𣎏吶𡀯如𠊛𣛠空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:1:7:text
msgid "@niko Not really."
msgstr "@niko 空𪳨。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:1:8:text
msgid "@niko_speak But... your head is a tv?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔。。。頭伴𪜀𠬠丐無線𦓡？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:1:9:text
msgid "W...what does that have to do with anything?"
msgstr "時。。。時連關之渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:1:11:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...nevermind."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。偈𠫾。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:2:1:text
msgid "We should probably fix the robot-repairing-robots first."
msgstr "衆些𢧚𢯢扔𠊛𣛠𢯢𠊛𣛠恪𠓀。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV007:2:2:text
msgid "But the higher-ups need these guys done first for some reason..."
msgstr "扔上層徠㦖𢯢𬉆󠄁尼𠓀幾。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd
#: room/right-robots/EV015:1:1:text
msgid "@niko This one isn't active..."
msgstr "@niko 𡥵尼當空活動。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/right-robots/map
#: event:1:1:text
msgid "[BOOP.]"
msgstr "【芣。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/2nd room/right-robots/map
#: event:1:2:text
msgid "[WE ARE WAITING TO BE REPAIRED.]"
msgstr "【衆𪝬當䟻𢯢𢵻。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV003:1:1:text
msgid "$SELF-CHARGING SOLAR BATTERY MODEL N-87\\n(One year warranty included)"
msgstr "$汴𩈘𡗶自𠻓母N-87\\n（包𠁟保行𠬠𢆥）"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV003:1:2:text
msgid ""
"$Simply place your self-charging battery in full daylight with the lens "
"facing up."
msgstr "$只懃撻汴𩈘𡗶自𠻓𧵑伴𨑜暎\\n𤏬𩈘𡗶喟透鏡向𬨠𨑗。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV003:1:4:text
msgid "$Charges in seconds, no external power is needed."
msgstr "$𠻓𥪝𣆰𣋩、空懃源電外。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV003:1:6:text
msgid "$TROUBLESHOOTING MANUAL."
msgstr "$向引克服纇"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV003:1:7:text
msgid ""
"$If the battery fails to charge, check to see if the lens on the front side "
"has not been dislodged during transport."
msgstr "$裊汴𠻓空𬨠、𢝙𢚸檢查透鏡\\n𨑗𩈘𠓀𣎏被𨖨𫥨𥪝過程\\n運轉唉空。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV003:1:8:text
msgid "$One charge cycle will last about ten days."
msgstr "$𠬠周期𠻓用得𥪝曠𨑮𣈜。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:13:text
msgid "@niko The screen says \"DOCUMENTS\"."
msgstr "@niko 幔形𥱬「DOCUMENTS」。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:14:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I can't seem to make the computer do anything else..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 䀡𫥨𨉟空𪵯之恪得喟丐𣛠併。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:21:text
msgid "@ed [The code is contained within a \\c[2]Document\\c[0].]"
msgstr "@ed 【密碼於𥪝𠬠\\c[2]Document\\c[0]。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:22:condition
msgid "Do you know where to find Documents, \\p?"
msgstr "伴別尋Documents於兜渚、\\p？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:24:text interior/pc:2:45:text
msgid "@ed [Good. Start looking.]"
msgstr "@ed 【卒。𠫾尋𠫾。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:27:text
msgid ""
"@ed [Don't you know that there's a designated area for \\c[2]Documents\\c[0] "
"on your own machine?]"
msgstr "@ed 【伴空別𨑗𣛠伴𣎏𠬠𡊲𥢆朱\\c[2]材料\\c[0]哰？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:28:text
msgid "@ed [Some god you are.]"
msgstr "@ed 【神聖矯之丕𡗶。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:30:text
msgid "@ed [Look in the Documents folder on your computer.]"
msgstr "@ed 【唉檢查𥪝書目Documents𨑗𣛠併𧵑伴。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:31:text
msgid "@ed [I don't think I could've made it any more clear.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𪝬吶𤽸𫥨耒蒂。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:40:text
msgid "@ed [I see you've made progress in this world, \\p.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𪝬𧡊伴㐌𣎏進步一定𥪝世界尼、\\p。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:41:text
msgid "@ed [But that progress stops here.]"
msgstr "@ed 【扔進步妬𠱊仃徠在低。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:42:text
msgid "@ed [I believe you need a code to unlock a certain box.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𪝬別伴懃𠬠密碼抵𢲫銙𠬠匣鬧妬。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:43:text
msgid "@ed [Well, the code no longer exists in THIS world.]"
msgstr "@ed 【時、密碼妬空哙存在𥪝世界尼𡛤。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:43:condition
msgid "...Do you understand what this means, \\p?"
msgstr "。。。伴矯條尼義𪜀之渚、\\p？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:48:text
msgid ""
"@ed [You... still don't know the extent of the world's deterioration, do "
"you, \\p?]"
msgstr "@ed 【勢𪜀。。。伴吻空曉世界尼㐌衰竭𦤾𣞪鬧、沛空、\\p？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:50:text
msgid ""
"@ed [...most of the time, stray pieces of this world would be lost to "
"blissful nothingness.]"
msgstr "@ed 【。。。份𡘯時間、仍𤗖砵𧵑世界尼𠱊𠭤城虛空。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:51:text
msgid "@ed [But this code, this \\c[2]Document\\c[0], is an exception.]"
msgstr "@ed 【扔密碼尼、\\c[2]材料\\c[0]尼、𪜀𠬠外例。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:52:text
msgid ""
"@ed [I was able to salvage it, because Niko needs the code to progress.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𪝬㐌救得伮、爲尼孤懃碼尼抵接續。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/pc:2:53:text
msgid "@ed [Now, go find it.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𣇞時𠫾尋伮𠫾。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:1:2:text
msgid "@niko This bar should open it."
msgstr "@niko 丐錆尼昃𪜀𠱊𢲫得伮。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:1:8:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed The pipe won't fit under the cracks, \\p!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 丐䈵尼空陧𣃣𠓨溪、\\p！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:1:9:text
msgid "@niko We'll need to flatten it somehow..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟𠱊沛尋格𡏽塝伮。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:1:14:text
msgid "@niko The screwdriver's not nearly big enough to pry it open."
msgstr "@niko 須𥿀時空覩𫰅抵𢭄𢲫伮。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:1:18:text
msgid "@niko_speak This box looks interesting!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 丐匣尼矓趣味妬！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:1:20:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I wish I had something to pry it open with..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣎏丐之抵𢭄𢲫伮時咍。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:2:4:text
msgid "@niko There's a little metal cube and some broken glass in here..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠬠塊金類𡮈𢭲𠬠𠃣水晶𥒮𥪝尼。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:2:5:text
msgid "@niko_speak Looks like what used to be a machine part."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏𨤔伮㐌層𪜀𠬠零件之妬。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:2:6:text
msgid "@niko It says 'Solar Battery' on the side."
msgstr "@niko 伮𣎏𥱬「汴𩈘𡗶」。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:3:1:text
msgid "@niko It's empty now."
msgstr "@niko 匣㐌筩。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/batbox:3:2:text
msgid "@niko Still got some shards of glass at the bottom, though."
msgstr "@niko 吻哙𠬠𠃣水晶於𨑜底。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV007:2:2:text
msgid "[DID YOU POWER THE GENERATOR?]"
msgstr "【伴㐌起動𣛠發電哰？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV007:2:3:text
msgid "@niko I...\\.\\. \\@niko_speak guess we did!"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟。。。\\.\\. \\@niko_speak 斷勢！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV007:2:4:text
msgid "@niko Right, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 沛空、\\p？"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV008:2:2:text
msgid "[I CAN WALK!]"
msgstr "【𪝬𣎏体𠫾徠耒！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Map events:1:1:text interior/Backroom/Map
#: events:2:1:text
msgid "@niko Dusty shelves."
msgstr "@niko 架冊𢵉𡏧。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV011:1:1:text
msgid ""
"$1. A robot may not injure a living person or, through inaction, allow a "
"person to come to harm."
msgstr "$一・𠊛𣛠空体𪵯損傷𠬠𠊛𤯩、或𠬃嚜𠬠𠊛𤯩被傷。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV011:1:3:text
msgid ""
"$2. A robot must obey the orders given to it by people, except where such "
"orders would conflict with the First Law."
msgstr "$二・𠊛𣛠沛遵守命令自𡥵𠊛、除欺命令妬矛盾𢭲條次一。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV011:1:5:text
msgid ""
"$3. A robot must protect its own existence as long as such protection does "
"not conflict with the First or Second Law."
msgstr "$三・𠊛𣛠沛保衛本身免𪜀空𠫾逆徠𢭲條次一或二。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV012:1:1:text interior/EV013:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a faded poster."
msgstr "@niko  𠬠𬌓押澼㗑𦭷。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV012:1:2:text
msgid "$REMINDER TO ALL WORKERS:"
msgstr "$通告朱全体工人："

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV012:1:3:text
msgid ""
"$The rarest form of blue phosphor is found during the phosphor shrimp's "
"spawn period."
msgstr "$𣎏体尋𧡊体險一𧵑光素青𥪝期生產𧵑𩵽光素。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV012:1:5:text
msgid ""
"$If you observe a pond with a bubbled-over surface, please contact "
"management immediately!"
msgstr "$裊伴發現湖渃𣎏皮𩈘撫琫琫、𢝙𢚸連係班管理𬆄立即！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV012:1:6:text
msgid "$We will dispatch a harvest team ASAP."
msgstr "$班𠱊舉隊摘出即時。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV013:1:2:text
msgid "$Five new positions available at the mines."
msgstr "$懃選𠄼位置㵋在𡌢𡎡。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV013:1:3:text
msgid "$Housing and other provisions are included upon hiring."
msgstr "$特權包𠁟茹於吧各助給恪。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV013:1:4:text
msgid "$First come, first serve."
msgstr "$優先𠊛登記𠓀。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV014:1:1:text
msgid "$The use of a robot as our replacement head engineer seems unorthodox."
msgstr "$使用𠬠𠊛𣛠𪵯技師長繼任𣎏𨤔咳不常。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV014:1:2:text
msgid "$...especially the one responsible for last year's incident."
msgstr "$。。。特別𪜀欺用𠊛𨠳𫥨事故𠄼𢫑。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV014:1:4:text
msgid ""
"$I suppose they had to get her away from the city, but that doesn't make it "
"easier to swallow for those of us who work here!"
msgstr "$昃𪜀𣱆沛迻姑𧘇𨖨𠺌城庯、扔拱空𪵯朱局𤯩𧵑衆𪝬易咀欣𪜀包！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV014:1:5:text
msgid "$I hope that man knows what he's doing."
msgstr "$懞英𧘇別𨉟當𪵯之。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/EV014:1:6:text
msgid "$--Management"
msgstr "$－－班管理"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV029:1:1:text
msgid "$Apparently, phase 1 of the evacuation ended prematurely."
msgstr "$形如、階段𠬠𧵑澾疏散㐌結束不常。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV029:1:2:text
msgid "$The big ships started malfunctioning only after a few round trips."
msgstr "$仍艚𡘯﨤軸𨁷只𢖖󠄁𠄧吝過徠。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV029:1:4:text
msgid "$They said it was due to... something with squares?"
msgstr "$𣱆𠸒哴由。。。塊𣃱之妬？"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV029:1:5:text
msgid "$I'm not sure what they mean by that."
msgstr "$空曉𣱆當吶之𡛤。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV029:1:7:text
msgid ""
"$Bummer, looks like they won't be able to transport most of these surplus "
"bots to the city at this rate."
msgstr "$啲、𣎏𨤔𣱆𠱊空轉及份𡘯仍𠊛𣛠餘𦤾城庯。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV029:1:8:text
msgid "$And we worked so hard on those!"
msgstr "$𦓡衆𪝬㐌𧶄𫥨包𡗉工飭𡏦𥩯衆渚！"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV029:1:10:text
msgid ""
"$But I suppose the rowbots are busy enough with transporting people as is."
msgstr "$扔𪝬擬仍𠊛𣛠棹船㐌覩絆褓運轉𠊛耒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV029:1:11:text
msgid "$I think it's going to be our turn soon..."
msgstr "$形如拱𢯛𦤾𦀎衆𪝬耒。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV030:1:1:text
msgid "$Looks like they're evacuating the few tamed robots we have here."
msgstr "$𣎏𨤔𣱆當疏散訥仍𠊛𣛠純化於低。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV030:1:2:text
msgid ""
"$Makes sense... no point in keeping them in the Barrens if all the people "
"are already gone."
msgstr "$拱合理啐。。。空体𡨺衆徠塳邊疆裊如𡥵𠊛㐌捽歇耒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV030:1:4:text
msgid "$I wonder if the engineer is going too..."
msgstr "$空別技師長𣎏𠫾蹺空。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV031:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Oh! It's another one of these small machines."
msgstr "@niko 溩！徠𪜀𠬠丐𣛠𡮈𡛤。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV031:2:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak There's writing on this one too!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨑗尼拱𣎏𡨸𢪏尼！"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/EV031:2:3:text
msgid "@niko It says \"Guardian of Residential Area\"."
msgstr "@niko 伮𥱬𪜀「𠊛更擱區民居」。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/fireflies:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Lots of tiny shrimp swimming in this jar..."
msgstr "@niko 窒𡗉𩵽𬈺𥪝丐𤮗尼。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Dormitories/119 - cell/fireflies:1:2:text
msgid "@niko It's looking a little dim..."
msgstr "@niko 咳𣋁𠬠𡭧。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/EV004:1:1:text sky/Apartments/EV005:1:1:text
#: sky/Apartments/EV006:1:1:text
msgid "APARTMENTS"
msgstr "區間戶"

#: Maps/SQUARES BE GONE/Gate/map events:1:2:text Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/map
msgid "@niko2 ...\\>\\nHe has no power..."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。\\>\\n舅𧘇空𣎏電。。。"

#: Maps/SQUARES BE GONE/Gate/map events:1:5:text
msgid ""
"@green_gatekeeper [Please do not approach.\\>\\nThis area is dangerous.]"
msgstr "@green_gatekeeper 【𢝙𢚸空徠近。\\>\\n區域尼危險。】"

#: Maps/SQUARES BE GONE/Gate/EV205:1:1:text Maps/POSTGAME
#: green/Gate/EV205:1:1:text
msgid "@niko3 The bridge is out..."
msgstr "@niko3 橋被閧耒。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/generator:1:17:text
msgid "@niko_speak The battery fits the slot perfectly!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫪐汴𣃣𢝛𠓨溪！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/generator:1:18:text
msgid "@niko Looks like we're on the right track."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔些當𠫾董向。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/generator:1:19:text
msgid "@niko ...but...nothing happened."
msgstr "@niko 。。。扔。。。空𣎏之侈耒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/generator:1:25:text
msgid "@niko_speak Let's hope the charged battery does something!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 懞𪜀𫪐汴𣹓𣎏体𪵯之妬！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/generator:1:51:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes Whoa!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 𫽿！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/generator:1:56:text
msgid "@niko_speak That's a big machine!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠬠鈷𣛠𡘯妬！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/generator:1:57:text
msgid "@niko It doesn't seem to be doing anything, though..."
msgstr "@niko 扔𣎏𨤔伮當空𪵯之。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/generator:1:58:text
msgid "@niko There's a rectangle-shaped hole in the middle."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠬠𡓇形𡨸日於𡧲。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/generator:1:59:text
msgid "@niko_speak Looks like something used to fit in here..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏𨤔㐌曾𣎏之妬𥪝尼。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/EV007:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A page with faded ink."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠張紙㐌沛墨。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/EV007:1:2:text
msgid ""
"$-able to provide power to all robots and machinery in the area via a large "
"electromagnetic field."
msgstr "$－体發電朱全部𠊛𣛠吧設備𥪝區域統過𠬠場電磁𡘯。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/EV007:1:3:text
msgid "$Maintenance efforts are quite high, as expected."
msgstr "$如預斷𠓀、懃可𡗉人力保持。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/EV007:1:5:text
msgid ""
"$We have provided customized backup cells for the few most important robots."
msgstr "$衆些㐌拱給汴預防隨整朱数𠃣𠊛𣛠關重一。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/EV007:1:6:text
msgid ""
"$Their electromagnetic fields are much weaker, and the signals are highly "
"specific."
msgstr "$場電磁𧵑衆要欣𡗉、吧信號特殊欣。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/EV007:1:8:text
msgid "$In other words, these small cells can only charge one single-"
msgstr "$吶格恪、汴尼只𣎏体𠻓𠬠－"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/EV007:1:9:text
msgid "@niko The rest of the page is unreadable."
msgstr "@niko 份哙徠𧵑張紙空体讀浽。"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/Map events:1:5:text
#: Maps/Green/Research Station/Power room/EV004:2:5:text
msgid "@niko_speak I don't wanna get shocked again, \\p!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟空㦖備𪮞電𡛤兜\\p！"

#: Maps/Blue/Outpost/Outpost interior/Backroom/Map events:1:12:text
#: Maps/Green/Research Station/Power room/EV004:2:12:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I just got shocked..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟𣃣備𪮞耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:4:text
#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:31:text
msgid "@watcher Good morning."
msgstr "@watcher 嘲𣇜𤏬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:8:text
#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:35:text
msgid "@watcher Good afternoon."
msgstr "@watcher 嘲𣇜朝。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:12:text
#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:39:text
msgid "@watcher Good evening."
msgstr "@watcher 嘲𣇜𣋁。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:15:text
#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:42:text
msgid "@watcher ...It's very late."
msgstr "@watcher 。。。㐌窒𣅘耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:22:text
msgid "@watcher Please leave me be."
msgstr "@watcher 吀唉抵𪝬安。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:23:text
msgid "@watcher We are running out of time."
msgstr "@watcher 時間當𣴓𢴍。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:26:text
msgid "@watcher Here we are, at the eleventh hour."
msgstr "@watcher 衆些當於低、𣇞次𨑮𠬠。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:28:text
msgid "@niko2 Shouldn't you be...\\.\\.with the other evacuees?"
msgstr "@niko2 拯沛伴𢧚。。。\\.\\.於邊各移民哙徠哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:29:text
msgid "@watcher Maybe."
msgstr "@watcher 𣎏体。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:31:text
msgid "@watcher I wonder if the big clock has reached zero yet..."
msgstr "@watcher 空別銅壺𡘯㐌𪮻数空貯。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/watcher:1:32:text
msgid "@watcher I want to be right here when everything ends."
msgstr "@watcher 𪝬㦖於低欺𤗆次𠫾𦤾回結。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:16:text
msgid "@watcher But... good day, I suppose."
msgstr "@watcher 扔。。。唒丕、𠬠𣈜惵𡗶。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:24:text
msgid "@watcher Your time here is precious."
msgstr "@watcher 時間𧵑伴於低窒貴價。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:25:text
msgid "@watcher Please, do cherish it."
msgstr "@watcher 吀唉珍重伮。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:26:text
msgid "@niko I will!"
msgstr "@niko 𫫡！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:43:text
msgid ""
"@watcher It's not healthy for children such as yourself to stay up at this "
"hour."
msgstr "@watcher 𥅞𣅘𦤾勢尼空卒朱稚㛪如㛪兜。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:44:text
msgid "@niko ...Really?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。實唹？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:45:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...I... didn't realize..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。㛪。。。空認𫥨。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:46:text
msgid "@watcher Can't blame you."
msgstr "@watcher 拱空責㛪得。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:47:text room/watcher:1:60:text
msgid "@watcher With the sun gone, the night never seems to end."
msgstr "@watcher 𢖖󠄁欺𩈘𡗶變𠅒、幔點羕如不盡。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:48:text
msgid "@niko_speak Then... how can you tell?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 勢時。。。𪵯哰英別得？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:49:text room/watcher:1:62:text
msgid "@niko Time, I mean."
msgstr "@niko 意㛪𪜀、𣇞𥋏𧘇。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:50:text room/watcher:1:63:text
msgid "@watcher I have my ways."
msgstr "@watcher 英𣎏格𧵑英。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:59:text
msgid "@watcher ...Well, the time of day doesn't really mean anything now."
msgstr "@watcher 。。。怞哰時、𣇞𥋏拱拯哙意義之𡛤耒。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/entry room/watcher:1:61:text
msgid "@niko_speak Then... How can you tell?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 丕時。。。𪵯哰英別得？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/Map Events:1:2:text
msgid "@silver [Wait!]"
msgstr "@silver 【寬㐌！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/Map Events:1:40:text
msgid "@silver [I saw you heading towards this direction.]"
msgstr "@silver 【姉𧡊㛪𠫾𧗱向尼。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/Map Events:1:41:text
msgid ""
"@silver [The mines have been abandoned for a long time, I cannot guarantee "
"that it's safe.]"
msgstr "@silver 【𡌢𡎡㐌備𠬃荒𠬠時間𨱽、姉空膽保伮哙安全。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/Map Events:1:42:text
msgid ""
"@silver [If you must enter it, it is my duty to accompany you at least once.]"
msgstr "@silver 【裊㛪㦖𠓨、姉𣎏義務沛蹺㛪𠓨𠃣一𠬠吝。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/Map Events:1:43:text
msgid "@niko Oh, thanks!"
msgstr "@niko 溩、感恩吖！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/Map Events:1:53:text
msgid ""
"@niko The entrance is roped off...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak And there's a sign "
"here:"
msgstr "@niko 𡓃𠓨備絏浱徠。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 吧𣎏匾報𥱬："

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/Map Events:1:54:text
msgid ""
"$WARNING:\\nAuthorized personnel only!\\n\\nVisitors must see the Head "
"Engineer for permission to enter the mines."
msgstr "$注意：\\n空分事免𠓨！\\n\\n客𦤾探沛﨤技師長抵得法𠓨𡌢𡎡。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/Map Events:1:55:text
msgid "@niko I guess we should find the Head Engineer..."
msgstr "@niko 衆𨉟𢧚𠫾尋技師長催。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/Power
#: room/npc_mechanic:1:2:text
msgid "[COMMUNICATIONS WITH THE SURFACE HAVE BEEN LOST.]"
msgstr "【㐌𠅒聯絡喟𩈘𡐙。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/Power
#: room/npc_mechanic:1:3:text
msgid "[I AM UNABLE TO DO ANYTHING.]"
msgstr "【𪝬空体𪵯之。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/Power
#: room/EV008:1:2:text
msgid "$WHO TOOK MY STAPLER"
msgstr "$埃𥙩𡏽捦𧵑𪝬耒"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/Power
#: room/EV009:1:1:text
msgid "@niko There are some small holes on the table..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠄧𡓇𡮈𨑗盤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/Power
#: room/EV009:1:2:text room/EV010:1:2:text
msgid "@niko Looks like something was bolted here before..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔㐌曾𣎏之妬得㨂釘𠓨低。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/entry room/Power
#: room/EV010:1:1:text
msgid "@niko There's some small holes on the table..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠄧𡓇𡮈𨑗盤。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:6:text
msgid "[ARE YOU HERE TO PURCHASE A COPY?]"
msgstr "【伴㦖𧷸𠬠版空？】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:7:text
msgid "@niko ...No?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:8:text
msgid "@niko_speak Newspapers are for grown-ups!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 報紙𪜀朱𠊛𡘯𦓡！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:9:text
msgid "[GROWN...UPS?]"
msgstr "【𠊛。。。𡘯？】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:11:text
msgid "[WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?]"
msgstr "【𪜀之丕？】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:12:text
msgid "@niko_speak It means people who aren't kids!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𪜀仍𠊛空沛稚𡥵𧘇！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:13:text
msgid "[KIDS?]"
msgstr "【稚𡥵？】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:14:text
msgid "@niko ...er...aren't you a kid?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。唹。。。舅空沛稚𡥵哰？】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:15:text
msgid "[I AM A ROBOT.]"
msgstr "【𪝬𪜀𠊛𣛠。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV008:1:16:text 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:32:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout
#: point/Cabin/npc_silver:4:44:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Right..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 沛耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:2:text
msgid "Don't lose faith."
msgstr "揨𠅒念信。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:6:text
msgid "@niko You alright?"
msgstr "@niko 伴穩渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:7:text
msgid "Ah, the messiah. Perhaps this is a sign."
msgstr "啊、𠎬救世。𣎏𨤰低𪜀恬報。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:8:text
msgid "Tell me, do you think you can fix the world with the sun?"
msgstr "伮𪝬𦖑、伴擬𣎏体𢯢𢵻全世界憑𩈘𡗶空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:9:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Honestly, I don't know..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 實𫥨、𨉟空別𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:10:text
msgid "@niko I've been getting mixed messages..."
msgstr "@niko 𤗆𠊛調𠸒𨉟仍次恪僥。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:11:text
msgid "I know."
msgstr "𪝬別。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:12:text
msgid "But what do YOU think?"
msgstr "扔伴實事擬哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:13:text
msgid "@niko I...think...."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟。。。擬。。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:14:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...I think I should listen to \\p!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟擬𨉟𢧚𦖑\\p！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:15:text
msgid "@niko After all, \\p helped me get this far."
msgstr "@niko 𢖖󠄁共時、\\p㐌𢴇𨉟𦤾得低。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:16:text
msgid "I will take your faith for an answer, then."
msgstr "丕𪝬𠱊𥙩德信𧵑伴𪵯舅㨋𠳒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:17:text
msgid "@niko What do you mean by that?"
msgstr "@niko 意伴𪜀哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/EV009:1:18:text
msgid "It means whatever you think it means."
msgstr "伴擬哰時伮𪜀丕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/npc_randy:1:2:text
msgid "@niko Beep boop."
msgstr "@niko 芣芣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/tower door right:1:1:text left:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's locked from the inside."
msgstr "@niko 伮備銙𥪝。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/elevator doors:3:1:text
msgid "@niko This elevator goes back up to the catwalks."
msgstr "@niko 簜𣛠尼𠭤徠各橺槊。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/elevator doors:3:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak We'll need to press the button if we wanna go back up!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 衆𨉟𠱊沛𢶸鈕抵𢮿徠！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/npc_plight:1:5:text
msgid "@plight Anyway, it was nice meeting you....uh"
msgstr "@plight 怞哰時、窒𢝙得﨤㛪、唹"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/npc_plight:1:6:text 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:70:text
msgid "@niko_speak Niko!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 尼孤！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/npc_plight:1:7:text
msgid "@plight ...Right. See you around, kid."
msgstr "@plight 。。。沛耒。𠻷﨤徠唲傉。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/npc_plight:1:8:text
msgid "@plight Gotta run now!"
msgstr "@plight 英沛速變耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/npc_plight:1:24:text
msgid "@niko He seems in a hurry..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔英𧘇𣎏役急。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/npc_plight:1:25:text
msgid "@niko I guess we should hurry too, \\p."
msgstr "@niko 衆𨉟拱𢧚𪬭蹎啐、\\p。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/npc_plight:1:26:text
msgid "@niko_speak People are counting on us!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𤗆𠊛撻念信𠓨衆𨉟妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/npc_plight:1:27:text
msgid "@niko Let's go find that library."
msgstr "@niko 𠫾尋書院鬧。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:3:text
msgid "@george1 Oh, do you need George to tell you what to do again?"
msgstr "@george1 溩、伴懃觫𪲍徠仍條懃𪵯哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:5:text
msgid ""
"@george1 According to the journal, you must go to the small room at the base "
"of the Tower while having three pieces of the previous sun in your "
"possession."
msgstr "@george1 蹺捲日記、㛪沛𠫾𠓨房𡮈於蹎座塔𢭲𠀧𤗖𧵑𩈘𡗶𫇰𥪝𢬣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:6:text
msgid ""
"@george1 With those three items at hand, you must stand in the room, and \\p "
"will do something about floor patterns and windows."
msgstr "@george1 喟𠀧物品妬、㛪𠱊𨅸𥪝房、吧\\p𠱊𪵯之妬喟仍𫔤擻吧花紋𨑗孱。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:7:text
msgid "@niko Alright... thank you!"
msgstr "@niko 得耒。。。感恩姉唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:8:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:42:text
msgid "@george1_smile Good luck on your journey, small child!"
msgstr "@george1_smile 祝㛪𢆪慜！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:9:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:43:text
msgid "@george1 George shall bid you farewell now."
msgstr "@george1 𣊾𣇞觫𠱊吶𠳒嘲暫別。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:12:text
msgid "@george1 I've done it!\\>\\n"
msgstr "@george1 姉𪵯得耒！\\>\\n"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:13:text
msgid ""
"@george1_smile I have finished the daunting task of translating this journal!"
msgstr "@george1_smile 姉㐌完成工役窒當𢜝妬𪜀翻譯卷日記尼！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:14:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:16:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:16:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! That was fast!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！𪬭實妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:15:text
msgid ""
"@george1_smug But of course! I AM the speediest translator in recent history."
msgstr "@george1_smug 必然耒！姉𪜀翻譯員速度一歷史近代𦓡。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:16:text
msgid ""
"@george1 Anyway, I made you a line-by-line transcript. \\>\\nIt looks like "
"this journal might be meant for \\p."
msgstr "@george1 吶終𪜀、姉㐌翻譯層𣳔𠬠𣎏㛪耒。 \\>\\n𣎏𨤔卷日記尼𧶄朱\\p。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:18:text
msgid "@george1 Here, take a look yourself."
msgstr "@george1 呢、讀𠫾。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:20:text
msgid "@george1 There, that's the last of it."
msgstr "@george1 仍張𡳃窮哙𨔊徠妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:21:text
msgid ""
"@george1 The rest of the pages are torn out.\\>\\n\\@george1_hm You didn't "
"do this, did you?"
msgstr "@george1 各張哙徠調被扯𧛊歇耒。\\>\\n\\@george1_hm 空沛𪜀由㛪、董空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:22:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:23:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:26:text
msgid "@niko_speak No!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 空！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:23:text
msgid ""
"@george1 A shame! I was wondering what \"window\" was supposed to mean."
"\\>\\n\\@george1 Ah well, I guess \\p will have to figure out that one."
msgstr ""
"@george1 惜實！姉當空別「𫔤擻」指丐之。\\>\\n\\@george1 𧘇它、\\p𠱊沛自尋𫥨"
"丕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:24:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:23:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:25:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:26:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:21:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:28:text
#: ground/backalley/EV007:1:14:text
msgid "@niko Right..."
msgstr "@niko 唹𤾟。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:25:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:24:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:26:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:27:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:29:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak By the way, what does it mean by \"three pieces of the previous "
"sun\"?\\>\\n\\@niko I only have this sun..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 𦓡、「𠀧𤗖𧵑𩈘𡗶𫇰」𪜀之勢吖？\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪只𣎏𩈘𡗶尼催。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:26:text
msgid ""
"@george1_hm Aha!\\>\\nThat... \\@george1_smug is a question George can "
"answer!"
msgstr "@george1_hm 啊𠹛！\\>\\n妬。。。 \\@george1_smug 𪜀𠬠句𠳨觫𣎏体㨋𠳒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:27:text
msgid ""
"@george1 It means you need items containing yellow phosphor, the rarest of "
"the phosphors.\\>\\n\\@george1 ...said to absorb sunlight for the longest "
"time and never fade out."
msgstr ""
"@george1 義𪜀㛪懃各𣘊物貯光素鐄、類光素險一。\\>\\n\\@george1 。。。𣎏体吸受"
"暎𤏬𩈘𡗶嘍一𦓡空包𣇞𤎕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:28:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:24:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:31:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Oh!\\>\\n\\@niko I do have a piece of amber and a feather, "
"they're both glowing yellow..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 溩！\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪𣎏𠬠𠰳琥珀吧𠬠隻𦒮羽、衆調發𤏬𦭷鐄。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:29:text
msgid "@george1_hm But alas, you are missing the third, no?"
msgstr "@george1_hm 扔𧯶沛㛪當少𠅒𦁺次𠀧哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:30:text
msgid ""
"@george1 Fear not! For George, collector of rare artifacts... \\@george1_hm "
"will assist you!\\>\\n\\@george1 Here."
msgstr ""
"@george1 揨𢥈！爲觫、茹搜尋仍遺物險。。。 \\@george1_hm 𠱊互助㛪！"
"\\>\\n\\@george1 低。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:38:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:40:text
msgid "@niko Oh...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak It looks... \\@niko_huh ...like you?"
msgstr "@niko 溩。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 伮矓。。。 \\@niko_huh 偅姉？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:39:text
msgid "@george1_smile Yes!"
msgstr "@george1_smile 董丕！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:40:text
msgid ""
"@george1_smile Now you'll never forget my face! \\>\\n\\@george1 The face... "
"\\>\\@george1_hm of knowledge."
msgstr ""
"@george1_smile 𣇞時㛪𠱊空包𣇞悁𩈘姉！ \\>\\n\\@george1 𦎛𩈘。。。 "
"\\>\\@george1_hm 𧵑知識。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:41:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:35:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:44:text
msgid "@niko_speak Ah, thank you!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 啊、感恩姉唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:52:text
msgid ""
"@george1 Yes, even someone as great as I must put the proper thought and "
"care into a task like this.\\>\\n"
msgstr "@george1 果然、𦤾𪥘󠄁𠬠𠊛偉大如姉拱沛𢭰心血𠓨𠬠役𪵯如勢尼。\\>\\n"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:53:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:57:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:56:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:45:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:58:text
msgid "@niko_yawn *yawn*..."
msgstr "@niko_yawn ＊哈＊。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:54:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Excuse me.... \\>\\n\\@niko ...again."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 吀纇。。。 \\>\\n\\@niko 。。。𡛤吖。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:55:text
msgid ""
"@george1 Go take a nap, small child! \\>\\n\\@george1_smug Take a nap and "
"appreciate my hospitality!"
msgstr ""
"@george1 𠫾𪵯𠬠𥋏𠫾、傉𡥵！ \\>\\n\\@george1_smug 唉𠫾𥄬𠬠𥋏吧珍重𢚸好客𧵑"
"姉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:56:text
msgid "@george1 Guest room's in the attic down the hall, in case you forgot."
msgstr "@george1 房客於𥪝閣𠃅𨑜層、裊㛪悁𠅒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:61:text
msgid ""
"@niko I do have this book, though!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak I...think it's written "
"in some sort of...words I don't recognize?"
msgstr ""
"@niko 扔㛪𣎏卷冊尼！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 形。。。如伮𢪏憑𠬠埬。。。詞語㛪空讀"
"曉？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:62:text
msgid ""
"@george1 Aha!\\>\\nAn ancient book!\\>\\nWritten by no less than the most "
"ancient... wait a minute."
msgstr "@george1 啊𠹛！\\>\\n𠬠卷冊古！\\>\\n𢪏𤳸空埃恪外。。。䟻㐌。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:63:text
msgid ""
"@george1_hm This isn't ancient at all!\\>\\n\\@george1 But it's written in a "
"dead language nevertheless."
msgstr "@george1_hm 冊尼拯古之叱！\\>\\n\\@george1 扔伮吻得𢪏憑𠬠言語𣩂。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:64:text
msgid "@george1_hm It's time...for me to unleash my brilliance!"
msgstr "@george1_hm 㐌𦤾𣅶。。。抵發揮才能𧵑姉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:65:text
msgid ""
"@george1 For George (me),\\npossessor of at least one PhD..."
"\\>\\n\\@george1_smug shall translate this!"
msgstr ""
"@george1 爲觫（姉）、\\n𠊛所有𠃣一𠬠憑教師。。。\\>\\n\\@george1_smug 𠱊翻譯"
"伮！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:66:text
msgid "@george1 ...this will take some time, however."
msgstr "@george1 。。。扔𠱊損𡭧時間。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:67:text
msgid "@niko I see...\\>\\n\\@niko_yawn *yawn*..."
msgstr "@niko 嗚雞。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_yawn ＊哈＊。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:68:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:73:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:75:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:79:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:64:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:84:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Excuse me...."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 吀纇。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:69:text
msgid "@george1_hm Oh? What's this? \\>\\nYou are sleepy?"
msgstr "@george1_hm 溩？哰丕？\\>\\n㛪𢞂𥄬嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:70:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:77:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed A little...."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𠬠𡭧。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:71:text
msgid ""
"@george1_smile Fear not! \\>Because I have read a book on hospitality before!"
msgstr "@george1_smile 揨𢥈！ \\>爲姉㐌讀冊𧗱𢚸好客耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:72:text
msgid "@george1_smug ...and thus, have prepared for this exact situation!"
msgstr "@george1_smug 。。。吧𢘾妬、㐌準備朱董情況尼！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:73:text
msgid "@george1 ...Guest room's in the attic down the hall."
msgstr "@george1 。。。房客於𥪝閣𠃅𨑜層。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:79:text
msgid "@niko So...."
msgstr "@niko 丕𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:80:text
msgid "@george1 If you have any questions regarding books, then fear not."
msgstr "@george1 裊㛪𣎏句𠳨之𧗱冊𦅴、揨垠礙。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:1:81:text
msgid ""
"@george1_smug For I, George the head librarian, know a lot about "
"\\c[3]books\\c[0]."
msgstr "@george1_smug 爲姉、守書觫、別窒𡗉𧗱\\c[3]冊\\c[0]。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:3:text
msgid "@george2_grr What? You need me to explain again?"
msgstr "@george2_grr 之幾？傉懃姉解釋徠嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:4:text
msgid "@george2_sigh FINE."
msgstr "@george2_sigh 得耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:5:text
msgid ""
"@george2 The Journal says you have to go to the small room at the base of "
"the Tower while holding three pieces of the previous sun."
msgstr "@george2 日記吶哴㛪沛𠓨房𡮈於蹎座塔喟𠀧𤗖𧵑𩈘𡗶𫇰𥪝𢬣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:6:text
msgid ""
"@george2 Since you already have those, you must stand in the room and wait "
"for \\p to do something about floor patterns and windows."
msgstr "@george2 爲㛪㐌𣎏伮耒、㛪只懃𨅸𥪝房吧䟻\\p𢱖𢵯之妬𧗱花紋孱吧𧵑擻。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:7:text
msgid "@niko Alright... that makes sense.\\>\\n\\@niko Thank you!"
msgstr "@niko 得耒。。。合理妬。\\>\\n\\@niko 感恩姉唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:8:text
msgid "@george2_sigh Well, bye."
msgstr "@george2_sigh 唹、嘲唲。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:11:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr THERE. FINALLY.\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh ...the translation is done."
msgstr "@george2_grr 蒂。得耒蒂。\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh 。。。版譯㐌完畢。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:12:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh!\\>\\n\\@niko That was faster than I thought!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！\\>\\n\\@niko 𪬭欣㛪想妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:13:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr Well, YEAH!\\>\\n\\@george2_stress You've been asleep for hours!"
msgstr "@george2_grr 徠𠁙勢！\\>\\n\\@george2_stress 㛪𥄬𠇍㗂連耒蒂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:15:text
msgid ""
"@george2_sigh Anyway...\\>\\n\\@george2_grr It looks like this journal was "
"meant for \\p."
msgstr ""
"@george2_sigh 𠬃過𡀯妬時。。。\\>\\n\\@george2_grr 䀡𫥨捲日記尼𧶄朱\\p。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:17:text
msgid "@george2_sigh Here. Read it yourself."
msgstr "@george2_sigh 低。自讀𥙩𠫾。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:19:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr That's all there is.\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh Someone tore out the "
"other pages."
msgstr "@george2_grr 𣎏饒妬催。\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh 仍張哙徠被扯𫥨𠅒耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:20:text
msgid "@george2_grr Did YOU do this???"
msgstr "@george2_grr 𪜀㛪妬嘑？？？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:21:text
msgid "@niko_huh No!"
msgstr "@niko_huh 空！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:22:text
msgid ""
"@george2_sigh Then you're on your own, kid. I'm not sure what \"window\" "
"means here.\\>\\n\\@george2 Maybe \\p will have to figure out that one."
msgstr ""
"@george2_sigh 勢時㛪沛自力耒傉。姉空別「𫔤擻」當指丐之。>\\n\\@george2 昃𪜀"
"\\p𠱊沛驗𫥨伮。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:25:text
msgid "@george2_grr Do I have to explain EVERYTHING..."
msgstr "@george2_grr 姉沛解釋歇𤗆次嘑。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:26:text
msgid ""
"@george2_sigh Sigh.\\>\\n\\@george2_grr It's just a fancy word for objects "
"containing yellow phosphor."
msgstr ""
"@george2_sigh 係。\\>\\n\\@george2_grr 伮只𪜀𠬠詞高超指仍物貯光素鐄催。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:27:text
msgid "@george2_sigh Y'know, stuff that glows yellow."
msgstr "@george2_sigh 時蒂、仍次發𤏬𦭷鐄。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:28:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh!\\>\\n\\@niko I do have a piece of amber and a feather!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪𣎏𠬠𠰳琥珀吧𠬠隻𦒮羽！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:29:text
msgid "@niko_speak They fit the description, right...?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 衆𨨤喟模寫、董空。。。？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:30:text
msgid "@george2_grr Yeah, but you only have TWO of them."
msgstr "@george2_grr 唹、扔㛪㵋𣎏𠄩𦁺催。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:31:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr And they're super rare so it's not like you're just gonna find "
"something like that on the ground."
msgstr "@george2_grr 吧衆超險𢧚空𣎏𡀯㛪自仍抇得𠬠𦁺𨑜𡐙兜。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:33:text
msgid "@george2_sigh ...\\>\\@george2_grr ...okay."
msgstr "@george2_sigh 。。。\\>\\@george2_grr 。。。得耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:34:text
msgid "@george2 Here. You can have this."
msgstr "@george2 低。擒𥙩丐尼𠫾。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:42:text
msgid "@niko Oh...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak It looks... \\@niko ...kinda like you?"
msgstr "@niko 溩。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 𣎏𨤔伮矓。。。 \\@niko 。。。偅姉？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:43:text
msgid "@george2_grr What? Never seen dice before?"
msgstr "@george2_grr 哰勢？貯𧡊劅色包𣇞啊？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:44:text
msgid "@niko_speak No!\\> I mean yes!\\>\\n\\@niko I mean, it's just..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 貯！\\> 意𪜀耒！\\>\\n\\@niko 意𪜀、伮唏。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:46:text
msgid "@george2_grr So... yeah.\\>\\nNeed anything else?"
msgstr "@george2_grr 𢧚𪜀。。。唹。\\>\\n懃之𡛤空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:47:text
msgid "@niko_speak I'm good, thank you!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 得耒、感恩姉唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:48:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr ...Off you go, then.\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh Don't screw this up, "
"okay?"
msgstr ""
"@george2_grr 。。。𠫾猛𠐞唲。\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh 揨𣎏𦓡𪵯之𥌧凌蒂、曉𣗓？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:58:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr What? Couldn't find it?\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh It's down the hall "
"and upstairs!"
msgstr "@george2_grr 哰？空尋𧡊嘑？\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh 𬆄𨑜行廊耒𠫾𬨠橋簜！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:59:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr Just go take a nap. \\>\\@george2_sigh Translating's gonna take "
"a while anyway."
msgstr "@george2_grr 𠫾打𠬠𥋏𠫾。\\>\\@george2_sigh 矯之時翻譯拱𠱊損時間催。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:64:text
msgid ""
"@niko I have this book!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak I...think it's written in some "
"sort of...words I don't recognize?"
msgstr ""
"@niko 㛪𣎏卷冊尼！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 形。。。如伮𢪏憑𠬠次。。。言語之妬？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:65:text
msgid "@george2 Oh? \\>\\nLemme see..."
msgstr "@george2 溩？ \\>\\n抵姉䀡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:66:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr ...oh.\\>\\n\\@george2_stress Of course... \\>\\@george2_NO OF "
"COURSE!!!"
msgstr ""
"@george2_grr 。。。溩。\\>\\n\\@george2_stress 必然。。。 \\>\\@george2_NO 必"
"然耒！！！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:68:text
msgid "@george2_sigh More work for George, FINE."
msgstr "@george2_sigh 徠添役𠓨頭觫、得耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:69:text
msgid "@george2_grr Hey uh, \\>\\@george2 kid..."
msgstr "@george2_grr 尼、唹、 \\>\\@george2 傉。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:71:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr Looks I'm gonna have to translate this for you."
"\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh Might take a while."
msgstr "@george2_grr 䀡𫥨姉𠱊沛翻譯伮朱㛪。\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh 𣎏体𠱊嘍蒂。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:72:text
msgid "@niko Alright...\\>\\n\\@niko_yawn *yawn*..."
msgstr "@niko 𠳐吖。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_yawn ＊哈＊。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:74:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr I know that feel, kid. \\>\\n\\@george2_stress I haven't had a "
"good night's sleep in weeks!"
msgstr ""
"@george2_grr 傉啊、姉曉𦓡。 \\>\\n\\@george2_stress 𪥘󠄁𠇍旬耒姉空得𥄬覩𥋏！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:75:text
msgid ""
"@niko_yawn *yawn*...\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed ...\\. that's \\.\\....not "
"good..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_yawn ＊哈＊。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 。。。\\.勢𪜀\\.\\.。。。空卒"
"兜吖。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:76:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr ...You know what?\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh I have a guest room in "
"the attic down the hall."
msgstr ""
"@george2_grr 。。。別之空？\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh 姉𣎏𠬠房接客𥪝閣𠃅𨑜𡳳行廊。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:77:text
msgid ""
"@george2 Go take a nap!\\>\\n\\@george2_stress Just looking at you getting "
"tired is making me tired!"
msgstr "@george2 𠫾𪵯𠬠𥋏𠫾！\\>\\n\\@george2_stress 𥆾㛪𤻻痗拱遣姉發𤻻𠅒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:83:text
msgid ""
"@george2_sigh Well, since you're already here.\\>\\n\\@george2_grr It'd be "
"rude for me to tell you to leave."
msgstr ""
"@george2_sigh 時、爲㛪㐌拮工𦤾低耒。\\>\\n\\@george2_grr 姉空𨘗㛪𠫾得。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:84:text
msgid "@george2 Do you uh...\\. got any questions about \\c[3]books\\c[0]..."
msgstr "@george2 㛪𣎏。。。\\.句𠳨之𧗱\\c[3]冊𦅴\\c[0]。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:2:85:text
msgid ""
"@george2_sigh Or you can read something here, I don't care. "
"\\>\\n\\@george2_grr Just don't make a mess!"
msgstr ""
"@george2_sigh 或㛪𣎏体檢之妬讀、隨㛪。\\>\\n\\@george2_grr 揨𪵯排耚𤗆次𫥨𪜀"
"得！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:3:text
msgid "@george3_sad Ohh... are you still lost?"
msgstr "@george3_sad 溩。。。㛪吻被落哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:4:text
msgid "@george3_sigh I KNEW I didn't explain it well enough..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 姉別𬆄𪜀姉解釋𣗓覩𤑟𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:5:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sad Alright... the journal says you must go to the small room at "
"the base of the Tower while having three pieces of the previous sun in your "
"possession."
msgstr ""
"@george3_sad 得耒。。。日記𥱬哴㛪沛𠫾𠓨間房𡮈於蹎座塔喟𠀧𤗖𧵑𩈘𡗶𫇰𥪝𢬣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:6:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sad And...since you have the three items... you need to stand in "
"the room, and \\p will do something about floor patterns and windows..."
msgstr ""
"@george3_sad 吧。。。爲㛪㐌𣎏𠀧𦁺妬。。。\\p𠱊𪵯之妬𧗱花紋孱吧𫔤擻。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:7:text
msgid "@niko That makes sense, thank you!"
msgstr "@niko 合理妬、感恩姉唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:8:text
msgid "@george3_sad Yeah... \\>\\@george3_sigh see you around, I guess..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 唹。。。 \\>\\@george3_sigh 昃𪜀、𠻷﨤徠㛪唲。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:11:text
msgid "@george3_sad .\\..\\..\\..\\.."
msgstr "@george3_sad 。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:12:text
msgid "@george3_sigh It's done..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 歱耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:13:text
msgid "@niko_speak That was fast! Thank you!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𪬭實妬！感恩姉唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:14:text
msgid "@george3_sad ...not... really."
msgstr "@george3_sad 。。。空。。。𪳨。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:15:text
msgid "@george3_sigh You've just been sleeping...."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 拯過𣅅𣇞㛪𥄬催。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:16:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:33:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Right."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 沛耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:17:text
msgid ""
"@george3_worry Anyway... \\.he...\\. this person... wrote this journal for "
"\\p... I think..."
msgstr ""
"@george3_worry 時。。。\\.翁𧘇。。。\\.𠊛尼。。。㐌曰捲日記尼朱\\p。。。姉擬"
"勢。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:19:text
msgid "@george3 I made you a transcript... here."
msgstr "@george3 姉㐌劄朱㛪𠬠版抄。。。低唲。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:21:text
msgid "@george3_cry Th...that was the last of it."
msgstr "@george3_cry 妬。。。妬𪜀仍之哙𨔊徠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:22:text
msgid ""
"@george3_worry A lot of the pages were torn out...\\>\\n\\@george3_cry Do "
"you know what happened?"
msgstr ""
"@george3_worry 份𡘯各張㐌被扯𫥨。。。\\>\\n\\@george3_cry 㛪𣎏別爲哰空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:24:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sad Ah... I don't know what \"window\" is supposed to mean."
"\\>\\n\\@george3_worry Maybe \\p will know..."
msgstr ""
"@george3_sad 啊。。。姉空別「𫔤擻」指丐之。\\>\\n\\@george3_worry 𣎏体\\p𠱊"
"別。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:27:text
msgid "@george3 Oh."
msgstr "@george3 溩。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:28:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sigh That's just referring to things with yellow phosphor in them."
"\\>\\n\\@george3 They uh... they glow for a long time!"
msgstr ""
"@george3_sigh 妬只𪜀仍次貯光素鐄催。\\>\\n\\@george3 衆唹。。。發𤏬窒嘍！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:29:text
msgid "@george3_worry But they're really rare..."
msgstr "@george3_worry 扔拱窒險。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:30:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Ooooh.\\>\\n\\@niko I have a piece of amber and a feather, "
"they're both glowing yellow..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 溩。\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪𣎏𠬠𠰳琥珀吧𠬠隻𦒮羽、調當發𤏬𦭷鐄。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:31:text
msgid "@george3_worry But that's just two..."
msgstr "@george3_worry 扔㛪㵋𣎏𠄩。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:32:text
msgid "@george3_sigh ...\\>\\n\\@george3 Here, you can have this."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 。。。\\>\\n\\@george3 低、㛪擒𥙩𠫾。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:41:text
msgid "@george3_sigh I... guess? It's just a die..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 昃。。。勢？姉𪜀四五催𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:42:text
msgid ""
"@george3_worry Ohhhh, but \"die\" isn't a good word!\\>\\nWhat if I jinx "
"your mission by giving you this?"
msgstr ""
"@george3_worry 喂、扔𡨸「四」𪜀共𠬠韻喟𡨸「死」！\\>\\n𢙲姉擣殀㛪𠇍耒時哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:43:text
msgid "@george3_cry THE WORLD IS GONNA DIE AND IT'S GONNA BE MY FAULT!"
msgstr "@george3_cry 世界𠱊𣩂吧悉𪥘󠄁𠱊𪜀由姉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:45:text
msgid "@niko I... think we'll be fine, miss!"
msgstr "@niko 㛪。。。擬𪜀衆㛪𠱊穩催！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:46:text
msgid "@george3_sad Are you sure?"
msgstr "@george3_sad 㛪昃空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:47:text
msgid "@niko_speak Yeah!\\> Thank you for helping us, by the way!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫫡！\\> 拱感恩姉㐌𢴇衆㛪唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:48:text
msgid "@george3_sad Alright... \\>\\@george3_sigh see you around, I guess..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 得耒。。。\\>\\@george3_sigh 丕時、𠻷﨤徠唲。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:57:text
msgid "@george3_cry I'm working as fast as I can...!!"
msgstr "@george3_cry 姉當𪵯役歇功率耒。。。！！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:58:text
msgid "@niko No worries!"
msgstr "@niko 空哰吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:59:text
msgid "@niko_yawn *yawn*... \\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed Excuse me...\\. again."
msgstr "@niko_yawn ＊哈＊。。。 \\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 㛪。。。\\.吀纇。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:60:text
msgid "@george3_sad You can go take a nap if you want..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 㛪𣎏体𠫾𥄬裊懃。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:61:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sad If you forgot, the guest room is down the hall and upstairs..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 裊㛪悁𠅒、時房客於𨑜行廊、𢖖󠄁妬𠫾橋簜𬨠。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:65:text
msgid "@niko_speak Excuse me!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 姉㗒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:66:text
msgid ""
"@niko I do have this book!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak I...think it's written in some "
"sort of...words I don't recognize?"
msgstr ""
"@niko 㛪𣎏卷冊尼！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 形。。。如伮𢪏憑仍。。。言詞㛪空曉得？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:67:text
msgid "@george3 Lemme see..."
msgstr "@george3 抵姉䀡鬧。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:68:text
msgid "@george3_sad Oh...\\>\\n\\@george3_worry Oh, dear...."
msgstr "@george3_sad 溩。。。\\>\\n\\@george3_worry 喂、𡗶㗒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:70:text
msgid "@george3_sad Hey uh... is it alright if I... borrow this..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 尼唹。。。㛪𣎏体。。。朱姉摱。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:71:text
msgid "@george3_worry There's no mistake... I have to translate it."
msgstr "@george3_worry 空𣎏差𨔊之於低𪥘󠄁。。。姉沛譯伮。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:72:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh, no problem!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩、空哰吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:73:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sad I'll try my best, but... \\>\\@george3_sigh It probably won't "
"be very fast."
msgstr "@george3_sad 姉𠱊固歇飭、扔。。。 \\>\\@george3_sigh 𠱊空𪬭𡗋兜。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:74:text
msgid "@niko That's okay.\\>\\n\\@niko_yawn *yawn*..."
msgstr "@niko 空哰吖。\\>\\n\\@niko_yawn ＊哈＊。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:76:text
msgid "@george3_worry Oh dear, are you... tired?"
msgstr "@george3_worry 喂、㛪。。。𢞂𥄬嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:78:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sad Ah, well...\\>\\n\\@george3 I do have a guest room upstairs..."
"\\>\\n\\@george3_sad Ah, but it's in the attic though..."
msgstr ""
"@george3_sad 啊、時。。。\\>\\n\\@george3 姉𣎏𠬠房客𨑗層。。。"
"\\>\\n\\@george3_sad 啊、扔伮於𥪝閣𠃅幾。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:79:text
msgid "@george3_sigh Sorry if it's not very comfortable..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 𢙲𣎏空𢗷㜥時姉吀纇唲。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:85:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sigh So... do you have any questions about \\c[3]books\\c[0]..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 時。。。㛪𣎏句𠳨之𧗱\\c[3]冊\\c[0]空。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:3:86:text
msgid "@george3_cry It's all I'm good forrrrrrr......."
msgstr "@george3_cry 姉只𪵯得每役妬催。。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:3:text
msgid "@george4_golly Oh, do you need me to explain again?"
msgstr "@george4_golly 溩、㛪懃姉解釋徠嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:5:text
msgid "@george4 Alright!"
msgstr "@george4 溩文雞！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:6:text
msgid ""
"@george4_golly The journal says... you must go to the small room at the base "
"of the Tower while having three pieces of the previous sun in your "
"possession."
msgstr "@george4_golly 日記𥱬哴。。。㛪沛𠓨間房𡮈𨑜蹎座塔喟𠀧𤗖𧵑𩈘𡗶𫇰𥪝𢬣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:7:text
msgid ""
"@george4 And then, you'll stand in the room, and \\p will do something about "
"floor patterns and windows."
msgstr "@george4 歱耒、㛪只懃𨅸𥪝房、吧\\p𠱊𪵯之妬𧗱各畫節𨑗孱吧𫔤擻。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:8:text
msgid "@george4_smile That's all there is to it!"
msgstr "@george4_smile 𣎏丕催妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:10:text
msgid "@george4 No problem! See you later!"
msgstr "@george4 空哰！﨤徠㛪𢖖󠄁唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:13:text
msgid "@george4 Heya! Had a good nap?"
msgstr "@george4 吀嘲！傉𥄬唁渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:15:text
msgid ""
"@george4 Goody!\\>\\n\\@george4_smile I finished translating the journal, by "
"the way!"
msgstr "@george4 絕𫚱貓！\\>\\n\\@george4_smile 因便時、姉譯歱卷日記耒妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:17:text
msgid ""
"@george4_oops Well, you were out for a while.\\>\\n\\@george4_golly Anyway, "
"it looks like this journal might be meant for \\p!"
msgstr ""
"@george4_oops 時、㛪拱𥄬可嘍耒。\\>\\n\\@george4_golly 𦓡、𣎏𨤔卷日記尼𧶄朱"
"\\p妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:19:text
msgid "@george4 Here, take a look yourself!"
msgstr "@george4 低、㛪䀡𠫾！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:21:text
msgid "@niko Is that all?"
msgstr "@niko 𣎏勢尼催吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:22:text
msgid "@george4_golly Yeah... the rest of the pages were torn out..."
msgstr "@george4_golly 唹。。。各張哙徠被扯𫥨歇耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:23:text
msgid "@george4 I...guess you don't know what happened to those?"
msgstr "@george4 昃。。。𪜀㛪空別仍張妬被之兜𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:24:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Nope..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 空吖。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:25:text
msgid ""
"@george4_oops Aww... I was wondering what \"window\" was supposed to mean."
"\\>\\n\\@george4_golly Ah well, I guess \\p will have to figure out that one."
msgstr ""
"@george4_oops 𫉩。。。姉當空別「𫔤擻」當指丐之。\\>\\n\\@george4_golly 𧘇它、"
"抵朱\\p驗𫥨丕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:28:text
msgid "@george4_omg Oh! Of course!"
msgstr "@george4_omg 溩！董耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:29:text
msgid ""
"@george4_smile That just means you need things that contain yellow phosphor!"
"\\>\\n\\@george4 They glow for a long time!"
msgstr ""
"@george4_smile 只義𪜀㛪懃仍物用𣎏光素鐄催！\\>\\n\\@george4 衆發𤏬窒嘍妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:30:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Ooh!\\>\\n\\@niko I do have a piece of amber and a feather, "
"they're both glowing yellow..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 溩溩！\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪𣎏𠬠𤗖琥珀吧𠬠隻𦒮羽、衆調當𤏬𦭷鐄。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:31:text
msgid "@george4_golly Aww, just two?"
msgstr "@george4_golly 𫉩、只𣎏𠄩𦁺催哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:32:textz
msgid "@george4 Here, you can have this then!"
msgstr "@george4 低、㛪擒𥙩丐尼𠫾！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:40:text
msgid "@niko Oh...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak It looks..."
msgstr "@niko 溩。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 矓伮偅。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:41:text
msgid "@george4_smile Like me, right?"
msgstr "@george4_smile 偅姉、沛空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:43:text
msgid "@george4_smile Now you have a little keepsake from the library!"
msgstr "@george4_smile 𣊾𣇞㛪𣎏𠬠𦁺𩛃紀念自書院耒妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:45:text
msgid "@george4 No problem! Looks like you're all set!"
msgstr "@george4 空哰！𣎏𨤔㛪㐌𠻿𠳹耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:46:text
msgid "@george4_smile Good luck now!"
msgstr "@george4_smile 祝㛪𢆪慜！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:55:text
msgid "@george4_oops Haha... it won't be done for a while, sorry!"
msgstr "@george4_oops 哬哬。。。𠱊損可嘍妬、姉吀纇唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:57:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Excuse me...\\.\\. again...."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 姉。。。\\.\\. 㗒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:58:text
msgid ""
"@george4_golly Seriously, you should go take a nap before you overexert "
"yourself!\\>\\n\\@george4 The guest room is in the attic down the hall, if "
"you forgot!"
msgstr ""
"@george4_golly 實蒂、㛪沛𠫾𥄬𠫾𪢤𣵰𫥨𤴥妬！\\>\\n\\@george4 房客於𥪝閣𠃅𨑜行"
"廊、裊㛪悁𠅒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:62:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Oh! I do have this!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak I...think it's written in "
"some sort of...words I don't recognize?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 溩！㛪𣎏丐尼！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 㛪。。。𧡊伮曰憑𠬠次。。。言語"
"之妬？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:63:text
msgid "@george4_golly Oh my gosh!"
msgstr "@george4_golly 喂𡗶㗒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:64:text
msgid "@george4 It's.... \\.\\.\\@george4_omg A book!"
msgstr "@george4 伮𪜀。。。。\\.\\.\\@george4_omg 𠬠卷冊！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:65:text
msgid ""
"@george4 And not just any book! \\>\\@george4_golly Golly... where did you "
"find this?"
msgstr ""
"@george4 𦓡拱拯沛冊尋常兜！ \\>\\@george4_golly 恩𡗶。。。㛪檢伮於兜勢？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:67:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:55:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:70:text
msgid "@niko I woke up with it."
msgstr "@niko 𣅶㛪醒𧻭啞。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:70:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:58:text
msgid ""
"@niko Somewhere in the barrens!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak Oh! We found it in a safe!"
"\\> Right, \\p?"
msgstr ""
"@niko 於兜妬𥪝塳邊疆！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 溩！𨉟尋𧡊伮𥪝𠬠咭鉄！\\>沛空、"
"\\p？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:73:text
msgid "@george4 Is that so!"
msgstr "@george4 實唹！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:74:text
msgid "@george4_smile In that case, I know what I have to do now!"
msgstr "@george4_smile 裊丕時、姉別沛𪵯之耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:75:text
msgid ""
"@george4 I need to borrow this journal for a bit, okay?\\>\\n\\@george4_omg "
"Gotta translate it!"
msgstr "@george4 姉懃摱卷日記𠬠𣋩、唲？\\>\\n\\@george4_omg 沛𠫾譯伮催！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:76:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh, cool!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩、唁！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:77:text
msgid "@george4_oops It... might take a while, though..."
msgstr "@george4_oops 扔。。。伮𣎏体𠱊唏嘍妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:78:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:83:text
msgid "@niko_speak That's fine!\\>\\n\\@niko_yawn *yawn*..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 空哰吖！\\>\\n\\@niko_yawn ＊哈＊。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:80:text
msgid "@george4_golly Gosh! You look really tired!"
msgstr "@george4_golly 𡗶！矓㛪𤻻痗過澄！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:81:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed A little, yeah...."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𠬠𡭧吖。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:82:text
msgid ""
"@george4_smile No worries! I have a guest room in the attic down the hall!"
msgstr "@george4_smile 空問題！姉𣎏𠬠房客𥪝閣𠃅𡳳行廊！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:83:text
msgid ""
"@george4 If you want, you can go take a nap!\\>\\n\\@george4_smile ... a "
"catnap!"
msgstr ""
"@george4 裊㦖、㛪𣎏体過妬𪵯𠬠𥋏！\\>\\n\\@george4_smile 。。。𠬠𥋏猫曥！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:90:text
msgid ""
"@george4 Well, since you're already here, feel free to check out my archives!"
msgstr "@george4 裊㛪㐌拮工𦤾低、唉試䀡過各材料𧵑姉𠫾！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:91:text
msgid ""
"@george4_omg Or better yet! If you have any questions about "
"\\c[3]books\\c[0], I can answer them!"
msgstr "@george4_omg 或卒欣𡛤！裊傉𣎏忑縸之𧗱\\c[3]冊\\c[0]、姉調𣎏体㨋𠳒歇！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:4:92:text
msgid "@george4 I love books.... books books books!"
msgstr "@george4 姉迷冊𡗋。。。冊冊冊！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:3:text
msgid "@george5 Oh! Would you like me to explain again?"
msgstr "@george5 溩！㛪𣎏懃姉解釋徠空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:5:textｗｄ
msgid ""
"@george5 According to the journal, you must go to the small room at the base "
"of the Tower while having three pieces of the previous sun in your "
"possession."
msgstr "@george5 蹺卷日記、㛪沛𠓨間房𡮈於蹎座塔喟𠀧𤗖𧵑𩈘𡗶𫇰。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:6:text
msgid ""
"@george5 ...and then, you must stand in the room, and \\p will do something "
"about floor patterns and windows."
msgstr "@george5 。。。吧耒、㛪沛𨅸𥪝房、抵\\p𪵯之妬喟各花紋𨑗孱吧𫔤擻。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:7:text
msgid "@niko Ooo, makes sense, thank you!"
msgstr "@niko 溩、合理妬、感恩姉吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:8:text
msgid "@george5 Best of luck, sweetie!"
msgstr "@george5 祝𣛠慜唲畺！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:11:text
msgid "@george5_smile Had a good nap, dear?"
msgstr "@george5_smile 畺𥄬唁空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:13:text
msgid "@george5_smile Wonderful!"
msgstr "@george5_smile 絕𡸏！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:14:text
msgid ""
"@george5 I have the translation ready for you now.\\>\\n\\@george5_hmm It "
"looks like this journal might be meant for \\p."
msgstr ""
"@george5 版譯㐌𠻿𠳹朱㛪低耒。\\>\\n\\@george5_hmm 𣎏𨤔捲日記尼𧶄朱\\p。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:16:text
msgid "@george5 Here, why don't you take a look?"
msgstr "@george5 低、㛪䀡試䀡！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:18:text
msgid ""
"@george5_hmm That is all there is to translate...\\>\\nLooks like the other "
"pages have been torn out."
msgstr "@george5_hmm 只𣎏𡗉妬抵翻譯催。。。\\>\\n各張哙徠𣎏𨤔㐌被扯𫥨歇耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:20:text
msgid ""
"@george5_hmm Quite a shame! I was wondering what \"window\" was supposed to "
"mean.\\>\\n\\@george5 Ah well, I guess \\p can figure that one out!"
msgstr ""
"@george5_hmm 可𪜀惜！姉當空別「𫔤擻」指丐之。\\>\\n\\@george5 係、昃𪜀\\p𣎏体"
"驗𫥨催！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:22:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Oh! What does it mean by \"three pieces of the previous sun\"?"
"\\>\\n\\@niko I only have this sun..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 溩！「𠀧𤗖𧵑𩈘𡗶𫇰」𪜀之丕吖？\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪只𣎏𩈘𡗶尼催。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:23:text
msgid ""
"@george5 That means the stuff containing yellow phosphor!"
"\\>\\n\\@george5_smile They glow for a very long time, so people call them "
"\"pieces of the sun\" sometimes!"
msgstr ""
"@george5 𪜀仍次貯光素鐄妬！\\>\\n\\@george5_smile 衆發𤏬窒嘍、𢧚𡗉欺𤗆𠊛哙衆"
"𪜀「𤗖𩈘𡗶」妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:25:text
msgid ""
"@george5 Very good, dear!\\>\\n\\@george5_smile And I can help you with the "
"last one!"
msgstr "@george5 窒卒耒㛪！\\>\\n\\@george5_smile 吧姉𣎏体𢴇㛪𥙩𦁺𡳳窮！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:33:text
msgid "@niko Oh...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak It looks....\\@niko_huh ...like you?"
msgstr ""
"@niko 溩。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 矓伮。。。。\\@niko_huh 。。。偅𩈘姉？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:34:text
msgid ""
"@george5_heh I know! Isn't it silly?\\>\\n\\@george5 But now you'll have "
"something to remind you of the library!"
msgstr ""
"@george5_heh 姉別𦓡！拯沛伮窒𢞂唭哰？\\>\\n\\@george5 扔𣇞㛪𣎏𩛃紀念𧵑書院耒"
"妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:36:text
msgid ""
"@george5_smile Good luck now, sweetie!\\>\\n\\@george5 I wish you safe "
"travels!"
msgstr "@george5_smile 祝𣛠慜唲畺！\\>\\n\\@george5 祝㛪上路平安！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:46:text
msgid ""
"@george5_smile Don't wear yourself out now, dear!\\>\\n\\@george5 The guest "
"room is just down the hall to the right."
msgstr "@george5_smile 揨𪵯役過飭渚畺！\\>\\n\\@george5 房客於𡳳行廊𥘶沛。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:50:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Oh! I do have this book!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak I...think it's "
"written in some sort of...words I don't recognize?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 溩！㛪𣎏卷冊尼！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 㛪。。。擬伮曰憑𠬠。。。言語"
"之妬㛪空曉？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:51:text
msgid ""
"@george5 Really now!\\>\\n\\@george5_hmm May I take a closer look, dear?"
msgstr "@george5 實唹！\\>\\n\\@george5_hmm 朱姉䀡技欣唲、畺？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:53:text
msgid "@george5 Oh!\\>\\n\\@george5_hmm Oh my! Where did you find this?"
msgstr "@george5 溩！\\>\\n\\@george5_hmm 喂𡗶！㛪尋𧡊伮於兜丕？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:61:text
msgid ""
"@george5_hmm Hmm...\\>\\n\\@george5 I think...\\.\\. I'm supposed to "
"translate this for you!"
msgstr "@george5_hmm 嘘。。。\\>\\n\\@george5 𣎏𨤔。。。\\.\\.姉沛譯伮朱㛪耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:62:text
msgid ""
"@george5_hmm Is it alright if I hold on to the journal for now, sweetheart?"
"\\>\\n\\@george5 It might take a little while, I'm afraid!"
msgstr ""
"@george5_hmm 丕時畺抵姉𡨺卷日記𠬠𣅶唲？\\>\\n\\@george5 姉㥋𪜀、伮𠱊損可嘍"
"妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:63:text
msgid "@niko_speak Go for it!\\>\\n\\@niko_yawn *yawn*..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 姉據𢱖𠫾！\\>\\n\\@niko_yawn ＊哈＊。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:65:text
msgid ""
"@george5_aww Aww, you poor baby!\\>\\n\\@george5 Goodness, you must've "
"worked so hard to help us!"
msgstr ""
"@george5_aww 𫉩、苦身㛪！\\>\\n\\@george5 𡗶吖、𪳨𪜀㛪㐌窒努力抵𢴇𪨠姉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:66:text
msgid "@george5_smile I think you deserve a nap, no?"
msgstr "@george5_smile 姉擬㛪懃𥄬𠬠𣋩、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:67:text
msgid "@niko_yawn A nap does sounds nice..."
msgstr "@niko_yawn 董𪜀𠫾𥄬𣊾𣇞𦖑窒合理吖。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:68:text
msgid ""
"@george5 I have a guest room upstairs! It's just down the hall to the right."
msgstr "@george5 姉𣎏𠬠房客𨑗層！㛪𠫾𬺗行廊𥘶沛𪜀𬧐。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:74:text
msgid "@george5_smile Can I help you with anything else, dear?"
msgstr "@george5_smile 姉𣎏体𢴇之畺𡛤空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:5:75:text
msgid ""
"@george5 If you have any questions about \\c[3]books\\c[0], well..."
"\\>\\n\\@george5_heh I AM a librarian!"
msgstr ""
"@george5 裊㛪𣎏舅𠳨之𧗱\\c[3]冊\\c[0]、時。。。\\>\\n\\@george5_heh 姉𪜀守書"
"𦓡！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:3:text
msgid "@george6_point You look a lil' lost still. Want some hot tips?"
msgstr "@george6_point 翁𡥙𣎏𨤔咳𦁀𦇒𠰚。懃𠄼𬣌伆空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:5:text
msgid ""
"@george6 Says here in this book that you gots'ta go to the teeny room at the "
"base of the Tower, all while holding those three pieces of the awesome glowy "
"stuff."
msgstr "@george6 𥪝冊𥱬𪜀翁𡥙沛𠓨丐房𡮈子於𨑜座塔、𥪝欺擒𠀧𤗖發𤏬湡䋘妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:6:text
msgid ""
"@george6 Once you got 'em (which you do), just stand in the room, and \\p "
"will do something about floor patterns and windows."
msgstr "@george6 𠬠欺㛪𣎏衆（即𪜀𣊾𣇞）、\\p𠱊𢱖𢵯之妬𧗱畫節𨑗孱吧各𫔤擻。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:7:text
msgid "@niko Alright...\\.\\.\\@niko_speak Thank you!"
msgstr "@niko 得耒。。。\\.\\.\\@niko_speak 感恩姉唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:8:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:45:text
msgid "@george6_fingerguns You're toooootally welcome!"
msgstr "@george6_fingerguns 空𣎏之！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:9:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:46:text
msgid "@niko Well, I guess we'll be on our way?"
msgstr "@niko 丕時、昃𪜀衆㛪𠱊𬨠塘催？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:10:text
msgid "@george6_smile Peace out, little fella!"
msgstr "@george6_smile 翁𡥙保重唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:11:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:48:text
msgid "@george6 You'll do us good, I know it."
msgstr "@george6 姉別㛪𠱊𢧚役𡘯催。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:14:text
msgid "@george6_fingerguns Eyyyyy, you're up!"
msgstr "@george6_fingerguns 𠲖、翁𡥙𧻭耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:15:text
msgid "@george6 Just finished translating this book for ya!"
msgstr "@george6 𣃣𣅶姉譯歱卷冊尼朱翁𡥙！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:17:text
msgid "@george6_fingerguns What can I say? I'm all that and a bag of chips!"
msgstr "@george6_fingerguns 哙之抵吶𡛤？姉渡齊如丕吧欣勢𡛤妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:18:text
msgid "@george6 By the by, it looks like this journal might be meant for \\p."
msgstr "@george6 因文便、𣎏𨤔卷日記尼𧶄朱\\p。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:20:text
msgid "@george6_point Here, check it out."
msgstr "@george6_point 低、㛪䀡尼。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:22:text
msgid "@george6 That's all, we juiced it!"
msgstr "@george6 𣎏丕催、姉𢪱歇可能耒妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:23:text
msgid "@niko_what ...juiced what?"
msgstr "@niko_what 。。。𢪱之吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:24:text
msgid "@george6_fingerguns I'm just sayin' that's the end of the book!"
msgstr "@george6_fingerguns 意姉𪜀卷冊只𣎏饒妬催啊。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:25:text
msgid ""
"@george6_shrug Rest of the pages are torn out.\\>\\n\\@george6 Do you know "
"what happened here?"
msgstr "@george6_shrug 各張哙徠被扯歇𠅒耒。\\>\\n\\@george6 㛪𣎏別伮被哰空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:27:text
msgid ""
"@george6_shrug Bummer! I was hoping to figure out what he meant by saying "
"\"window\" here.\\>\\n\\@george6 Guess we'll leave that up to \\p, huh?"
msgstr ""
"@george6_shrug 𠩕！姉當㦖尋𫥨翁𧘇當指蓋「𫔤擻」之。\\>\\n\\@george6 䀡𫥨些沛"
"付託𡀯妬朱\\p、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:30:text
msgid ""
"@george6_point Oh! That's just stuff with yellow phosphor in 'em!"
"\\>\\n\\@george6 The kind of stuff that glows forever, dude."
msgstr ""
"@george6_point 溩！只𪜀仍次𣎏光素鐄催！\\>\\n\\@george6 仍次發𤏬𫡠𫡠𧘇、翁𡥙"
"啊。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:32:text
msgid "@george6_fingerguns Eyyyy! Now that's what I'm talkin about!"
msgstr "@george6_fingerguns 𠲖𠲖𠲖！勢𦓡徠咍！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:33:text
msgid "@george6 ...Hold up, you only have two."
msgstr "@george6 。。。寬㐌、翁𡥙㵋只𣎏𠄩𦁺。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:34:text
msgid ""
"@george6_point But we coo'!\\>\\n\\@george6_fingerguns I gotcha covered, "
"lil' fella!\\>\\n\\@george6 Here ya go."
msgstr ""
"@george6_point 扔空沛𦀵！\\>\\n\\@george6_fingerguns 姉𢶢𨉞翁𡥙低！"
"\\>\\n\\@george6 擒𥙩呢。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:42:text
msgid "@niko Oh...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak It looks...\\@niko_huh ...like you?"
msgstr ""
"@niko 溩。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 矓伮偅。。。\\@niko_huh 。。。𩈘姉𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:43:text
msgid ""
"@george6_fingerguns The freshest face you've ever seen, ehhhhh?"
"\\>\\n\\@george6 And it's all yours."
msgstr "@george6_fingerguns 𦎛𩈘鮮一㛪層𧡊、擟？\\>\\n\\@george6 𧵑㛪歇妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:47:text
msgid "@george6_smile Peace out, lil' fella!"
msgstr "@george6_smile 𡨺𢷹唲、翁𡥙！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:57:text
msgid ""
"@george6_shrug Bruh, it's gonna take some time to make this book readable, "
"know what I'm sayin'?"
msgstr "@george6_shrug 翁𡥙、𠱊損可可時𣇞抵𪵯卷冊讀得、曉意姉渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:59:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Excuse me....\\>\\n\\@niko ...again."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 姉。。。\\>\\n\\@niko 。。。㗒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:60:text
msgid "@george6 Don't sweat it!\\>\\n\\@george6_fingerguns Go catch some Z's!"
msgstr "@george6 空沛𦀵！\\>\\n\\@george6_fingerguns 𠫾打𠬠𥋏氐！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:61:text
msgid "@george6 Guest room's in the attic down the hall, FYI."
msgstr "@george6 因便、房客𨑜行廊𥘶沛。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:65:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! I do have this book!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！㛪𣎏卷冊尼！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:66:text
msgid "@george6 ...yo."
msgstr "@george6 。。。嗚。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:67:text
msgid "@george6_point .....YOOOOO."
msgstr "@george6_point 。。。。。嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:68:text
msgid "@george6 Where'd you find this?"
msgstr "@george6 㛪檢伮於兜勢？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:73:text
msgid "@niko Somewhere in the Barrens!"
msgstr "@niko 兜妬𥪝塳邊疆吖!"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:76:text
msgid "@george6 Cuz that's..."
msgstr "@george6 爲伮𣎏。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:77:text
msgid "@george6_point ...got that symbol and everything."
msgstr "@george6_point 。。。蓋表象妬吧𤗆次。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:78:text
msgid "@george6 Here, lemme read it..."
msgstr "@george6 鬧、抵姉讀試。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:79:text
msgid "@george6 ...aw seriously? He even used that language..."
msgstr "@george6 。。。實㫻？慃哙用𪥘󠄁丐言語妬𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:80:text
msgid "@george6 I gotta translate this, man.\\>\\nMind if I borrow this?"
msgstr "@george6 姉沛譯伮催。\\>\\n朱姉摱得渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:81:text
msgid "@niko_speak Not at all!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 空哰吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:82:text
msgid ""
"@george6 Sweeeeet.\\>\\n\\@george6_point It's gon' take a while tho, you "
"cool with that?"
msgstr "@george6 唁㫻。\\>\\n\\@george6_point 𠱊懃𠃣𤼵妬、翁𡥙溩雞渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:85:text
msgid "@george6 Whoa dude, you look wiped, kiddo!"
msgstr "@george6 𢭶掌、翁𡥙矓𨠣癲。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:86:text
msgid "@niko ...Huh?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。㖡？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:87:text
msgid "@george6_point You look totally tapped out, dude!"
msgstr "@george6_point 矓翁𡥙𢯔吀杈萊實𧘇！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:88:text
msgid "@niko_speak I look... what?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:89:text
msgid "@george6 You look like you're ready to take five, bruh!"
msgstr "@george6 矓如翁𡥙𢯛𠻅𫥨妬𧘇！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:90:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...yeah I don't get it."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。唹㛪𠁙曉之叱。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:91:text
msgid ""
"@george6 Don't worry I gotcha.\\>\\n\\@george6_smile I got a guest room in "
"the attic down the hall!"
msgstr "@george6 空哰𪥘󠄁。\\>\\n\\@george6_smile 姉𣎏𠬠房客𥪝閣𠃅𡳃行廊妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:92:text
msgid "@george6 If you wanna crash there, go for it!"
msgstr "@george6 裊㦖蹸𫥨妬時據自然！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:98:text
msgid "@george6 So how do you like my books, bruh."
msgstr "@george6 丕翁𡥙擬之𧗱冊𡲈𧵑姉。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:99:text
msgid "@niko They're... nice?"
msgstr "@niko 衆可。。。咍吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/npc_george:6:100:text
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map Events:7:109:text
msgid "@george6_fingerguns Eyyyyyy."
msgstr "@george6_fingerguns 𠲖𠲖𠲖𠲖𠲖。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/EV002:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Even the painting is books."
msgstr "@niko 𦤾幅𠬉拱𦘧冊。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:1:1:text
msgid "@niko The fridge is full of bottled water and take-out boxes."
msgstr "@niko 𣗿冷𣹓仍渃㨂𥑂吧匣𣘊咹噲𧗱。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:2:1:text
msgid "@niko A small bed."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠丐床𡮈。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:2:2:text
msgid "@niko I guess she lives here..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔姉𧘇𤯩於低。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:3:3:text
msgid "@george1_smug Thanks to my superb organizational skills..."
msgstr "@george1_smug 𠾒技能𢯛攝超項𧵑姉。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:3:4:text
msgid ""
"@george1 I have kept a copy of every single one of The Author's books in the "
"archival room!"
msgstr "@george1 姉㐌集合各本抄𧵑全部冊𢪏𤳸作者創世𥪝房留貯！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:3:5:text
msgid ""
"@george1 Feel free to peruse the mass sea of knowledge that I helped "
"contribute!"
