#: Events:4:80:text
msgid ""
"@george4 It's really impressive how fast he can crank these scripts out!"
msgstr "@george4 寔事印象喟格慃據連續朱𫥨仍版草尼催！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:81:text
msgid "@george4_golly Like, where does that guy get all that time?"
msgstr "@george4_golly 矯、慃檢時間兜𫥨丕？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:85:text
msgid "@george5_smile This is the box I'll get to publish this week!"
msgstr "@george5_smile 姉𠱊出版匣尼𥪝旬尼！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:86:text
msgid ""
"@george5 Oh, oh! Did I mention this gentleman's books are quite popular?"
msgstr "@george5 溩、溩！姉㐌吶哴冊𧵑貴翁尼可浽㗂𣗓𧘇𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:87:text
msgid ""
"@george5_smile You might be a little too young to understand them, but the "
"older kids love them!"
msgstr "@george5_smile 𣎏体㛪哙過𡮈抵讀曉衆、扔仍𠀲𡘯欣時適迷衆㫻！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:89:text
msgid "@george5_smile Lots and lots of things!"
msgstr "@george5_smile 窒窒𡗉次！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:90:text
msgid "@george5 Everything from plants and animals to machines and robots!"
msgstr "@george5 悉𪥘󠄁𤗆次自𦹯𣘃動物朱𦤾𣛠𢪮吧𠊛𣛠！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:91:text
msgid "@george5_smile Some of his books even have pictures!"
msgstr "@george5_smile 𠬠数卷𧵑慃哙𣎏幀影𡛤幾！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:95:text
msgid "@george6 That box's got stuff I can publish this week!"
msgstr "@george6 桶妬𣎏冊姉𠱊出版旬尼妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:96:text
msgid ""
"@george6_point I better up my game, dude. \\> Peeps are lining up to read "
"his books!"
msgstr "@george6_point 姉沛㨢尋局𨔈催。\\>𤗆𠊛當攝行䟻讀冊𧵑慃箕！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:98:text
msgid "@george6_shrug Dude, what DOESN'T he write about!"
msgstr "@george6_shrug 𡗶、𣎏之慃空𢪏空幾渚！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:99:text
msgid "@george6_smile Like I said, he's got passion, lots of it!"
msgstr "@george6_smile 姉吶耒妬、慃超無窮心血㫻！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:100:text
msgid ""
"@george6_shrug It's like every time I turn around he just writes another "
"huge anthology about the universe."
msgstr "@george6_shrug 偅如矯每吝姉𢮿𨉞𠬠丐𪜀慃㐌歱𠬠選集宇宙㵋耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:101:text
msgid "@george6 Gotta respect that."
msgstr "@george6 古典、尊重。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:120:text Events:4:137:text Events:4:155:text Events:4:170:text
#: Events:4:186:text
msgid "@niko These boxes are full of loose papers and notebooks."
msgstr "@niko 仍桶尼𣹓紙𥛭吧擻𢬣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:121:text
msgid "@george1 Oh! I see you are curious about my job."
msgstr "@george1 溩！䀡𫥨㛪徂摸𧗱工役𧵑姉。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:122:text
msgid "@george1_hm ...My very important job!"
msgstr "@george1_hm 。。。工役窒關重𧵑姉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:123:text
msgid ""
"@george1_smug You see, The Author has entrusted ME with his all his ideas!"
msgstr "@george1_smug 㛪𧡊妬、作者全世㐌撻畢𪥘󠄁意想𧵑慃𥪝𢬣姉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:124:text
msgid ""
"@george1_hm That's right... the author sends his manuscripts directly to ME!"
msgstr "@george1_hm 董丕。。。作者寄各版草𧵑慃直接朱姉㫻！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:125:text
msgid ""
"@george1_smug  I am in charge of publishing all of his books that everyone "
"loves!"
msgstr "@george1_smug  姉擔認重責出版仍卷冊𦓡𤗆𠊛調適迷妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:127:text
msgid "@george1 Although... he hasn't been sending me anything as of late!"
msgstr "@george1 雖然。。。澾近低慃拯寄之朱姉歇！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:128:text
msgid "@george1_hm I wonder, I wonder..."
msgstr "@george1_hm 思維、思維。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:129:text
msgid ""
"@george1_smile Perhaps he decided that, since I work so hard, I deserve a "
"break?"
msgstr "@george1_smile 𣎏体慃擬哴、爲姉㐌𪵯役歇𨉟、𢧚姉懃𠬠𣈜儗？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:130:text
msgid "@george1 As brilliant as I am, I still can't keep up with him!"
msgstr "@george1 怞𣎏偉大如丕、姉吻空体𨘗及慃！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:131:text
msgid ""
"@george1 Even AFTER he stopped sending me things, I still can't catch up."
msgstr "@george1 𠸥𪥘󠄁𢖖󠄁欺慃凝寄版草㵋、姉吻空才鬧𨘗及。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:132:text
msgid ""
"@george1_hm Of course, I have published book after book after book, but..."
msgstr "@george1_hm 必然、姉㐌出版歇卷尼𦤾卷恪、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:133:text
msgid "@george1 The box of manuscripts just seems to be growing on its own!"
msgstr "@george1 矯如桶版草自胓𫥨𧘇！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:138:text
msgid "@george2_grr What? You ain't never seen manuscripts before?"
msgstr "@george2_grr 哰勢？傉𣗓𧡊版草包𣇞嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:139:text
msgid ""
"@george2_sigh That's what books look like before they get published, kid."
msgstr "@george2_sigh 冊𠓀欺出版矓如丕妬傉。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:140:text Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/garden:2:11:text
msgid "@niko I see!"
msgstr "@niko 𫥨丕！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:141:text
msgid "@niko Do you help him publish books?"
msgstr "@niko 姉𢴇翁𧘇出版冊吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:142:text
msgid ""
"@george2_stress Well, DUH!\\>\\n\\@george2_grr Why do you THINK I have "
"literal mountains of his manuscripts, here?"
msgstr ""
"@george2_stress 徠𠁙勢！\\>\\n\\@george2_grr 勢㛪擬爲哰姉𣎏𪥘󠄁𡶀版草𧵑慃於低幾"
"渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:143:text
msgid "@george2 He just WOULDN'T STOP SENDING ME THINGS!!!"
msgstr "@george2 慃拯包𣇞空寄姉添版草𪥘󠄁！！！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:144:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr Like, man oh MAN does that guy work fast.\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh "
"I just couldn't keep up!"
msgstr "@george2_grr 矯、慃𪵯役癲實𧘇。\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh 姉空才鬧扒及㫻！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:145:text
msgid ""
"@george2 But one day he just, stopped.\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh ABOUT TIME, I "
"would say.\\>\\n\\@george2 But it's also weird since it's HIM."
msgstr ""
"@george2 扔𦤾𠬠𣈜、慃空寄之𡛤。\\>\\n\\@george2_sigh 姉擬𪜀拱𦤾𣅶耒妬。"
"\\>\\n\\@george2 扔拱窒𪜀𨓐爲𪜀慃𦓡。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:146:text
msgid "@george2_grr BUT! Worst part of all?"
msgstr "@george2_grr 扔！弊欣𪥘󠄁？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:147:text
msgid ""
"@george2_stress Even after he stopped bombarding me, the piles of material I "
"have on hand never seem to get any smaller!"
msgstr "@george2_stress 𬆄𪥘󠄁𢖖󠄁欺慃催𣾶版草𬨠頭姉、埬材料𧵑姉𣎏𨤔拯𡮈𠫾之歇！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:148:text
msgid ""
"@george2_no IT'S LIKE THE BOXES ARE MAGICALLY FILLING THEMSELVES BACK UP "
"EVERY TIME I TURN AROUND!!!!"
msgstr "@george2_no 矯如各桶自𣹓𬨠每欺姉𢮿𨉞𠫾𧘇！！！！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:149:text
msgid "@george2_stress WHAT IS EVEN HAPPENING!"
msgstr "@george2_stress 丐之當侈𫥨丕𡗶！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:150:text
msgid "@niko_huh Are you okay?"
msgstr "@niko_huh 姉穩空丕？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:151:text
msgid "@george2_no NO!!!!!!"
msgstr "@george2_no 空！！！！！！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:156:text
msgid "@george3_sad Siiiigh..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 係。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:157:text
msgid "@george3_sigh You just had to remind me..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 㛪𠯅姉㵋𢖵妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:158:text
msgid "@niko_speak What's wrong?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 哰丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:159:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sad The author hasn't shown up lately, nor has he sent me any new "
"manuscripts..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 䟞尼姉空𧡊𩈘作者兜、𦓡拱空𧡊翁𧘇寄姉版草㵋鬧歇。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:161:text
msgid "@george3_sad I'm his editor and publisher, you know..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 姉𪜀編緝員兼茹出版𧵑慃𧘇𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:162:text
msgid "@george3_cry What if he doesn't want me to help him anymore?"
msgstr "@george3_cry 𢙲慃空㦖𠾒姉𢴇𡛤時哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:163:text
msgid "@george3_worry He's brilliant, he works so fast...."
msgstr "@george3_worry 翁過才能、𪵯役過能率。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:164:text
msgid ""
"@george3_worry I'm so behind with publishing his books....what if he thinks "
"I'm too slow..."
msgstr "@george3_worry 姉踸進度出版過。。。𢙲慃擬姉過踸時哰。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:165:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sigh Even after he's stopped sending me things, I still can't keep "
"up..."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 𠸥𪥘󠄁𢖖󠄁欺翁凝寄版草㵋、姉吻空体扒及得。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:166:text
msgid "@george3_sad The pile seems to just keep growing..."
msgstr "@george3_sad 𥔧紙如矯據接續胓𫥨丕。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:171:text
msgid "@george4_omg Oh! These are the manuscripts The Author sent me!"
msgstr "@george4_omg 溩！低𪜀仍版草作者創世寄姉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:172:text
msgid ""
"@george4 As the head librarian, it's my job to help him with the publication "
"process."
msgstr "@george4 喟資格守書、任務𧵑姉𪜀𢴇翁𧘇𥪝過程出版。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:173:text
msgid "@george4_golly But ah... lately he hasn't been sending me anything."
msgstr "@george4_golly 扔啊。。。𨄹尼慃空寄姉之歇。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:174:text
msgid "@george4_golly This isn't like him..."
msgstr "@george4_golly 空偅慃𧘇𠬠𡭧鬧。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:175:text
msgid ""
"@george4 I mean, I guess it does give me some extra time to work through "
"this backlog!"
msgstr "@george4 意𪜀、姉拱𣎏添𠃣時𣇞抵扒及仍版草哙當存！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:176:text
msgid "@george4_oops To be honest, I'm a little behind, haha!"
msgstr "@george4_oops 實事抵𦓡吶、姉唏踸進度妬、哬哬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:177:text
msgid "@george4_omg That guy works really fast!"
msgstr "@george4_omg 翁𧘇𪵯役𨘱實！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:179:text
msgid ""
"@george4 ...the weird part is,\\>\\nI've been publishing book after book "
"AFTER he stopped sending me things, right?"
msgstr ""
"@george4 。。。𨓐於𠬠𡊲𪜀、\\>\\n自𢖖󠄁欺慃凝寄版草、姉吻出版調憚層卷層卷董空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:180:text
msgid ""
"@george4_golly But the pile of manuscripts never seems to get any smaller!"
msgstr "@george4_golly 扔𥔧版草矓拯𣎏𨤔之𪜀𡮈𠫾𪥘󠄁！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:181:text
msgid "@george4_golly ...at all!"
msgstr "@george4_golly 。。。怞只𠬠𡭧！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:182:text
msgid "@george4_oops Golly, you think I'm going bonkers?"
msgstr "@george4_oops 喂𡗶、㛪𣎏擬姉𠅒智耒空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:187:text
msgid "@george5_smile I see you've taken an interest to the manuscripts!"
msgstr "@george5_smile 姉𧡊㛪𣎏𨤔可適趣各版草！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:188:text
msgid "@niko What are they for?"
msgstr "@niko 衆抵𪵯之丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:189:text
msgid "@george5_aww Well, aren't you curious, little one!"
msgstr "@george5_aww 㛪實徂摸妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:190:text
msgid "@george5 The Author passed these drafts to me, you see!"
msgstr "@george5 作者創世迻姉扔版草尼、㛪𧡊妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:191:text
msgid ""
"@george5_smile Since I'm the head librarian, I am supposed to help him "
"publish these!"
msgstr "@george5_smile 爲姉𪜀守書、姉沛𢴇翁𧘇出版衆！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:192:text
msgid "@george5_hmm But... oh, I haven't seen that gentleman lately...."
msgstr "@george5_hmm 扔。。。喂、𨄹尼姉空𧡊翁𧘇兜𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:193:text
msgid ""
"@george5 Which is quite strange! Usually he delivers these manuscripts to me "
"faster than I can work on them!"
msgstr "@george5 可𨓐常妬！平常慃轉版草𦤾𨘱欣速度𪵯役𧵑姉㫻！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:194:text
msgid ""
"@george5_heh I guess now it just means I get a little more breathing room, "
"hohoho!"
msgstr "@george5_heh 昃𪜀自𣇞姉𣎏添𠃣時間𣇝𡂳、唬唬唬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:195:text
msgid "@niko_speak That's good!\\>\\@niko ...right?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 丕𪜀卒妬！\\>\\@niko 。。。沛空𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:196:text
msgid "@george5_hmm I don't know! I AM quite worried about him."
msgstr "@george5_hmm 姉空別𡛤！姉實事可𢥈𢠯𧗱翁意妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:197:text
msgid "@george5_hmm I hope he hasn't fallen ill from all that stress!"
msgstr "@george5_hmm 懞𪜀慃空𢭰病爲壓力工役！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:198:text
msgid "@george5_smile At least I got my hands full for the time being."
msgstr "@george5_smile 暫時時姉拱𣎏役𣹓𢬣耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:199:text
msgid ""
"@george5 Even though he's stopped sending me things, it doesn't feel like he "
"did at all!"
msgstr "@george5 怞慃空寄姉之𡛤、扔感覺吻如𫇰丕！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:200:text
msgid ""
"@george5_heh The pile of manuscripts I still need to proofread doesn't seem "
"to get smaller, haha!"
msgstr "@george5_heh 量版草姉沛讀閱𣎏𨤔吻空減𠫾、哬哬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:205:text
msgid "@niko This box is full of loose papers and notebooks."
msgstr "@niko 桶貯𣹓紙𥛭吧擻𢬣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:206:text
msgid "@george6_point Yo, these are the manuscripts The Author gave me."
msgstr "@george6_point 𠴗、低𪜀埬版草作者創世迻姉。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:207:text
msgid "@george6_smile I'm supposed to like, help him publish and stuff."
msgstr "@george6_smile 姉沛、矯、𢴇慃出版吧𤗆次。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:208:text
msgid "@george6 But he hasn't shown his face 'round these parts lately."
msgstr "@george6 扔𨄹尼拯𧡊慃𥌧𩈘𬨠於兜之歇。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:209:text
msgid "@george6 That's like, throwin off my groove, man."
msgstr "@george6 矯、伮𪵯秩喋𧵑姉啞。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:210:text
msgid ""
"@george6_shrug Like, I'm used to him sending me new stuff all that time."
msgstr "@george6_shrug 矯、𣇞姉㐌慣役𣅶鬧慃拱寄材料㵋朱姉耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:211:text
msgid ""
"@george6 I mean, of course I can't keep up with the pace that he's writin', "
"but he don't mind."
msgstr "@george6 意𪜀、必然姉空体蹺及速度𢪏攊𧵑慃、扔𣎏𨤔慃空抵心𡗋。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:212:text
msgid "@george6_fingerguns Guy's just tooootally passionate 'bout his job!"
msgstr "@george6_fingerguns 單簡𪜀慃超㤇藝催啊！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:213:text
msgid "@george6_smile Makes me wanna work hard too, so I do!"
msgstr "@george6_smile 慃哙傳感興朱姉𪵯役能率欣𡛤！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:214:text
msgid ""
"@george6 I've been playin catchup with the stuff I haven't gotten to finish "
"yet."
msgstr "@george6 姉吻當𨔈𨘗扒喟埬役姉貯完成。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:215:text
msgid "@george6_point But you know what's weird?"
msgstr "@george6_point 扔㛪別𨓐於𡊲鬧空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:216:text
msgid "@niko What?"
msgstr "@niko 𡊲鬧吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:217:text
msgid "@george6_shrug The stuff I'm supposed to finish don't get finished."
msgstr "@george6_shrug 仍次當𫥨姉沛𪵯歱時空包𣇞歱𪥘󠄁。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:218:text
msgid ""
"@george6 Like I've put out book after book but the work pile don't get any "
"smaller."
msgstr "@george6 矯姉㐌朱𫥨歇頭冊尼𦤾頭冊恪扔𥔧役拯𡮈𠫾𡭧鬧𪥘󠄁。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:4:219:text
msgid "@george6_shrug ...Have I really been slackin' that much?"
msgstr "@george6_shrug 。。。姉𢜞𪵯𦤾勢哰？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:6:1:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak The computer screen says something about \"updated databases\"."
msgstr "@niko_speak 幔形𣛠併𥱬之妬𧗱「基礎與料及日」。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:7:text
msgid ""
"@george1 So!\\>\\n\\@george1_smug Someone here to see the brilliant George, "
"eh?"
msgstr "@george1 溩！\\>\\n\\@george1_smug 𣎏𠊛𦤾低抵﨤觫大才、𠯋？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:8:text
msgid ""
"@george1_smug Caught wind of my genius and couldn't help but come see for "
"yourself, eh?"
msgstr "@george1_smug 𦖑訰𠺙𧗱智慧天才𧵑姉耒空体強徠、𠯋？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:10:text
msgid "@george1 ...don't answer!\\>\\n\\@george1_smug Of course you are."
msgstr "@george1 。。。空沛㨋𠳒兜！\\>\\n\\@george1_smug 昃𥗜𪜀如丕耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:11:text
msgid "@george1_smile What else could you ~possibly~ want?"
msgstr "@george1_smile 㛪哙𣎏体懃之～恪～𡛤渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:12:text
msgid ""
"@niko Actually... \\@niko_speak I need your help!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak Can you "
"tell me what I need to do?"
msgstr ""
"@niko 寔𫥨。。。\\@niko_speak 㛪懃姉𢴇吖！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 姉𣎏体朱㛪別沛"
"𪵯之空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:13:text
msgid "@niko I think... I'm supposed to go in the Tower..."
msgstr "@niko 㛪擬。。。㛪沛𠓨座塔。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:14:text
msgid "@george1_smug Ah, but of course I can help!"
msgstr "@george1_smug 啊、扔必然姉吻𣎏体𢴇扡渚！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:15:text
msgid ""
"@george1 For I...the brilliant and intelligent head librarian George, "
"beholder of all knowledge........"
msgstr "@george1 爲姉。。。守書偉大吧智慧觫、仉捻𡨺𤗆知識。。。。。。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:16:text
msgid "@george1_hm ...Believe you're supposed to go in the Tower!"
msgstr "@george1_hm 。。。擬哴㛪沛𠓨座塔！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:17:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed That's what I said...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak But how, exactly?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 時㛪吶丕𦓡。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 扔憑格鬧㵋得渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:18:text
msgid "@george1 Through the Tower entrance room!"
msgstr "@george1 過房𫔤𠓨𧵑座塔！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:19:text
msgid ""
"@george1_hm Alas, going beyond that small entrance room requires ancient, "
"forbidden knowledge that eludes even George."
msgstr "@george1_hm 雖然、抵越過間房𡮈妬要求見識禁古代㑲㘉外尋曉別𧵑觫。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:20:text
msgid "@george1 ...but fear not!"
msgstr "@george1 。。。扔𠤌𣎏𢜝駭！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:21:text
msgid ""
"@george1 If that knowledge happens to be recorded in some cryptic tome in a "
"long-dead language..."
msgstr "@george1 裊見識妬得𥱬劄徠憑𠬠言語𣩂𥪝𠬠捲密書鬧妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:22:text
msgid ""
"@george1_smug Then know that I, George, am fluent in several dead languages!"
msgstr "@george1_smug 時唉𢖵哴姉、觫、通繰𡗉次言語𣩂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:23:text
msgid "@niko I...see!"
msgstr "@niko 𫥨。。。勢！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:27:text
msgid "@niko Excuse me..."
msgstr "@niko 姉㗒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:28:text
msgid "@george2_stress Hey!!!"
msgstr "@george2_stress 尼！！！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:29:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr Who the heck do you think you are, barging in here like that?"
msgstr "@george2_grr 𠎩擬𠎩𪜀埃𦓡自便𠓨低勢嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:30:text
msgid ""
"@george2_NO I don't care if you're the Messiah, manners are still a thing!"
msgstr "@george2_NO 𠋥𣎏𪜀𠎬救世時吻沛遵蹺法則渚！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:31:text
msgid "@niko I'm... \\>\\@niko_speak sorry?"
msgstr "@niko 㛪。。。 \\>\\@niko_speak 吀纇？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:32:text
msgid "@george2 Well? Are you just here to apologize?"
msgstr "@george2 哰？𠎩𦤾低只抵吀纇催嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:33:text
msgid "@niko ...Yes? \\.\\.\\n\\@niko_speak I mean, no!"
msgstr "@niko 。。。𠳐？ \\.\\.\\n\\@niko_speak 意𪜀、空吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:34:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed I mean, I need your help...\\>\\n\\@niko I'm not sure what I "
"need to do next."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 意𪜀、㛪懃姉𢴇吖。。。\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪空別沛𪵯之接蹺。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:35:text
msgid "@niko I think I need to go in the Tower?"
msgstr "@niko 㛪擬㛪沛𠓨座塔吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:36:text
msgid "@george2 Seriously? You haven't figured that one out yet?"
msgstr "@george2 實㫻？㛪貯解決得伮嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:37:text
msgid "@niko_speak I don't know how to get in!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 㛪空別𠓨矯之！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:38:text
msgid ""
"@george2_grr Well, I don't know either.\\n\\>\\@george2 Shouldn't \\p help "
"you with that?"
msgstr ""
"@george2_grr 時、姉拱𠁙別兜。\\n\\>\\@george2 當𫥨\\p沛𪜀𠊛𢴇㛪𠓨妬渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:39:text
msgid ""
"@george2_sigh All I know is that nobody from this world can get in there."
msgstr "@george2_sigh 姉只別𪜀空𠬠埃𧵑世界尼𣎏体𠓨妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:40:text
msgid "@george2_grr Not beyond that tiny entrance room, anyway."
msgstr "@george2_grr 𠃣一𪜀空体過丐房𠓨𡮣俏妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:41:text
msgid ""
"@george2 If anything, there might be a book on how the Messiah of all people "
"can get in."
msgstr "@george2 𣎏欺徠𣎏冊之妬𧗱格𠎬救世𣎏体𠓨妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:42:text
msgid "@george2_sigh But I don't got anything like that in MY collection."
msgstr "@george2_sigh 扔𥪝部搜集𧵑姉拯𣎏之如丕歇。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:43:text
msgid "@george2_grr Would like to, though."
msgstr "@george2_grr 𣎏時㐌咍。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:48:text
msgid "@george3_sad Si\\.i\\.i\\.\\.i\\.\\.igh."
msgstr "@george3_sad 𡗶\\.－\\.－\\.\\.－\\.\\.吖。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:49:text
msgid "@niko Um... hi?"
msgstr "@niko 𫫡。。。姉㗒？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:50:text
msgid "@george3_sigh ...\\.Hi."
msgstr "@george3_sigh 。。。\\.嘲㛪。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:51:text
msgid "@niko_speak Are you alright?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 姉穩空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:52:text
msgid "@george3_sad .\\..\\..\\.."
msgstr "@george3_sad 。\\.。\\.。\\.。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:53:text
msgid "@niko .\\..\\..\\.."
msgstr "@niko 。\\.。\\.。\\.。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:54:text
msgid "@george3_worry Can I... help you..."
msgstr "@george3_worry 姉𣎏体。。。𢴇之㛪空。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:55:text Maps/Green/Village/friendly child npc:1:4:text
#: npc:1:13:text Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV020:1:11:text
msgid "@niko_speak Yeah!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:56:text
msgid "@niko I was wondering if you can tell me what I should do next?"
msgstr "@niko 空別姉𣎏体朱㛪別𢧚𪵯之接蹺空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:57:text
msgid "@niko I...think I'm supposed to go in the Tower."
msgstr "@niko 㛪擬。。。㛪沛𠓨座塔。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:58:text
msgid ""
"@george3_sad ...the Tower....\\>\\n\\@george3_sigh A grim obelisk... "
"\\>\\@george3_sigh a solemn reminder of our fate."
msgstr ""
"@george3_sad 。。。座塔。。。。\\>\\n\\@george3_sigh 𠬠像臺盡世。。。 "
"\\>\\@george3_sigh 𠬠𠳒𠯅嚴毅𧗱数分𧵑衆些。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:59:text
msgid "@george3_cry We're all gonna dieeeeeee...."
msgstr "@george3_cry 衆些𢯛𠅒命𪥘󠄁耒。。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:61:text
msgid ""
"@niko_what ...so...\\>\\@niko_eyeclosed how do I... \\>\\@niko_speak Get in?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_what 。。。勢時。。。\\>\\@niko_eyeclosed 㛪。。。\\>\\@niko_speak 𠓨矯"
"之丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:62:text
msgid ""
"@george3_cry I don't know...!!!\\>\\n\\@george3_sad I've been reading and "
"studying all my life, and yet..."
msgstr ""
"@george3_cry 姉空別。。。！！！\\>\\n\\@george3_sad 姉㐌𧶄𪥘󠄁𠁀學吧讀、丕"
"𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:63:text
msgid "@george3_cry I haven't even found any books about entering the Tower!"
msgstr "@george3_cry 姉吻貯尋得冊鬧𢪏𧗱役𠓨座塔𪥘󠄁！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:64:text
msgid ""
"@george3 Oh, I know there's a small room you can go in, but..."
"\\>\\n\\@george3_cry Everybody knows that!"
msgstr ""
"@george3 溩、姉別𣎏𠬠房𡮈㛪𣎏体𠓨、扔。。。\\>\\n\\@george3_cry 丐蒂時埃𠁙"
"別！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:69:text
msgid "@george4_smile Helloooo~!\\>\\nYou must be the savior!"
msgstr "@george4_smile 吀嘲～！\\>\\n𪳨㛪𪜀𠎬救世！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:70:text
msgid "@george4_omg I'm soooo happy I actually get to meet you! <3"
msgstr "@george4_omg 姉窒窒𢝙𡳳窮拱得﨤㛪！<3"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:71:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's nice to meet you too, miss!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 㛪拱窒𢝙得﨤姉吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:72:text
msgid ""
"@george4 So! Are you here to check out the archives?\\>\\n\\@george4_omg I "
"can give you a tour!"
msgstr ""
"@george4 嗏！丕𪜀㛪𦤾低抵參觀庫留貯嘑？\\>\\n\\@george4_omg 姉𣎏体引㛪𠫾衝"
"𨒺！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:73:text
msgid "@niko Actually... \\>\\n\\@niko_speak I need your help!"
msgstr "@niko 寔𫥨。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 㛪懃姉𢴇吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:74:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Can you tell me what I need to do next?\\>\\n\\@niko I think... "
"I'm supposed to go in the Tower..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 姉朱㛪別沛𪵯之接蹺空吖？\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪擬。。。㛪沛𠓨座塔"
"吖。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:75:text
msgid "@george4 Yup!"
msgstr "@george4 董丕！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:76:text
msgid "@niko Do you know how I can get in?"
msgstr "@niko 姉別㛪𣎏体𠓨勢鬧空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:77:text
msgid "@george4 Nope!"
msgstr "@george4 空！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:78:text
msgid ""
"@george4_golly Gosh, I don't think ANYONE's supposed to get inside the Tower!"
msgstr "@george4_golly 𡗶、姉空擬𣎏埃𣎏体𠓨𥪝妬兜！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:79:text
msgid ""
"@george4 I mean, there's a little room that you can go into..."
"\\>\\n\\@george4_golly But there's no stairs or elevators or anything else..."
msgstr ""
"@george4 意𪜀、𥪝妬𣎏𠬠房𡮈㛪𣎏体𠓨。。。\\>\\n\\@george4_golly 扔空𣎏橋簜咍"
"簜𣛠咍之𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:80:text
msgid "@george4 If you want my guess, you'll probably need \\p's help?"
msgstr "@george4 裊㛪㦖𠬠倣斷自姉、𣎏𨤰㛪𠱊懃事助𢴇𧵑\\p庄？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:81:text
msgid "@george4_oops I don't know how exactly..."
msgstr "@george4_oops 姉空別正確如勢鬧。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:82:text
msgid ""
"@george4 In my experience, that kind of knowledge is usually recorded in "
"some sort of cryptic book."
msgstr "@george4 蹺經驗𧵑姉、類見識妬常㑲𥪝𠬠卷密書鬧妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:83:text
msgid ""
"@george4_golly But I haven't read anything like that before..."
"\\>\\n\\@george4_oops Sorry!"
msgstr ""
"@george4_golly 扔姉貯曾讀冊鬧如丕𪥘󠄁。。。\\>\\n\\@george4_oops 吀纇唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:88:text
msgid "@george5 Oh, hello there!"
msgstr "@george5 溩、嘲㛪！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:89:text
msgid "@george5_smile You must be the savior!"
msgstr "@george5_smile 㛪𪜀𠎬救世𠰚！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:90:text
msgid "@george5_aww And also, the cutest darn thing I have ever seen!"
msgstr "@george5_aww 吧拱𪜀𠀲𡮈易傷一姉曾𧡊妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:91:text
msgid "@niko U- um... \\>\\n\\@niko_speak Thank you!"
msgstr "@niko 唹－𫫡。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 感恩姉唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:92:text
msgid "@george5_smile Can I help you with anything, sweetie?"
msgstr "@george5_smile 姉𣎏体𢴇之畺空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:93:text
msgid "@niko Mhm!\\>\\n\\@niko I want to know what I should do next!"
msgstr "@niko 唹𠼯！\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪㦖別沛𪵯之接蹺吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:94:text
msgid "@niko I think I'm supposed to go in the Tower?"
msgstr "@niko 形如㛪沛𠓨座塔吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:95:text
msgid "@george5 Oooh that's right, the Tower!"
msgstr "@george5 溩董耒、座塔！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:96:text
msgid "@george5_smile I know there's a small room that you can go into, but..."
msgstr "@george5_smile 姉別𣎏𠬠房𡮈㛪𣎏体𠓨、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:97:text
msgid "@george5_hmm ...I'm afraid nobody knows how to get in beyond that!"
msgstr "@george5_hmm 。。。姉㥋𪜀空埃別格進漊欣兜！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:98:text
msgid ""
"@george5_heh Not even silly ol' me, who spent her entire life reading books "
"about the world..."
msgstr "@george5_heh 𦤾𪥘󠄁姉、㐌𧶄𪥘󠄁𠁀讀𨁥類冊𧗱世界哙空別幾𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:100:text
msgid ""
"@george5 I think you need some help from \\p, but I don't know any details!"
msgstr "@george5 𣎏𨤔㛪懃𠬠𠃣𢶢𨉞自\\p、扔姉空別枝節欣丕！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:101:text
msgid ""
"@george5_hmm I've never found any books about this before..."
"\\>\\n\\@george5_smile You'd think there would be at least ONE book on this, "
"but I guess that's just how it is!"
msgstr ""
"@george5_hmm 姉𣗓曾𧡊頭冊鬧𧗱題材尼𪥘󠄁。。。\\>\\n\\@george5_smile 𣎏𨤔沛𣎏𠃣"
"一𠬠卷、扔事𠁀𪜀丕𦓡！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:102:text
msgid "@george5_hmm Goodness, this is quite the dilemma!"
msgstr "@george5_hmm 𡗶、可𪜀𤐓蒂！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:106:text
msgid "@george6 Hey, lil' fella!"
msgstr "@george6 盧翁𡥙！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:107:text sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:78:text
msgid "@niko_speak Hello!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 吀嘲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:108:text
msgid ""
"@george6_point So you're gonna like, save the world and stuff!"
"\\>\\n\\@george6_smile Didn't think I'd run into ya. But now I did!"
msgstr ""
"@george6_point 丕𪜀翁𡥙𠱊、解救世界吧𨁥次恪妬！\\>\\n\\@george6_smile 姉空擬"
"𠱊﨤得翁𡥙。扔𣇞時耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:110:text
msgid "@niko_speak Um, thanks?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫫡、感恩吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:111:text
msgid "@george6 So like, what up?\\>\\n\\@george6_smile Can I getcha anything?"
msgstr "@george6 丕時、𣎏之㵋？\\>\\n\\@george6_smile 姉𣎏体𪵯之朱㛪空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:112:text
msgid "@niko_speak Yeah! I heard you can help me!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏吖！㛪𦖑𪜀姉𣎏体𢴇㛪！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:113:text
msgid "@niko I'm not sure what I'm supposed to do now..."
msgstr "@niko 㛪空別𣊾𣇞沛𪵯之。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:114:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I think I'm supposed to go in the Tower...\\>\\n\\@niko But how "
"do I do that?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 形如㛪沛𠓨座塔。。。\\>\\n\\@niko 扔憑格鬧丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:115:text
msgid "@george6 Ya don't.\\>\\n\\@george6_shrug At least, WE don't."
msgstr "@george6 㛪空体。\\>\\n\\@george6_shrug 或𠃣一𪜀、𪨠姉空体。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:116:text
msgid ""
"@george6 The Tower's only got one teeny room in it, it ain't even got stairs!"
msgstr "@george6 座塔只𣎏董𠬠房𡮣俏、哙𠁙𣎏橋簜𡛤幾！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:117:text
msgid ""
"@george6_point I bet you need \\p's help on this one, pal..."
"\\>\\n\\@george6_shrug Exactly how? I dunno."
msgstr ""
"@george6_point 可昃翁𡥙𠱊懃\\p助𢴇頗尼妬。。。\\>\\n\\@george6_shrug 正確勢鬧"
"嘑？姉𠹾。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:118:text
msgid ""
"@george6 But I bet'cha anything that sorta knowledge is in some mystery book "
"somewhere."
msgstr "@george6 扔姉亇𪜀丐矯見識如勢只𣎏体於𥪝𠬠卷冊秘隱於兜妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/Map
#: Events:7:119:text
msgid "@george6_shrug Nothin' in my collection fits the description, tho."
msgstr "@george6_shrug 𥪝部搜集𧵑姉空𣎏之如丕歇。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/first aid
#: kit:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A book is poking out from the shelf."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠬠卷冊攂𫥨𠺌架冊。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/first aid
#: kit:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak Ah, this looks like a sketchbook of some sort!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 啊、𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠卷擻樸草！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/first aid
#: kit:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak Hey!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 尼！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/first aid
#: kit:1:3:text
msgid "@niko I think this book is actually about clovers..."
msgstr "@niko 形如卷尼𧗱𦹯𠀧蘿實。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/EV022:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A box full of notebooks."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠匣𣹓擻𢬣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/EV024:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Looks like a scanner."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𪜀𣛠𢭯。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library
#: entrance/stairwell/GeorgeRoom/EV025:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Looks like a printer."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𪜀𣛠印。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/EV004:1:1:text
#: deck/Cafe/EV006:1:1:text Maps/Red sky/Cafe/EV004:1:1:text
#: sky/Cafe/EV006:1:1:text
msgid "CAFE"
msgstr "館咖啡"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/EV007:1:1:text
#: deck/Cafe/EV008:1:1:text Maps/Red sky/Cafe/EV007:1:1:text
#: sky/Cafe/EV008:1:1:text
msgid "MEOW"
msgstr "渵"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:2:text
msgid "@niko \\p and I fixed the camera!"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟吧\\p㐌𢯢得𣛠影耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:3:text
msgid "Aw, sweet!"
msgstr "喂、絕𡸏！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:7:text 2/npc_camera:1:23:text
msgid "Are you here for your photos?"
msgstr "伴𦤾低執影嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:8:text
msgid "@niko_speak Actually, yeah!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫫡！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:9:text
msgid "@niko I need to take a picture for....\\. reasons."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟懃𨄴影爲。。。。\\.𡗉理由。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:10:text
msgid "Well, I got good news and bad news."
msgstr "時、𪝬𣎏信卒吧信醜。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:11:text
msgid "The good news is that the photo center is right behind me."
msgstr "信卒𪜀中心影𥮋𬆄𢖖󠄁𪝬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:12:text
msgid "@niko The bad news is that.... it doesn't work, right?"
msgstr "@niko 信醜𪜀。。。伮閧耒、沛空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:13:text
msgid "Heh, you're catching on quick."
msgstr "嗘、伴𨘱眜蒂。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:14:text
msgid "After operations ended in the Barrens, this place got shut down."
msgstr "𢖖󠄁欺活動在塳邊疆被停止、坭尼被㨂𫔤。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:15:text
msgid "All of the engineers lost their jobs and became street vendors."
msgstr "全部技事𠅒役吧𠫾𬥓行𨀐歇耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:16:text
msgid "@niko_speak Maybe \\p and I can figure it out from them!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏体𨉟吧\\p𠱊論𫥨得𤗆次自𣱆！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:17:text
msgid "That's good!"
msgstr "卒耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:18:text
msgid "It would certainly help out people with expired IDs."
msgstr "𠱊𢴇益可𡗉朱仍埃𣎏根腳歇限。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:19:text
msgid "...Like me."
msgstr "。。。如𪝬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:25:text
msgid "Alrighty then."
msgstr "得耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:26:text
msgid "I'll just... uh..."
msgstr "丕𪝬𠱊。。。唹。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/npc_camera:1:27:text
msgid "...stand here."
msgstr "。。。𨅸低。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:2:text
msgid "Hey kid!"
msgstr "尼傉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:3:text
msgid ""
"Want some soup dumplings? They're guaranteed to contain only a minimal "
"amount of industrial byproducts!"
msgstr "嗟湯包空？擔保只𣎏𠬠量最少化質工業！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:4:text
msgid "@niko I'll... pass..."
msgstr "@niko 催。。。吖。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:8:text
msgid "@niko Can you tell me how to get the camera working again?"
msgstr "@niko 英指㛪格起動徠𣛠影空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:9:text
msgid ""
"Yes, yes, certainly. The thick lens should be positioned to the left of both "
"of the curved lenses."
msgstr "𣎏、𣎏、必然耒。透鏡𪠗於邊債𪥘󠄁𠄩透鏡𢏣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:3:text
msgid "@niko Actually... I do want to hear about it!"
msgstr "@niko 寔𫥨。。。㛪𣎏㦖𦖑吖！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:4:text
msgid "Curiosity killed the cat, eh?"
msgstr "哙貓𣩂爲徂摸、擟？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:5:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'm not a cat..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪空沛貓。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:6:text 2/!vendor:1:27:text
msgid "Ok so!"
msgstr "溩雞時！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:7:text 2/!vendor:1:28:text
msgid ""
"I've invented a medicine to prepare everyone for the upcoming water shortage!"
msgstr "影㐌發明𫥨𠬠類𧆄抵準備𤗆𠊛朱澾割渃𢯛𬧐！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:8:text 2/!vendor:1:29:text
msgid "All you gotta do is dissolve one of these pills in water."
msgstr "只懃𢯠𠬠圓尼𠓨渃。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:9:text 2/!vendor:1:30:text
msgid "And then you drink the water."
msgstr "耒㕵渃。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:10:text 2/!vendor:1:31:text
msgid "And then you never need to drink water again!"
msgstr "耒㛪𠱊包𣇞沛㕵渃𡛤！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:11:text 2/!vendor:1:32:text
#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:47:text
msgid "@niko_speak What!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 實哰！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:12:text 2/!vendor:1:33:text
msgid "It also makes plants grow faster!"
msgstr "伮拱𢴇𣘃樻𠚐𨘱欣𡛤！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:13:text 2/!vendor:1:34:text
msgid "@niko How... does it work?"
msgstr "@niko 伮。。。活動勢鬧丕？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:14:text 2/!vendor:1:35:text
msgid "Here, why don't you take a free sample?"
msgstr "低、哰㛪空用試免費𠬠圓𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:16:text 2/!vendor:1:37:text
msgid "@niko Thanks?"
msgstr "@niko 感恩吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:17:text 2/!vendor:1:38:text
msgid "Don't thank me! Go spread the word!"
msgstr "空沛感恩英兜！關報朱𤗆𠊛𠫾！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:23:text
msgid "Hey hey!"
msgstr "尼尼！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:24:text
msgid "Ready for me to blow your mind?"
msgstr "㐌𠻿𠳹抵影𪵯砮腦貯？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:44:text
msgid "Aww, but..."
msgstr "𫉩、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:53:text 2/!vendor:2:16:text
msgid "@niko_speak Can you tell me how to fix the camera?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 英𣎏体只㛪格𢯢𣛠影得空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:54:text 2/!vendor:2:17:text
msgid "Hmm... It's been a while."
msgstr "嘘。。。㐌可嘍耒。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:55:text 2/!vendor:2:18:text
msgid ""
"I'm pretty sure that the bulgy lens goes on one of the ends, but I forget "
"which."
msgstr "影𢖵可𤑟𪜀透鏡𡋃𡋃㑲於𠬠頭、扔影空𢖵𪜀頭鬧。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:2:3:text
msgid "This is going to help so many people..."
msgstr "伮𠱊𢴇得無數𠊛。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:2:4:text
msgid "...and also make me rich and famous and cool."
msgstr "。。。吧拱𪵯影𢀭𫰅、浽㗂吧惵𤳆𡛤。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:2:7:text
msgid "Actually... I exaggerated."
msgstr "寔𫥨。。。影吶放大妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:2:8:text
msgid "The effects of the pill wears off in like a week."
msgstr "功用𧵑圓𧆄𠅒𠫾𢖖󠄁曠𠬠旬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:2:9:text
msgid "But all you have to do is just take another pill!"
msgstr "扔只懃𪵯添圓𡛤𪜀歱！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:2:text
msgid "@niko This stand smells a bit like burnt sugar..."
msgstr "@niko 柜尼苿唏偅糖𪸔。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:3:text
msgid "Yup... still gettin' the hang of making these fried candy skewers..."
msgstr "唹、姉吻當固𪵯朱卒仍釺𥼱𤓢尼。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:4:text
msgid "They don't taste too bad, though! Do you want one?"
msgstr "衆拱空弊𡗋兜！㛪㦖試𠬠釺渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:5:text
msgid "@niko It's okay, thank you!"
msgstr "@niko 催吖、感恩姉！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:9:text
msgid "@niko_speak You used to be one of the camera engineers, right?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 姉曾𪜀技師𣛠影、沛空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:10:text
msgid ""
"The camera? Oh, joyous memories. We went through thick and thin together."
msgstr "𣛠影嘑？喂、仍記憶絕𡸏。𪨠姉𠓀𤘁𢖖󠄁𪠗𣎏僥。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:11:text
msgid "And by that I mean the concave lens did."
msgstr "意𪜀丐透鏡𡔑𪵯丕啞。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak This smells kinda nice!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 苿𦹳𠺳！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:3:text
msgid "@niko What is it?"
msgstr "@niko 𦁺之丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:4:text
msgid "Breaded fish!"
msgstr "𩵜襆餅麪𤓢妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:5:text
msgid "I toasted the bread myself!"
msgstr "自𢬣英𤓢餅麪妬！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:6:text
msgid "@niko_what ...I... see..."
msgstr "@niko_what 。。。𫥨。。。勢。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:10:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Is there anything you remember about how to work the camera?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 影𣎏𢖵之𧗱格運行𣛠影空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/!vendor:1:11:text
msgid ""
"Let me see... When arranging the lenses, make sure that the thin lens is "
"positioned between the two curved ones."
msgstr "抵䀡鬧。。。欺𢯛攝各透鏡、𢖵撻透鏡𤘁𡧲𠄩透鏡𢏣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:23:text
msgid "@plight_2 Well, good luck..."
msgstr "@plight_2 時、祝㛪𢆪慜唲。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:24:text
msgid "@niko_speak You too! \\>\\@niko With the lamp."
msgstr "@niko_speak 影拱丕唲！\\>\\@niko 喟丐畑。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:27:text
msgid "@plight Hey, you lookin for something?"
msgstr "@plight 尼、㛪懃尋之嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:28:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Yeah... I need to go find a library card now...\\>\\n\\@niko "
"Any idea where I can get one?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed 唹。。。𣇞㛪沛𠫾尋𥮋書院。。。\\>\\n\\@niko 影𣎏別㛪𣎏体檢𠬠"
"丐於兜空吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:29:text
msgid "@plight From...\\> the...\\> library?"
msgstr "@plight 自。。。\\> 書。。。\\>院？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:30:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed I tried that already!\\>\\n\\@niko The person in charge "
"wasn't here."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪試耒！\\>\\n\\@niko 𠊛管書院徠空於妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:31:text
msgid "@plight Oh, uh..."
msgstr "@plight 溩、唹。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:32:text
msgid ""
"@plight_2 Maybe check out the factory? You just take the stairs at the end "
"of this street and make a turn."
msgstr "@plight_2 𣎏欺㛪䀡試茹𣛠䀡？㛪𠫾橋簜於𡳳塘尼歱𥘶。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:33:text
msgid ""
"@plight There's a lot of scientists there.\\>\\n\\@plight_worry "
"Scientists... read books, right?"
msgstr ""
"@plight 𣎏𡗉茹科學於妬妬。\\>\\n\\@plight_worry 茹科學時。。。讀冊、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:34:text
msgid "@plight They might help you..."
msgstr "@plight 𣎏体𣱆𠱊𢴇㛪妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:41:text
msgid "@niko He looks busy..."
msgstr "@niko 矓愥𣎏𨤔絆。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:42:text
msgid "@plight_why You can tell, huh..."
msgstr "@plight_why 㛪別、𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:45:text
msgid "@plight Oh, hey there."
msgstr "@plight 溩、吀嘲。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:46:text
msgid "@plight_2 You, uh... \\.\\.doing okay?"
msgstr "@plight_2 㛪、唹。。。\\.\\.穩渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:47:text
msgid "@niko Yup!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak What are you doing?"
msgstr "@niko 𫫡！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 影當𪵯之丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:48:text
msgid "@plight Just filling this lamp here..."
msgstr "@plight 當針油朱丐畑尼催。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:49:text
msgid "@plight_2 It's...\\.\\.\\. taking a while..."
msgstr "@plight_2 當。。。\\.\\.\\.唏損時間𠬠𡭧。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:1:50:text
msgid "@plight_worry I...\\.\\. think it might be leaking..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 影。。。\\.\\.擬伮當被𣼼油。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:2:text
msgid "@plight Well, good luck..."
msgstr "@plight 時、祝𢆪慜唲。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:6:text
msgid ""
"@plight Thanks for taking them off my hands, I guess?\\>\\nThe lenses, that "
"is."
msgstr "@plight 感恩㛪㐌𥙩衆𠫾護影？\\>\\n意𪜀、透鏡意。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:7:text
msgid ""
"@plight_2b The scientists wanted me to use them to fix the camera in the "
"photo booth, but..."
msgstr "@plight_2b 各茹科學㦖影用衆抵𢯢𣛠影𥪝店影、仍𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:8:text
msgid "@plight_why ...you can imagine how that went."
msgstr "@plight_why 。。。㛪𣎏体想像伮𫥨哰耒蒂。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:9:text
msgid "@plight_worry I'm just glad I didn't break anything..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 𢆪𪜀影空𪵯閧丐之。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:13:text
msgid "@plight_shock Hey! Isn't that..."
msgstr "@plight_shock 尼！拯沛𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:14:text
msgid "@plight_wtf ..."
msgstr "@plight_wtf 。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:15:text
msgid ""
"@plight_worry (oH GOODNESS GRACIOUS DID THE MESSIAH AND LITERALLY GOD "
"THEMSELF JUST BREAK INTO MY HOUSE.)"
msgstr "@plight_worry （𢭶𬇓實事𠎬救世吧正𠎬全能𣃣𨇍𠓨茹𨉟蒂嘑。）"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:16:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! Was that... your..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！𣎏沛。。。𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:17:text sky/Elevator deck/Elevator
#: inside/elevator chat:1:15:text
msgid "@plight_wtf You heard me??"
msgstr "@plight_wtf 㛪𦖑𧡊英嘑？？？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:18:text
msgid "@plight_worry (IT KEEPS HAPPENING.)"
msgstr "@plight_worry （伮據侈𫥨懷催。）"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:19:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed ...sorry about breaking into your house.\\>\\n\\@niko We "
"didn't actually break anything, but..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed 。。。吀纇爲㐌突入𠓨茹英。\\>\\n\\@niko 𪨠㛪空𥙩之、扔"
"𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:20:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak \\p said I should take these plastic disks, for some reason?"
"\\>\\n\\@niko Should we put them back?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak \\p吶哴㛪懃仍𥐨𣺾尼、爲𠬠理由鬧妬？\\>\\n\\@niko 𪨠㛪𣎏𢧚㨋衆徠空"
"吖？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:21:text
msgid "@plight_2 It's okay, keep 'em."
msgstr "@plight_2 空哰、據𥙩𠫾。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/map events:2:22:text
msgid "@plight_worry I wouldn't have been able to fix that machine anyway..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 怞之英拱𠁙𢯢得丐𣛠妬兜𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/plight work:1:1:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak A streetlamp!\\>\\n\\@niko This one seems taller than the "
"others..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠬠榾畑塘！\\>\\n\\@niko 丐尼𣎏𨤔高欣仍丐哙徠。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:2:text
msgid ""
"@niko You want me use the crowbar to open the safe, \\p? \\>\\nI'll... try!"
msgstr "@niko 舅㦖𨉟用錆㖼𩿙抵𢲫咭嘑\\p？\\>\\n𨉟𠱊。。。固！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:4:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 The door is sealed flush! \\>\\@niko_eyeclosed We might need the code "
"after all..."
msgstr "@niko2 空𣎏溪抵𢭄㫻！\\>\\@niko_eyeclosed 𣎏𨤔衆些𠱊懃密碼妬。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:7:text
msgid "@niko A metal safe.\\nSeems like it's locked with a 6-digit code."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠隻咭鉄。\\n𣎏𨤔伮被銙憑𠬠碼𦒹𡨸数。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:8:text
msgid "@niko I don't... remember seeing any 6-digit codes. Do you, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 形如。。。𨉟貯﨤碼𦒹数鬧𪥘󠄁。舅𣎏𧡊之空、\\p？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:9:text
msgid "[ENTER CODE:]"
msgstr "【入碼：】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:21:text
msgid "@niko_speak Woah! It worked!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫽿！伮活動實尼！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:22:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 Wait, how did you know the code,\\n\\p?\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed I "
"still don't remember seeing one..."
msgstr ""
"@niko2 寬、𪵯哰舅別得密𦓡丕、\\n\\p？\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟㐌𧡊丐鬧兜"
"𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:24:choice:0
msgid "I had some help."
msgstr "𨉟㐌認𠬠𠃣助𢴇。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:24:choice:1
msgid "I have my ways."
msgstr "𨉟𣎏格𧵑𨉟。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:28:text
msgid "@niko_speak Really?\\>\\n\\@niko From who?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 實唹？\\>\\n\\@niko 自埃丕？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:30:choice:0
msgid "Don't worry about it."
msgstr "揨𢥈。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:40:text
msgid "@niko I...\\.\\.see!"
msgstr "@niko 𫥨。。。\\.\\.丕！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:44:choice:0
msgid "What's in the safe, Niko?"
msgstr "𥪝咭𣎏之丕、尼孤？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:50:text
msgid "@niko Oh! Right.\\n\\.\\.Let's see..."
msgstr "@niko 溩！沛耒。\\n\\.\\.䀡鬧。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:51:text
msgid "@niko_speak Ah! \\.\\. I found a gas mask!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 啊！\\.\\.𣎏𠬠𩈘𠌧防毒！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:54:text
msgid "@niko_speak Also... there's this weird-looking book!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 喟徠。。。卷冊奇𨓐尼！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:55:text
msgid "@niko I can't read it, though..."
msgstr "@niko 扔𨉟空讀得伮。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:56:text
msgid "@niko2 ...not that I can't read or anything! Because I can!"
msgstr "@niko2 。。。空沛爲𨉟瞙𡨸唉之兜！𨉟別讀𦓡！"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:57:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I just don't know what language this is..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 只𪜀𨉟空別低𪜀言語之催。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:1:73:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed That wasn't it..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 差耒。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/safe:2:1:text
msgid "@niko It's empty."
msgstr "@niko 𤿰空。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV111:1:1:text
msgid ""
"$Although the poisonous gas is highly localized to the vent zones, Barrens "
"workers were still recommended to wear gas masks."
msgstr "$雖氣毒主要集中𨒺各𡓇脫氣、工人漨邊疆吻得勸告㧅𩈘𠌧房毒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV111:1:2:text
msgid "$These masks were mandatory around active vent sites, of course."
msgstr "$必然𩈘𠌧𪜀扒𫃚𨒺各𡓇脫氣當活動j。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV111:1:4:text
msgid ""
"$As more and more of the workforce got replaced by robots, we found "
"ourselves with a surplus of abandoned gas masks."
msgstr "$欺人工𢴍被𠊛𣛠𠊝替、衆些𣎏𠬠量𡘯𩈘𠌧餘剩。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV111:1:5:text
msgid ""
"$It seemed like a waste to get rid of them all, so we kept a few for "
"emergencies."
msgstr "$𠬃歇衆𠫾時窒浪費、𢧚些𡨺徠𠬠𠄧隻朱場合緊急。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV112:1:1:text
msgid "$The sun will not return and the abyss is calling my name."
msgstr "$𩈘𡗶𠱊空𠭤徠吧淢瀋當哙𠸜𪝬。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV112:1:2:text
msgid "$I'm sorry, everyone..."
msgstr "$吀纇𤗆𠊛。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV112:1:3:text
msgid "$...for choosing to leave before the darkness suffocates us all."
msgstr "$。。。爲㐌𢵬𨖨𠫾𠓀欺琫𣋁𠸂洆衆些。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV113:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A torn page with faded ink."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠張紙𧛊㐌㗑墨。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV113:1:2:text
msgid ""
"$XX/XX/XX\\n\\nWith the mining operations going smoothly, materials are no "
"longer our limiting factor."
msgstr ""
"$𣈜——𣎃——𢆥——\\n\\n原物料空哙𪜀要素界限衆些欺各活動開拓鑛產㐌運行𣹗咮。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV113:1:4:text
msgid "$We will be able to build more resilient robots, both in body and mind."
msgstr "$衆些𠱊𣎏体𡏦仍𠊛𣛠堅強欣、𪥘󠄁𧗱体質吧精神。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/EV113:1:5:text
msgid ""
"$Specifically, the discovery of metal alloy 291 will likely allow the "
"development of highly efficient circuitry."
msgstr "$具体欣、勘破𧗱合金291可能𠱊引𦤾事發展各脈電效率高。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/glitch pixel:2:11:text
msgid "@niko_speak What IS that?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 丐之丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/Bed room/EV003:2:9:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I can't sleep now, \\p!\\>\\n\\@niko I need to get Calamus and "
"Alula to the sacred grounds."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 𣊾𣇞𨉟空𥄬得兜\\p！\\>\\n\\@niko 𨉟沛迻哥羅𡃙吧阿瞜羅𦤾聖地。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/pc:2:5:text
msgid "@ed [So, you figured out the code without fully exposing the film.]"
msgstr "@ed 【嗏、伴㐌論𫥨得碼数𦓡空懃𤇨𤏬全部𬌓眨。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/pc:2:6:text
msgid "@ed [Good for you.]"
msgstr "@ed 【卒耒。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/pc:2:10:text
msgid "@ed [You didn't need my help for this puzzle.]"
msgstr "@ed 【伴空懃𪝬助𢴇𥪝句賭尼。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/pc:2:11:text
msgid "@ed [And yet you're still here talking to me?]"
msgstr "@ed 【𦓡伴吻儺徠吶𡀯喟𪝬哰？】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/pc:2:12:text
msgid "@ed [How quaint.]"
msgstr "@ed 【寔𪜀奇𨓐。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:1:2:text events:1:96:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:1:57:text
msgid "@niko A heavy piece of metal set into the wall."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠塊金類𡘯沈𥪝墻。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:1:3:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I think it might be a door or some kind of vault."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣎏体𪜀𠬠𦑃𫔤咍咭鉄之妬。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:1:4:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid "@niko There's a small screen here, in the middle."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠬠幔形𡮈於𡧲。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:1:38:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed The door is locked."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𫔤被銙。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:1:39:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid "@niko Looks like it's asking for a password."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔伮要求入密口。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:1:40:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid ""
"@niko2 The word \"DOCUMENTS\" is on the screen, above the password prompt."
msgstr "@niko2 𨑗幔形𥱬詞「DOCUMENTS」、𨑗塢入密口。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:1:81:text events:1:87:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:1:50:text
msgid "@niko That wasn't it..."
msgstr "@niko 差耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:1:97:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:1:58:text
msgid "@niko_speak Looks like a door of some sort!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠𦑃𫔤！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:1:98:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:1:59:text
msgid "@niko There's a glowing lock symbol on a small screen."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠬠表象銙發𤏬𨑗幔形𡮈。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:2:2:text events:2:12:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid "@niko A row of glass tubes are set into the wall."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠行䈵驗水晶拫𠓨墻。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:2:3:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid "@niko They're high up!"
msgstr "@niko 衆於𨑗高過！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:2:7:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid ""
"@niko This looks like a countdown of some sort.\\>\\n\\@niko2 All the tubes "
"say \"0\"."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠銅壺點逆。\\>\\n\\@niko2 各䈵調現数「0」。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:2:8:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid ""
"@niko ...I guess it finished counting down to...whatever it was counting "
"down to?\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed Or maybe it's just broken."
msgstr "@niko 。。。𣎏𨤔伮㐌點歱次伮懃點耒？\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 或𪜀伮閧。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:2:9:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid "@niko2 You'd think the door would be open, yet..."
msgstr "@niko2 想𪜀𫔤𠱊𢲫、扔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/map events:2:13:text Maps/POSTGAME RED
#: SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map
msgid "@niko_speak I wonder what those numbers mean..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 空別仍哙数妬𣎏意義之。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:2:text
msgid "@ling_hm So..."
msgstr "@ling_hm 時。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:3:text
msgid "@ling Can I... get you anything to eat?"
msgstr "@ling 英𣎏体。。。𪵯之朱㛪咹空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:4:text
msgid "@niko2 No thank you!"
msgstr "@niko2 催吖！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:6:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed (Even though I could go for some pancakes right now...)"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed （嚜怞𨉟㦖咹𠄼丐餅喼𣊾𣇞。。。）"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:7:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed (There just isn't time...)"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed （空𣎏時間𡛤。。。）"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:11:text
msgid "@ling_hm At least people won't starve here..."
msgstr "@ling_hm 𠃣一時𤗆𠊛𠱊空𣩂𩟡於低。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:12:text
msgid "@ling_smile The perks of using a cafe as an emergency shelter, huh?"
msgstr "@ling_smile 用館咖啡𪵯坭住隱緊急拱𣎏利㗶、擟？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:16:text
msgid "@ling2 Oh!"
msgstr "@ling2 溩！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:17:text
msgid "@ling Hello, Messiah!"
msgstr "@ling 吀嘲、𠎬救世！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:18:text
msgid "@ling_hm You, um..."
msgstr "@ling_hm 㛪、唹。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:19:text
msgid "@ling_sigh You came at a bad time..."
msgstr "@ling_sigh 㛪𦤾唏差時点。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:20:text
msgid ""
"@ling_hm The apartment in the west sector got destroyed by squares a day "
"ago..."
msgstr "@ling_hm 區間戶於塳西被各塊𣃱破毀𠃣𣈜𠓀。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:21:text
msgid "@ling_sigh Terrible, isn't it?"
msgstr "@ling_sigh 實弊、沛空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:24:text
msgid "@ling_hm2 Ah, but at least the evacuees seem to be doing ok."
msgstr "@ling_hm2 啊、扔暫時仍移民吻穩。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/ling:1:25:text
msgid "@ling_hm2 We're letting them stay here for now."
msgstr "@ling_hm2 英當抵𣱆於暫低。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV002:1:1:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Apartments/Hall1/Room2 - peng/EV001:1:1:text
msgid "..............."
msgstr "。。。。。。。。。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV002:1:2:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Apartments/Hall1/Room2 - peng/EV001:1:2:text
msgid "@niko ......................."
msgstr "@niko 。。。。。。。。。。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV002:1:3:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Apartments/Hall1/Room2 - peng/EV001:1:3:text
msgid "..............................."
msgstr "。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV002:1:4:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Apartments/Hall1/Room2 - peng/EV001:1:4:text
msgid "@niko_speak ..................................."
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV002:1:5:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Apartments/Hall1/Room2 - peng/EV001:1:5:text
msgid "............................................."
msgstr "。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV002:1:6:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...same as usual, huh..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。吻如𫇰、嘑。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV003:1:5:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Now's not really the time to talk to penguins, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣊾𣇞空沛𣅶吶𡀯喟𪀄𦑃𡭕兜\\p。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV003:1:8:text
msgid "@niko2 Oh, it's that penguin..."
msgstr "@niko2 溩、𪜀注𪀄𦑃𡭕妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV003:1:12:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...yep."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。沛耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV006:1:1:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Cafe/Cafe
msgid "@niko Milk and sugar."
msgstr "@niko 𣷱吧糖！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV006:1:2:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Cafe/Cafe
msgid "@niko_speak I like both!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟適𪥘󠄁𠄩！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV006:1:3:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Cafe/Cafe
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...but not in coffee."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。扔空沛𠫾喟咖啡。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV007:1:1:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Cafe/Cafe sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV012:1:1:text
msgid "@Niko A coffee machine."
msgstr "@Niko 𠬠𣛠𢯠咖啡。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV007:1:2:text Maps/Red
#: sky/Cafe/Cafe
msgid "@niko_speak It's nearly full!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 伮近𣹓耒！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV009:1:2:text
msgid "I don't know what I'm gonna do without Model C-WT 2nd gen unit 4E!"
msgstr "𨉟空沛𪵯之欺空𣎏單位母C-WT𠁀次𠄩！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV009:1:5:text
msgid "Our apartment got evacuated while my parents were at work..."
msgstr "區間戶𧵑𨉟沛疏散𥪝欺爸媽𨉟當𠫾𪵯。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV009:1:6:text
msgid "...I'm waiting for them to pick us up now."
msgstr "。。。𨉟當䟻𣱆𦤾迍𨉟。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV009:1:7:text
msgid "I hope they're ok..."
msgstr "懞𣱆吻穩。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV009:1:8:text
msgid "At least my robot's with me..."
msgstr "𠃣一時𨉟吻哙𠊛𣛠𧵑𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV012:1:2:text
#: inside/EV012:1:7:text
msgid "[SQUARES ARE BAD]"
msgstr "【仍塊𣃱窒醜】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV012:1:5:text
msgid "[SQUARES MAKE THE PEOPLE EVACUATE]"
msgstr "【塊𣃱𪵯𠊛些沛疏散】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV012:1:6:text
msgid "[EVACUATION MAKES THE GIRL SAD]"
msgstr "【疏散𪵯姑𡛔𢞂】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV013:1:2:text
msgid "Scarves are great."
msgstr "巾𫏈𦙶絕𡸏實。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV013:1:3:text
msgid "If I had my stuff back.. I'd knit one for everyone here!"
msgstr "裊姉𥙩徠得𣘊𧵑姉。。。姉𠱊撣巾朱𤗆𠊛於低！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV013:1:6:text
msgid "Hey."
msgstr "尼。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV013:1:8:text
msgid "Is it me, or is it really cold outside?"
msgstr "𪜀英催、咍𡗶𣋚𠉞冷憞𠊛丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV013:1:9:text
msgid "@niko2 ...y'know, now that you've mentioned it..."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。英𠯅㛪㵋認𫥨。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV013:1:10:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed (it IS really chilly this time around, \\p...)"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed （吝尼寔事窒冷妬\\p。。。）"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV013:1:11:text
msgid "Good thing you've got a scarf, huh?"
msgstr "𢆪𪜀㛪𣎏巾𫏈、𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV015:1:2:text
msgid "Bessie's lookin pretty bummed about this too..."
msgstr "𦛺差拱𣎏𨤔𣝀㗴𧗱丐冷𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV015:1:3:text
msgid "There there, girl..."
msgstr "鬧鬧、𡛔㗒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV015:1:6:text
msgid "Dang it!"
msgstr "𡗶吖！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV015:1:7:text
msgid "I JUST moved into my apartment!"
msgstr "𪝬𣃣㵋轉𠓨間戶㵋𦓡！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/EV015:1:8:text
msgid "Now where am I gonna go!"
msgstr "𣇞時𠫾兜𧗱兜𣊾𣇞！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:2:text
msgid "@mason Black clovers are so resilient...\\.\\.I wonder how they do it?"
msgstr "@mason 𦹯𠀧蘿黰實堅強。。。\\.\\.空別衆𤯩勢鬧𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:7:text
msgid ""
"@mason It's really a shame that the Glen is starting to erode so fast now..."
msgstr "@mason 實惜欺區潭浰當潵沲𪬭𦤾丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:8:text
msgid "@mason Soon, the world won't have much room for plants left..."
msgstr "@mason 拯𠇍𡛤𦓡世界𠱊歇𡊲朱𣘃𦹯。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:9:text
msgid "@mason ...asides from black clovers, I mean."
msgstr "@mason 。。。意𪜀、外除𦹯𠀧蘿黰𫥨。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:12:text
msgid "@mason Bummer!"
msgstr "@mason 媄！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:13:text
msgid "@mason I had to leave most of my plants behind."
msgstr "@mason 英沛𠬃徠侯歇𣘃樻𧵑英。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:14:text
msgid "@mason This stinks!"
msgstr "@mason 㘛實！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:15:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Sorry to hear..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪窒惜。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:16:text
msgid "@mason Oh, speaking of plants..."
msgstr "@mason 溩、𠯅𦤾𦹯𣘃。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:17:text
msgid "@mason I heard the Glen is just COVERED in vines now."
msgstr "@mason 英𦖑信塳潭浰𣇞撫𡫨絏蹽耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:18:text
msgid "@mason Is that true?"
msgstr "@mason 𣎏沛丕空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:19:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...yeah..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。㖡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:20:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 The plant lady was using them to keep the land from falling away..."
msgstr "@niko2 姉𠊛𣘃用衆抵𡨺朱𩈘𡐙空𥒮砵𫥨。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:21:text
msgid "@mason The plant spirit?\\.\\. Maize?"
msgstr "@mason 木精零嘑？\\.\\.梅嘑？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:22:text
msgid "@mason I figured..."
msgstr "@mason 英拱擬勢。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:23:text
msgid "@mason ...say, how is she doing?"
msgstr "@mason 。。。𦓡、姉𧘇哰耒？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:25:text
msgid "@mason ...ah."
msgstr "@mason 。。。啊。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:26:text
msgid "@mason ...she's... gone, isn't she?"
msgstr "@mason 。。。姉𧘇。。。𠅒耒、𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:27:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed She said she was using up the last of her powers..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 姉𧘇吶𪜀𠱊用訥飭力𡳃窮𧵑姉。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:28:text
msgid "@mason I wouldn't be surprised."
msgstr "@mason 英空不㘈。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Cafe/Cafe inside/npc_mason:1:29:text
msgid "@mason She always did her best to protect everyone..."
msgstr "@mason 姉𧘇㫻㫻努力歇飭抵保衛𤗆𠊛。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/To Tower/map events:1:1:text sky/Apartments/Communal
#: area/north exit:1:7:text
msgid "@niko It looks like I can unlock this door..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𨉟𣎏体𢲫銙𦑃𫔤尼。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:4:text
msgid "@rowbot [.\\..\\..\\..]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【。\\.。\\.。\\.。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:8:text
msgid "@rowbot [OH!]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【溩！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:9:text
msgid "@rowbot [THIS IS AMBER FROM THE GLEN.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【低𪜀琥珀自塳潭浰。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:10:text
msgid "@rowbot [I CAN REMEMBER NOW!]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【𪝬𢖵徠耒！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:11:text
msgid "@rowbot [ACTIVATING TRACKING SYSTEM...]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【激活系統紬塘。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:12:text
msgid "@rowbot [SETTING COURSE...]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【設立路程。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:13:text
msgid "@rowbot [WAIT.\\>\\nTHIS BOAT IS OVER CAPACITY.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【寬。\\>\\n船現當過載。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:14:text
msgid "@rowbot [YOU'LL NEED TO LEAVE BEHIND SOME OF YOUR POSSESSIONS.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【伴𠱊沛𠬃徠𠬠數物用。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:15:text
msgid ""
"@niko Oh.\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed Well... I don't think I'll be needing this "
"crowbar anymore...\\>\\nOr this gas mask and gloves..."
msgstr ""
"@niko 溩。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 時。。。𣎏𨤰𨉟𠱊空懃錆𡎡𩿙尼𡛤。。。\\>\\n"
"或𪜀𩈘𠌧防毒喟對矜尼。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:27:text
msgid "@rowbot [THAT IS ACCEPTABLE.\\>\\nONWARDS WE GO.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【執認得。\\>\\n鬧些𠫾。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:55:text
msgid "@niko um.... \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 𫫡。。。 \\p？"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:56:text
msgid "@niko Is it alright if... you let me take a nap somewhere before we go?"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟𣎏体。。。𥄬於兜妬𠓀欺𠫾空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:57:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'm so tired I can't even see straight anymore..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟𤻻𦤾餒拯𥆾𣦎得𡛤耒。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:62:text
msgid "@rowbot [HAVE YOU TALKED TO THE HEAD ENGINEER YET?]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【伴㐌吶𡀯喟技師長𣗓？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:63:text
msgid "@rowbot [SHE LIVES NEAR THE MINE ENTRANCE.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【姑𧘇𤯩近𡓃𠓨𡌢𡎡。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:64:text
msgid "@rowbot [I  WOULD HAVE GIVEN YOU THE COORDINATES, BUT...]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【當𫥨  𪝬𠱊朱伴座度、扔𦓡。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:71:text
msgid "@niko_speak I need something I can use to wash the robot with!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟懃之妬抵𣳮𠊛𣛠尼！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:75:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed A sponge alone isn't going to remove all this rust..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 指𥢆𠬠𠰳渤㴜時空𢮭歇釲𡏥尼兜。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:83:text
msgid "@niko Alright.... hold still..."
msgstr "@niko 得耒。。。𡓮安唲。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:84:text
msgid "@rowbot [I HAVE NO OTHER CHOICE.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【𪝬空哙攄譔恪。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:86:text
msgid "@niko_speak There!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 妬！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:87:text
msgid "@niko How's that?"
msgstr "@niko 哰耒！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:88:text
msgid "@rowbot [...I... ]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【。。。𪝬。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:89:text
msgid "@rowbot [...CAN MOVE AGAIN.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【。。。𣎏体舉動徠得耒。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:90:text
msgid "@rowbot [THANK YOU!]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【吀感恩！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:93:text
msgid "@rowbot [I AM ABLE TO FULFILL MY PURPOSE AGAIN.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【𪝬𣎏体寔現任務𠭤徠耒。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:94:text
msgid "@rowbot [WHERE WOULD YOU LIKE TO GO?]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【伴㦖𠫾兜？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:95:text
msgid "@niko_speak Can you take me to the Tower?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 伴𣎏体迻𨉟𦤾座塔空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:96:text
msgid "@rowbot [CALCULATING...]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【當併算。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:97:text
msgid "@rowbot [CLOSEST DESTINATION TO THE TOWER IS...]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【点𦤾近座塔一𪜀。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:98:text
msgid "@rowbot [THE GLEN, PORT NUMBER - ]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【塳潭浰、港數－】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:101:text
msgid "@rowbot [MY BUILT-IN NAVIGATION CIRCUITS HAVE FRIED.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【脈電定位𧵑𪝬㐌閧。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:102:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak I'm.... \\.\\. \\@niko_eyeclosed gonna assume that's not good."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟。。。。 \\.\\. \\@niko_eyeclosed 𠱊假定妬空沛條卒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:103:text
msgid "@rowbot [IT IS NOT GOOD AT ALL.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【空卒𠬠𡭧鬧。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:104:text
msgid "@rowbot [ONCE AGAIN I CANNOT FOLLOW MY PROGRAMMING.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【𠬠吝𡛤𪝬空体遵蹺立程。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:106:text
msgid "@niko_speak Is there anything I can do to help?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟𣎏体𢴇之空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:107:text
msgid ""
"@rowbot [IN THE EVENT OF AN ERROR, YOU SHOULD SPEAK WITH THE HEAD ENGINEER.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【𥪝場合﨤纇、伴𢧚參問技師長。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:108:text
msgid "@rowbot [SHE WILL KNOW WHAT TO DO.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【姑𧘇𠱊別沛𪵯之。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:114:text
msgid "@niko_speak Wait! I need to protect my hands!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 寬！𨉟沛保衛𢬣𧵑𨉟㐌！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:115:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I don't wanna burn off my fingers..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空㦖被𤊡歇各𢭫𢬣兜。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:120:text
msgid "@niko Hang in there!"
msgstr "@niko 䟻𡭧唲！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:135:text
msgid "@rowbot [I AM FUNCTIONAL!]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【𪝬㐌活動𠭤徠！】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:136:text
msgid "@rowbot [WAS IT YOU WHO FIXED THE GENERATOR?]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【𪜀伴𢯢𣛠發電嘑？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:137:text
msgid "@niko_speak Well, \\p helped me!"
msgstr "@niko_speak \\p拱𣎏𢴇𨉟𠬠𡭧！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:138:text
msgid "@niko But yeah!"
msgstr "@niko 扔唹！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:139:text
msgid "@rowbot [HELLO. NICE TO MEET YOU.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【吀嘲。窒𢝙得﨤伴。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:140:text
msgid "@rowbot [I AM ROWBOT #310.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【𪝬𪜀𠊛𣛠棹船數310。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:141:text
msgid "@rowbot [WOULD YOU LIKE ME TO TAKE YOU SOMEWHERE?]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【伴𣎏㦖𠫾兜空？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:142:text Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:143:text
msgid "@rowbot [...]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【。。。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:149:text
msgid "@niko_speak Are you... okay?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 伴。。。穩渚？"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:150:text
msgid "@rowbot [I CANNOT MOVE.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【𪝬空体舉動。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:151:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Well, you're still really rusty..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 時、董𪜀伴當窒釲𡏥實。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:152:text
msgid "@rowbot [THAT IS TRUE.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【果𪜀如丕。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:153:text
msgid "@niko Hold on... \\p and I will find a way to help you!"
msgstr "@niko 䟻𪨠𨉟唲。。。𨉟吧\\p𠱊尋格𢴇舅！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:176:text
msgid "@niko I don't...think this battery is supposed to be for the robot..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟空。。。擬𫪐汴尼用朱𠊛𣛠兜。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:179:text
msgid "@niko_speak Um... hello?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫫡。。。吀嘲？"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:180:text
msgid "@rowbot_off  ..."
msgstr "@rowbot_off  。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:184:text
msgid "@niko This robot doesn't have power."
msgstr "@niko 𠊛𣛠尼空𣎏電。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:185:text
msgid "@niko_speak It might help us get across the ocean if we fix it!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏体伮𠱊𢴇𨉟越㴜裊𨉟𢯢得伮！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:188:text
msgid "@niko \\p, are you there?"
msgstr "@niko \\p、舅𣎏妬空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:194:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh, good!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩、咍！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:198:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Aw, bummer!"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𫉩、𤐓勢！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:199:text
msgid "@niko ...wait. \\.\\.\\@niko_speak You just answered me!"
msgstr "@niko 。。。寬。\\.\\.\\@niko_speak 舅𣃣㨋𠳒𨉟𦓡！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:200:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...you sure have a sense of humor, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。𢴉咍妬、\\p。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:203:text
msgid "@niko_speak There's a robot here, attached to a boat."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏𠬠𠊛𣛠於低、拫𠓨𠬠𡥵船。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:204:text
msgid ""
"@niko It doesn't seem to have power, and its joints are rusted over as well."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔伮空𣎏電、吧各𨨤拱㐌釲𡏥歇𪥘󠄁。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:205:text
msgid "@niko_speak But I think we should be able to fix it!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔昃𪜀𨉟𠱊𢯢伮得催！"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:1:206:text
msgid "@niko After all, we'll need to cross this ocean to get to the Tower..."
msgstr "@niko 矯之衆𨉟拱𠱊沛越大洋抵𦤾座塔𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:2:2:text
msgid ""
"@rowbot [`P%\\.\\.#L\\.E  A\\.SE D0 \\.N0@\\.\\. T AP \\.PRO%\\.\\.4AC \\."
"\\.H]"
msgstr ""
"@rowbot 【`口%\\.\\.#\\.千  扌\\.亭0 \\.彳0@\\.\\. 來\\.貝%\\.\\.近\\.\\.】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:2:3:text
msgid "@niko Oh no!\\>\\nIs there anything I can do to help?"
msgstr "@niko 喂空！\\>\\n𨉟𣎏体𢴇之舅空？"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:2:4:text
msgid ""
"@rowbot [IT\\. % \\.\\.IS DA-`\\.NGER\\.OU%S TO T\\.\\.RY A  ND A \\."
"$SIS\\.T M  E.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【空\\. % \\.\\.年-`\\.成\\.固%亘\\.\\.力  彳\\.$來\\.近。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:2:5:text
msgid "@rowbot [L\\.\\.EA\\.VE  `\\.T#HIS A\\.R`E \\.A.]"
msgstr "@rowbot 【氵\\.\\.來\\.口  `\\.鬼#亻氐\\.耳`宜\\.。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/npc_rowbot:2:9:text
msgid "@niko2 Oh no...\\>\\nIt's some weird... square stuff?"
msgstr "@niko2 喂空。。。\\>\\n𠬠次。。。塊𣃱之妬？"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/EV016:1:2:text Maps/Blue/Docks/EV020:1:2:text
#: Maps/Blue/Docks/EV021:1:2:text Maps/Blue/Docks/EV022:1:2:text
#: Maps/Blue/Docks/EV023:1:2:text Maps/Blue/Docks/EV024:1:2:text
#: Maps/Blue/Docks/EV025:1:2:text Maps/Blue/Docks/EV230:1:2:text Maps/SQUARES
#: BE GONE/Docks/EV016:1:2:text GONE/Docks/EV020:1:2:text
#: GONE/Docks/EV021:1:2:text GONE/Docks/EV022:1:2:text
#: GONE/Docks/EV023:1:2:text GONE/Docks/EV024:1:2:text
#: GONE/Docks/EV025:1:2:text
msgid "@niko I can see a green glow in the distance."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟𧡊𠬠暎𤏬青蘿自騰賒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/EV016:1:5:text Maps/Blue/Docks/EV020:1:5:text
#: Maps/Blue/Docks/EV021:1:5:text Maps/Blue/Docks/EV022:1:5:text
#: Maps/Blue/Docks/EV023:1:5:text Maps/Blue/Docks/EV024:1:5:text
#: Maps/Blue/Docks/EV025:1:5:text Maps/Blue/Docks/EV230:1:5:text Maps/SQUARES
#: BE GONE/Docks/EV016:1:5:text GONE/Docks/EV020:1:5:text
#: GONE/Docks/EV021:1:5:text GONE/Docks/EV022:1:5:text
#: GONE/Docks/EV023:1:5:text GONE/Docks/EV024:1:5:text
#: GONE/Docks/EV025:1:5:text
msgid "@ed [The horizon glows a faint green.]"
msgstr "@ed 【塘蹎𡗶𪹟暎𤏬青蘿𥊚。】"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:2:text
msgid "@ling_smile Hang in there.\\>\\nYou can do it."
msgstr "@ling_smile 固𬨠。\\>\\n㛪𪵯得𦓡。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:7:text
msgid ""
"@ling_shock Oh hey, you're back!\\>\\n\\@ling Did you manage to fix the "
"elevator?"
msgstr "@ling_shock 嗚尼、㛪𢮿徠耒！\\>\\n\\@ling 㛪𢯢得簜𣛠耒渚？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:8:text
msgid ""
"@niko Mhm!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak \\p and I went to the surface already!"
"\\>\\n\\@niko And..."
msgstr ""
"@niko 𫫡！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 㛪吧\\p㐌𬺗𩈘𡐙耒吖！\\>\\n\\@niko 吧。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:13:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed ...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak Well, I remembered there being a cafe "
"here!\\>\\n\\@niko Do you have pancakes?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed 。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 時、㛪𢖵𨑗尼𣎏𠬠館咖啡！"
"\\>\\n\\@niko 於低𣎏餅喼空吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:14:text
msgid "@ling We sure do!"
msgstr "@ling 必然耒！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:15:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Wait! I don't have any money...\\>\\n\\@niko Maybe I can help "
"you wash dishes...or... something?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 喂！㛪空𣎏錢。。。\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪𣎏体𣳮鉢護暎。。。咍。。。之"
"妬？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:16:text
msgid ""
"@ling_smile No, no! It's on the house!\\>\\n\\@ling The least I can do for "
"the savior, right?"
msgstr "@ling_smile 空懃兜！英包！\\>\\n\\@ling 條𠃣一暎𣎏体𪵯朱𠎬救世、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:17:text
msgid ""
"@ling Here, why don't you take a seat?\\>\\nI'll go fry some up for you."
msgstr "@ling 低、㛪𡓮𠫾。\\>\\n暎𠱊𠫾炟㫻𠇍丐朱㛪。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:18:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes Pancakes..."
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 餅喼。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:30:text
msgid ""
"@niko These pancakes are so good...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak Thank you so much!"
msgstr "@niko 餅喼唁過。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 感恩暎窒𡗉！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:31:text
msgid "@ling No problem!\\>\\nYou looked really hungry."
msgstr "@ling 空𣎏之！\\>\\n矓㛪𣎏𨤔𩟡𡗋。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:32:text
msgid ""
"@niko Yeah... I thought this would be my last chance to eat something before "
"I go in the Tower."
msgstr "@niko 𫫡。。。㛪擬低𠱊𪜀𩛷𡳃𧵑㛪𠓀欺𠓨座塔。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:33:text
msgid "@ling_hm2 Ah, gotcha."
msgstr "@ling_hm2 啊、曉。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:34:text
msgid "@ling So... I guess pancakes are your favorite food?"
msgstr "@ling 丕。。。暎斷餅喼𪜀𦁺𣗿𧵑㛪嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:35:text
msgid "@niko Mhm!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak ...well, almost!"
msgstr "@niko 𫫡！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 。。。近如丕！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:36:text
msgid ""
"@niko_pancakes My favorite food in the world are the special pancakes that "
"my mama makes!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 𦁺㛪適咹一果𡐙尼𪜀𦁺餅喼特別媄㛪𪵯！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:37:text
msgid "@niko She likes to pick hazelnuts and grind them up into the batter."
msgstr "@niko 媄適𢲨籺𣏌吧𢴘衆𫥨抵𢶿𠓨𥹸餅。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:38:text
msgid "@ling_smile Oh, wow, that sounds amazing!"
msgstr "@ling_smile 溩、𫽿、𦖑唁𠰘妬！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:39:text
msgid ""
"@niko_pancakes They TASTE amazing!\\>\\n\\@niko She always made them when I "
"was feeling sad.\\>\\n\\@niko Or lonely... or..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_pancakes 衆寔事超唁妬！\\>\\n\\@niko 媄咍𪵯衆欺㛪𢞂。\\>\\n\\@niko 或孤"
"單。。。或。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:40:text
msgid "@niko_sad ..."
msgstr "@niko_sad 。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:41:text
msgid "@niko_sad Mama...\\>\\n\\@niko_sad I really miss her..."
msgstr "@niko_sad 媄㗒。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_sad 㛪𢖵媄𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:42:text
msgid ""
"@niko_less_sad ...I just...\\>\\n\\@niko_sad ...I just have a bad feeling "
"all of a sudden!"
msgstr ""
"@niko_less_sad 。。。㛪。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_sad 。。。自仍㛪徠感𧡊𣎏之妬空穩！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:43:text
msgid ""
"@niko_distressed_meow Am I... even here to save the world?\\>\\nPeople have "
"been saying how the sun won't fix anything!"
msgstr ""
"@niko_distressed_meow 㛪𣎏實事。。。𦤾低抵救世界空丕？\\>\\n埃拱𠸒𪜀𣎏𩈘𡗶拱"
"拯解決得之歇！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:44:text
msgid ""
"@niko_sad I don't even know why I'm here...\\>\\n\\@niko_less_sad I just "
"wanna see my mama again..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_sad 㛪哙𠁙別在哰㛪𦤾低𡛤。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_less_sad 㛪只㦖﨤徠媄"
"催。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:45:text
msgid ""
"@ling2 Oh, uh...\\>\\n\\@ling_oh There, there...\\>\\n\\@ling_smile It's "
"gonna be okay!"
msgstr ""
"@ling2 溩、唹。。。\\>\\n\\@ling_oh 鬧、鬧。。。\\>\\n\\@ling_smile 𤗆次𠱊穩"
"催！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:46:text
msgid ""
"@ling_hm And...\\@ling I'm sure you'll be able to save the world! "
"\\>\\n\\@ling_smile You're a tough kid, you managed to get this far already, "
"right?"
msgstr ""
"@ling_hm 吧。。。\\@ling 暎昃𪜀㛪𠱊救得世界𦓡！\\>\\n\\@ling_smile 㛪𪜀𠬠𠀲稚"
"堅強𦓡、㛪㐌𦤾得盡低耒、沛空鬧？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:47:text
msgid "@niko_distressed_meow Yeah... \\.\\. but..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed_meow 𫫡。。。\\.\\.扔。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:48:text
msgid "@ling And you'll get to go home afterwards, right?"
msgstr "@ling 吧歱耒㛪𠱊得𧗱茹𦓡、董空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:49:text
msgid "@niko_less_sad Right..."
msgstr "@niko_less_sad 沛。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:50:text
msgid "@ling_smile ...Hey, want some more pancakes?"
msgstr "@ling_smile 。。。尼、㛪㦖添𠄧餅𡛤空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:51:text
msgid "@niko_cry It's ok...\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed ...I'll be fine."
msgstr "@niko_cry 催吖。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 。。。㛪𠱊穩催吖。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:61:text
msgid "@ling_smile So... yeah!\\>\\nThanks for coming by!"
msgstr "@ling_smile 𢧚𪜀。。。唹！\\>\\n感恩㛪㐌踦過唲！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:62:text
msgid ""
"@niko Mhm! Thanks for listening... \\>\\n\\@niko_speak ...AND for the "
"pancakes!"
msgstr "@niko 𫫡！感恩暎㐌𢠯𦖑。。。 \\>\\n\\@niko_speak 。。。吧𪥘󠄁爲餅喼𡛤！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:63:text
msgid "@ling No problem. Good luck!"
msgstr "@ling 空𣎏之。祝㛪𢆪慜！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:70:text
msgid "@ling_shock Oh, sorry about the trash on the floor..."
msgstr "@ling_shock 溩、吀纇爲埬𧅫𨑗孱唲。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:71:text
msgid ""
"@ling3 I was gonna throw it out earlier, but...\\>\\n\\@ling_oh ...then my "
"coworkers caught on fire and I had to drop everything to help them."
msgstr ""
"@ling3 暎𣃣定𫼳衆𠫾𢭰、扔𦓡。。。\\>\\n\\@ling_oh 。。。同業𧵑暎扑𪸔吧暎沛𠬃"
"𬆄𤗆次抵𠫾救𪝳。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:72:text
msgid ""
"@ling_sigh They're fine now though...\\>\\n\\@ling It's a good thing fire "
"doesn't hurt robots, huh?"
msgstr "@ling_sigh 𣊾𣇞時𪝳穩耒。。。\\>\\n\\@ling 𢆪𪜀焒空𪵯害𠊛𣛠、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:77:text
msgid "@ling Oh, hi there!"
msgstr "@ling 溩、吀嘲！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:79:text
msgid "@niko How come... there aren't any people here?"
msgstr "@niko 哰。。。𥪝館空𣎏客丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:80:text
msgid "@niko_speak Normally cafes have tons of people!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 平常館咖啡𣎏𣹓客𦓡！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:81:text
msgid "@ling_hm Yeah, it's a really slow day..."
msgstr "@ling_hm 𫫡、𣋚𠉞可𪜀靜𣼽。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:82:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Do you think it's because the ground access elevator is broken?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 英𣎏擬𪜀爲簜𣛠𬺗𩈘𡐙被閧耒空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:83:text
msgid "@ling_sigh So I've been told."
msgstr "@ling_sigh 英𦖑𠸒勢。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:84:text
msgid "@ling2 The city's infrastructure has been suffering a lot lately."
msgstr "@ling2 𨄹尼下層𧵑城庯被墟害窒𡗉。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:85:text
msgid "@ling_oh Skywalks and stairs breaking off left and right..."
msgstr "@ling_oh 行廊吧橋簜淶𢭮歇𡊲尼𦤾𡊲恪。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:86:text
msgid "@ling3 Now the only reliable way of transport are those elevators..."
msgstr "@ling3 𣇞方便𠫾徠唯一𪜀隻簜𣛠妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:87:text
msgid "@ling_sigh ...Until now, anyway..."
msgstr "@ling_sigh 。。。𠃣一𪜀朱𦤾𣊾𣇞。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:92:text
msgid ""
"@ling_hm You know, the tall guy came in here earlier saying the same thing."
"\\>\\nHe asked me if I've seen a button that says \"ground\" on it."
msgstr ""
"@ling_hm 㛪別之空、英𤳆高高𣃣𠓨低拱吶依頡。\\>\\n愥𠳨暎𧡊丐鈕鬧𥱬𪜀「𩈘𡐙」"
"空。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:93:text
msgid ""
"@ling He looked pretty stressed, so I wanted to cheer him up..."
"\\>\\n\\@ling_smile I told him the only \"ground\" I've seen today is coffee "
"grounds!"
msgstr ""
"@ling 愥矓𣎏𨤔可𢫮𣦎、𢧚暎㦖𪵯之妬抵愥𢝙𬨠𡭧。。。\\>\\n\\@ling_smile 暎𠸒𪝳"
"丐「𡐙」唯一暎𧡊𣋚尼𪜀𡐙𡥴！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:94:text
msgid "@ling3 He, um..."
msgstr "@ling3 愥、唹。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:97:text
msgid "@ling_hm He didn't get it..."
msgstr "@ling_hm 愥空曉得。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:102:text
msgid ""
"@ling3 I see him around a lot, but he never seems to have time to eat a "
"proper meal..."
msgstr "@ling3 英𧡊愥𨒺低窒𡗉、扔𣎏𨤔𪝳空欺鬧𣎏時𣇞抵咹𠬠𩛷仔細𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:103:text
msgid ""
"@ling_hm He kinda just, rushes in here, drinks a whole pot of coffee, and "
"then rushes back out?"
msgstr "@ling_hm 矯、愥衝𠓨低、𪵯元𠬠瓶咖啡、歱徠衝𫥨𧘇？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:104:text
msgid "@ling_hm2 He uh, he really... takes his job to the extreme."
msgstr "@ling_hm2 愥唹、愥實事。。。𪵯役憑𪥘󠄁性命妬。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:105:text
msgid ""
"@ling_oh ...I mean, it's an important job, but nothing is worth that amount "
"of stress, I think..."
msgstr "@ling_oh 。。。意𪜀、工役關重實、扔英擬空𣎏之當沛𢫮𣦎𦤾勢𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:106:text
msgid "@niko_speak What does he do?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 愥𪵯之丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:107:text
msgid ""
"@ling_hm2 Maintenance, I believe.\\>\\n\\@ling_hm Something to do with the "
"lights, but I don't know the details."
msgstr ""
"@ling_hm2 形如𪜀𪵯工作保持。\\>\\n\\@ling_hm 𣎏連關𦤾畑炶、扔英空𤑟枝節𡗋。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:108:text
msgid "@ling Maybe you can ask him later?"
msgstr "@ling 㛪𣎏体𠳨愥𢖖󠄁拱得？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:113:text
msgid ""
"@ling2 Oh! You're still here...\\>\\n\\@ling_smile Would you, um, like "
"anything?"
msgstr "@ling2 溩！㛪吻當低。。。\\>\\n\\@ling_smile 㛪、𫫡、𣎏㦖咹之空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:114:text
msgid "@ling I can cook something for you, if you want..."
msgstr "@ling 裊㛪𩟡、愥𣎏体𤍇之妬朱㛪。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:115:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's alright, thank you!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 空哰兜吖、感恩英𡗉吖！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/cafe counter:1:119:text
msgid ""
"@ling_smile Well, don't be afraid to ask if you do get hungry!\\>\\nI'll be "
"happy to make something for you!"
msgstr "@ling_smile 時、揨垠礙裊㛪𩟡唲！\\>\\n英𠱊窒𠻿𢚸𤍇之妬朱㛪！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Cafe/Cafe inside/tin:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's an empty coffee tin."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠錀咖啡筩。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/sleepville/Map events:1:2:text
msgid "@niko I can't sleep now, \\p."
msgstr "@niko 𣊾𣇞𨉟空𥄬得兜\\p。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/sleepville/Map events:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak I gotta take this guy to the elevators!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟沛迻英尼𦤾簜𣛠！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:8:text
msgid "@niko_speak Wow...."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫽿。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:10:text
msgid "@niko I've...actually never been to a big city before!"
msgstr "@niko 寔𫥨。。。𨉟𣗓𦤾𠬠城庯𡘯包𣇞！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:11:text
msgid "@niko All these lights... all these people..."
msgstr "@niko 仍暎畑尼。。。仍𡥵𠊛尼。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:12:text
msgid "@niko I guess most of this world's population lives here..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔份𡘯民数世界尼𤯩於低。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:19:text
msgid "@niko It's very different from my village."
msgstr "@niko 窒恪𬧺喟廊𧵑𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:20:text
msgid "@niko_speak The village is very small, and surrounded by huge fields!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 廊窒𡮈、吧衝𨒺𪜀𬏇垌包羅！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:21:text
msgid "@niko You saw a bit of that in one of my dreams from a while ago..."
msgstr "@niko 舅拱𧡊伮𠬠𠃣欺𨉟𢠩𠓀妬妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:22:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak The tallest buildings in our village are only two stories tall!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𡾵茹高一廊𨉟只𣎏𦤾𠄩層催！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:34:text
msgid "@niko_speak What about you, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 哙舅時哰、\\p？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:35:text
msgid "@niko Where do you live?"
msgstr "@niko 舅𤯩於兜丕？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:36:choice:0
msgid "A city"
msgstr "城庯"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:36:choice:1
msgid "A village"
msgstr "廊"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:36:choice:2
msgid "Someplace else"
msgstr "𠬠坭恪"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:39:text
msgid "@niko_speak A city? Like this?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠬠城庯？如尼哰？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:40:text
msgid "@niko Wow...."
msgstr "@niko 𫽿。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:41:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I can't imagine living in a city..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空体想像浽𤯩𥪝城庯𠱊𫥨哰。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:42:text
msgid "@niko_speak Must be exciting!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𪳨𪜀𠾽喋𡗋！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:43:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...And... kinda scary..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。吧。。。唏當𢜝𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:44:text
msgid "@niko The view is nice, though!"
msgstr "@niko 扔景觀惵㗶！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:47:text
msgid "@niko A village?"
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𡾵廊哰？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:48:text
msgid "@niko_speak Just like me!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 依如𨉟！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:49:text
msgid "@niko Can you imagine living in a city like this?"
msgstr "@niko 舅𣎏体想像浽𤯩𥪝城庯𠱊𫥨哰空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:50:text Events:1:60:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I can't..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟空。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:51:text Events:1:61:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...It's... kinda scary...."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。伮。。。當𢜝實。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:52:text Events:1:62:text
msgid "@niko_speak But also really cool!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 扔拱窒湡𡛤！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:55:text
msgid "@niko_speak Something that isn't a city or village?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠬠坭空沛廊拱拯沛城庯哰？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:57:text
msgid "@niko_speak Like a ship?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 矯𠬠𡥵船𧘇嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:58:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...Well, maybe not a ship..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。時、𣎏体空沛𪜀船。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:59:text
msgid "@niko Can you imagine living in a city like this, though?"
msgstr "@niko 舅𣎏体想像浽𤯩𥪝城庯𠱊𫥨哰空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/fish house/npc_fishbowl:1:2:text
msgid "Nope... not looking forward to that water shortage."
msgstr "空。。。實事空懞待澾割渃𢯛𬧐兜。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/fish house/npc_fishbowl:1:5:text
msgid "Oh, hey there."
msgstr "嗚、吀嘲。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/fish house/npc_fishbowl:1:6:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes You have a lot of fish!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 英𣎏𡗉𩵜㗶！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/fish house/npc_fishbowl:1:7:text
msgid "Yeah... I'm worried about them."
msgstr "唹。。。英可𢥈𧗱衆。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/fish house/npc_fishbowl:1:9:text
msgid ""
"I heard something about how the square particle stuff just took out a major "
"pipeline."
msgstr "英𣃣𦖑風聲務𠇍塊𣃱𣃣破閧𠬠塘䈵𡘯。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/fish house/npc_fishbowl:1:10:text
msgid ""
"I guess I should take advantage of the running water while I still can..."
msgstr "英擬𪜀英𢧚盡用源渃哙徠欺哙𣎏体。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:41:text
msgid "@rue_oh !!!"
msgstr "@rue_oh ！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:42:text
msgid "@rue_oh You guys are... \\.\\.okay?"
msgstr "@rue_oh 𤗆𠊛。。。\\.\\.穩渚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:43:text
msgid "@cedric_sigh Yup!"
msgstr "@cedric_sigh 𫫡！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:44:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_sigh2 When the factory started collapsing, I really thought we "
"didn't have a chance..."
msgstr "@cedric_sigh2 欺茹𣛠𨀎𢭰、英㐌實事擬𨉟㐌歇機會。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:45:text
msgid ""
"@cedric3 ...Fortunately, the robot assembly rooms were built pretty tough."
msgstr "@cedric3 。。。𢆪𪜀、各房擸撘𠊛𣛠可凭侢。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:46:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_hmm And... it actually did not take me long to bring Proto back."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 吧。。。寔𫥨英空損過𡗉時間抵迻一號𠭤徠。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:47:text
msgid "@cedric_smile ...all thanks to father's book!"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 。。。悉𪥘󠄁𠾒冊𧵑仛！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:49:text
msgid ""
"@proto1c [He had made my design documents to be compatible with the assembly "
"machines there.]"
msgstr "@proto1c 【翁㐌𢪏材料設計𧵑英哰朱衆相適喟各𣛠擸撘在妬。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:50:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_smile All I had to do was scan in the blueprints and reconfigure "
"some machine settings!"
msgstr "@cedric_smile 英只懃迻各版𦘧𠓨𢭯吧𢯢徠𠬠𠄧掑撻！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:51:text
msgid "@proto1b [...Father really does think of everything.]"
msgstr "@proto1b 【。。。仛實事㐌併歇𤗆條。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:52:text
msgid "@rue_smile That he does!"
msgstr "@rue_smile 果丕！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:53:text
msgid "@rue_sigh I'm... just glad everyone is ok."
msgstr "@rue_sigh 姉。。。𢜏𪜀𤗆𠊛吻全命。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/stairwell/map events:3:55:text
msgid "@rue_smile We're ready to go now, Niko."
msgstr "@rue_smile 衆些𠻿𠳹出發耒、尼孤。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/EV005:1:2:text
msgid "A quick death promises the least pain, don't you agree?"
msgstr "𠬠丐𣩂𨘱厲時𠱊𠃣𤴬疸一、伴𣎏擬勢空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/EV005:1:8:text
msgid "To be honest, I'd rather the former."
msgstr "抵𦓡吶、𪝬適丐𠓀欣。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/EV007:1:2:text
msgid "[THE LIBRARY IS UP AHEAD.]"
msgstr "【書院於𠌨𠓀。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/EV007:1:3:text
#: sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:28:text
msgid "@niko_speak Thanks!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 感恩唲！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/pancake hint:2:6:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko Hey, \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 尼\\p？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/pancake hint:2:7:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko_speak Do you remember where the cafe is?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 舅𣎏𢖵館咖啡於兜空？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/pancake hint:2:13:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko Oh, good!"
msgstr "@niko 溩、卒耒！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/pancake hint:2:18:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Wait! I think I remember!\\>\\n\\@niko It's up the elevator, and "
"then we take a right and go down some stairs!"
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 寬！形如𨉟𢖵𫥨耒！\\>\\n\\@niko 𨉟𠫾簜𣛠𬨠、𢖖󠄁妬𥘶沛耒𬺗橋簜！"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/pancake hint:2:21:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko I'm asking because...well..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟𠳨。。。爲。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/pancake hint:2:23:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I'm... a little hungry...."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟。。。唏𩟡。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/pancake hint:2:24:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Actually I'm REALLY hungry!\\>\\n\\@niko I haven't eaten "
"anything since I got here..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 寔𫥨𨉟窒𩟡！\\>\\n\\@niko 自欺𦤾低𨉟𣗓𣎏之𠬃𠰘𪥘󠄁。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/pancake hint:2:25:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko So...is it ok if we go get some food before we enter the Tower?"
msgstr "@niko 𢧚𪜀。。。𨉟𣎏体咹之妬𠓀欺𠓨座塔得渚？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 1/Library entrance/pancake hint:2:26:text
#: Maps/POSTGAME RED GROUND/ground
msgid "@niko_pancakes I hope they have pancakes..."
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 懞𣱆𣎏餅喼。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak Time to put the seed in the planter."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𦤾𣅶撻籺𥞖𠓨𡊱耒。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:1:7:text gate/Garden/EV001:2:20:text
msgid ""
"@niko ...\\>\\nThere's no dirt in this pot.\\>\\nWill the seed really grow "
"like this?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。\\>\\n𥪝𡊱空𣎏𡐙。\\>\\n勢尼時籺𥞖𣎏䄧𦹰得空丕？"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:1:13:text
msgid "@niko \\p, I need to put in the seed first before I put in the dirt."
msgstr "@niko \\p、𨉟沛撻籺𥞖𠓀欺𢭰𡐙𠓨。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:1:16:text
msgid ""
"@niko This is where I'm supposed to put the seed... \\>\\nBut there's no "
"dirt in this pot."
msgstr "@niko 低𪜀𡊲𨉟沛撻籺偅。。。\\>\\n扔𥪝𡊱空𣎏𡐙。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:2:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak I hope this helps you grow, little seed."
msgstr "@niko_speak 希望伴𣎏体𡘯劸、籺𥞖。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:2:7:text gate/Garden/EV001:3:28:text
msgid "@niko The seed's in the soil, but it looks a bit dry."
msgstr "@niko 籺𥞖㐌於𥪝𡐙、扔𣎏𨤔伮唏枯。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:2:13:text gate/Garden/EV001:2:17:text
msgid ""
"@niko I can't just pour the water on the seed.\\>\\nIt needs dirt before we "
"can water it."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟空𢭰𣦎渃𬨠籺𥞖得。\\>\\n沛𣎏𡐙時𨉟㵋洒得。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:3:2:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Good thinking, \\p!\\>\\n\\@niko Water should help this seed "
"grow."
msgstr "@niko_speak 合理妬\\p！\\>\\n\\@niko 𣎏渃時𠱊𢴇籺𥞖䄧𦹰。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:3:7:text
msgid "@niko Hmm... the dirt's nice and moist now, but..."
msgstr "@niko 嘘。。。𡐙㐌𤀔卒耒、扔。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:3:8:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak What if it dries out? \\.\\. \\@niko_eyeclosed There's only so "
"much water from this little tube..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 𢙲伮𠎩唏歇時哰？\\.\\. \\@niko_eyeclosed 𥪝䈵尼只𣎏澄妬渃催"
"啊。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:3:9:text
msgid "@niko ...I'll hold on to the tube for now, just in case..."
msgstr "@niko 。。。暫時𨉟𠱊𡨺徠丐䈵、抵提防。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:3:16:text gate/Garden/EV001:4:2:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Good thinking, \\p!\\>\\n\\@niko This water should really help "
"this seed grow."
msgstr "@niko_speak 合理妬\\p！\\>\\n\\@niko 渃尼𠱊寔事𢴇籺𥞖䄧𦹰。"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:3:23:text gate/Garden/EV001:4:9:text
msgid "@niko_speak It sprouted a tiny leaf!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏𠬠丐蘿子絲攂𬨠耒尼！"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:4:14:text
msgid "@niko We've given it dirt and water.\\>\\nBut will that be enough?"
msgstr "@niko 𨉟㐌朱伮𡐙吧渃耒。\\>\\n扔料澄妬𣎏覩空？"

#: Maps/Red sky/City gate/Garden/EV001:5:1:text
msgid "@niko_speak Good luck, little plant!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 祝𢆪慜唲、䒹𣘃𡮈！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:58:text
msgid "@niko6 This is the room I first woke up in..."
msgstr "@niko6 低𪜀間房𣅶頭𨉟醒𧻭尼。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:60:text
msgid "@niko_speak \\p? Are you still here?"
msgstr "@niko_speak \\p？舅吻於低渚？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:62:text
msgid "@niko2 ...\\p?"
msgstr "@niko2 。。。\\p？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:64:choice:0
#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:16:choice:0
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr "𣎏？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:70:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes \\p!!!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes \\p！！！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:71:text
msgid "@niko_speak I... I think..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟。。。𨉟擬。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:72:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes I think it worked!!!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 𨉟擬伮活動耒！！！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:73:choice:0
msgid "It did!"
msgstr "董丕！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:79:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak The sun is back!\\>\\nAnd I actually got to see it this time!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𩈘𡗶㐌𠭤徠！\\>\\n吧吝尼𨉟㐌寔事得𧡊伮呢！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:80:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes We... actually did it...!"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 衆些。。。㐌成功耒。。。！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:81:text
msgid "@niko5 So... \\>\\@niko6 what do we do now?"
msgstr "@niko5 丕時。。。\\>\\@niko6 𨉟𪵯之𣇞？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:82:text
msgid "@niko I guess I should figure out how to get home from here..."
msgstr "@niko 昃𪜀𨉟𢧚尋格𧗱茹自低。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:92:text
msgid "@niko2 This... \\.\\.isn't a door, is it?"
msgstr "@niko2 低。。。\\.\\.空沛𫔤、沛空𠰚？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:94:text
msgid ""
"@niko This looks like one of those portals we saw all the way back in the "
"city."
msgstr "@niko 矓偅仍丐𨶛𨉟𧡊自𥪝城庯。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:95:text
msgid "@niko6 In the room behind the big clock."
msgstr "@niko6 𥪝間房𢖖󠄁銅壺𡘯。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:96:text
msgid "@niko And... and..."
msgstr "@niko 吧。。。吧。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:97:text
msgid "@niko_speak I see a wheat field on the other side!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟𧡊𠬠𦑃垌穭於邊其！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:98:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes ...I see my village..."
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 。。。𨉟𧡊廊𧵑𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:99:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes I hear...\\.\\. my mama...."
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 𨉟𦖑𧡊。。。\\.\\.媄。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:100:text
msgid "@niko2 She's looking for me..."
msgstr "@niko2 媄當尋𨉟。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:101:text
msgid "@niko3 ...."
msgstr "@niko3 。。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:102:text
msgid "@niko3 Ah, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko3 啊、\\p。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:103:text
msgid "@niko5 This...\\.\\. isnt the first time we've said goodbye, is it?"
msgstr "@niko5 低。。。\\.\\.空沛吝頭先𨉟𢺹𢬣、沛空𠰚？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:105:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 But... this'll be the last time, won't it?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 扔。。。低𠱊𪜀吝𡳳共、𠰚？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:106:text
msgid ""
"@niko_distressed I don't think we'll ever see each other again after this..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed 𨉟空擬衆些𠱊包𣇞﨤徠僥吝𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:108:text
msgid "@niko_distressed ...and... what will become of the world?"
msgstr "@niko_distressed 。。。吧。。。世界尼𠱊𠫾兜𧗱兜？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:109:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed2 ...after all we've been through."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed2 。。。𢖖󠄁悉𪥘󠄁仍之衆些㐌𣥱過。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:110:text
msgid "@niko3 After everything we've done..."
msgstr "@niko3 𢖖󠄁悉𪥘󠄁仍之衆些㐌𪵯。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:111:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 I still... \\>\\@niko_distressed don't know..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 𨉟吻。。。\\>\\@niko_distressed 空別。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:112:choice:0
msgid "This place..."
msgstr "坭尼。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:116:choice:0
msgid "These people..."
msgstr "仍𡥵𠊛尼。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:120:choice:0
msgid "Won't stop existing."
msgstr "𠱊空變𠅒。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:127:choice:0
msgid "They'll be in your memory."
msgstr "𣱆𠱊於𥪝記憶𧵑舅。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:131:choice:0
msgid "They'll be in my memory, too"
msgstr "𣱆拱𠱊於𥪝記憶𧵑𨉟𡛤。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:137:text
msgid "@niko2 ...."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:139:text
msgid "@niko2 I... \\>\\@niko_speak promise I'll never forget this world!"
msgstr "@niko2 𨉟。。。\\>\\@niko_speak 許𠱊空包𣇞悁世界尼！"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:140:text
msgid "@niko3 I promise... \\@niko I'll never forget you, \\p."
msgstr "@niko3 𨉟許。。。\\@niko 𨉟𠱊空包𣇞悁舅兜、\\p。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:141:text
msgid "@niko2 So... take care of yourself, okay?"
msgstr "@niko2 𢧚𪜀。。。唉保重、唲？"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:142:choice:0
msgid "You too."
msgstr "舅拱丕唲。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:148:text
msgid "@niko Mhm...."
msgstr "@niko 𫫡。。。。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:154:choice:0
msgid "Goodbye, Niko."
msgstr "嘲暫別、尼孤。"

#: Maps/FINALE/Last room/EV003:1:161:text
msgid "@niko2 Goodbye, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko2 嘲暫別、\\p。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV002:1:1:text area/EV003:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Just a trash can..."
msgstr "@niko 只𪜀𠬠桶𧅫。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV004:1:1:text area/EV026:1:1:text
#: area/EV027:1:1:text sky/Apartments/Hall1/Room3 - bot friend/EV005:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A pile of large books."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𥔧冊𡘯。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV004:1:2:text
msgid "@niko They look like phonebooks."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𪜀名簿。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/north exit:1:7:text
msgid "@niko It looks like I can unlatch this door..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟𣎏体𢲫銙𫔤尼。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV009:1:1:text
msgid "Hey there."
msgstr "盧。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV009:1:2:text
#: Maps/Green/Village/shephard:1:24:text Maps/Green/Research Station/water
#: room/robot standing:1:6:text
msgid "@niko Hello."
msgstr "@niko 吀嘲。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV009:1:3:text
msgid "You the messiah?"
msgstr "𠎬救世妬嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV009:1:5:text
msgid "......"
msgstr "。。。。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV009:1:6:text
msgid "I like your scarf."
msgstr "巾𫏈惵妬。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV009:1:8:text
msgid "@niko Mama made it for me!"
msgstr "@niko 媄撣朱𨉟妬！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV009:1:9:text
msgid "Tell her I like her needlework."
msgstr "𠸒婆𧘇哴𪝬窒技術𥿤𧵑婆窒卒。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV009:1:11:text
msgid "@niko ...when I see her again!"
msgstr "@niko 。。。欺𨉟﨤徠媄！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/Map Events:1:1:text
msgid "@niko This fridge has magnets on it!"
msgstr "@niko 𣗿冷尼𣎏南針！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/Map Events:1:2:text
msgid "@niko Maybe they'll come handy?"
msgstr "@niko 𣎏体衆𠱊𢴇益？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/Map Events:1:3:text
msgid "@niko I hope nobody will mind us taking them..."
msgstr "@niko 希望空埃抵心役𨉟𥙩衆𠫾。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV012:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's very warm!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 窒𤋾！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV013:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak I'm too young to drink coffee!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟𣗓覩歲㕵咖啡！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV022:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A photograph of the city skyline."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅影塘蹎𡗶城庯。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV023:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A photograph of some buildings."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅影𨄴𠄧座茹。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV024:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A photograph of a factory."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅影𨄴茹𣛠。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV025:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A photograph of some railings."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅影𨄴欄杆。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV026:1:2:text
msgid "@niko Some of the pages are dog-eared."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𠄧張被岋打𨁪。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV028:1:1:text
msgid ""
"@niko It's a photograph of the cafe.\\>\\nLooks like it was a busy day..."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅影𨄴館咖啡。\\>\\n𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠𣈜𠾽喋。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV029:1:1:text
msgid ""
"@niko A photograph of the mines.\\>\\nThere are many robots at work in the "
"photo, extracting large deposits of ore."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅影𨄴𡌢𡎡。\\>\\n𣎏𡗉𠊛𣛠當𪵯役、掏仍𡎡礦𡘯。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV030:1:1:text
msgid ""
"@niko A photograph of the Tower.\\>\\nThe sunlight makes it hard to make out "
"much in this photo."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅影𨄴座塔。\\>\\n空𧡊得之𡗉由暎𩈘𡗶過𤆷。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Communal area/EV031:1:1:text
msgid ""
"@niko A photograph of a house in the Glen.\\>\\nLooks like it was taken when "
"people were still living in the ruins..."
msgstr ""
"@niko 𠬠幅影𨄴𠬠間茹𥪝塳潭浰。\\>\\n𣎏𨤔伮得𨄴欺𤗆𠊛吻哙𤯩矓區殘跡。。。"

#: Maps/Unused/IGNORE ToLibrary/IGNORE ToFactory/EV002:1:1:text
msgid "FACTORY"
msgstr "茹𣛠"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/pipe :bottom:1:2:text
msgid "@niko It's a metal pipe."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠䈵金類。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/pipe :bottom:1:3:text
msgid "@niko Must've broken off from one of these terminals..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔𪜀被𢭮𫥨自𠬠𣛠入令。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/pipe :bottom:1:8:text
msgid "@ed It's a broken-off section of railing."
msgstr "@ed 𠬠份欄杆被𢭮。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/pipe :bottom:1:11:text
msgid "@ed Niko takes it."
msgstr "@ed 尼孤𥙩伮。"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/map event:1:8:text
msgid "@ed [This bed probably looks familiar to you, \\p]"
msgstr "@ed 【隻床尼𣎏𨤔親屬喟伴、\\p】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/map event:1:9:text
msgid "@ed [Niko first woke up in this world here.]"
msgstr "@ed 【尼孤𥅞𧻭吝頭於低。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/map event:1:10:text
msgid "@ed [It's important that you allow Niko to sleep once in a while.]"
msgstr "@ed 【抵尼孤𥄬常川𪜀窒關重。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/map event:1:11:text
msgid ""
"@ed [The game will exit automatically and can be continued later. Don't be "
"alarmed.]"
msgstr "@ed 【𠻀𨔈𠱊自動脫吧𣎏体接續𢖖󠄁。吀揨𤮗𢠯。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Docks/Bed room/map event:1:12:text
msgid "@ed [But now is no time for rest.]"
msgstr "@ed 【雖然𣊾𣇞空沛𣅶𥄬。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV001:1:1:text
#: room/EV001:3:1:text
msgid "@niko This one is blue."
msgstr "@niko 丐尼𦭷青洋。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV001:1:3:text
msgid "@proto2 [That's mine, then.]"
msgstr "@proto2 【丕𪜀𧵑英。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV001:4:1:text
msgid "@niko A portal glowing blue."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𦑃𨶛𤏬𦭷青洋。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV002:1:1:text
#: room/EV002:3:1:text
msgid "@niko This one is green."
msgstr "@niko 𨶛尼𦭷青蘿。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV002:1:3:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm This one is configured to my code, I think."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 𣎏𨤔𨶛尼𨨤喟碼𧵑英。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV002:2:1:text
msgid "@cedric Salutations!"
msgstr "@cedric 吀敬嘲！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV002:4:1:text
msgid "@niko A portal glowing green."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𦑃𨶛𤏬𦭷青蘿。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV003:1:1:text
#: room/EV003:3:1:text
msgid "@niko This one is red."
msgstr "@niko 𨶛尼𦭷𧹻。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV003:1:4:text
msgid "@rue_talk This one would be meant for me, then."
msgstr "@rue_talk 𣎏𨤔𨶛尼𧶄朱姉。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV003:2:1:text
msgid "@rue Hello."
msgstr "@rue 吀嘲。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV003:4:1:text
msgid "@niko A portal with a red glow."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𦑃𨶛𪹟𤏬𦭷𧹻。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed The squares are here too now..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 各塊𣃱拱㐌𦤾盡低耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:1:54:text
#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/locked events:1:1:text events:2:1:text
msgid "@niko This elevator won't open."
msgstr "@niko 簜𣛠尼空𢲫𫔤。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:1:55:text
#: Maps/Red sky/Office/stairwell/locked events:1:2:text events:2:2:text
msgid "@niko Looks like it's stuck on another floor?"
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𨤔伮被𠹳於𠬠層恪？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:2:2:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed There's squares here too, now..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 於低拱𣎏塊𣃱耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:2:30:text
msgid "@niko We need to find a way to reach that lever up there."
msgstr "@niko 衆𨉟懃尋格𢭲𬧐丐芹拔𨑗其。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:2:31:text
msgid "@niko6 We might need a grownup for this..."
msgstr "@niko6 𣎏𨤔𨉟𠱊懃𠬠𠊛𡘯妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:2:34:text
msgid "@niko This elevator has no button panel."
msgstr "@niko 簜𣛠尼空𣎏榜鈕。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:2:35:text
msgid "@niko Tapping the door doesn't open it either, hmm..."
msgstr "@niko 𢫈𠓨𫔤拱空𧡊伮𢲫𫥨、嘘。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:2:36:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed That usually works..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 平常𨉟𪵯勢𪜀得𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:2:40:text
msgid "@niko6 Wait..."
msgstr "@niko6 寬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:2:41:text
msgid "@niko_speak There's a lever hanging from the ceiling!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨑗塵茹𣎏𠬠丐芹拔撩竉㖫尼！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:2:61:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...can't reach it."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。空𢭲得。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:4:text
msgid "@rue Where...\\.\\. are the other two?"
msgstr "@rue 𠄩。。。\\.\\.𠊛哙徠兜耒？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:5:text
msgid "@rue Prototype? Cedric?"
msgstr "@rue 一號？察嚦？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:6:text
msgid "@rue_sad They're supposed to be here already..."
msgstr "@rue_sad 當𫥨𣱆沛於低自𠓀耒渚。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:10:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 They..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 𣱆。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:12:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Prototype's body was destroyed back in the Barrens."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 機体𧵑一號被破毀外塳邊疆。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:13:text
msgid "@rue_oh ..."
msgstr "@rue_oh 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:14:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Cedric was going to bring him back with the memory disk, "
"but..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 察嚦定迻英𧘇𠭤徠憑𥐨𢖵、扔。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:15:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 He was in the lab complex when it collapsed..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 愥被縸𠹳𥪝座茹研究欺伮𨀎𢭰。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:16:text
msgid "@niko_distressed I... \\.\\.don't think he made it..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed 㛪。。。\\.\\.空擬英𧘇哙全命吖。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:17:text
msgid "@rue_oh Oh.."
msgstr "@rue_oh 喂。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:18:text
msgid "@rue_sad No..."
msgstr "@rue_sad 空。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:21:text
msgid "@rue_sad There goes our only chance..."
msgstr "@rue_sad 丕𪜀機會𧵑衆些𠫾淙耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:23:text
msgid "@niko_upset2 I... \\.\\.I'm sorry..."
msgstr "@niko_upset2 㛪。。。\\.\\.㛪吀纇。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:24:text
msgid "@rue_sigh It's not your fault, Niko..."
msgstr "@rue_sigh 空沛纇㛪兜、尼孤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:25:text
msgid "@rue_sad If anything... \\.\\.I should be apologizing to you."
msgstr "@rue_sad 寔𫥨。。。\\.\\.姉沛吀纇㛪㵋董。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:27:text
#: deck/Office/observation deck/Map Events:1:63:text Events:1:178:text
msgid "@rue_sad ..."
msgstr "@rue_sad 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:28:text
msgid "@rue ...There's..."
msgstr "@rue 。。。哙。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:29:text
msgid "@rue One last thing I want to do."
msgstr "@rue 𠬠役𡳃窮姉㦖𪵯。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:4:30:text
msgid "@rue_talk Come on, let's go upstairs."
msgstr "@rue_talk 鬧、𬨠層喟姉。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:3:text
msgid "@cedric_talk Oh...\\.\\. this is..."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 溩。。。\\.\\.低𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:5:text
msgid "@proto1 [...no wonder he wanted us to all be here for this.]"
msgstr "@proto1 【。。。𠸒哰仛㦖衆些聚於低。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:10:text
msgid "@niko2 Um... what are these things, anyway?"
msgstr "@niko2 𫫡。。。低𪜀之丕吖？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:11:text
msgid "@proto2 [Code portals.]"
msgstr "@proto2 【𨶛碼。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:12:text
msgid "@proto1c [They... \\.\\.temporarily remove us from the world.]"
msgstr "@proto1c 【衆。。。\\.\\.𠱊暫時迻𪨠英𨖨𠺌世界尼。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:13:text
msgid "@niko2 ....what?"
msgstr "@niko2 。。。。嘑？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:14:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm It's... a bit hard to explain..."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 唏。。。𠸋解釋。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:15:text
msgid ""
"@cedric2 But... basically, my father has hidden a decryption key in our "
"code, with a .txt file as its shell..."
msgstr ""
"@cedric2 扔。。。大概𪜀、仛㐌𢭳𠬠匙解碼𥪝碼𧵑𪨠英、喟𤿭外𪜀𠬠𣜿.txt。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:16:text
msgid ""
"@proto2 [...But to get to them, we have to be removed from the world and "
"decompiled.]"
msgstr "@proto2 【。。。扔抵𬧐得衆、沛迻𪨠英𨖨世界尼吧譯逆碼。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:17:text
msgid ""
"@proto2b [...When our keys are combined into a central location, it will "
"activate an encrypted part of this world, which will...]"
msgstr ""
"@proto2b 【。。。欺各匙銙𧵑𪨠英聚徠在𠬠地点、伮𠱊激活𠬠份被碼𧵑世界尼、吧"
"耒。。。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:18:text
msgid "@niko_what *confused cat noises*"
msgstr "@niko_what ＊㗂貓𠸋曉＊"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:19:text
msgid "@proto_eyeclosed [...]"
msgstr "@proto_eyeclosed 【。。。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:20:text
msgid "@proto2b [...Rue, maybe it's better if you explain.]"
msgstr "@proto2b 【。。。𠱋、𣎏𨤰姉解釋𠱊易曉欣。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:21:text
msgid "@rue_sigh I'll attempt."
msgstr "@rue_sigh 姉𠱊試。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:22:text
msgid ""
"@rue Basically... these portals all represent a physical location on \\p's "
"machine."
msgstr "@rue 單簡𪜀。。。仍𦑃𨶛尼調代面朱𠬠地点物理𨑗𣛠𧵑\\p。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:23:text
msgid "@niko2 ...oooh."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。溩溩溩。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:24:text
msgid ""
"@rue_talk And... when we enter these portals, we will be sent to that "
"location..."
msgstr "@rue_talk 吧。。。欺𪨠姉𠓨𨶛、𪨠姉𠱊得迻𦤾地点妬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:25:text
msgid "@proto2 [...Wherever that is.]"
msgstr "@proto2 【。。。空別𪜀處鬧𡛤。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:26:text
msgid ""
"@rue I'm... sure \\p is already pretty familiar with retrieving puzzle "
"pieces from this world on their computer."
msgstr "@rue 姉。。。信\\p㐌慣喟役尋各𤗖句賭自世界尼𨑗𣛠併𧵑𨉟。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:27:text
msgid ""
"@rue_talk ...But this time, \\p would need to move around some things, as "
"well."
msgstr "@rue_talk 。。。扔吝尼、\\p拱𠱊沛移轉𠬠𠄧次。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:28:text
msgid ""
"@cedric_talk ...specifically, by moving the keys from the small portal to "
"the big one."
msgstr "@cedric_talk 。。。具体𪜀、迻匙銙自各𨶛𡮈𠓨𨶛𡘯。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:29:text
msgid "@cedric_hmm I... don't know what happens next, though."
msgstr "@cedric_hmm 扔英。。。空別𢖖󠄁妬𠱊𪜀之。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:31:text
msgid "@niko_speak Does \\p know where these portals lead, at least?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。𠃣一時、\\p𣎏別𨶛引𦤾兜空吖？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:32:text
msgid "@rue You should probably ask \\p on this..."
msgstr "@rue 姉擬㛪沛自𠳨\\p妬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:36:text
msgid "@niko2 ...Hold on."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。徐㐌。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/map events:5:50:text
msgid "@niko6 The journal is glowing again, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko6 卷日記徠發𤏬耒\\p。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:2:text
msgid "@plight_worry ...This room gives me the creeps, man..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 。。。房尼𪵯英囒𩯀𬛑過𠋥。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh, same!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩、㛪拱勢！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:4:text
msgid "@plight_worry ....yup."
msgstr "@plight_worry 。。。。𫫡。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:5:text
msgid "@plight3 So um... \\>\\@plight_2b what did you need help with again?"
msgstr "@plight3 勢唹。。。\\>\\@plight_2b 㛪懃英𢴇之𧘇𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:12:text
msgid "@niko Can you reach the lever up there?"
msgstr "@niko 英𢭲𬧐丐芹妬得空吖？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:13:text
msgid "@plight_worry Oh, right..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 啊、唹。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:14:text
msgid "@plight_worry2 Wait..."
msgstr "@plight_worry2 寬。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:15:text
msgid "@plight_why ...I'm not THAT tall!"
msgstr "@plight_why 。。。英空高𦤾勢！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:16:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed (Well it was worth a shot.)"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed （催時拱當試𠬠吝。）"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:17:text
msgid "@plight_worry2 ..."
msgstr "@plight_worry2 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:18:text
msgid "@plight_2b ...wait, I got this."
msgstr "@plight_2b 。。。寬、抵英。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:53:text
msgid "@niko_speak Nice!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 唁！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:54:text
msgid "@niko Thank you, mister!"
msgstr "@niko 感恩英吖！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:55:text
msgid "@plight No prob, kid."
msgstr "@plight 空𣎏之兜傉。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/plight:1:57:text
msgid "@plight3 So... you coming?"
msgstr "@plight3 勢。。。㛪𣎏𠫾空？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV031:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed The lever won't do much for us now, \\p..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣊾𣇞丐芹𠱊空𢴇之𨉟兜\\p。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV031:1:6:text
msgid "@niko There's a lever hanging from the ceiling..."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠬠丐芹拔撩竉㖫𨑗塵。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME RED SKY/Elevator deck/Office/locked room/EV031:1:7:text
msgid "@niko_speak We should find someone tall to reach it for us, \\p!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟𢧚尋埃妬高高抵𢭲護𨉟𠫾、\\p！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall1/bathroom/scissors:1:1:text
msgid "@niko There's a pair of scissors on the ground...."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠬠𣘃𨦀𨑗孱。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall1/bathroom/scissors:1:2:text
msgid "@niko ...on....a pile of hair?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。𨑗。。。𠬠埬𩯀？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall1/bathroom/scissors:1:3:text
msgid "@niko I don't think anyone's using it anymore, so..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟擬𪜀空埃用伮𡛤兜、𢧚𪜀。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall1/bathroom/soap:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Soap dispenser."
msgstr "@niko 𣛠捨硨肪。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall1/bathroom/EV005:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A small potted plant."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𡊱𣘃𡮈。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:1:text
msgid ""
"@niko It's the lightbulb.\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed2 Thank goodness it's safe..."
msgstr "@niko 琫畑\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed2 𢆪𪜀伮吻全捖。。。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 ...\\>\\n\\@niko_sad ..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_sad 。。。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:4:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 ...I guess \\p isn't coming back..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 昃𪜀\\p𠱊空𢮿徠𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:8:choice:0
msgid "Niko, I'm here."
msgstr "尼孤、𨉟低。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:14:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes ...\\p?"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 。。。\\p？"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:22:text
msgid "@niko_pancakes Is that... really you?"
msgstr "@niko_pancakes 𣎏實。。。𪜀舅空？"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:23:text
msgid "@niko_distressed2 I thought... you were gone..."
msgstr "@niko_distressed2 𨉟想。。。舅㐌𠫾𠅒耒。。。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:25:choice:0
msgid "I never left you."
msgstr "𨉟㫻於低𦓡。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:25:choice:1
msgid "I'm back now."
msgstr "𨉟㐌𠭤徠。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:29:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Oh! \\@niko_eyeclosed I was... feeling a bit scared back there..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！\\@niko_eyeclosed 𠓀妬。。。𨉟𣎏唏𢜝𠬠𡭧。。。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:30:text
msgid "@niko_speak I thought I was completely alone!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨉟想𨉟完全孤單幾！"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:31:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed But that was silly of me to assume, wasn't it?"
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 扔化𫥨𨉟㐌差、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:35:text
msgid "@niko_speak Where did you go?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 舅𠫾兜丕？"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:36:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I was so scared all by myself..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟㐌窒𢜝妬。。。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:37:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...but I guess... it's okay now."
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。扔昃𪜀。。。𤗆次穩耒。"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:41:text
msgid "@niko Ah, guess we need to figure out where to go now, and-"
msgstr "@niko 啊、衆𨉟𢧚尋䀡𢧚𠫾兜接蹺、吧－"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:1:69:text
msgid "@niko The sun!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak It lit up on its own!"
msgstr "@niko 𩈘𡗶！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 伮自𤏬𬨠耒尼！"

#: Maps/Tower/Sunroom/lightbulb:2:1:text
msgid "@niko Guess I should pick it up, right \\p?"
msgstr "@niko 丕𪜀𨉟𢧚擒伮𬨠、𠰚\\p？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:7:text
#: chat:1:78:text
msgid "@plight .\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\.."
msgstr "@plight 。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:8:text
#: chat:1:79:text chat:2:7:text chat:2:10:text
msgid "@niko  .\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\.."
msgstr "@niko  。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:9:text
msgid "@plight .\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\.."
msgstr "@plight 。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:10:text
#: chat:2:8:text
msgid "@niko  .\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\..\\.."
msgstr "@niko  。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。\\.。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:11:text
msgid "@plight Sure is taking a while..."
msgstr "@plight 嘍㗶𠰚。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:12:text
#: chat:2:9:text
msgid "@niko m-hm!"
msgstr "@niko 𫫡！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:13:text
msgid ""
"@plight_worry (oh goodness gracious I'm stuck in an elevator with the "
"messiah and also literally god themself this is awkward)"
msgstr "@plight_worry （梶𪥘󠄁籠𠋺被𠹳𥪝簜𣛠𢭲𠎬救世吧正𠎬全能喂𡗶㗒𨆃腍癲）"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:14:text
msgid "@niko Oh, maybe we can chat to pass the time, then?"
msgstr "@niko 溩、丕衆𨉟𣎏体讚㗕朱𪲽時間得𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:16:text
msgid "@plight_worry I mean, sure..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 𧘇𪜀、拱得催。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:29:text
msgid "@niko Alright, \\p, should I..."
msgstr "@niko 嗚雞、\\p、𨉟𢧚。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:29:choice:0
msgid "Ask about his job"
msgstr "𠳨愥𪵯藝之"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:29:choice:1
msgid "Ask about this city"
msgstr "𠳨𧗱城庯尼"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:29:choice:2
msgid "Ask about the library"
msgstr "𠳨𧗱書院"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:29:choice:3
msgid "Resume awkward silence"
msgstr "接續唵𣼽𨆃腍"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:32:text
msgid "@niko So...what do you do at your job?"
msgstr "@niko 勢。。。英𪵯藝之丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:33:text
msgid "@niko_speak You seem really busy!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 英𣎏𨤔絆褓㗶！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:34:text
msgid "@plight_2 I...uh...."
msgstr "@plight_2 英。。。唹。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:35:text
msgid "@plight I fix lights, mostly."
msgstr "@plight 英主要𢯢畑炶。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:36:text
msgid ""
"@plight_2b But now I also deliver and refill high-energy phosphor to "
"structures that need them."
msgstr "@plight_2b 扔𣇞英拱運轉吧納光素高能朱各下層懃衆。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:37:text
msgid "@niko High energy?"
msgstr "@niko 高能？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:38:text
msgid ""
"@plight Y'know, the super concentrated glowy stuff they had to process in "
"factories, it's what powers most of this city's stuff."
msgstr "@plight 時蒂、次質發𤏬超湛特𣱆沛初製𥪝茹𣛠妬、伮𪜀源能量正朱城庯尼。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:39:text
#: ground/backalley/EV007:1:29:text
msgid "@niko Oooh!"
msgstr "@niko 溩溩溩！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:40:text
msgid "@plight We used to have a small army of delivery robots doing that..."
msgstr "@plight 層𣎏𠬠隊軍𡮈仍𠊛𣛠運轉𪵯役妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:41:text
msgid "@plight_worry But lately a bunch of them have been breaking down?"
msgstr "@plight_worry 。。。扔澾近低份𡘯衆㐌被閧時沛？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:42:text
msgid "@plight_2 So until they fix them, I'll just have more work on my plate."
msgstr "@plight_2 𢧚𪜀朱𦤾欺𣱆𢯢衆、英徠沛揞添役。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:43:text
msgid "@plight_why I haven't slept in so long..."
msgstr "@plight_why 㐌嘍𡗋耒英空𥄬。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:44:text
msgid "@niko_speak When will the robots get fixed?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 包𣇞𠊛𣛠得𢯢丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:45:text
msgid ""
"@plight_2 I have no idea, it's all up to the scientists over at the labs."
msgstr "@plight_2 英𠹾、𢘾各茹科學𥪝房試驗𪥘󠄁妬。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:46:text
msgid ""
"@plight_worry But they seem REALLY concerned about something else lately..."
msgstr "@plight_worry 扔𨄹尼𣱆𣎏𨤔窒窒𢥈礙𧗱𠬠次之妬恪。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:48:text
msgid ""
"@plight_worry ...Never a good sign when even the smart folks are worried."
msgstr "@plight_worry 。。。仍佉聰明𢥈𢠯空𠸒𣇞𪜀䀨卒。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:52:text
msgid "@niko This city is very big!"
msgstr "@niko 城庯尼𤳱𠺳！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:53:text
msgid "@plight_2b It's smaller than it looks."
msgstr "@plight_2b 寔𫥨伮空𫰅𦤾勢。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:54:text
msgid "@plight_2 Getting pretty crowded too..."
msgstr "@plight_2 喟徠拱扒頭佟𠊛耒妬。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:55:text
msgid ""
"@plight_2 First there was the refugees from the Barrens, and now more Glen "
"folks are moving in too."
msgstr "@plight_2 班頭𪜀仍𠊛避難自塳邊疆、耒𣇞𣎏添𠄧佉自塳潭浰𡛤。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:57:text
msgid "@plight It's just safer here, y'know?"
msgstr "@plight 矯、於低安全欣意？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:58:text
msgid "@plight I mean, it's not a haven by any means."
msgstr "@plight 意𪜀、伮空沛𪜀天堂之兜。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:59:text
msgid "@plight_worry That square stuff that we just saw?"
msgstr "@plight_worry 埬塊𣃱些𣃣𧡊𧘇嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:60:text
msgid "@plight_worry We get more of that here than anywhere else, apparently."
msgstr "@plight_worry 於低衆出現𡗉欣悉𪥘󠄁仍𡊲哙徠。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:61:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I noticed..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 㛪𣎏抵意。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:62:text
msgid ""
"@plight_2 ...We're lucky it only seems to affect the city's infrastructure."
msgstr "@plight_2 。。。𢆪𪜀衆𣎏𨤔只作動𦤾下層城庯。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:63:text
msgid "@plight The landmass itself is still holding up."
msgstr "@plight 本身𩈘𡐙吻𠹾得。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:64:text
msgid ""
"@plight_2b Which is good, since there isn't much solid land here in the "
"first place."
msgstr "@plight_2b 𪜀𠬠條窒卒、爲自頭於低拱拯𣎏𠇍𡐙凭。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:68:text
msgid "@niko Can you tell me about the library?"
msgstr "@niko 英𣎏体朱㛪別𧗱書院得空吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:69:text
msgid "@niko_speak I'm supposed to go there!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 㛪沛𦤾妬吖！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:70:text
