#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:72:text
msgid ""
"@plight_worry But I always feel out of place surrounded by smart people!"
msgstr "@plight_worry 扔衝𨒺全𠊛聰明礙𡗋！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Elevator deck/Elevator inside/elevator chat:1:73:text
msgid ""
"@plight Well, I guess you're pretty smart yourself, so you'll fit in fine."
