#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:46:text
msgid "@en3 [\\p...\\> you're... back.]"
msgstr "@en3 【\\p。。。\\>伴。。。𥒥𠭤徠。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:47:text
msgid "@en_upset2 [I restored the world, I sent Niko home...]"
msgstr "@en_upset2 【𪝬㐌恢復世界、𪝬㐌迻尼孤𧗱茹。。。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:48:text
msgid "@en4 [Are you...\\.\\.\\@en3 not happy?]"
msgstr "@en4 【伴。。。\\.\\.\\@en3 𣗓滿願哰？】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:50:text
msgid "@en_upset2 [Even if you wanted to see Niko again...]"
msgstr "@en_upset2 【怞伴𣎏㦖﨤尼孤𠬠吝𡛤。。。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:51:text
msgid "@en_eyeclosed [You can't, \\p.\\>  Niko's gone.]"
msgstr "@en_eyeclosed 【空体得、\\p啊。\\>  尼孤空哙於低𡛤。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:52:text
msgid ""
"@en_eyeclosed2 [And without Niko, there is no story for me to tell, no "
"messiah to traverse across the land.]"
msgstr "@en_eyeclosed2 【空𣎏尼孤、空𣎏𡀯抵𠸥、空𣎏𠎬救世遊玩𨑗𡎝尼。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:53:text
msgid "@en_eyeclosed [...No way for you to connect with the world.]"
msgstr "@en_eyeclosed 【。。。空𣎏之抵伴結綏喟世界尼。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:55:text
msgid "@en2 [But...\\.\\.Niko still remembers this place.]"
msgstr "@en2 【扔。。。\\.\\.尼孤吻𢖵𧗱坭尼。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:57:text
msgid "@en3 [If you really want to see this world again, I could still...]"
msgstr "@en3 【裊伴寔事㦖𧡊世界尼𠬠吝𡛤、𪝬吻𣎏体。。。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:58:text
msgid "@en_distressed2 [Oh...\\.\\. but it won't be the same.]"
msgstr "@en_distressed2 【喂。。。\\.\\.扔伮𠱊空如𫇰。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:59:text
msgid ""
"@en_distressed2 [It'll just be a recording.\\>\\nIt'll just be me using "
"Niko's memories.]"
msgstr ""
"@en_distressed2 【𠱊只𪜀𠬠澾發徠催。\\>\\n𠱊只𪜀𪝬使用記憶𧵑尼孤𦓡催。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:60:text
msgid "@en_eyeclosed [...Just like how I'm using Niko's reflection now...]"
msgstr "@en_eyeclosed 【。。。如丐格𪝬當用形影𧵑尼孤𬆄𣊾𣇞丕。。。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:61:text
msgid "@en3 [Is that...\\.\\. what you want?]"
msgstr "@en3 【伴。。。\\.\\.㦖丕哰？】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:68:text
msgid "@en3 [I will go rewind the story.]"
msgstr "@en3 【𪝬𠱊鬚徠句𡀯。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:69:text
msgid "@en4 [...so that you can relive it from the beginning.]"
msgstr "@en4 【。。。抵伴𣎏体𤯩徠伮自点起頭。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:79:text
msgid "@en_eyeclosed [I see.]"
msgstr "@en_eyeclosed 【𪝬曉。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:80:text
msgid "@en4 [If you change your mind, though... feel free to come back.]"
msgstr "@en4 【裊伴𣎏𢷮意。。。據役𢮿徠唲。】"

#: Maps/FINALE/Memory/niko reflection:1:81:text
msgid "@en_eyeclosed [It's not like I'm going anywhere.]"
msgstr "@en_eyeclosed 【𪝬拱拯𠫾兜兜。】"

