#: Maps/Green/Research Station/EV003:1:7:text Station/EV010:1:7:text
msgid "[WELCOME TO THE RESEARCH STATION.]"
msgstr "【嘲𢜏𦤾喟站研究。】"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/EV003:1:9:text Maps/POSTGAME green/Research
#: Station/EV003:1:10:text
msgid "[ARE YOU SENT HERE BY DR. SILVERPOINT?]"
