#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:106:text
msgid "@silver [Guess we should head back soon.]"
msgstr "@silver 【些𢧚𢮿徠𣋽催。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:116:text
msgid ""
"@silver_lookup [Even without the squares, the mines are not a safe place to "
"be.]"
msgstr "@silver_lookup 【怞空被染塊𣃱、𡌢𡎡拱空沛坭安全之朱甘。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:117:text
msgid "@silver2 [Come on, I'll wait for you outside.]"
msgstr "@silver2 【𠫾催、姉𠱊待㛪於外。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:118:text
msgid "@niko3 Wait! I want to ask you-"
msgstr "@niko3 寬㐌！㛪㦖𠳨姉－"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:133:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed She left."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 姉𧘇𠫾𠅒耒。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:134:text
msgid ""
"@proto1b [...If you were going to ask her about being \"not real\", save "
"your breath.]"
msgstr "@proto1b 【。。。裊㛪定𠳨姉𧘇𧗱務姉𧘇「空𣎏實」時𠺌擬𠫾。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:139:text
msgid "@proto1b [None of the people here know their predicament.]"
msgstr "@proto1b 【空埃於低別𧗱数分𧵑本身𪥘󠄁。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:140:text
msgid "@proto1c [In fact... I don't think they can even comprehend it.]"
msgstr "@proto1c 【甚至。。。英哙空擬𣎏体曉得伮。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:141:text
msgid ""
"@proto2 [It would be in your best interest to just... pretend like we never "
"had this conversation.]"
msgstr "@proto2 【卒一𪜀㛪。。。𢧚假噅些𣗓曾伮𧗱𡀯尼。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:142:text
msgid ""
"@proto2b [Causing mass confusion in the world's residents would likely "
"result in unfavorable conditions for you.]"
msgstr "@proto2b 【𨠳𫥨鬧亂面㢅朱各居民可能高𠱊引𦤾條件不利朱㛪。】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:145:text
msgid "@niko3 ...wait, then what about you?"
msgstr "@niko3 。。。寬、哙英時哰？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:146:text
msgid "@niko3 How did YOU know?"
msgstr "@niko3 哰英徠別丕？"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:147:text
msgid "@proto2b [...\\.\\.We never had this conversation, remember?]"
msgstr "@proto2b 【。。。\\.\\.衆些𣗓曾吶𧗱𡀯尼𦓡？】"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server
#: room/backroom/proto:5:148:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Sigh."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 係。"

