msgstr "@niko2 㛪拱拯劸𦤾丕。。。"

#: Maps/Blue/Cliffs/Lookout point/Mineshaft entrance/server room/backroom/npc
#: proto2:1:16:text
msgid "@proto1c [If that doesn't work, we might need to dig around it, and...]"
