msgstr "@silver_eyeclosed 【。。。𣎏𨤔𪜀被隱𠫾耒。】"

#: Maps/Tower/Summit/map event:2:1:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed No turning back now..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 空哙塘𨆢耒。。。"

#: Maps/Tower/Summit/map event:3:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak So this is where the sun belongs..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 丕低𪜀𡊲𧵑𩈘𡗶。。。"

#: Maps/Tower/Summit/map event:3:3:text
msgid ""
"@niko2 If I put the sun in here, we'll be able to save the world, right?"
msgstr "@niko2 裊𨉟㨋徠𩈘𡗶、些𠱊救得世界、沛空？"

#: Maps/Tower/Summit/map event:3:4:text
msgid ""
"@niko ...but if I want to go home... \\> \\@niko_distressed I'll have to... "
"\\> \\@niko_distressed_meow break it?"
msgstr ""
"@niko 。。。扔裊𨉟㦖𧗱茹。。。\\> \\@niko_distressed 𨉟𠱊沛。。。\\> "
"\\@niko_distressed_meow 㧺𥒮伮哰？"

#: Maps/Tower/Summit/map event:3:5:text
