msgid "@niko How do I...solve this..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟。。。解丐尼矯之些。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/npc_mmrobot:1:10:text
msgid "[THAT IS PART OF THE TEST.]"
msgstr "【妬𪜀𠬠份𧵑排檢查。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/npc_mmrobot:1:11:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Bummer."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𠩕。"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/npc_mmrobot:1:14:text
msgid "[IN ORDER TO GAIN FURTHER ACCESS TO THE LABS.]"
msgstr "【抵𣎏体𠓨各房試驗邊𥪝。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/npc_mmrobot:1:15:text
msgid "[YOU MUST PASS THE SECURITY SYSTEM TEST.]"
msgstr "【伴沛越過排檢查係統保密。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/npc_mmrobot:1:16:text
msgid "@niko The... huh?"
msgstr "@niko 丐。。。嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/npc_mmrobot:1:17:text
msgid ""
"[YOU MUST CHANGE THE COLOR OF THE LIGHTS INTO A SPECIFIC CONFIGURATION.]"
msgstr "【伴沛𠊝𢷮𦭷畑蹺𠬠次序一定。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/npc_mmrobot:1:18:text
msgid "[ALLOW ME.]"
msgstr "【吀法。】"

#: Maps/Red ground/ground 2/Factory Entrance/1st room/door GRAPHIC:1:1:text
#: room/door:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Locked."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 被銙耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/glitch left:1:1:text
msgid "@niko4 They're in the door..."
msgstr "@niko4 衆於𥪝𫔤。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/map events:1:5:text
msgid "@green_gatekeeper [P\\.#L.%%E\\.AS;E D\\.o No//t AP\\.PR#OACH.]"
msgstr "@green_gatekeeper 【口\\.#千.%%扌\\.亭\\.彳//來\\.近。】]"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/map events:1:6:text
msgid ""
"@green_gatekeeper [TH\\.#e.%%G\\.AT;E IS\\. C//L OSE\\.D UN\\.T\\.#IL "
"FU\\.#RT\\|HER N\\.%O\\.TIC\\.E.]"
msgstr ""
"@green_gatekeeper 【門\\.#貢.%%被\\.金;、夸\\. 朱//至\\.旦\\.辶\\.#甬\\.#報"
"\\|扌\\.%妾\\.足\\.堯。】"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/EV135:1:8:text
msgid "@niko3 Isn't that...\\.\\.the city gate?"
msgstr "@niko3 拯沛妬𪜀。。。\\.\\.𨶛𠓨城庯哰？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/EV135:1:9:text
msgid "@niko4 It's..."
msgstr "@niko4 伮。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/EV207:1:1:text
msgid "@niko4 The bridge is broken..."
msgstr "@niko4 橋𢭮耒。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/EV210:1:2:text
msgid "@niko2 ...looks like parts of the ground is missing."
msgstr "@niko2 。。。𣎏𨤔𠬠𠄧份𩈘𡐙㐌變𠅒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/EV210:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I wonder if it's safe to walk across these vines..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 空別𣎏体𠫾𨑗仍絏蹽尼空。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/EV210:1:5:text
msgid "@niko6 ...one way to find out, I guess..."
msgstr "@niko6 。。。沛試㵋別得。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Gate/EV211:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed They're safe..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 衆安全。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/calamus npc:2:6:text
msgid ""
"@niko I lent it to someone in the ruins.\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed She said she "
"wanted to feel the sun again, before she..."
msgstr ""
"@niko 𨉟朱埃妬𥪝殘跡摱暫耒。\\>\\n\\@niko_eyeclosed 姉𧘇吶姉㦖感認𩈘𡗶𠬠吝"
"𡛤、𠓀欺。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/calamus npc:2:7:text
msgid "@calamus_speak Oh, you must be talking about Maize."
msgstr "@calamus_speak 溩、丕舅當吶𧗱姉梅。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/calamus npc:2:8:text
msgid "@niko_speak Is that her name?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠸜姉𧘇妬嘑？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/calamus npc:2:9:text
msgid ""
"@calamus_speak She's a powerful plant spirit. She used to protect the Glen."
msgstr "@calamus_speak 姉𧘇𪜀𠬠木靈窒猛。姉𧘇曾鎮𡨺塳潭浰。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/calamus npc:2:10:text
msgid "@calamus_sad ...but once the sun died, her health rapidly deteriorated."
msgstr "@calamus_sad 。。。扔欺𩈘𡗶𣩂、飭劸𧵑姉衰𪽳嚴重。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/calamus npc:2:12:text
msgid "@calamus I'm glad you were able to find her in time."
msgstr "@calamus 𢆪𪜀舅尋𧡊姉𧘇及時。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/calamus npc:2:13:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed I think we might be already too late to save her..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𨉟擬㐌過悶抵救姉𧘇耒。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/calamus npc:2:14:text
msgid "@calamus_sad I know."
msgstr "@calamus_sad 𨉟別。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/calamus npc:2:15:text
msgid "@calamus But I'm glad she got to see the sun again."
msgstr "@calamus 扔𢜏𪜀姉𧘇得𧡊𩈘𡗶𠬠吝𡳳。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/calamus npc:2:22:text
msgid "@calamus I hope the squares don't spread too fast..."
msgstr "@calamus 懞仍塊𣃱空攔過𨘱。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:1:1:text
msgid "@alula_speak You're here! You're here!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 舅𦤾耒！舅𦤾耒！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:1:3:text
msgid "@alula I'll go get the thing!"
msgstr "@alula 𨉟𠱊𠫾𥙩丐妬！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:2:text
msgid ""
"@calamus_smile So uh...welcome to our home!\\>\\n\\@calamus_heh I know it's "
"not much, but...\\>\\n\\@calamus_smile feel free to make yourself "
"comfortable."
msgstr ""
"@calamus_smile 時唹。。。嘲𢜏𦤾茹𧵑衆𨉟！\\>\\n\\@calamus_heh 𨉟別伮空㢅𠸤𪜀"
"包、扔。。。\\>\\n\\@calamus_smile 據自然如於茹唲。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:6:text
msgid "@alula Ah! There it is!"
msgstr "@alula 啊！其耒！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:29:text
msgid "@alula_speak Here, we want you to have this!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 低、衆𨉟㦖贈舅丐尼！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:41:text
msgid "@niko Oh, a feather!\\>\\n\\@niko_speak The edges are glowing yellow!"
msgstr "@niko 溩、𠬠隻𦒮羽！\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 各紒發𤏬𦭷鐄！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:42:text
msgid "@calamus_speak It's a sacred feather from the great Prophet."
msgstr "@calamus_speak 𠬠隻𦒮羽𪬮自茹先知。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:45:text
msgid "@alula She's this old lady our dad used to know!"
msgstr "@alula 仛衆𨉟曾慣姉𧘇！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:46:text
msgid ""
"@alula_gasp Her feathers can glow in the dark and she can see into the "
"future!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 𦒮姉𧘇發𤏬𥪝琫𣋁吧姉𧘇𣎏体別𠓀將來！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:48:text
msgid "@alula Or... something like that!"
msgstr "@alula 或。。。大類丕！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:49:text
msgid "@calamus_speak She gave one of her feathers to father before she died."
msgstr "@calamus_speak 姉㐌迻仛𠬠隻𦒮𠓀欺𣩂。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:50:text
msgid ""
"@calamus Father wanted to pass this down as an heirloom, although..."
"\\>\\n\\@calamus_smile ...it feels more fitting for you to have it."
msgstr ""
"@calamus 仛㦖伮𪵯𧵑家傳、扔。。。\\>\\n\\@calamus_smile 。。。𨉟擬伮𠱊合舅欣"
"妬。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:51:text
msgid "@niko A-are you sure?"
msgstr "@niko 舅－舅昃渚？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:52:text
msgid "@alula_speak Totally sure!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𠬠𤾓份𤾓！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:2:53:text
msgid "@calamus I think that's what father would have wanted."
msgstr "@calamus 𨉟擬仛拱𠱊㦖如丕。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:2:text
msgid "@alula That's the sun!"
msgstr "@alula 妬𪜀𩈘𡗶！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:6:text
msgid "@alula It's a book!"
msgstr "@alula 𠬠卷冊！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:7:text
msgid "@alula_speak I can't read yet!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𨉟𣗓別讀！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:8:text
msgid "@alula Our friend says he'll teach me when I'm older, though!"
msgstr "@alula 扔伴衆𨉟吶哴𠱊𠰺𨉟欺𨉟𡘯欣妬！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:12:text
msgid "@alula_speak It's a pretty feather, isn't it?"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𠬠隻𦒮惵、𠰚？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:16:text
msgid "@alula_speak Wooow! \\>That's a pretty necklace!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𫽿！\\>隻𤥑𦙶惵妬！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:17:text
msgid "@niko The robot lady from the Barrens gave it to me!"
msgstr "@niko 𠬠姉𠊛𣛠外塳邊疆朱𨉟妬！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:18:text
msgid "@alula_gasp You've been to the Barrens?"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 舅㐌𦤾塳邊疆耒哰？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:19:text
msgid "@niko_speak Yeah! \\p and I came from there, actually!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𫫡！寔𫥨、\\p吧𨉟𦤾自妬𦓡！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:20:text
msgid "@alula_pout But... I thought you came from another world..."
msgstr "@alula_pout 扔。。。𨉟想舅𦤾自世界恪𦓡。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:21:text
msgid "@niko Ah, I just meant we were there first, before we got to the Glen!"
msgstr "@niko 啊、意𪜀衆𨉟𦤾妬頭先、𠓀欺𬧐塳潭浰𧘇！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:22:text
msgid "@alula_speak That makes more sense!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 合理欣妬！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/alula npc:3:25:text
msgid "@alula_speak It's good to be home again!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 實𢝙欺𠭤𧗱茹！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV003:1:1:text
#: In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV004:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Fireflies!"
msgstr "@niko 炶炶！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV005:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Fireflies light up this room."
msgstr "@niko 炶炶𤏧𤏬間房尼。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV009:1:1:text
#: In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV010:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed The back room is full of dust and cobwebs..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 房𢖖󠄁撫𣹓𡏧吧𦁸蝒。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV014:1:2:text
#: In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV014:1:9:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Looks like spoiled food."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𣎏𨤔𪜀𣘊咹燒。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV014:1:6:text
msgid "@calamus_heh I'll... deal with it later."
msgstr "@calamus_heh 𨉟𠱊。。。解決伮𢖖󠄁。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV014:1:10:text
msgid "@calamus_shame Oh no!"
msgstr "@calamus_shame 喂空！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV014:1:11:text
msgid ""
"@calamus_heh I guess that's what happens if you leave your house for three "
"days..."
msgstr "@calamus_heh 昃𪜀由𨉟㐌𠀧𣈜𨉟空於茹。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV015:1:2:text
msgid "@niko They're cold now."
msgstr "@niko 衆冷𠖯耒。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:2:text
msgid "@niko It's a book with a clover on the cover."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠卷冊𣎏𠬠𣘃𦹯𠀧蘿𨑗柀。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:6:text
msgid "@calamus_heh I really need to finish this..."
msgstr "@calamus_heh 𨉟沛讀歱伮𣋽催。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:9:text
msgid "@niko There's a clover symbol on the cover of this book."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠬠表象𦹯𠀧蘿𨑗柀卷冊尼。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:10:text
msgid "@niko_speak Hey! Just like-"
msgstr "@niko_speak 尼！依如－"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:11:text
msgid "@calamus_speak Oh! My book!"
msgstr "@calamus_speak 溩！冊𧵑𨉟！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:12:text
msgid "@calamus_shame Gosh, I still need to finish studying it..."
msgstr "@calamus_shame 𡗶、𨉟沛讀歱伮𣋽催。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:14:text
msgid "@calamus My friend gave it to me for Solstice Day."
msgstr "@calamus 伴𨉟贈𨉟因𣋑夏至。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:15:text
msgid "@calamus_speak He's the one who wrote it, actually!"
msgstr "@calamus_speak 寔𫥨舅𧘇拱𢪏伮㫻！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:16:text
msgid "@calamus_smile He's also the one who taught me how to read!"
msgstr "@calamus_smile 拱𪜀舅𧘇𠰺𨉟讀妬！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV016:1:18:text
msgid "@calamus_smile I have a few more of his books somewhere..."
msgstr "@calamus_smile 𨉟哙添冊𧵑舅𧘇𨒺低幾。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:2:text
#: In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:11:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's a plush toy!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠬠𡥵獸抐葻！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:3:text
msgid "@niko I have one at home too..."
msgstr "@niko 𨉟拱𣎏𠬠𡥵於茹！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:4:text
msgid "@niko_83c But mine's an owl and not a fox!"
msgstr "@niko_83c 扔𧵑𨉟𪜀𫚱渚空沛𤞺！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:8:text
msgid "@alula My fox is named Ruby, by the way!"
msgstr "@alula 因便、𤞺𧵑𨉟𠸜𪜀玉宝妬！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:12:text
msgid ""
"@alula_speak That's mine! \\>\\@alula Our friend gave it to me last year!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𪜀𧵑𨉟妬！\\>\\@alula 伴𨉟贈𢆥𢫑妬！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:14:text
msgid "@alula_gasp Yeah! He has a fox too!\\nAnd she can even talk!"
msgstr "@alula_gasp 𫫡！舅𧘇拱𣎏𠬠注𤞺！\\n哙吶𡀯得幾！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:16:text
msgid "@alula_speak I know! I thought she was the coolest thing ever!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 𨉟別𦓡！𨉟擬妬𪜀次湡一菓𡐙㫻！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:17:text
msgid "@alula So he got me a fox plush for Solstice Day!"
msgstr "@alula 𢧚舅𧘇贈𨉟𠬠注𤞺抐葻因𣈜夏至！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:18:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! That's nice of him!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！舅𧘇卒䏾實！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV017:1:19:text
msgid "@alula_speak He's the best!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 舅𧘇𪜀数𠬠㫻！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV020:1:2:text
#: In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV020:1:9:text
msgid "@niko It's a fishing pole."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𣘃竿鉤𩵜。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV020:1:6:text
msgid "@calamus That reminds me, I need to go fishing later..."
msgstr "@calamus 𠯅㵋𢖵、子𨉟沛𠫾鉤催。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV020:1:10:text
msgid "@alula Do you like fish, Niko?"
msgstr "@alula 舅𣎏適咹𩵜空、尼孤？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV020:1:12:text
msgid "@alula_speak So do we! \\|\\@alula They're good in stews."
msgstr "@alula_speak 衆𨉟拱勢！\\|\\@alula 𤐚𬨠咹窒唁。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV020:1:13:text
msgid "@niko_speak Or soups!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 或欺𪵯𣼳！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV020:1:14:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed ...but I know some people back home who like to eat them raw."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。扔𨉟別𣎏𠬠数𠊛適咹𩵜𤯩。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV020:1:15:text
msgid "@alula_speak Ewww!"
msgstr "@alula_speak 㕭！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV020:1:16:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Yeup."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𫫡。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV027:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Jars full of dried fish."
msgstr "@niko 仍𤮗𣹓𩵜枯。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV028:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a jar full of worms!"
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𤮗𧉙！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV029:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Jars full of dried moss."
msgstr "@niko 仍𤮗𦼔𤇨枯。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Birdhouse/EV030:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Jars full of beans."
msgstr "@niko 仍𤮗豆菶。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:6:text
msgid "@mason Good luck with that seed, now!"
msgstr "@mason 祝㛪𢆪慜㵋籺偅妬唲！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:9:text
#: plant/npc_mason:1:41:text
msgid "@mason Most of the plants in our world tend to grow in The Glen."
msgstr "@mason 份𡘯植物𨑗世界尼生長𥪝塳潭浰。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:10:text
#: plant/npc_mason:1:42:text
msgid ""
"@mason Even if it's facing the flooding issues, it's still in better "
"condition than the other two areas."
msgstr "@mason 怞伮當﨤問題汲𣹕、伮吻𥪝情狀卒欣𠄩塳哙徠。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:11:text
#: plant/npc_mason:1:43:text
msgid "@mason The Barrens is... well, the barrens."
msgstr "@mason 塳邊疆時。。。𪜀塳邊疆。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:12:text
#: plant/npc_mason:1:44:text
msgid ""
"@mason And Refuge city has barely enough ground to stand on, let alone grow "
"stuff!"
msgstr "@mason 吧城庯時哙𠁙𨁥𡊲𨅸、渚揨吶𦤾𣑺𣘃！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:13:text
#: plant/npc_mason:1:45:text
msgid "@mason ...On a larger scale than this, I mean."
msgstr "@mason 。。。意英𪜀、𨑗規模𡘯欣勢尼。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:19:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! \\.\\.\\@niko You're a gardener, right?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！\\.\\.\\@niko 英𪜀𠊛𪵯園、沛空吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:20:text plant/Map
#: Events:1:16:text
msgid "@mason Yup!"
msgstr "@mason 董！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:21:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Do you... happen to have any dirt?\\>\\n\\@niko For growing "
"plants, I mean!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 英。。。𣎏𡐙空吖？\\>\\n\\@niko 意㛪𪜀、抵𣑺𣘃吖！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:22:text
msgid "@mason Yup!\\>\\nDo you need some?"
msgstr "@mason 英𣎏！\\>\\n㛪懃嘑？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:23:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Yes!\\>\\n\\@niko I'm supposed to plant this seed left behind by "
"a plant lady..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠳐吖！\\>\\n\\@niko 㛪沛𣑺籺𥞖𦓡𠬠姉𠊛𣘃抵徠。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:24:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...but the pot in the garden doesn't have any soil..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。扔𡊱𣘃𥪝園時空𣎏𡐙。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:25:text
msgid "@mason I see...."
msgstr "@mason 𫥨丕。。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:26:text
msgid "@mason I know who you're talking about, yeah."
msgstr "@mason 英別㛪當𠯅𦤾埃、𫫡。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:27:text
msgid "@mason Here, take this whole bag!"
msgstr "@mason 低、㛪擒𥙩𪥘󠄁甓𠫾！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:38:text
msgid "@mason Feel free to ask me about the plants!"
msgstr "@mason 據自然𠳨英𧗱𣘃𦹯唲！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:51:text
msgid "@mason Hello there!"
msgstr "@mason 吀嘲！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:52:text
msgid "@niko_speak You have a lot of plants!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 英𣎏𡗉𣘃樻𠺳！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:53:text
msgid "@mason I do!\\nGrew all of these myself, y'see."
msgstr "@mason 董丕妬！\\n調由英自𣑺𪥘󠄁蒂。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/npc_mason:1:54:text
msgid "@mason Feel free to ask me about them!"
msgstr "@mason 裊㦖𠳨英時據自然唲！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/trowel:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A small garden trowel. The handle part is shaped like... an owl?"
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𣘃剷𪵯園𡮈。份𢬣擒𣎏形。。。哙𤠲？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/trowel:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_83c I get it!"
msgstr "@niko_83c 啊！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/watering can:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A watering can. It's half full."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠平洒𣘃。𣹓𠬠姅。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/bucket:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Filled with plant clippings."
msgstr "@niko 貯𣹓仍蘿𣘃㐌𢲟。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/flowerpot:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Empty flowerpot..."
msgstr "@niko 𡊱花筩。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:2:text
msgid "@niko So... is it a tree?"
msgstr "@niko 丕。。。伮𣎏沛𣘃空吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:3:text
msgid "@mason Only in name!"
msgstr "@mason 只𨑗名義催！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:6:text
msgid "@mason That's a phosphor tree."
msgstr "@mason 妬𪜀𣘃光素。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:7:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! Like the ones we saw in the glen!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！偅仍𣘃𨉟𧡊𥪝塳潭浰！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:8:text
msgid "@niko I always wondered... where are the leaves?"
msgstr "@niko 㛪咍自𠳨。。。蘿衆兜歇耒吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:9:text
msgid "@niko2 They're not... dead, are they?"
msgstr "@niko2 𣘃𣗓。。。𣩂、沛空吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:10:text
msgid "@mason Oh, not at all!"
msgstr "@mason 溩、空兜！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:11:text
msgid ""
"@mason Although these trees are composed of a woody tissue, they're closer "
"to grass, anatomy-wise."
msgstr "@mason 雖仍𣘃尼得構城自各膜楛、𧗱𩈘解剖、衆近喟𦹯欣。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:12:text
msgid "@niko ...So the branches are actually leaves?"
msgstr "@niko 。。。息𪜀各莄實𫥨徠𪜀蘿吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:13:text
msgid "@mason Sorta!"
msgstr "@mason 矯丕！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:14:text
msgid ""
"@mason What's interesting about these plants is the amount of phosphor sap "
"they can generate."
msgstr "@mason 條獸物𧗱仍𣘃尼𪜀量蠟光素衆𣎏体產生。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:15:text
msgid "@niko Phosphor... that's the glowy stuff, right?"
msgstr "@niko 光素。。。𪜀仍次發𤏬、董空吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:17:text
msgid "@mason Phosphor can store light energy and slowly emit it over time."
msgstr "@mason 光素𣎏体績貯能量光學吧徐徐解放衆蹺時間。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:18:text
msgid ""
"@mason Most of the phosphor from this world still contains energy from "
"before the sun went out."
msgstr "@mason 份𡘯光素𥪝世界尼吻哙貯能量自𠓀欺𩈘𡗶𣩂。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:19:text
msgid "@mason Without the sun to recharge them, though..."
msgstr "@mason 扔裊空𣎏𩈘𡗶抵納徠能量朱衆。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:1:20:text
msgid "@mason ...well, let's talk about something else."
msgstr "@mason 。。。催、些𠴞𡀯恪𠫾。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:2:2:text
msgid "@niko The pots are labeled with different species names."
msgstr "@niko 各𡊱𣘃得𬖭𣠰𠸜各類恪僥。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:2:3:text
msgid "@niko Oh! The sprouts are stretching towards the sun..."
msgstr "@niko 溩！仍䒹𣘃當向𧗱𠌨𩈘𡗶。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:2:6:text
msgid "@mason Be sure not to touch these!"
msgstr "@mason 揨𪮻𠓨衆唲！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:2:7:text
msgid "@mason These are the plants have only recently sprouted."
msgstr "@mason 仍𣘃尼𣃣㵋𠛌䒹近低。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:2:8:text
msgid "@mason It's not easy for a plant to make it out there these days."
msgstr "@mason 𥪝時𣇜尼時抵𣘃𠚐拱拯易揚之。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:2:9:text
msgid ""
"@mason We got these growing lamps, but they're a poor substitute for the sun!"
msgstr "@mason 𪨠英𣎏仍丐畑尼、扔吻空体𠁔憑𩈘𡗶得！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:2:text
msgid "@mason Ah, black clovers..."
msgstr "@mason 啊、𦹯𠀧蘿黰。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:3:text
msgid ""
"@mason Probably the only plant hardy enough to survive naturally outside the "
"Glen."
msgstr "@mason 𣎏𨤰𪜀類𣘃唯一𨁥勁哈抵生存自然外塳潭浰。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:4:text
msgid "@mason Personally? I think they're really boring to look at."
msgstr "@mason 意見個人時、英擬衆矓𢥇無窮。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:5:text
msgid "@mason One of my customers really loves them though."
msgstr "@mason 扔英𣎏𠬠客行窒適衆。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:6:text
msgid ""
"@mason I think all of the black clovers I'm growing here are for him, "
"actually."
msgstr "@mason 形如悉𪥘󠄁仍𣘃𦹯𠀧蘿黰英當𣑺𪜀朱翁𧘇意。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:7:text
msgid "@mason ...Come to think of it, I haven't seen him in a while."
msgstr "@mason 。。。𠯅㵋𢖵、拱唏嘍耒英空﨤慃。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:8:text
msgid "@mason I wonder when is he coming to pick these up?"
msgstr "@mason 空別包𣇞慃徠𦤾𥙩衆低？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:12:text
msgid "@mason The clover guy... he's actually pretty cool!"
msgstr "@mason 丐翁伽𦹯尼。。。寔𫥨拱𫥨之蒂渚！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:13:text
msgid ""
"@mason He's an author, and apparently he's some sort of big deal? Or at "
"least he's really passionate about his work."
msgstr "@mason 慃𪜀𠬠作者、吧𣎏𨤔𪜀𠬠𠊛可浽㗂？或𠃣一𪜀慃超心血喟工程𧵑慃。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:14:text
msgid ""
"@mason I don't know him that well, although sometimes I stumble across "
"articles about him in the news..."
msgstr "@mason 英空親喟慃𡗋、扔拱𣎏仍𣅶英讀各排報𧗱慃𨑗版信。。。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:15:text
msgid "@mason I'd love to chat with him, if I run into him again!"
msgstr "@mason 裊𣎏𣋑﨤徠、英窒㦖讚㗕喟慃𠬠吝𡛤！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:18:text
msgid "@niko Black clovers."
msgstr "@niko 𦹯𠀧蘿黰。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:3:19:text
msgid "@niko They're kinda shiny."
msgstr "@niko 𤏬𣈖。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:2:text
msgid "@niko It's wheat."
msgstr "@niko 穭麥。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:3:text
msgid "@mason That golden color is quite something, no?"
msgstr "@mason 色鐄妬拱𫥨之㗶渚𠰚？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:6:text
msgid "@niko_speak It's wheat!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𪜀穭麪！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:7:text
msgid "@niko Why is it in a flowerpot?"
msgstr "@niko 在哰伮徠𥪝𡊱花丕吖？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:8:text
msgid "@mason Well, doesn't it look nice?"
msgstr "@mason 時、拯沛伮窒惵哰？"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:9:text
msgid "@niko I guess!"
msgstr "@niko 昃丕！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:10:text
msgid ""
"@niko I like to stand in the middle of the wheat field back in my village."
msgstr "@niko 㛪適𨅸𡧲𦑃垌穭於廊㛪。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:11:text
msgid "@niko_speak It goes on for miles!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 伮𣥱𨱽行𨤮㫻！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:12:text
msgid "@mason Ah... I wish I could have seen it!"
msgstr "@mason 啊。。。約之英拱𣎏体𧡊伮！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:13:text
msgid ""
"@mason In our world, wheat is usually only grown in small isolated plots."
msgstr "@mason 𥪝世界𧵑𪨠英、穭麪常只得𣑺𥪝各所𬏇𡮈𥛭。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:4:14:text
msgid "@mason ...Or in a flowerpot."
msgstr "@mason 。。。或𥪝𡊱。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:5:2:text
msgid "@niko A small tree with leaves."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠丐𣘃𡮈𣎏蘿。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:5:3:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed ...Apparently they are rare."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 。。。䀡𫥨衆可險。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:5:6:text
msgid "@niko This tree has leaves!"
msgstr "@niko 𣘃尼𣎏蘿尼！"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:5:7:text
msgid "@mason Ah yes, true foliage is hard to come by nowadays."
msgstr "@mason 啊唹、𣈜𠉞𠸋檢仍傘𣘃實事𡗋。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:5:8:text
msgid "@mason You hardly ever see trees like these in the wild anymore."
msgstr "@mason 外自然窒險﨤仍𣘃勢尼。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/Map Events:5:9:text
msgid ""
"@mason And the ones you do see are pretty much all raised artificially by "
"people like me, mostly for nostalgia purposes."
msgstr "@mason 吧裊㛪𣎏𧡊、時近如全𪜀仍𣘃由仍𠊛如英𣑺、主要抵服務目的懷古。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/cactus:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Cactus."
msgstr "@niko 𩩫𧏵。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/cactus:1:2:text
msgid "@mason Cactus."
msgstr "@mason 𩩫𧏵。"

#: Maps/Red sky/Apartments/Hall2/Room6 - plant/cactus:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Cactus."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𩩫𧏵。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV001:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak The blanket has quite a few patches."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𬌓𧜖𣎏可𡗉𤗖𬗵𦀪。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV001:2:1:text
msgid "@niko An empty glass jar with a wire handle."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𤮗水晶筩𣎏𢬣擒絏𨨧。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV001:3:1:text
msgid "@niko Some empty glass jars."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𠄧𤮗水晶筩。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV002:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A jar full of red glowing fluid."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𤮗貯質𣿅𧹻發𤏬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV003:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A lantern plant."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𣘃畑籠。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV003:1:2:text
msgid "@niko There's a note attached."
msgstr "@niko 𣎏𠬠畝𥱬注釘兼。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV003:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_speak It says \"Thank you for working so hard, Mr. Lamplighter!\""
msgstr "@niko_speak 伮𥱬𪜀「感恩英𠏲畑㐌㫻努力𪵯役！」"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV006:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A framed photo of someone."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠幅影㨂椌𨄴埃妬。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV007:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Empty coffee cups."
msgstr "@niko 仍𤭏咖啡筩。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV008:1:1:text
msgid "@niko_speak There's an empty coffee cup on the chair."
msgstr "@niko_speak 𨑗𧦕𣎏𠬠𤭏咖啡筩。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV009:1:1:text
msgid "@niko Big books."
msgstr "@niko 仍卷冊𫰅。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV009:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak ...Ah, these are dictionaries."
msgstr "@niko_speak 。。。啊、低𪜀詞典。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV009:1:3:text
msgid "@niko Some of the words are underlined."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𠄧詞得劃蹎。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV009:1:4:text
msgid "@niko ....*most* of the words are underlined."
msgstr "@niko 。。。＊份𡘯＊各自調得劃蹎。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV012:1:1:text
msgid "@niko A rusty metal garbage can."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠桶𧅫金類釲𡏥。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV012:1:2:text
msgid "@niko There's some broken glass in here."
msgstr "@niko 𥪝尼𣎏𠃣水晶𥒮。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/glentree:1:1:text
msgid "@niko An empty glass jar."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠𤮗水晶筩。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/glentree:1:2:text
msgid "@niko The handle on this one looks broken."
msgstr "@niko 𬗜擒𧵑丐尼𣎏𨤔㐌𢭮。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/lenses:1:1:text
msgid "@niko There's some big plastic disks in here."
msgstr "@niko 𥪝尼𣎏𠄧隻𥐨𣺾𡘯。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/lenses:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak Looks like they're supposed to go in something?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𣎏𨤔沛朱衆𠓨兜妬？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/lenses:1:4:text
msgid "@niko_what Wait, \\p, are we really gonna take these with us?"
msgstr "@niko_what 寬、\\p、衆些寔事𠱊𫼳衆蹺嘑？"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/lenses:1:5:text
msgid "@niko_what But they look so heavy..."
msgstr "@niko_what 扔衆𣑺𥘀𡗋。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/lenses:1:14:text
msgid "@niko_speak Hey! They're actually pretty light!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 尼！䀡𫥨衆珥㗶！"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/lenses:2:1:text
msgid "@niko It's empty now..."
msgstr "@niko 𣇞伮筩耒。。。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV022:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's a big book."
msgstr "@niko 𠬠卷冊𡘯。"

#: Maps/Red ground/backalley/lamplighter house/EV022:1:2:text
msgid "@niko_speak The title says \"understanding robots\"."
msgstr "@niko_speak 標題𪜀「透曉𠊛𣛠」。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/girl:1:1:text
msgid "My mommy is making food for everyone!"
msgstr "媄𨉟當𤍇咹朱𤗆𠊛！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/girl:1:2:text
msgid "I want to help her catch fish, but I'm not a grownup yet!"
msgstr "𨉟㦖𢴇媄扒𩵜、仍𨉟𣗓沛𠊛𡘯！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:2:text
msgid ""
"@magpie By the way... if you ever see a big guy with goggles and a cool "
"helmet.."
msgstr "@magpie 因便。。。裊㛪𣎏﨤𠬠翁伽𫰅高㧅鏡保護吧𢃱保險湡䋘。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:3:text
msgid "@magpie_smile Tell him the trader in the Glen said hi!"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 寄𠳒嘲自商家𥪝塳潭浰唲！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:4:text
msgid "@magpie Also ask him if he has any more music boxes for trading."
msgstr "@magpie 拱𠳨䀡慃哙匣樂鬧抵𢭂𢷮空唲。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:5:text
msgid "@niko Will do!"
msgstr "@niko 𠳐吖！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:9:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! You're the trader guy!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！英𪜀俚販尼！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:10:text
msgid "@magpie_smile Sure am!\\>\\n\\@magpie You here to trade?"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 董丕！\\>\\n\\@magpie 㛪𦤾低交易嘑？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:11:text
msgid "@magpie_hm 'Cause if you are, then I got bad news for ya."
msgstr "@magpie_hm 爲裊勢時、英𣎏信空卒𡗋。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:12:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_hm A lot of my stuff is back at my cart, which was sadly abandoned "
"when I was running for my life."
msgstr "@magpie_hm 份𡘯行𧵑英被𠬃徠於車𢩽、𦓡𣃣沛𠬃伮𧼋𥙩𠊛。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:13:text
msgid "@magpie So my collection is...\\.\\. very limited right now."
msgstr "@magpie 𢧚部搜集現在𧵑英。。。\\.\\.窒界限。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:14:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_smile Managed to grab some of my favorite things before I left, "
"though!"
msgstr "@magpie_smile 扔英吻及救得𠄧𦁺㤇適一𠓀欺𠬃𧼋、唲！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:15:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! Uh..."
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！唹。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:16:text
msgid "@niko Do you have anything like...\\.\\. gears?"
msgstr "@niko 英𣎏丐之如。。。\\.\\.𨋣𪘵空吖？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:17:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_oh Gears?\\.\\. Like... the metal spinny things? \\>\\@magpie I "
"don't think I have anything like that..."
msgstr ""
"@magpie_oh 𨋣𪘵嘑？\\.\\.𠇍次金類搓搓𧘇嘑？\\>\\@magpie 英空擬英𣎏之如"
"丕。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:19:text
msgid "@magpie_oh Wait."
msgstr "@magpie_oh 寬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:20:text
msgid "@magpie I do have this box thing that you can wind up and play a song."
msgstr "@magpie 英𣎏丐匣尼㛪𣎏体𬨠絏嗗吧發樂。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:21:text
msgid "@niko_speak That's a music box!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 𠬠匣樂！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:22:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_smile Yeah!\\n\\>\\@magpie I bet there's lots of little metal bits "
"in there!"
msgstr ""
"@magpie_smile 𫫡！\n"
"\\>\\@magpie 英𩵜𥪝妬𣎏窒𡗉零件金類𢳝伆𥪝妬！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:23:text
msgid "@niko_speak Oh! That might work!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 溩！𣎏欺用得妬！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:24:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_hm But I'm not sure if I want to trade it away...\\>\\nIt's one of "
"my favorite things!"
msgstr "@magpie_hm 扔英空昃𣎏㦖𬥓伮𠫾空。。。\\>\\n𠬠𥪝仍𦁺英𢛨一妬！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:25:text
msgid "@niko_eyeclosed Aw..."
msgstr "@niko_eyeclosed 𫉩。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:26:text
msgid "@magpie_hm ..."
msgstr "@magpie_hm 。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:27:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_oh Oh, what am I saying!\\>\\n\\@magpie_smile You're the savior!"
msgstr "@magpie_oh 喂、英當話之丕𡗶！\\>\\n\\@magpie_smile 㛪𪜀𠎬救世其𦓡！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:28:text
msgid "@magpie_hm Things have been getting bad around here lately."
msgstr "@magpie_hm 𨄹尼𤗆次唏弊𡭧。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:29:text
msgid ""
"@magpie_smile If I don't help you, I might not even be around much longer..."
msgstr "@magpie_smile 裊英空𢴇㛪、𣎏欺𢯛𬧐英哙空全命𡛤幾。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:30:text
msgid "@magpie You need this to save the world, right?\\>\\nTake it."
msgstr "@magpie 㛪懃丐尼抵救世界、董空？\\>\\n㛪據𥙩𠫾。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/trader:1:31:text
msgid "@niko_speak Ah! Thank you!"
msgstr "@niko_speak 啊！感恩英吖！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/friendly child npc:1:1:text
msgid "*sniff*"
msgstr "＊泏哳＊"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/friendly child npc:1:2:text
msgid "@niko Are you okay?"
msgstr "@niko 㛪穩空丕？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/friendly child npc:1:3:text
msgid "I WANNA GO BACK HOME!!!"
msgstr "㛪㦖𧗱茹！！！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/moss npc:1:1:text
msgid "This island has more moss covering than our village did."
msgstr "𡉕島尼𣎏𡗉𦼔撫欣廊𫇰𧵑衆𪝬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/moss npc:1:2:text
msgid "Would've been nice to build a settlement here."
msgstr "𡏦得𠬠區定居於低時㐌咍。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/moss npc:1:3:text
msgid "...too late now, I guess."
msgstr "。。。𣇞時過悶耒。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/worried npc:1:1:text
msgid "The land fragmentation is happening faster and faster now..."
msgstr "𩈘𡐙當分沲𪨈𣈜𪨈𨘱。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/worried npc:1:2:text
msgid "But...\\.\\. looks like the vines are slowing it down..."
msgstr "扔。。。\\.\\.固𨤔仍絏蹽當𪵯踸伮徠。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/fisherman npc:1:1:text
msgid "Our village was ransacked by the squares not long ago..."
msgstr "廊衆𪝬被塊𣃱破閧空嘍𧗱𠓀。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/fisherman npc:1:2:text
msgid "Most of us made it out alive, but we can't really go back anymore."
msgstr "份𡘯𠊛民㐌全命遁脫、扔衆𪝬空𠭤𧗱得𡛤。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/fisherman npc:1:4:text
msgid "Squares are bad news, man."
msgstr "塊𣃱𪜀恬醜妬。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/pessimistic npc:1:2:text
msgid "We won't last long now, will we?"
msgstr "時間拱拯哙𡗉、𠰚？"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/pessimistic npc:1:3:text
msgid "The sun can't fix the squares..."
msgstr "𩈘𡗶空体𢯢得仍塊𣃱。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/pessimistic npc:1:4:text
msgid "The sun can't restore the land..."
msgstr "𩈘𡗶空体恢復徠𩈘𡐙。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/child npc:1:1:text
msgid "The vines are everywhere!"
msgstr "絏蹽於泣坭！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/child npc:1:2:text
msgid "The plant lady must be protecting us!"
msgstr "木靈扶護衆些！"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/child npc:1:3:text
msgid "@niko_upset ...yeah..."
msgstr "@niko_upset 。。。唹。。。"

#: Maps/POSTGAME green/Dock/shephard:1:1:text
msgid "@shepherd What a day..."
msgstr "@shepherd 果𪜀𠬠𣈜𨱽。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:11:text
msgid "@alula_pout Niko?"
msgstr "@alula_pout 尼孤？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:16:text
msgid ""
"@niko_speak Earlier I was in the Barrens area, and I kind of... saw "
"something?\\>\\n\\@niko It was like a dream, but only for a split second..."
msgstr ""
"@niko_speak 𨉟𣃣於塳邊疆、吧𨉟㐌。。。𧡊之妬時沛？\\>\\n\\@niko 偅如𠬠𥋏𢠩、"
"扔只𥪝𣆰𣋩催。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:17:text
msgid "@calamus_speak A vision?"
msgstr "@calamus_speak 𠬠景夢嘑？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:18:text
msgid "@niko2 Vision?"
msgstr "@niko2 景夢？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:19:text
msgid "@calamus Like something a prophet would see."
msgstr "@calamus 𠬠次𦓡各茹先知咍𧡊𧘇。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:21:text
msgid ""
"@calamus_speak I mean, if you can talk to \\p, it would make sense, right?"
msgstr "@calamus_speak 𧘇𪜀、舅𣎏体交接喟\\p𦓡、𢧚伮吻合理、沛空？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:23:text
msgid ""
"@calamus ...or not, I don't know. \\>\\n\\@calamus_smile I've only read "
"about it before."
msgstr ""
"@calamus 。。。或空、𨉟空別。\\>\\n\\@calamus_smile 𠓀低𨉟只㵋讀𧗱伮催。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:24:text
msgid "@niko Oooh...\\>\\n\\@niko_speak Anyway, what is this place?"
msgstr "@niko 溩溩溩。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak 𦓡、低𪜀兜丕？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:31:text
msgid "@niko It looks like it used to lead somewhere."
msgstr "@niko 固𨤔伮曾引𦤾兜妬。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:32:text
msgid ""
"@alula_speak Yeah, the sacred grounds!\\>\\n\\@alula It's been a while since "
"we went there..."
msgstr "@alula_speak 𫫡、𦤾聖地妬！\\>\\n\\@alula 拱可嘍耒衆𨉟空𦤾妬。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:35:text
msgid ""
"@calamus We don't have a way getting there now, remember?\\>\\nThere isn't a "
"boat and none of us can swim, and..."
msgstr "@calamus 𣇞𨉟𠿒格𦤾妬耒、㛪𢖵空？\\>\\n空𣎏船、吧𨉟空𬈺得、吧。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:36:text
msgid "@niko_speak What's...the sacred grounds?"
msgstr "@niko_speak 聖地。。。𪜀之丕？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:37:text
msgid "@calamus It's where our people are buried."
msgstr "@calamus 𪜀坭居民於低得墫拮妬。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:38:text
msgid ""
"@alula Sometimes we go there to visit mom!\\>\\n\\@alula_oh Well, her grave, "
"anyway."
msgstr "@alula 對欺衆𨉟𦤾探媄於妬！\\>\\n\\@alula_oh 時、𦤾探墓𧵑媄。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:39:text
msgid ""
"@niko_eyeclosed Oh....\\>\\n\\@niko_speak -wait, how do you get there?"
"\\>\\n\\@niko I thought you said there isn't a boat?"
msgstr ""
"@niko_eyeclosed 溩。。。。\\>\\n\\@niko_speak －寬、舅𦤾妬憑格鬧丕？"
"\\>\\n\\@niko 𨉟想𪜀空𣎏船𦓡？"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:40:text
msgid "@alula Oh, our friend helps us!"
msgstr "@alula 溩、伴𧵑衆𨉟𢴇𠬠𢬣！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:41:text
msgid "@calamus He has some sort of machine that allows him to fly."
msgstr "@calamus 英𧘇𣎏𠬠丐𣛠之妬𣎏体𢒎。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:42:text
msgid "@alula Sometimes he takes us along!"
msgstr "@alula 對欺英𧘇朱𨉟𠫾𦵗𡛤！"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:43:text
msgid ""
"@calamus But like I was about to say, we haven't seen him around for a while."
msgstr "@calamus 扔如𨉟吶低、㐌嘍耒衆𨉟空𧡊英𧘇𨒺低。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:44:text
msgid ""
"@alula I wonder when he'll come back?\\>\\nI wish we could go see mom "
"again..."
msgstr "@alula 空別包𣇞影𢮿徠𠰚？\\>\\n約之𣎏体𦤾探媄吝𡛤。。。"

#: Maps/Green/Ruins In/Birdhall/Courtyard/passage/alula npc:2:47:text
msgid "@calamus Come on, Alula, let's go back to the courtyard now."
msgstr "@calamus 𠫾鬧、阿瞜羅、𧗱𡑝𥪝催。"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/water room/robot standing:1:2:text
msgid "[TAKE CARE NOW, PERSON!]"
msgstr "【保重唲、𡥵𠊛！】"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/water room/robot standing:1:5:text
msgid "[HELLO, LIVING PERSON.]"
msgstr "【吀嘲、𠊛𤯩。】"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/water room/robot standing:1:7:text
msgid "[I HAVE COLLECTED A DUPLICATE WATER SAMPLE.]"
msgstr "【𪝬㐌收拾剩𠬠母渃。】"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/water room/robot standing:1:8:text
msgid "[WOULD YOU LIKE IT?]"
msgstr "【伴𣎏㦖𥙩伮空？】"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/water room/robot standing:1:10:text
msgid "[MY PROGRAMMING SAYS THAT ORGANIC BEINGS NEED WATER TO SURVIVE.]"
msgstr "【立程𧵑𪝬𪲍哴各寔体懃渃。】"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/water room/robot standing:1:11:text
msgid "[SO I SHALL OFFER IT TO YOU.]"
msgstr "【𢧚𪝬𠱊朱伴。】"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/water room/robot standing:1:12:text
msgid "@niko Oh, uh,\\. \\@niko_speak Sure! We'll take it."
msgstr "@niko 溩、唹、\\. \\@niko_speak 嗚雞！𨉟吀。"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/water room/EV004:1:1:text
msgid "[BEEP BOOP. WATER COLLECTION PROJECT RESUMING...]"
msgstr "【芣芣。預案收拾渃當接續。。。】"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/water room/EV005:1:1:text
msgid "@niko It's full of little glass tubes of water."
msgstr "@niko 𣹓仍䈵驗𡮈貯渃。"

#: Maps/Green/Research Station/water room/EV005:1:5:text
msgid "[WATER SAMPLES!]"
msgstr "【母渃！】"

